"Cuanto menos puntos de vida tenga la unidad, más ataques obtiene. Hasta un "
"máximo de 6 ataques."

#. SPECIAL_NOTES_RAVAGE
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/macros/abilities-macro.cfg:60
msgid ""
" The less hitpoints the unit has, the more attacks he gets. Up to a max. of "
"6 attacks."
msgstr ""
" Cuanto menos puntos de vida tenga la unidad, más ataques obtiene. Hasta un "
"máximo de 6 ataques."

#. SPECIAL_NOTES_TRAMPLE
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/macros/abilities-macro.cfg:64
msgid "This unit can overrun enemy units."
msgstr "Esta unidad puede arrollar a unidades enemigas."

#. [resistance], id=fortify
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/macros/abilities-macro.cfg:75
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/macros/abilities-macro.cfg:97
msgid "fortify"
msgstr "fortificar"

#. [resistance], id=fortify
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/macros/abilities-macro.cfg:76
msgid ""
"This unit and all friendly units around it gain a 10% resistance to pierce, "
"blade and impact attacks on defense."
msgstr ""
"Esta unidad y todas las unidades aliadas cercanas ganan un 10% de "
"resistencia a ataques de penetración, corte e impacto en defensa."

#. SPECIAL_NOTES_FORTIFY
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/macros/abilities-macro.cfg:89
msgid ""
"A unit with the fortify ability increases the defense of nearby units "
"against pierce, blade and impact on defense by +10%. Stacks."
msgstr ""
"Una unidad con la habilidad fortificar aumenta la defensa de las unidades "
"cercanas contra penetración, corte e impacto en defensa en +10%. Se acumula."

#. [resistance], id=fortify
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/macros/abilities-macro.cfg:98
msgid ""
"This unit and all friendly units around it gain a 20% resistance to blade, "
"pierce and impact attack"
msgstr ""
"Esta unidad y todas las unidades aliadas cercanas ganan un 20% de "
"resistencia a ataques de corte, penetración e impacto"

#. SPECIAL_NOTES_PROTECT
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/macros/abilities-macro.cfg:111
msgid ""
"A unit with the protect ability increases the defense of nearby units "
"against pierce, blade and impact by +20%. Stacks."
msgstr ""
"Una unidad con la habilidad proteger aumenta la defensa de las unidades "
"cercanas contra penetración, corte e impacto en +20%. Se acumula."

#. [leadership], id=inspire
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/macros/abilities-macro.cfg:121
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/units/heroes/ibnkhazul.cfg:112
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/units/heroes/ridwan.cfg:43
msgid "inspire"
msgstr "inspirar"

#. [leadership], id=inspire
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/macros/abilities-macro.cfg:122
msgid "female^inspire"
msgstr "inspirar"

#. [leadership], id=inspire
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/macros/abilities-macro.cfg:123
msgid ""
"This unit can inspire our own units that are next to it, making them fight "
"better.\n"
"\n"
"Adjacent own units of will do more damage in battle. When a unit adjacent to "
"a unit with Inspire engages in combat, its attacks do 25% more damage."
msgstr ""
"Esta unidad puede inspirar a nuestras propias unidades adyacentes, haciendo "
"que luchen mejor.\n"
"\n"
"Las unidades aliadas adyacentes infligen más daño en batalla. Cuando una "
"unidad adyacente a una con Inspirar entra en combate, sus ataques hacen un "
"25% más de daño."

#. SPECIAL_NOTES_INSPIRE
#. [abilities], id=inspire
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/macros/abilities-macro.cfg:134
msgid "This unit inspires nearby units to fight +25% better."
msgstr ""
"Esta unidad inspira a las unidades cercanas para que luchen un 25% mejor."

#. [hides], id=sandstalk
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/macros/abilities-macro.cfg:139
msgid "sandstalk"
msgstr "acechar en arena"

#. [hides], id=sandstalk
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/macros/abilities-macro.cfg:140
msgid "female^sandstalk"
msgstr "acechar en arena"

#. [hides], id=sandstalk
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/macros/abilities-macro.cfg:141
msgid ""
"This unit can hide in sand and remain undetected by its enemies.\n"
"\n"
"Enemy units cannot see this unit while it is resting in  sand, except if "
"they have units next to it. Any enemy unit that first discovers this unit "
"immediately loses all its remaining movement."
msgstr ""
"Esta unidad puede ocultarse en la arena y permanecer indetectada por sus "
"enemigos.\n"
"\n"
"Las unidades enemigas no pueden ver a esta unidad mientras descansa en "
"arena, excepto si tienen unidades adyacentes. Cualquier unidad enemiga que "
"la descubra por primera vez pierde inmediatamente todo su movimiento "
"restante."

#. [abilities], id=inspire
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/macros/abilities-macro.cfg:156
msgid ""
"In sand, this unit’s ambush skill renders it invisible to enemies unless it "
"is immediately adjacent or has revealed itself by attacking."
msgstr ""
"En arena, la habilidad de emboscada de esta unidad la hace invisible para "
"los enemigos a menos que esté adyacente o se haya revelado al atacar."

#. [dummy], id=knockback_slow
#. [knockback]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/macros/abilities-macro.cfg:161
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/units/heroes/ilaroth.cfg:120
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/units/heroes/ilaroth.cfg:229
msgid "knockback"
msgstr "repulsión"

#. [dummy], id=knockback_slow
#. [knockback]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/macros/abilities-macro.cfg:162
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/units/heroes/ilaroth.cfg:121
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/units/heroes/ilaroth.cfg:230
msgid ""
"When a unit is hit with a knockback attack, it is immediately pushed back "
"one hex away from the attacker. Units cannot be knocked back into an "
"occupied hex, out of villages or onto terrain they normally could not move "
"to, they will be slowed instead. Only works on offense."
msgstr ""
"Cuando una unidad recibe un ataque de repulsión, es empujada inmediatamente "
"un hexágono hacia atrás. Las unidades no pueden ser empujadas a un hexágono "
"ocupado, fuera de aldeas o a terreno al que normalmente no podrían moverse; "
"en su lugar se ralentizarán. Solo funciona en ataque."

#. [unstore_unit]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/macros/abilities-macro.cfg:244
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/macros/abilities-macro.cfg:305
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/units/heroes/ilaroth.cfg:354
msgid "slowed"
msgstr "ralentizado"

#. [unstore_unit]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/macros/abilities-macro.cfg:285
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/macros/abilities-macro.cfg:461
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/units/heroes/ilaroth.cfg:395
msgid "Knockback!"
msgstr "¡Repulsión!"

#. [dummy], id=knockback_poison
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/macros/abilities-macro.cfg:337
msgid "wyvern knockback"
msgstr "repulsión de guiverno"

#. [dummy], id=knockback_poison
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/macros/abilities-macro.cfg:338
msgid ""
"When a unit is hit with a knockback attack, it is immediately pushed back "
"one hex away from the attacker. Units cannot be knocked back into an "
"occupied hex, out of villages or onto terrain they normally could not move "
"to, they will be poisoned instead. Only works on offense."
msgstr ""
"Cuando una unidad recibe un ataque de repulsión, es empujada inmediatamente "
"un hexágono hacia atrás. Las unidades no pueden ser empujadas a un hexágono "
"ocupado, fuera de aldeas o a terreno al que normalmente no podrían moverse; "
"en su lugar serán envenenadas. Solo funciona en ataque."

#. [unstore_unit]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/macros/abilities-macro.cfg:420
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/macros/abilities-macro.cfg:481
msgid "poisoned"
msgstr "envenenado"

#. [teleport], id=side_by_side
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/macros/abilities-macro.cfg:514
msgid "Side by side"
msgstr "Codo con codo"

#. [teleport], id=side_by_side
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/macros/abilities-macro.cfg:516
msgid "Teleports to nearby friendly units"
msgstr "Teletransporta a unidades aliadas cercanas"

#. [unstore_unit]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/macros/abilities-macro.cfg:557
msgid "Spurt!"
msgstr "¡Impulso!"

#. [advancement], id=amla_heroes_heroic
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/macros/amla-macro.cfg:25
msgid "Heroic"
msgstr "Heroico"

#. [advancement], id=amla_heroes_heroic
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/macros/amla-macro.cfg:26
msgid "      grants +5 hitpoints"
msgstr "      otorga +5 puntos de vida"

#. [event]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/macros/campaign-macro.cfg:14
