msgid "Ilriel"
msgstr "Ilriel"

#. [objective], condition=lose
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/macros/campaign-macro.cfg:26
msgid ""
"Any hero dies <small>(a hero is marked with a silver or golden crown)</small>"
msgstr ""
"Muere cualquier héroe <small>(un héroe está marcado con una corona plateada "
"u dorada)</small>"

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/macros/campaign-macro.cfg:39
msgid "Without her, there's no hope to save these lands now..."
msgstr "Sin ella, ya no hay esperanza de salvar estas tierras..."

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/macros/campaign-macro.cfg:52
msgid "Dawoud!!! How will we confront the darkness that is coming upon us?"
msgstr ""
"¡Dawoud! ¿Cómo enfrentaremos la oscuridad que se acerca sobre nosotros?"

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/macros/campaign-macro.cfg:65
msgid "Noooooo, who will rule our lands now? Don't abandon me, Nuvdael!"
msgstr ""
"¡Nooooooo! ¿Quién gobernará nuestras tierras ahora? ¡No me abandones, "
"Nuvdael!"

#. [message], speaker=Ibn Khazul
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/macros/campaign-macro.cfg:78
msgid "I'm sorry Ridwan, I couldn't be strong enough for our nation."
msgstr ""
"Lo siento, Ridwan, no pude ser lo suficientemente fuerte por nuestra nación."

#. [message], speaker=Ibn Khazul
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/macros/campaign-macro.cfg:91
msgid "Our nation will be lost without our might leader."
msgstr "Nuestra nación se perderá sin nuestro poderoso líder."

#. [message], speaker=Iskandar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/macros/campaign-macro.cfg:104
msgid "No, no, no! His task is not yet done! We need him!"
msgstr "¡No, no, no! ¡Su tarea aún no ha terminado! ¡Lo necesitamos!"

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/macros/campaign-macro.cfg:117
msgid ""
"We won't be able to move on without his knowledge, all hope is gone now..."
msgstr ""
"No podremos seguir adelante sin su conocimiento, toda esperanza se ha "
"perdido..."

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/macros/campaign-macro.cfg:130
msgid "It's a shame that we couldn't protect such an interesting dwarf!"
msgstr ""
"Es una lástima que no hayamos podido proteger a un enano tan interesante."

#. [message], speaker=Iskandar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/macros/campaign-macro.cfg:143
msgid "I wonder what was in store for this tortured soul in his future."
msgstr "Me pregunto qué le deparaba el futuro a esta alma atormentada."

#. [message], speaker=Wahdet
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/macros/campaign-macro.cfg:156
msgid ""
"I just wanted to atone for my sins. I guess I can't run away from them "
"anymore..."
msgstr ""
"Solo quería expiar mis pecados. Supongo que ya no puedo huir de ellos..."

#. [message], speaker=Iskandar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/macros/campaign-macro.cfg:169
msgid ""
"It was already a risk having freed her from her own prison, who knows what "
"will happen now?"
msgstr ""
"Ya fue un riesgo haberla liberado de su propia prisión, ¿quién sabe qué "
"pasará ahora?"

