#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/macros/tharwya-scenery.cfg:22
msgid "Dondolin"
msgstr "Dondolin"

#. [then]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/macros/tharwya-scenery.cfg:43
msgid "Karah"
msgstr "Karah"

#. [then]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/macros/tharwya-scenery.cfg:64
msgid "Balariel"
msgstr "Balariel"

#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/macros/tharwya-scenery.cfg:77
msgid "Sharaf"
msgstr "Sharaf"

#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/macros/tharwya-scenery.cfg:81
msgid "Jadar"
msgstr "Jadar"

#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/macros/tharwya-scenery.cfg:93
msgid "Sakran"
msgstr "Sakran"

#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/macros/tharwya-scenery.cfg:132
msgid "Biqu"
msgstr "Biqu"

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/macros/tharwya-scenery.cfg:210
msgid "<i>Mhhh, I sense something familiar here.</i>"
msgstr "<i>Mhhh, percibo algo familiar aquí.</i>"

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/macros/tharwya-scenery.cfg:222
msgid "<i>Ahhh, a wose, a shepherd of the forests. Here?</i>"
msgstr "<i>Ahhh, un wose, un pastor de los bosques. ¿Aquí?</i>"

#. [event]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/macros/tharwya-scenery.cfg:230
msgid "Yugrusailth"
msgstr "Yugrusailth"

#. [message], speaker=Yugrusailth
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/macros/tharwya-scenery.cfg:234
msgid ""
"Ahhh, a forest spirit. Now it is time to break free and feel life again!"
msgstr ""
"¡Ahhh, un espíritu del bosque! ¡Ahora es tiempo de liberarme y sentir la "
"vida otra vez!"

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/macros/tharwya-scenery.cfg:273
msgid ""
"Another elf? Here in the midst of the deserts? I am Ilriel, the keeper of "
"the Southwoods. What's your name, elf?"
msgstr ""
"¿Otra elfa? ¿Aquí en medio de los desiertos? Soy Ilriel, la guardiana de los "
"Bosques del Sur. ¿Cuál es tu nombre, elfa?"

#. [message], speaker=Balariel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/macros/tharwya-scenery.cfg:278
msgid ""
"A . . . a forest spirit? Here? How is that . . . even possible? My people of "
"the Aethenwoods called me Balariel, but they think I am dead now. But I am "
"not dead. Not yet . . ."
msgstr ""
"¿Un... un espíritu del bosque? ¿Aquí? ¿Cómo es que... eso es posible? Mi "
"gente de los Bosques de Edén me llamaba Balariel, pero creen que estoy "
"muerta ahora. Pero no estoy muerta. Todavía no..."

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/macros/tharwya-scenery.cfg:283
msgid "I will get you out of the cage, Balariel. Trust me."
msgstr "Te sacaré de la jaula, Balariel. Confía en mí."

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/macros/tharwya-scenery.cfg:288
msgid "Desert man, why has the woman been caged?"
msgstr "Hombre del desierto, ¿por qué han encerrado a la mujer?"

#. [message], speaker=Karah
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/macros/tharwya-scenery.cfg:293
msgid "That's none of your business, woman."
msgstr "Eso no es asunto tuyo, mujer."

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/macros/tharwya-scenery.cfg:298
msgid "It is. She is one of my kin."
msgstr "Sí lo es. Es de mi linaje."

#. [message], speaker=Karah
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/macros/tharwya-scenery.cfg:303
msgid "She is just a woman. She is worth less than the sands under my foot."
msgstr "Solo es una mujer. Vale menos que la arena bajo mi pie."

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/macros/tharwya-scenery.cfg:308
msgid "'Just a woman'? That's enough to imprison her? Your moral sickens me."
msgstr ""
"¿«Solo una mujer»? ¿Eso es suficiente para encarcelarla? Tu moral me enferma."

#. [message], speaker=Wahdet
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/macros/tharwya-scenery.cfg:313
msgid "Not everyone shares his values."
msgstr "No todos comparten sus valores."

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/macros/tharwya-scenery.cfg:318
msgid ""
"So why did no one take action against this injustice? In my lands, the word "
"of a woman has the same weight as the word of a man."
msgstr ""
"Entonces, ¿por qué nadie tomó acción contra esta injusticia? En mis tierras, "
"la palabra de una mujer tiene el mismo peso que la de un hombre."

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/macros/tharwya-scenery.cfg:327
msgid ""
"Listen here, desert merchant, you are freeing her now, or else I shall. . ."
msgstr "Escucha, mercader del desierto, la liberas ahora o si no yo..."

#. [message], speaker=Karah
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/macros/tharwya-scenery.cfg:332
msgid "Hold your tongue, woman!"
msgstr "¡Cállate la boca, mujer!"

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/macros/tharwya-scenery.cfg:337
msgid ""
"*whispers* Balariel, I feel that you are not a normal elf. You are like me. "
"You are both heart and soul of a forest."
msgstr ""
"*susurra* Balariel, siento que no eres una elfa normal. Eres como yo. Eres "
"corazón y alma de un bosque."

#. [message], speaker=Balariel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/macros/tharwya-scenery.cfg:342
msgid ""
"*whispers* And as such, freedom is what I need. Help me, Ilriel! Break the "
"iron that is imprisoning me and I shall deal with my hostage-taker."
msgstr ""
"*susurra* Y por eso, la libertad es lo que necesito. ¡Ayúdame, Ilriel! Rompe "
"el hierro que me aprisiona y yo me encargaré de quien me tomó como rehén."

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/macros/tharwya-scenery.cfg:347
msgid "*whispers* Sure, sister. Be ready."
msgstr "*susurra* Claro, hermana. Prepárate."

#. [message], speaker=Karah
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/macros/tharwya-scenery.cfg:358
msgid "What are you doing?!"
msgstr "¡¿Qué estás haciendo?!"

#. [message], speaker=Balariel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/macros/tharwya-scenery.cfg:363
msgid "Just a woman, desert man?"
msgstr "¿Solo una mujer, hombre del desierto?"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/macros/tharwya-scenery.cfg:369
msgid ""
"Suddenly, Balariel's body emerges in light forming ethereal armour that "
"slowly sheets her body."
msgstr ""
"De repente, el cuerpo de Balariel se ilumina formando una armadura etérea "
"que envuelve lentamente su cuerpo."

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/macros/tharwya-scenery.cfg:388
msgid "An Aethensylph!"
msgstr "¡Una silfa de Edén!"

#. [message], speaker=Biqu
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/macros/tharwya-scenery.cfg:394
msgid "What is going on down there? Guards!"
msgstr "¿Qué está pasando allá abajo? ¡Guardias!"

#. [message], speaker=Iskandar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/macros/tharwya-scenery.cfg:399
msgid "There is no need for guards."
msgstr "No hay necesidad de guardias."

#. [message], speaker=Biqu
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/macros/tharwya-scenery.cfg:405
msgid ""
"A . . . an . . . Athvari. Sure . . . no guards. Everything is . . . fine. "
"So . . . sorry."
msgstr ""
"Un... un... athvari. Claro... nada de guardias. Todo está... bien. Lo... "
"siento."

#. [message], speaker=Balariel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/macros/tharwya-scenery.cfg:410
msgid ""
"This woman you caged in could scatter your remains all over the marketplace "
"and for sure, nothing could stop me from doing so. Except my morals. And "
"therefore, I spare your life."
msgstr ""
"Esta mujer que encerraste podría esparcir tus restos por todo el mercado y "
"seguro nada podría detenerme. Excepto mis principios. Y por eso, te perdono "
"la vida."

#. [message], speaker=Karah
#. [message], speaker=Alwat
#. [message], speaker=Iskandar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/macros/tharwya-scenery.cfg:415
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:285
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:903
msgid "I . . . I . . . "
msgstr "Yo... yo..."

#. [message], speaker=Balariel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/macros/tharwya-scenery.cfg:420
msgid ""
"You better get lost into the deserts, before I decide that my morals aren't "
"so important anymore."
msgstr ""
"Mejor desaparece en los desiertos, antes de que decida que mis principios ya "
"no son tan importantes."

#. [message], speaker=Balariel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/macros/tharwya-scenery.cfg:449
msgid ""
"Thank you, Ilriel. We have to hold together, the deserts are dangerous. I "
"shall accompany you on your journey."
msgstr ""
"Gracias, Ilriel. Debemos permanecer unidas, los desiertos son peligrosos. Te "
"acompañaré en tu viaje."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/macros/tharwya-scenery.cfg:539
msgid "Th'arwya - city of gold, city of merchants"
msgstr "Th'arwya - ciudad de oro, ciudad de mercaderes"

#. [part]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/01_From_Afar.cfg:6
msgid ""
"Warning! Oath of Allegiance plays different compared to the mainline "
"campaigns. It contains items, hero units with unique AMLAs and plenty of "
"other stuff not featured in mainline campaigns. It is still adviced to have "
"a good idea about the standard Wesnoth gameplay, before starting this "
"campaign."
msgstr ""
"¡Advertencia! Juramento de Lealtad se juega de forma diferente a las "
"campañas principales. Contiene objetos, unidades heroicas con AMLAs únicas y "
"muchas otras cosas no presentes en las campañas principales. Se recomienda "
"tener una buena idea del juego estándar de Wesnoth antes de comenzar esta "
"campaña."

#. [part]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/01_From_Afar.cfg:10
msgid ""
"We write the year 696 YW when a great civil war rages across the realm of "
"Wesnoth in the aftermath of the death of Konrad II, effectively ending the "
"Garardine dynasty, that restored Wesnoth after the desolation of the Eastern "
"Invasion. The Silver Age that promised prosperity and peace for the people "
"of Wesnoth, found its end, bringing in its place an era of war and chaos."
msgstr ""
"Escribimos el año 696 YW cuando una gran guerra civil asola el reino de "
"Wesnoth tras la muerte de Konrad II, poniendo fin efectivamente a la "
"dinastía Garardine, que había restaurado Wesnoth después de la devastación "
"de la Invasión del Este. La Edad de Plata que prometía prosperidad y paz "
"para el pueblo de Wesnoth llegó a su fin, trayendo en su lugar una era de "
"guerra y caos."

#. [part]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/01_From_Afar.cfg:14
msgid ""
"Yet the elves of the southwestern forests of Wesnoth are surprisingly "
"unaffected by these events. Living peacefully since the beginning of the "
"rule of Konrad II, it seems like the Silver Ages never ended for them."
msgstr ""
"Sin embargo, los elfos de los bosques del suroeste de Wesnoth se ven "
"sorprendentemente afectados por estos eventos. Viviendo en paz desde el "
"comienzo del reinado de Konrad II, parece que la Edad de Plata nunca terminó "
"para ellos."

#. [part]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/01_From_Afar.cfg:18
msgid ""
"It's in the Southwoods, the greatest of the southern forests, where lives "
"Ilriel. It is said that she is the spirit of the forest itself, having "
"manifested itself in the body of a young elvish woman. As a result of not "
"aging, she has seen wars come and go, eras of strife and peace alternating "
"like the tides of the oceans or the days and nights to come. But something "
"is approaching them now. Something different. Something known from times of "
"old. Remembering the pain of long forgotten times, the plants refuse to "
"grow, the wild animals deny food and even the faces of the ancient "
"inhabitants of the forest have not been seen smiling for some time."
msgstr ""
"Es en los Bosques del Sur, el más grande de los bosques sureños, donde vive "
"Ilriel. Se dice que ella es el espíritu del bosque mismo, manifestado en el "
"cuerpo de una joven elfa. Al no envejecer, ha visto guerras ir y venir, eras "
"de conflicto y paz alternando como las mareas de los océanos o los días y "
"noches venideros. Pero algo se acerca ahora. Algo diferente. Algo conocido "
"de tiempos antiguos. Recordando el dolor de épocas olvidadas, las plantas se "
"niegan a crecer, los animales salvajes rechazan la comida e incluso los "
"rostros de los antiguos habitantes del bosque no han sido vistos sonriendo "
"desde hace algún tiempo."

#. [part]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/01_From_Afar.cfg:22
msgid ""
"It seems that life itself is retreating from what is coming to the forests. "
"Yet in the end, it is only life that matters and decides upon the stories "
"being told in the hereafter. But what will the stories be like?"
msgstr ""
"Parece que la vida misma se retira de lo que se acerca a los bosques. Sin "
"embargo, al final, solo la vida importa y decide las historias que se "
"contarán en el más allá. ¿Pero cómo serán esas historias?"

#. [part]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/01_From_Afar.cfg:26
msgid ""
"The clouds become darker than usual. The ones coming are already near. Now "
"allow me to tell you a story. The story of an . . ."
msgstr ""
"Las nubes se vuelven más oscuras de lo habitual. Los que vienen ya están "
"cerca. Ahora permítanme contarles una historia. La historia de un..."

#. [scenario], id=01_From_Afar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/01_From_Afar.cfg:45
msgid "From Afar"
msgstr "Desde Lejos"

#. [side], type=Nuvdael
#. [event]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/01_From_Afar.cfg:86
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/01_From_Afar.cfg:91
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/07_Face_to_Face_with_the_Snake.cfg:66
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/07_Face_to_Face_with_the_Snake.cfg:72
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/19_Above_the_Stars_and_below_Earth.cfg:332
msgid "Nuvdael"
msgstr "Nuvdael"

#. [side]
#. [event]
#. [side], type=Ibn Khazul
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/01_From_Afar.cfg:113
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/01_From_Afar.cfg:202
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/02_Drought.cfg:65
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:130
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/19_Above_the_Stars_and_below_Earth.cfg:334
msgid "Ibn Khazul"
msgstr "Ibn Khazul"

#. [event]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/01_From_Afar.cfg:145
msgid "Yarlbrombrom"
msgstr "Yarlbrombrom"

#. [message], speaker=Nuvdael
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/01_From_Afar.cfg:159
msgid ""
"The birds sing no longer, the wind blows no more, the whisper of the woses "
"is no longer to be heard. The scent of war lies in the air. Something is "
"coming at us, Ilriel, something invisible to our eyes."
msgstr ""
"Los pájaros ya no cantan, el viento ya no sopla, el susurro de los woses ya "
"no se escucha. El aroma de la guerra flota en el aire. Algo se acerca a "
"nosotros, Ilriel, algo invisible a nuestros ojos."

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/01_From_Afar.cfg:164
msgid ""
"It is not invisible to the eyes of the creatures of this forest. Cowering in "
"fear, they foresee the near future. A great danger approaches."
msgstr ""
"No es invisible a los ojos de las criaturas de este bosque. Acobardadas por "
"el miedo, prevén el futuro cercano. Un gran peligro se acerca."

#. [message], speaker=Nuvdael
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/01_From_Afar.cfg:169
msgid ""
"Is a hostile army approaching? How is this possible, Iriel? Our folk had "
"always remained neutral. Who could be filled with rage against our kin?"
msgstr ""
"¿Se acerca un ejército hostil? ¿Cómo es posible, Ilriel? Nuestro pueblo "
"siempre ha permanecido neutral. ¿Quién podría estar lleno de ira contra los "
"nuestros?"

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/01_From_Afar.cfg:174
msgid ""
"It is not a war they are searching for. It seems like they are not the "
"danger the woses feel. A danger lies behind them, in their past, in their "
"homelands. Whatever they might be, I can hear them marching; jarring of "
"irons, swords in the winds, earth trembling beneath the steeds; forsooth, "
"whoever is entering our realm at present moved the heaven and earth to reach "
"us."
msgstr ""
"No es una guerra lo que buscan. Parece que no son el peligro que sienten los "
"woses. Un peligro yace detrás de ellos, en su pasado, en sus tierras "
"natales. Sean lo que sean, puedo oírlos marchar; el entrechocar de hierros, "
"espadas en el viento, la tierra temblando bajo los corceles; en verdad, "
"quien sea que esté entrando en nuestro reino ahora movió cielo y tierra para "
"alcanzarnos."

#. [message], speaker=Nuvdael
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/01_From_Afar.cfg:179
msgid ""
"Whatever they might be, entering our realms while being heavily armed is an "
"insult to the ancient beings living in these woods. No one shall desecrate "
"the Southwoods. Archers, prepare your arrows."
msgstr ""
"Sean lo que sean, entrar en nuestros dominios fuertemente armados es un "
"insulto a los antiguos seres que viven en estos bosques. Nadie profanará los "
"Bosques del Sur. Arqueros, preparen sus flechas."

#. [event]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/01_From_Afar.cfg:182
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/07_Face_to_Face_with_the_Snake.cfg:145
msgid "Kenlaed"
msgstr "Kenlaed"

#. [message], speaker=Kenlaed
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/01_From_Afar.cfg:190
msgid "Arrows ready!"
msgstr "¡Flechas listas!"

#. [message], speaker=Nuvdael
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/01_From_Afar.cfg:195
msgid "At the horizon!"
msgstr "¡En el horizonte!"

#. [event]
#. [side], type=Ibn Khazul
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/01_From_Afar.cfg:212
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/02_Drought.cfg:59
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/02_Drought.cfg:130
msgid "Dawoud"
msgstr "Dawoud"

#. [object]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/01_From_Afar.cfg:222
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/02_Drought.cfg:137
msgid "Dawoud-OoA-changes"
msgstr "Dawoud-OoA-cambios"

#. [advancement], id=amla_ilaroth_athvari
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/01_From_Afar.cfg:240
msgid ""
"<span color='#63bfe5'><b>Unknown powers</b></span>\n"
"\t\t\t"
msgstr ""
"<span color='#63bfe5'><b>Poderes desconocidos</b></span>\n"
"\t\t\t"

#. [advancement], id=amla_ilaroth_athvari
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/01_From_Afar.cfg:241
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/02_Drought.cfg:152
msgid "      grants the arcane attack type"
msgstr "      otorga el tipo de ataque arcano"

#. [event]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/01_From_Afar.cfg:287
msgid "Karim"
msgstr "Karim"

#. [message], speaker=Ibn Khazul
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/01_From_Afar.cfg:299
msgid ""
"Bunlar, Dawoud sozunu ettigi ormanlari vardir. Sonra gidip sakinleri konusun."
msgstr ""
"Bunlar, Dawoud sozunu ettigi ormanlari vardir. Sonra gidip sakinleri konusun."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/01_From_Afar.cfg:304
msgid "Su var ki."
msgstr "Su var ki."

#. [message], speaker=Nuvdael
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/01_From_Afar.cfg:309
msgid "What are they saying? Are they preparing an attack?"
msgstr "¿Qué están diciendo? ¿Están preparando un ataque?"

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/01_From_Afar.cfg:314
msgid ""
"A foreign tongue, nothing I've ever encountered before. They must come from "
"realms outside Wesnoth."
msgstr ""
"Una lengua extranjera, nada que haya encontrado antes. Deben venir de reinos "
"fuera de Wesnoth."

#. [message], speaker=Nuvdael
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/01_From_Afar.cfg:319
msgid ""
"We can't risk the lives within the Southwoods. Wind wafts! Wind storms! "
"Season them with your arrows, Kenlaed! Black out the sun!"
msgstr ""
"No podemos arriesgar las vidas dentro de los Bosques del Sur. ¡Vientos "
"soplen! ¡Tormentas de viento! ¡Sazónenlos con sus flechas, Kenlaed! "
"¡Oscurezcan el sol!"

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/01_From_Afar.cfg:327
msgid "Halt! Nobody moves!"
msgstr "¡Alto! ¡Nadie se mueva!"

#. [message], speaker=Nuvdael
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/01_From_Afar.cfg:332
msgid "Il . . . Ilriel?"
msgstr "Il... ¿Ilriel?"

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/01_From_Afar.cfg:338
msgid ""
"There is no need to splatter blood on the earth nourishing these holy woods."
msgstr ""
"No hay necesidad de salpicar sangre en la tierra que nutre estos bosques "
"sagrados."

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#. [message], speaker=Ridwan
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/01_From_Afar.cfg:343
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/17_The_Great_Wall.cfg:576
msgid "Look!"
msgstr "¡Miren!"

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/01_From_Afar.cfg:348
msgid ""
"We are coming in peace, men and women of the forests. But war lies behind us."
msgstr ""
"Venimos en paz, hombres y mujeres de los bosques. Pero la guerra yace detrás "
"de nosotros."

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/01_From_Afar.cfg:355
msgid ""
"You speak the tongue of our kin, man of the foreignness, and you've entered "
"the realm of my kin. As I am the highest of the keepers of this forest, I "
"urge you to explain yourself."
msgstr ""
"Hablas la lengua de los nuestros, hombre de tierras extrañas, y has entrado "
"en el reino de mi gente. Como soy la más alta de las guardianas de este "
"bosque, te insto a que te expliques."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/01_From_Afar.cfg:360
msgid ""
"I am Dawoud and I am from lands far away, lands behind the vast deserts. For "
"a long time have our eyes watched you."
msgstr ""
"Soy Dawoud y vengo de tierras lejanas, tierras detrás de los vastos "
"desiertos. Durante mucho tiempo nuestros ojos los han observado."

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/01_From_Afar.cfg:365
msgid ""
"For ages, no one dared to enter the realm of the Southwoods. Any spy would "
"have found his grave below the roots of the woses."
msgstr ""
"Durante siglos, nadie se atrevió a entrar en el reino de los Bosques del "
"Sur. Cualquier espía habría encontrado su tumba bajo las raíces de los woses."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/01_From_Afar.cfg:370
msgid ""
"We know your power and your power is what we are in need of. A great danger "
"lies beneath the sands that are our home, a danger that is slowly devouring "
"the will of our people. The Dune Warmaster of the city of Serrul has been "
"poisoned. But it is not a poison we can cure. It is . . . more than that."
msgstr ""
"Conocemos tu poder y es tu poder lo que necesitamos. Un gran peligro yace "
"bajo las arenas que son nuestro hogar, un peligro que lentamente devora la "
"voluntad de nuestro pueblo. El Maestro de Guerra de la ciudad de Serrul ha "
"sido envenenado. Pero no es un veneno que podamos curar. Es... más que eso."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/01_From_Afar.cfg:375
msgid ""
"We need your help in order to cure his illness as our people cannot make use "
"of magic. You have to cure the Dune Warmaster, so he can lead our troops to "
"repel the terror. Your magic is able to avert the dangers terrorizing our "
"people."
msgstr ""
"Necesitamos tu ayuda para curar su enfermedad ya que nuestro pueblo no puede "
"usar magia. Debes curar al Maestro de Guerra para que pueda liderar nuestras "
"tropas y repeler el terror. Tu magia puede alejar los peligros que "
"aterrorizan a nuestro pueblo."

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/01_From_Afar.cfg:380
msgid ""
"I value the life of any being with a pure heart fighting for its cause, but "
"why should I trust you?"
msgstr ""
"Valoro la vida de cualquier ser con un corazón puro que lucha por su causa, "
"pero ¿por qué debería confiar en ti?"

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/01_From_Afar.cfg:385
msgid ""
"The city of Serrul is a bulwark to the east. Once Serrul falls, the evil "
"powers reigning beyond will pour into the realms of the west, into your "
"beloved woods. Any man, any woman and any child of both our kin will face "
"the consequences."
msgstr ""
"La ciudad de Serrul es un baluarte al este. Una vez que Serrul caiga, los "
"poderes malvados que reinan más allá se derramarán en los reinos del oeste, "
"en tus amados bosques. Cualquier hombre, mujer o niño de ambos linajes "
"enfrentará las consecuencias."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/01_From_Afar.cfg:390
msgid "The threat I am talking about is not new to your people."
msgstr "La amenaza de la que hablo no es nueva para tu pueblo."

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/01_From_Afar.cfg:395
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/22_Timeless.cfg:268
msgid "What do you mean?"
msgstr "¿Qué quieres decir?"

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/01_From_Afar.cfg:400
msgid "Take a look at this."
msgstr "Mira esto."

#. [object]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/01_From_Afar.cfg:406
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:1187
msgid "Acorn of the Great Tree"
msgstr "Bellota del Gran Árbol"

#. [object]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/01_From_Afar.cfg:408
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:1189
msgid ""
"An enormous, foot-long acorn. For sure this is no ordinary fruit. It must be "
"very old, yet it has been conserved well."
msgstr ""
"Una enorme bellota de un pie de largo. Sin duda no es un fruto ordinario. "
"Debe ser muy antigua, pero se ha conservado bien."

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/01_From_Afar.cfg:417
msgid "This . . . this is a great acorn from . . ."
msgstr "Esto... esta es una gran bellota de..."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/01_From_Afar.cfg:422
msgid "An acorn from the ancient beings inhabiting your forests."
msgstr "Una bellota de los antiguos seres que habitan tus bosques."

#. [message], speaker=Yarlbrombrom
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/01_From_Afar.cfg:427
msgid "Brothers . . . sisters . . . I . . . feel . . . them . . ."
msgstr "Hermanos... hermanas... yo... los... siento..."

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/01_From_Afar.cfg:432
msgid ""
"Where did you get it? The woses of the Southwoods have not born these fruits "
"for ages, yet they had hundreds of years ago."
msgstr ""
"¿Dónde la conseguiste? Los woses de los Bosques del Sur no han dado estos "
"frutos durante siglos, aunque los tuvieron hace cientos de años."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/01_From_Afar.cfg:437
msgid ""
"Our history is connected, Ilriel. There is so much more behind the sands "
"that seem like a barrier to your kin. You have to come with us to protect "
"our common legacy. Your pain is our pain and our pain is yours. It is my kin "
"that relies on you. Come with us."
msgstr ""
"Nuestra historia está conectada, Ilriel. Hay mucho más detrás de las arenas "
"que parecen una barrera para tu gente. Debes venir con nosotros para "
"proteger nuestro legado común. Tu dolor es nuestro dolor y nuestro dolor es "
"tuyo. Es mi pueblo el que depende de ti. Ven con nosotros."

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/01_From_Afar.cfg:442
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/22_Timeless.cfg:278
msgid "I . . . I . . ."
msgstr "Yo... yo..."

#. [message], speaker=Nuvdael
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/01_From_Afar.cfg:447
msgid "Ilriel is not going with you."
msgstr "Ilriel no irá contigo."

#. [message], speaker=Yarlbrombrom
#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/01_From_Afar.cfg:456
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/07_Face_to_Face_with_the_Snake.cfg:232
msgid "Nuvdael!"
msgstr "¡Nuvdael!"

#. [message], speaker=Nuvdael
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/01_From_Afar.cfg:461
msgid "Yarlbrombrom . . ."
msgstr "Yarlbrombrom..."

#. [message], speaker=Yarlbrombrom
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/01_From_Afar.cfg:466
msgid ""
"The forest demands it. As a keeper of the forest, as our soul and heart, "
"Ilriel has to secure the continuance of the forests. My kin is slowly dying, "
"the Southwoods are slowly dying. She has to find out what is going on."
msgstr ""
"El bosque lo exige. Como guardiana del bosque, como nuestra alma y corazón, "
"Ilriel debe asegurar la continuidad de los bosques. Mi pueblo se está "
"muriendo lentamente, los Bosques del Sur se están muriendo lentamente. Ella "
"debe descubrir qué está pasando."

#. [message], speaker=Nuvdael
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/01_From_Afar.cfg:471
msgid "Then we are coming with you."
msgstr "Entonces iremos contigo."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/01_From_Afar.cfg:476
msgid ""
"Serrul is in danger and your kin can't get quickly through the sands. We "
"have to go alone."
msgstr ""
"Serrul está en peligro y tu gente no puede cruzar las arenas rápidamente. "
"Debemos ir solos."

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/01_From_Afar.cfg:481
msgid "Nuvdael, we can trust them."
msgstr "Nuvdael, podemos confiar en ellos."

#. [message], speaker=Nuvdael
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/01_From_Afar.cfg:486
msgid ""
"The bond between you and the forest shall not diminish, Ilriel. Take care."
msgstr "El vínculo entre tú y el bosque no debe debilitarse, Ilriel. Cuídate."

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/01_From_Afar.cfg:491
msgid "Thanks, Nuvdael. You are a good leader, guide our people well.."
msgstr "Gracias, Nuvdael. Eres un buen líder, guía bien a nuestro pueblo."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/01_From_Afar.cfg:496
msgid ""
"We shall never forget your support, men and women of the forests. I hereby, "
"as a general of Serrul, make an Oath of Allegiance to you, Nuvdael, and your "
"kin. I shall take care that you and Ilriel unite again after the task has "
"been done. May your forests stay verdant and fruitful."
msgstr ""
"Nunca olvidaremos su apoyo, hombres y mujeres de los bosques. Yo, como "
"general de Serrul, hago aquí un Juramento de Lealtad a ti, Nuvdael, y a tu "
"pueblo. Me aseguraré de que tú e Ilriel se reúnan nuevamente una vez "
"cumplida la tarea. Que tus bosques permanezcan verdes y fructíferos."

#. [message], speaker=Nuvdael
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/01_From_Afar.cfg:501
msgid "Then you have my blessings. Take care of her."
msgstr "Entonces tienes mi bendición. Cuida de ella."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/01_From_Afar.cfg:506
msgid "Let us start our journey."
msgstr "Comencemos nuestro viaje."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/01_From_Afar.cfg:511
msgid "Ibn Khazul, gidebiliriz."
msgstr "Ibn Khazul, gidebiliriz."

#. [message], speaker=Ibn Khazul
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/01_From_Afar.cfg:516
msgid "Anlastik, gidelim."
msgstr "Anlastik, gidelim."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/01_From_Afar.cfg:521
msgid "Farewell, elves."
msgstr "Adiós, elfos."

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/01_From_Afar.cfg:526
msgid "Farewell, brothers and sisters."
msgstr "Adiós, hermanos y hermanas."

#. [part]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/02_Drought.cfg:7
msgid ""
"Day and night passed, as Ilriel and the men of the foreignness left the "
"Southwoods behind and entered the drylands. Lands, that are untameable and "
"wild. The quest towards Serrul had just begun, yet Dawoud felt the cold grip "
"of his homelands that forced him to act quickly. They had to reach Serrul in "
"time. "
msgstr ""
"Día y noche pasaron mientras Ilriel y los hombres de tierras extrañas "
"dejaban atrás los Bosques del Sur y entraban en las tierras áridas. Tierras "
"indomables y salvajes. La búsqueda hacia Serrul apenas había comenzado, pero "
"Dawoud sentía el frío agarre de su tierra natal que lo obligaba a actuar "
"rápido. Tenían que llegar a Serrul a tiempo."

#. [scenario], id=02_Drought
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/02_Drought.cfg:18
msgid "Drought"
msgstr "Sequía"

#. [side], type=Bandit
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/02_Drought.cfg:87
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/02_Drought.cfg:92
msgid "Esgolf"
msgstr "Esgolf"

#. [side], type=Fugitive
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/02_Drought.cfg:110
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/02_Drought.cfg:115
msgid "Alfarn"
msgstr "Alfarn"

#. [advancement], id=amla_ilaroth_athvari
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/02_Drought.cfg:151
msgid "Unknown powers\n"
msgstr "Poderes desconocidos\n"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/02_Drought.cfg:194
msgid ""
"After listening to the foreign men for a few days, Ilriel slowly begins to "
"understand their unfamiliar tongue."
msgstr ""
"Después de escuchar a los hombres extranjeros durante unos días, Ilriel "
"comienza lentamente a entender su lengua desconocida."

#. [message], speaker=Ibn Khazul
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/02_Drought.cfg:199
msgid ""
"We should have marched through the night. There is not much time left before "
"Serrul is sieged."
msgstr ""
"Deberíamos haber marchado durante la noche. No queda mucho tiempo antes de "
"que Serrul sea sitiada."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/02_Drought.cfg:204
msgid ""
"The men are tired, there is no other choice. If we continued our march like "
"this, even our surfooted men would misstep for sure. Fatigue and accidents "
"would ensure our road home to take even longer."
msgstr ""
"Los hombres están cansados, no hay otra opción. Si continuáramos la marcha "
"así, incluso nuestros hombres de a pie tropezarían seguro. El cansancio y "
"los accidentes harían que el camino a casa tome aún más tiempo."

#. [message], speaker=Ibn Khazul
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/02_Drought.cfg:209
msgid ""
"You are right, Dawoud. It is just that the whole situation looks so "
"hopeless. We shouldn't be here, right now, we should be in Serrul."
msgstr ""
"Tienes razón, Dawoud. Es solo que toda la situación se ve tan "
"desesperanzada. No deberíamos estar aquí ahora, deberíamos estar en Serrul."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/02_Drought.cfg:222
msgid "Ahh, Kartal! What news do you bring?"
msgstr "¡Ah, Kartal! ¿Qué noticias traes?"

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/02_Drought.cfg:227
msgid "Mhhh."
msgstr "Mhhh."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/02_Drought.cfg:232
msgid "What?!"
msgstr "¡¿Qué?!"

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/02_Drought.cfg:237
msgid ""
"Serrul is under attack! Apparently a vanguard of the forces of Kesh took "
"advantage of the state of the Dune Warmaster!"
msgstr ""
"¡Serrul está bajo ataque! ¡Al parecer una vanguardia de las fuerzas de Kesh "
"aprovechó el estado del Maestro de Guerra!"

#. [message], speaker=Ibn Khazul
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/02_Drought.cfg:242
msgid "Then we have to take action, Dawoud."
msgstr "Entonces tenemos que actuar, Dawoud."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/02_Drought.cfg:247
msgid "What do you suggest?"
msgstr "¿Qué sugieres?"

#. [message], speaker=Ibn Khazul
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/02_Drought.cfg:252
msgid ""
"We have to split into two groups. I will take my riders and press onwards to "
"Serrul."
msgstr ""
"Tenemos que dividirnos en dos grupos. Yo tomaré a mis jinetes y avanzaré "
"hacia Serrul."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/02_Drought.cfg:257
msgid "And risk getting drawn into fights in these hostile lands?"
msgstr "¿Y arriesgarse a ser arrastrados a combates en estas tierras hostiles?"

#. [message], speaker=Ibn Khazul
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/02_Drought.cfg:262
msgid ""
"There is no choice to be made. If we don't reach Serrul quickly, it will "
"fall. And then there's no Dune Warmaster to be cured and the bulwark breaks."
msgstr ""
"No hay elección que hacer. Si no llegamos rápido a Serrul, caerá. Y entonces "
"no habrá Maestro de Guerra que curar y el baluarte se rompe."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/02_Drought.cfg:267
msgid "What will happen to Ilriel?"
msgstr "¿Qué pasará con Ilriel?"

#. [message], speaker=Ibn Khazul
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/02_Drought.cfg:272
msgid ""
"She will stay with you. The battle we will be fighting won't be easy. A "
"carpet of blood will cover the sands of Serrul. This will be no place for "
"her. You are my most loyal general, Dawoud, I trust you."
msgstr ""
"Ella se quedará contigo. La batalla que libraremos no será fácil. Una "
"alfombra de sangre cubrirá las arenas de Serrul. Este no será lugar para "
"ella. Eres mi general más leal, Dawoud, confío en ti."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/02_Drought.cfg:277
msgid ""
"We shall follow you as quickly as possible. Fight hard so we shall meet "
"again."
msgstr ""
"Te seguiremos lo más rápido posible. Lucha con fuerza para que nos "
"encontremos de nuevo."

#. [message], speaker=Ibn Khazul
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/02_Drought.cfg:282
msgid "We will. Riders! To Serrul!"
msgstr "Lo haremos. ¡Jinetes! ¡A Serrul!"

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/02_Drought.cfg:302
msgid "Now we are on our own in these lost forests."
msgstr "Ahora estamos solos en estos bosques perdidos."

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/02_Drought.cfg:307
msgid "Even the woses detest this place."
msgstr "Incluso los woses detestan este lugar."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/02_Drought.cfg:312
msgid ""
"We will rest here for this night, though, as our men demanded it. At "
"sunrise, we will move on."
msgstr ""
"Descansaremos aquí esta noche, tal como exigieron nuestros hombres. Al "
"amanecer continuaremos."

#. [message], speaker=Esgolf
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/02_Drought.cfg:322
msgid ""
"Oh, you won't be moving anywhere, man of the desert. This woman is mine! "
"It's been a long time since I saw someone like her! Hand her to me!"
msgstr ""
"Oh, no irás a ninguna parte, hombre del desierto. ¡Esta mujer es mía! ¡Hace "
"mucho tiempo que no veía a alguien como ella! ¡Entrégamela!"

#. [message], speaker=Alfarn
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/02_Drought.cfg:327
msgid "Esgolf, you fool! Now the lady has a false impression of us!"
msgstr "¡Esgolf, idiota! ¡Ahora la dama tiene una impresión falsa de nosotros!"

#. [message], speaker=Esgolf
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/02_Drought.cfg:332
msgid ""
"Haha! What's false about it?! Free the lady from the hands of the desert men!"
msgstr ""
"¡Jaja! ¿Qué hay de falso en eso? ¡Libera a la dama de las manos de los "
"hombres del desierto!"

#. [event]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/02_Drought.cfg:338
msgid "Sam"
msgstr "Sam"

#. [message], speaker=Esgolf
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/02_Drought.cfg:350
msgid "Eh, so what are your last words?"
msgstr "Eh, ¿cuáles son tus últimas palabras?"

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/02_Drought.cfg:355
msgid "Men! Protect her! Don't let the bandits seize her!"
msgstr "¡Hombres! ¡Protéjanla! ¡No dejen que los bandidos la capturen!"

#. [message], speaker=Esgolf
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/02_Drought.cfg:360
msgid ". . . wrong words."
msgstr "... palabras equivocadas."

#. [message], speaker=Esgolf
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/02_Drought.cfg:365
msgid "Sam!"
msgstr "¡Sam!"

#. [message], speaker=Sam
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/02_Drought.cfg:370
msgid "Ayeee!"
msgstr "¡Ayeee!"

#. [animate_unit]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/02_Drought.cfg:384
msgid "Die, desert rat!"
msgstr "¡Muere, rata del desierto!"

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/02_Drought.cfg:442
msgid "Ughh."
msgstr "Ughh."

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/02_Drought.cfg:447
msgid "Dawoud!"
msgstr "¡Dawoud!"

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/02_Drought.cfg:452
msgid "You . . . you are not bleeding? How . . ."
msgstr "Tú... ¿no estás sangrando? ¿Cómo...?"

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/02_Drought.cfg:457
msgid "They . . . they didn't hit me . . ."
msgstr "Ellos... no me golpearon..."

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/02_Drought.cfg:462
msgid "They pierced your armor!"
msgstr "¡Perforaron tu armadura!"

#. [message], speaker=Esgolf
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/02_Drought.cfg:467
msgid "Men! Men! Into the woods! That man is not from this world!"
msgstr "¡Hombres! ¡Hombres! ¡Al bosque! ¡Ese hombre no es de este mundo!"

#. [message], speaker=Alfarn
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/02_Drought.cfg:472
msgid ""
"Esgolf, I told you that you were a fool! Now you are fleeing! Pah! You are "
"staying with me! We will bring them down. Once his head swims down the "
"river, he is done anyway!"
msgstr ""
"¡Esgolf, te dije que eras un idiota! ¡Ahora huyes! ¡Pah! ¡Te quedas conmigo! "
"Los derribaremos. ¡Una vez que su cabeza flote río abajo, estará acabado de "
"todos modos!"

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/02_Drought.cfg:480
msgid "Dawoud, are you fine?"
msgstr "Dawoud, ¿estás bien?"

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/02_Drought.cfg:485
msgid "Yes . . . yes, I am fine."
msgstr "Sí... sí, estoy bien."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/02_Drought.cfg:490
msgid ""
"This land truly houses a lot of bandits and thieves. We will have to fight "
"them off. Stay close to my men, they shall give their life for yours."
msgstr ""
"Esta tierra realmente alberga muchos bandidos y ladrones. Tendremos que "
"combatirlos. Quédate cerca de mis hombres, ellos darán su vida por la tuya."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#. [message], speaker=Ibn Ghani
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/02_Drought.cfg:495
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/16_Return_to_Tharwya.cfg:613
msgid "Men! To arms!"
msgstr "¡Hombres! ¡A las armas!"

#. [message], speaker=Alfarn
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/02_Drought.cfg:500
msgid "Great, Esgolf. Really great!"
msgstr "Genial, Esgolf. ¡Realmente genial!"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/02_Drought.cfg:511
msgid ""
"Both Ilriel and Dawoud can recruit units. As hero units, they are able to "
"unlock several abilities and improvements through advancing. Hero units have "
"an improved default AMLA, giving them +5hp and +1 damage."
msgstr ""
"Tanto Ilriel como Dawoud pueden reclutar unidades. Como unidades heroicas, "
"pueden desbloquear varias habilidades y mejoras al avanzar. Las unidades "
"heroicas tienen un AMLA predeterminado mejorado, que les otorga +5 PV y +1 "
"de daño."

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/02_Drought.cfg:520
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/04_A_Whisper_in_the_Sands.cfg:469
msgid "Defeat the bandit leaders"
msgstr "Derrota a los líderes de bandidos"

#. [object]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/02_Drought.cfg:540
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:541
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/12_Cloud_River.cfg:370
msgid "New Recruits:"
msgstr "Nuevos reclutas:"

#. [object]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/02_Drought.cfg:541
msgid ""
"\n"
"The Dune Soldier pose as excellent melee fighters that are able to easily "
"cut through the enemies defense.\n"
"\n"
"The Dune Skirmisher is a weak but versatile fighter. It is capable to ignore "
"the Zone of Control of the enemy.\n"
"\n"
"The Dune Rover has no real weakness, and as such, he plays a great part in "
"any Dunefolk army.\n"
"\n"
"The Dune Herbalist is a supportive unit with a strong +4 healing ability, "
"yet he is not able to cure poisons.\n"
"\n"
"The Dune Burner is a specialised unit with a fire attack type, which is "
"unique among the units of the Dunefolk."
msgstr ""
"\n"
"El Soldado barján se presenta como un excelente luchador cuerpo a cuerpo "
"capaz de atravesar fácilmente la defensa enemiga.\n"
"\n"
"El Hostigador barján es un luchador débil pero versátil. Es capaz de ignorar "
"la Zona de Control del enemigo.\n"
"\n"
"El Caminante barján no tiene debilidades reales y por eso juega un gran "
"papel en cualquier ejército barján.\n"
"\n"
"El Herborista barján es una unidad de apoyo con una fuerte habilidad de "
"sanación +4, aunque no puede curar venenos.\n"
"\n"
"El Incendiario barján es una unidad especializada con tipo de ataque de "
"fuego, único entre las unidades barjanes."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/02_Drought.cfg:569
msgid ""
"A sword has been washed up next to the river bed. Only units with an blade "
"melee attack should pick it up. Be reminded, that once a unit picked up an "
"item, it can not pick up another one and it can't lay it down. So be careful "
"who picks it up."
msgstr ""
"Una espada ha sido arrastrada junto al lecho del río. Solo unidades con "
"ataque cuerpo a cuerpo de corte deben recogerla. Recuerda que una vez que "
"una unidad recoge un objeto, no puede recoger otro ni soltarlo. Así que ten "
"cuidado quién la recoge."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/02_Drought.cfg:582
msgid ""
"Once picked up, an icon appears above the unit, showing that this unit wears "
"an item. Items can be used to compensate the weaknesses of a unit, "
"emphasizing the strengths of it, or to fill another role. There's some items "
"to be found, watch out! When hovering above the unit type of the unit "
"displayed in the unit panel, the item that the unit is wielding is shown in "
"the text."
msgstr ""
"Una vez recogido, aparece un ícono sobre la unidad que indica que lleva un "
"objeto. Los objetos se pueden usar para compensar debilidades de una unidad, "
"resaltar sus fortalezas o cumplir otro rol. Hay algunos objetos por "
"encontrar, ¡estén atentos! Al pasar el cursor sobre el tipo de unidad en el "
"panel, se muestra el objeto que lleva la unidad en el texto."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/02_Drought.cfg:592
msgid ""
"I miss the old times. Times when such large groups were not pressed to "
"banditry and theft. Chaos is ruling these days, the world's framework became "
"fragile and decadent. And as the days pass by, it's just getting worse."
msgstr ""
"Echo de menos los viejos tiempos. Tiempos en los que grupos tan grandes no "
"se veían obligados a la bandidaje y el robo. El caos gobierna estos días, el "
"marco del mundo se volvió frágil y decadente. Y a medida que pasan los días, "
"solo empeora."

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/02_Drought.cfg:597
msgid ""
"The chaos also affected Serrul. But is it also the pinnacle of chaos or just "
"a mere shadow of dark schemings that are unknown to our very own eyes?"
msgstr ""
"El caos también afectó a Serrul. Pero ¿es también la cúspide del caos o solo "
"una mera sombra de oscuros planes desconocidos para nuestros propios ojos?"

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/02_Drought.cfg:602
msgid ""
"We are both eager to find that answer. Serrul relies on us, we can't let the "
"people down, they need us."
msgstr ""
"Ambos estamos ansiosos por encontrar esa respuesta. Serrul depende de "
"nosotros, no podemos defraudar al pueblo, nos necesitan."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/02_Drought.cfg:621
msgid "Words in an unknown language are carved in stone. It says:"
msgstr "Palabras en una lengua desconocida están talladas en piedra. Dice:"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/02_Drought.cfg:627
msgid "BAIR HERNUM BLACKQVASTEN DEORE ATUM"
msgstr "BAIR HERNUM BLACKQVASTEN DEORE ATUM"

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/02_Drought.cfg:643
msgid "I hope you've learned your lesson, you dishonorable bandit!"
msgstr "¡Espero que hayas aprendido la lección, bandido deshonroso!"

#. [message], speaker=Esgolf
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/02_Drought.cfg:648
msgid "What . . . what are you?"
msgstr "¿Qué... qué eres?"

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/02_Drought.cfg:660
msgid "That serves him right!"
msgstr "¡Se lo merece!"

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/02_Drought.cfg:671
msgid "That's the other one."
msgstr "Ese es el otro."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/02_Drought.cfg:676
msgid "You are of a warrior's nature, Ilriel. I didn't expect that."
msgstr "Tienes naturaleza de guerrera, Ilriel. No lo esperaba."

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/02_Drought.cfg:681
msgid ""
"The blood of my ancestors flows in my veins. They had a power that has been "
"forgotten these days."
msgstr ""
"La sangre de mis ancestros corre por mis venas. Ellos tenían un poder que se "
"ha olvidado en estos días."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/02_Drought.cfg:686
msgid "This reminds me of my own past. We have much in common."
msgstr "Esto me recuerda mi propio pasado. Tenemos mucho en común."

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/02_Drought.cfg:691
msgid "So what happened to your Dune Warmaster?"
msgstr "¿Qué le pasó a tu Maestro de Guerra?"

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/02_Drought.cfg:696
msgid ""
"The Dune Warmaster of Serrul, Ridwan, fell victim to a strange disease, "
"poisoning his mind and rendering him unable to rule his realms. Uthman, the "
"sovereign of Kesh, a city in the east of the ashland deserts that is widely "
"known throughout the lands of my kin for its strong military force, got wind "
"of his weakened state and now lusts for his blood and throne. As long as the "
"Dune Warmaster of Serrul is ill, the power-hungry will be drawn to Serrul "
"like moths to the flame."
msgstr ""
"El Maestro de Guerra de Serrul, Ridwan, cayó víctima de una extraña "
"enfermedad que envenenó su mente y lo dejó incapaz de gobernar sus tierras. "
"Uthman, el soberano de Kesh, una ciudad al este de los desiertos de ceniza "
"conocida en las tierras de mi pueblo por su fuerte fuerza militar, se enteró "
"de su estado debilitado y ahora ansía su sangre y su trono. Mientras el "
"Maestro de Guerra de Serrul esté enfermo, los sedientos de poder se sentirán "
"atraídos por Serrul como polillas a la llama."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/02_Drought.cfg:701
msgid ""
"We assume Uthman is already preparing an attack on Serrul to plunge its "
"citizens into slavery and death in order to extend his own power."
msgstr ""
"Suponemos que Uthman ya está preparando un ataque contra Serrul para sumir a "
"sus ciudadanos en la esclavitud y la muerte con el fin de extender su propio "
"poder."

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/02_Drought.cfg:706
msgid "How far away is Serrul? Is there a chance we will arrive in time?"
msgstr ""
"¿Qué tan lejos está Serrul? ¿Hay alguna posibilidad de que lleguemos a "
"tiempo?"

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/02_Drought.cfg:711
msgid ""
"It is a long journey and we will walk for some months. If we move quickly, "
"we might still make it. But I see there are already a lot of worries resting "
"on your shoulders. You should sleep well this night, the forthcoming days "
"will be demanding. We will wander through the Mountains of Peril."
msgstr ""
"Es un viaje largo y caminaremos durante algunos meses. Si nos movemos "
"rápido, aún podríamos lograrlo. Pero veo que ya hay muchas preocupaciones "
"sobre tus hombros. Deberías dormir bien esta noche, los días venideros serán "
"exigentes. Atravesaremos las Montañas del Peligro."

#. [message], speaker=Alfarn
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/02_Drought.cfg:721
msgid "At last our hunting party has arrived. Time to finish this squabble!"
msgstr "¡Por fin llegó nuestro grupo de caza! ¡Es hora de terminar esta pelea!"

#. [message], speaker=Esgolf
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/02_Drought.cfg:726
msgid "Don't worry maiden, we're coming to rescue you!"
msgstr "¡No te preocupes doncella, venimos a rescatarte!"

#. [part]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/03_Peril.cfg:7
msgid ""
"After a long march, the group reached a huge mountainside known as the "
"Mountains of Peril. Wanderers avoid this place, where many a wanderer was "
"never seen again. But beholding Ilriel, Dawoud knew that she was the one "
"with the ability to help him with his cause. Hope resurging, Dawoud has "
"sworn to safely bring the group through the mountain pass."
msgstr ""
"Después de una larga marcha, el grupo llegó a una enorme cordillera conocida "
"como las Montañas del Peligro. Los viajeros evitan este lugar, donde muchos "
"nunca fueron vistos de nuevo. Pero al contemplar a Ilriel, Dawoud supo que "
"ella era la indicada con la habilidad para ayudarlo en su causa. Con la "
"esperanza renovada, Dawoud juró llevar al grupo sano y salvo a través del "
"paso de montaña."

#. [scenario], id=03_Peril
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/03_Peril.cfg:18
msgid "Peril"
msgstr "Peligro"

#. [side], type=Troll Warrior
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/03_Peril.cfg:58
msgid "Trolls"
msgstr "Trolls"

#. [side], type=Troll Warrior
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/03_Peril.cfg:64
msgid "Rumms"
msgstr "Rumms"

#. [side]
#. [unit], id=Narfi, type=Elvish Outrider
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/03_Peril.cfg:100
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/03_Peril.cfg:268
msgid "Narfi"
msgstr "Narfi"

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/03_Peril.cfg:159
msgid ""
"These are the foothills of the Mountains of Peril. Only the valley is now "
"separating us from my kin. A great desert lies behind it."
msgstr ""
"Estas son las estribaciones de las Montañas del Peligro. Solo el valle nos "
"separa ahora de mi pueblo. Detrás hay un gran desierto."

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/03_Peril.cfg:164
msgid ""
"The Mountains of Peril . . . they are enormous. I've never seen them with my "
"own eyes."
msgstr ""
"Las Montañas del Peligro... son enormes. Nunca las había visto con mis "
"propios ojos."

#. [message], speaker=Rumms
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/03_Peril.cfg:169
msgid ""
"You! Desert men! Pay troll or die! Uhm. . . the toll is . . . your life! Die "
"or . . . uhm . . . die!"
msgstr ""
"¡Ustedes! ¡Hombres del desierto! ¡Paguen al troll o mueran! Uhm... ¡el peaje "
"es... su vida! ¡Mueran o... uhm... mueran!"

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/03_Peril.cfg:174
msgid "Trolls? So far away from their mountains of the Northlands?"
msgstr "¿Trolls? ¿Tan lejos de sus montañas de las Tierras del Norte?"

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/03_Peril.cfg:179
msgid ""
"'Trolls'? So that's how your kin calls them? My people call them "
"'Stoneborn', because that's what they are; they are born here, they die "
"here. They've always inhabited these mountains."
msgstr ""
"¿«Trolls»? ¿Así los llama tu gente? Mi pueblo los llama «Hijos de la "
"Piedra», porque eso es lo que son; nacen aquí, mueren aquí. Siempre han "
"habitado estas montañas."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/03_Peril.cfg:184
msgid ""
"But this won't stop us from crushing through their lines, for whoever "
"hinders us from pursuing our duty has deserved nothing more than death "
"itself! To arms!"
msgstr ""
"Pero esto no nos detendrá de atravesar sus líneas, ¡porque quien nos impida "
"cumplir nuestro deber no merece nada más que la muerte misma! ¡A las armas!"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/03_Peril.cfg:193
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/03_Peril.cfg:371
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/03_Peril.cfg:465
msgid "Reach the signpost in the east with Dawoud or defeat all enemies"
msgstr ""
"Llega al poste de señalización del este con Dawoud o derrota a todos los "
"enemigos"

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/03_Peril.cfg:210
msgid ""
"We should not attack the stoneborn at night, men! Their blunt attacks may "
"easily break our bones; use fire and arrows to wear them down!"
msgstr ""
"¡No debemos atacar a los hijos de la piedra por la noche, hombres! Sus "
"ataques contundentes pueden romper nuestros huesos fácilmente; ¡usen fuego y "
"flechas para desgastarlos!"

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/03_Peril.cfg:220
msgid "Did Ibn Khazul ride through this mountain pass?"
msgstr "¿Ibn Khazul cruzó este paso de montaña?"

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/03_Peril.cfg:225
msgid ""
"There is a long way around the northern side of the mountains. But that way "
"would take too much time; they probably rode through this pass here."
msgstr ""
"Hay un camino largo rodeando el lado norte de las montañas. Pero ese camino "
"tomaría demasiado tiempo; probablemente cruzaron por este paso."

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/03_Peril.cfg:230
msgid "I see no signs of fighting."
msgstr "No veo señales de pelea."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/03_Peril.cfg:235
msgid ""
"You are right, then they paid the taxes. The Stoneborn must've hidden the "
"gold somewhere. Let us find it and return what is rightfully ours."
msgstr ""
"Tienes razón, entonces pagaron los impuestos. Los Hijos de la Piedra deben "
"haber escondido el oro en alguna parte. Encontremoslo y recuperemos lo que "
"es legítimamente nuestro."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/03_Peril.cfg:246
msgid "Hear that? The earth shakes! Galloping horses!"
msgstr "¿Oyen eso? ¡La tierra tiembla! ¡Caballos al galope!"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/03_Peril.cfg:255
msgid "At turn 8 elvish riders will appear at the marked field."
msgstr "En el turno 8 aparecerán jinetes elfos en el campo marcado."

#. [message], speaker=Narfi
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/03_Peril.cfg:289
msgid ""
"Ilriel! Finally we've found you! My name is Narfi, prince of the Southwoods. "
"How . . . how could you leave the Southwoods? You are our forest spirit! It "
"is too dangerous for you to leave the ones protecting you! You have to stay "
"with us!"
msgstr ""
"¡Ilriel! ¡Por fin te encontramos! Mi nombre es Narfi, príncipe de los "
"Bosques del Sur. ¿Cómo... cómo pudiste dejar los Bosques del Sur? ¡Eres "
"nuestro espíritu del bosque! ¡Es demasiado peligroso para ti dejar a quienes "
"te protegen! ¡Debes quedarte con nosotros!"

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/03_Peril.cfg:294
msgid "Narfi? Prince of the Southwoods? I . . . I . ."
msgstr "¿Narfi? ¿Príncipe de los Bosques del Sur? Yo... yo..."

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/03_Peril.cfg:299
msgid ""
"I've never heard about you or any prince. The Southwoods belong to Nuvdael "
"and to no one else."
msgstr ""
"Nunca había oído de ti ni de ningún príncipe. Los Bosques del Sur pertenecen "
"a Nuvdael y a nadie más."

#. [message], speaker=Narfi
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/03_Peril.cfg:304
msgid ""
"I AM the prince of the Southwoods! And we, you and I, are determined for "
"each other!"
msgstr ""
"¡YO SOY el príncipe de los Bosques del Sur! ¡Y nosotros, tú y yo, estamos "
"destinados el uno para el otro!"

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/03_Peril.cfg:309
msgid ""
"You're a liar and a self-proclaimed prince, Narfi, a snake, that's creeping "
"across the dirt and threw away every virtue of the elves."
msgstr ""
"Eres un mentiroso y un príncipe autoproclamado, Narfi, una serpiente que se "
"arrastra por la tierra y tiró por la borda toda virtud de los elfos."

#. [message], speaker=Narfi
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/03_Peril.cfg:314
msgid ""
". . . what? Did they brainwash you? I've gained the backing of my community, "
"rode days and days and moved heaven and earth to reach you. They have "
"poisoned your mind! I cannot return without taking you with me! It'd be a "
"disgrace . . . the Southwoods need you . . . and they sure need me!"
msgstr ""
"¿...qué? ¿Te lavaron el cerebro? Gané el respaldo de mi comunidad, cabalgué "
"días y días y moví cielo y tierra para alcanzarte. ¡Te han envenenado la "
"mente! ¡No puedo regresar sin llevarte conmigo! Sería una desgracia... ¡los "
"Bosques del Sur te necesitan... y a mí también!"

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/03_Peril.cfg:319
msgid ""
"Your intentions are as clear as the amber hearts of the woses, but you will "
"not take me as a leverage against the rightful reign of Nuvdael."
msgstr ""
"Tus intenciones son tan claras como los corazones de ámbar de los woses, "
"pero no me usarás como palanca contra el legítimo reinado de Nuvdael."

#. [message], speaker=Narfi
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/03_Peril.cfg:324
msgid ""
"Men! Ilriel betrayed her folk! She betrayed the elves and the ancient beings "
"inhabiting the Southwoods!"
msgstr ""
"¡Hombres! ¡Ilriel traicionó a su pueblo! ¡Traicionó a los elfos y a los "
"antiguos seres que habitan los Bosques del Sur!"

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/03_Peril.cfg:329
msgid "Don't listen to him, elves!"
msgstr "¡No lo escuchen, elfos!"

#. [message], speaker=Narfi
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/03_Peril.cfg:334
msgid ""
"They understand your betrayal very well, Ilriel! You've left behind the "
"woods whose heart you are! You are no longer one of us! Men! Capture her and "
"bring her back to our Southwoods!"
msgstr ""
"¡Entienden muy bien tu traición, Ilriel! ¡Has dejado atrás los bosques de "
"los que eres el corazón! ¡Ya no eres una de nosotros! ¡Hombres! ¡Captúrenla "
"y llévenla de vuelta a nuestros Bosques del Sur!"

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/03_Peril.cfg:339
msgid "They leave us no choice."
msgstr "No nos dejan otra opción."

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/03_Peril.cfg:344
msgid ""
"No! Do not harm them! Hasten away into the sands, their horses can't follow "
"us there. And once we've manage to escape, they'll return to the Southwoods "
"and Nuvdael shall be their judge."
msgstr ""
"¡No! ¡No les hagan daño! Apresúrense hacia las arenas, sus caballos no "
"podrán seguirnos allí. Y una vez que logremos escapar, regresarán a los "
"Bosques del Sur y Nuvdael será su juez."

#. [message], speaker=Rumms
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/03_Peril.cfg:349
msgid "You! Elves! Even more elves! Pay troll or die!"
msgstr "¡Ustedes! ¡Elfos! ¡Más elfos! ¡Paguen al troll o mueran!"

#. [message], speaker=Rumms
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/03_Peril.cfg:354
msgid "Uhhmmpff, much tax."
msgstr "Uhhmmpff, mucho impuesto."

#. [message], speaker=Narfi
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/03_Peril.cfg:359
msgid "Hold your tongue, troll!"
msgstr "¡Cállate la boca, troll!"

#. [message], speaker=Rumms
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/03_Peril.cfg:364
msgid "Rumms will turn you into elven-mush, tree-hugger!"
msgstr "¡Rumms te convertirá en puré de elfo, abrazador de árboles!"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/03_Peril.cfg:375
msgid "Optional: Kill Narfi"
msgstr "Opcional: Matar a Narfi"

#. [objective], condition=lose
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/03_Peril.cfg:379
msgid "An enemy elvish unit attacks Ilriel"
msgstr "Una unidad elfa enemiga ataca a Ilriel"

#. [note]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/03_Peril.cfg:385
msgid "Killing Narfi will grant you a bonus."
msgstr "Matar a Narfi te otorgará una bonificación."

#. [note]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/03_Peril.cfg:388
msgid "Ilriel is allowed to attack the elves, but not the other way around."
msgstr "Ilriel puede atacar a los elfos, pero no al revés."

#. [message], speaker=Narfi
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/03_Peril.cfg:405
msgid "Il . . . Ilriel. How. . . how could you . . ."
msgstr "Il... Ilriel. ¿Cómo... cómo pudiste...?"

#. [then]
#. [event]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/03_Peril.cfg:424
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/03_Peril.cfg:538
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/03_Peril.cfg:648
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/19_Above_the_Stars_and_below_Earth.cfg:337
msgid "Uthain"
msgstr "Uthain"

#. [message], speaker=Uthain
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/03_Peril.cfg:434
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/03_Peril.cfg:658
msgid "Hey, you! Don't forget about me, will ya?!"
msgstr "¡Hey, tú! ¡No te olvides de mí, ¿eh?!"

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/03_Peril.cfg:439
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/03_Peril.cfg:663
msgid "Huh, a dwarf? What are you doing in these far away lands, dwarf?"
msgstr "¿Eh, un enano? ¿Qué haces en estas tierras tan lejanas, enano?"

#. [message], speaker=Uthain
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/03_Peril.cfg:444
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/03_Peril.cfg:558
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/03_Peril.cfg:668
msgid ""
"I am an adventurer in search of the runes of the dwarvish forefathers. "
"Forsooth, their realm once spanned the continent! Unfortunately . . . the "
"trolls  forced me to retreat into this mine and I had no opportunity to "
"leave this place. I see you are approaching the great desert! Let me join "
"you, certainly I can find more relicts of the past of my kin! And . . . "
"maybe I'll lend you my hammer!"
msgstr ""
"Soy un aventurero en busca de las runas de los antepasados enanos. ¡En "
"verdad, su reino alguna vez abarcó el continente! Desafortunadamente... los "
"trolls me obligaron a refugiarme en esta mina y no tuve oportunidad de salir "
"de este lugar. ¡Veo que se acercan al gran desierto! Déjenme unirme a "
"ustedes, ¡seguro podré encontrar más reliquias del pasado de mi pueblo! Y... "
"¡tal vez les preste mi martillo!"

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/03_Peril.cfg:449
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/03_Peril.cfg:673
msgid "Uhh, we'd be happy about any support we can get. Join us!"
msgstr "Uhh, cualquier apoyo es bienvenido. ¡Únete a nosotros!"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/03_Peril.cfg:455
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/03_Peril.cfg:564
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/03_Peril.cfg:679
msgid ""
"Uthain is a hero unit and as such, he is able to unlock several abilities "
"and improvements through advancing. Hero units may not die, yet you can "
"decide whether or not you recall them. In certain scenarios, hero units are "
"automatically recalled to support the cause of Ilriel and Dawoud. Hero units "
"have an improved default AMLA, giving them +5hp and +1 damage."
msgstr ""
"Uthain es una unidad heroica y como tal puede desbloquear varias habilidades "
"y mejoras al avanzar. Las unidades heroicas no pueden morir, pero puedes "
"decidir si las reincorporas o no. En ciertos escenarios, las unidades "
"heroicas son reincorporadas automáticamente para apoyar la causa de Ilriel y "
"Dawoud. Las unidades heroicas tienen un AMLA predeterminado mejorado que les "
"otorga +5 PV y +1 de daño."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/03_Peril.cfg:483
msgid ""
"The elves are striking us at a time when we are most vulnerable and in need "
"to quickly leave these lands behind us. Did Nuvdael trick us and feeling "
"forsaken by your departure to force you back to the Southwoods?"
msgstr ""
"Los elfos nos atacan en un momento en que somos más vulnerables y "
"necesitamos dejar estas tierras rápidamente. ¿Nuvdael nos engañó y, "
"sintiéndose abandonado por tu partida, te obliga a volver a los Bosques del "
"Sur?"

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/03_Peril.cfg:488
msgid ""
"Nuvdael has the nature of a warrior and it's hard to argue with him. But he "
"has a pure heart and is a good and honest king who would never conspire "
"against the direct advice of his people, as he highly values them. The elves "
"who arrived here must be rebels. Rebels who seek for means to press Nuvdael, "
"in order to challenge him and his crown."
msgstr ""
"Nuvdael tiene naturaleza de guerrero y es difícil discutir con él. Pero "
"tiene un corazón puro y es un buen y honesto rey que nunca conspiraría "
"contra el consejo directo de su pueblo, ya que lo valora mucho. Los elfos "
"que llegaron aquí deben ser rebeldes. Rebeldes que buscan medios para "
"presionar a Nuvdael y desafiarlo a él y a su corona."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/03_Peril.cfg:493
msgid ""
"A king that sides with his people? I've only experienced a few of them in "
"the lands where I'm coming from."
msgstr ""
"¿Un rey que se pone del lado de su pueblo? Solo he conocido a unos pocos en "
"las tierras de donde vengo."

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/03_Peril.cfg:498
msgid ""
"In former times we were not led by a high king but by several sages, each "
"originating from a nearby forest. However, a century ago the Southwoods were "
"poisoned and cursed by a shadow inhabiting the black forests in the south of "
"our woods. He was one of the few who didn't accept the demise of our home "
"and thus he bravely led his troops against the forces of  darkness, fighting "
"them back and cleansing the Southwoods from them. It was in that time when "
"our sages recognized that wisdom and words alone can't always protect our "
"realms from danger, there will always come times calling for active and "
"practical response. That day Nuvdael was crowned high king."
msgstr ""
"En tiempos pasados no éramos liderados por un gran rey sino por varios "
"sabios, cada uno originario de un bosque cercano. Sin embargo, hace un siglo "
"los Bosques del Sur fueron envenenados y malditos por una sombra que "
"habitaba los bosques negros al sur de nuestros bosques. Él fue uno de los "
"pocos que no aceptó la caída de nuestro hogar y así valientemente lideró sus "
"tropas contra las fuerzas de la oscuridad, rechazándolas y limpiando los "
"Bosques del Sur de ellas. Fue en ese tiempo cuando nuestros sabios "
"reconocieron que la sabiduría y las palabras solas no siempre pueden "
"proteger nuestros reinos del peligro, siempre vendrán tiempos que exijan una "
"respuesta activa y práctica. Ese día Nuvdael fue coronado gran rey."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/03_Peril.cfg:510
msgid ""
"The Stoneborn is dead! May he return to the massif he once originated from."
msgstr ""
"¡El Hijo de la Piedra está muerto! Que regrese al macizo del que una vez "
"surgió."

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/03_Peril.cfg:534
msgid "An entrance to a mine! For sure this is a site of dwarves!"
msgstr "¡Una entrada a una mina! ¡Seguro es un sitio de enanos!"

#. [message], speaker=Uthain
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/03_Peril.cfg:548
msgid ""
"Aahhh! Elves? Here? I hoped I'd never have to see one of your kin again!"
msgstr ""
"¡Aahhh! ¿Elfos? ¿Aquí? ¡Esperaba no volver a ver a uno de los tuyos nunca "
"más!"

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/03_Peril.cfg:553
msgid "What are you doing in these far away lands, dwarf?"
msgstr "¿Qué haces en estas tierras tan lejanas, enano?"

#. [message], speaker=Uthain
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/03_Peril.cfg:584
msgid "You smelly blockhead!"
msgstr "¡Cabeza de bloque apestoso!"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/03_Peril.cfg:603
msgid "Pay Rumms, the troll, the toll\n"
msgstr "Paga a Rumms, el troll, el peaje\n"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/03_Peril.cfg:604
msgid "hint: toll is your life"
msgstr "pista: el peaje es tu vida"

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/03_Peril.cfg:619
msgid "You are coming with me to the Aethenwoods, Ilriel!"
msgstr "¡Vendrás conmigo a los Bosques de Edén, Ilriel!"

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/03_Peril.cfg:638
msgid ""
"Make haste! The Sandy Wastes lie ahead of us! In a few months we've reached "
"Serrul!"
msgstr ""
"¡Apresúrense! ¡Los Yermos Arenados están delante de nosotros! ¡En unos meses "
"habremos llegado a Serrul!"

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/03_Peril.cfg:698
msgid ""
"We have wasted too much time in the forsaken mountains, we'll never reach "
"Serrul in time!"
msgstr ""
"Hemos perdido demasiado tiempo en las montañas abandonadas, ¡nunca "
"llegaremos a Serrul a tiempo!"

#. [part]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/04_A_Whisper_in_the_Sands.cfg:7
msgid ""
"The group of Ilriel and Dawoud left behind the Mountains of Peril and "
"entered the desert realms. The deserts felt strange to Ilriel. In some way "
"they were just like the oceans, wave after wave of endless sands formed the "
"horizon, quickly devouring the ones who were not able to walk any further. "
"She had never seen something like that and, being in the deserts for some "
"days, Ilriel noticed that the desert plains were harsher than any place she "
"had ever visited. With grains of sand cutting her skin, she felt like the "
"desert itself tried to prevent them from reaching Serrul."
msgstr ""
"El grupo de Ilriel y Dawoud dejó atrás las Montañas del Peligro y entró en "
"los reinos del desierto. Los desiertos se sentían extraños para Ilriel. De "
"alguna manera eran como los océanos, ola tras ola de arenas infinitas "
"formaban el horizonte, devorando rápidamente a quienes no podían caminar "
"más. Nunca había visto algo así y, después de estar algunos días en los "
"desiertos, Ilriel notó que las llanuras desérticas eran más duras que "
"cualquier lugar que hubiera visitado. Con granos de arena cortándole la "
"piel, sentía como si el desierto mismo intentara impedirles llegar a Serrul."

#. [part]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/04_A_Whisper_in_the_Sands.cfg:11
msgid ""
"But does she have a choice? Her help is needed in these realms. The king of "
"a rich city fell victim to a strange disease. A warrior king that used to "
"fight back the hordes of the sand."
msgstr ""
"Pero ¿tiene elección? Su ayuda es necesaria en estos reinos. El rey de una "
"rica ciudad cayó víctima de una extraña enfermedad. Un rey guerrero que "
"solía rechazar las hordas de arena."

#. [part]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/04_A_Whisper_in_the_Sands.cfg:15
msgid ""
"However, the acorn of the great tree still fascinated Ilriel. How is it "
"possible that the fruits of the great trees were found in the desert realms? "
"She had to find out."
msgstr ""
"Sin embargo, la bellota del gran árbol aún fascinaba a Ilriel. ¿Cómo es "
"posible que los frutos de los grandes árboles se encontraran en los reinos "
"del desierto? Tenía que descubrirlo."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/04_A_Whisper_in_the_Sands.cfg:44
msgid "This stone looks strange . . . let me . . . touch it . . ."
msgstr "Esta piedra se ve extraña... déjame... tocarla..."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/04_A_Whisper_in_the_Sands.cfg:68
msgid "Whoa, it seems like this stone is emanating energy!"
msgstr "¡Whoa, parece que esta piedra está emanando energía!"

#. [scenario], id=04_A_Whisper_in_the_Sands
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/04_A_Whisper_in_the_Sands.cfg:141
msgid "A Whisper in the Sands"
msgstr "Un Susurro en las Arenas"

#. [side], type=Dune Firetrooper
#. [side], type=Dune Marauder
#. [side], type=Dune Wayfarer
#. [side]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/04_A_Whisper_in_the_Sands.cfg:190
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/04_A_Whisper_in_the_Sands.cfg:217
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/04_A_Whisper_in_the_Sands.cfg:245
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/12_Cloud_River.cfg:94
msgid "Bandits"
msgstr "Bandidos"

#. [side], type=Dune Firetrooper
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/04_A_Whisper_in_the_Sands.cfg:196
msgid "Mhassoud"
msgstr "Mhassoud"

#. [side], type=Dune Marauder
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/04_A_Whisper_in_the_Sands.cfg:223
msgid "Mawardi"
msgstr "Mawardi"

#. [side], type=Dune Wayfarer
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/04_A_Whisper_in_the_Sands.cfg:251
msgid "Siham"
msgstr "Siham"

#. [side]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/04_A_Whisper_in_the_Sands.cfg:273
msgid "Trading Post"
msgstr "Puesto Comercial"

#. [side]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/04_A_Whisper_in_the_Sands.cfg:303
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/17_The_Great_Wall.cfg:101
msgid "Inhabitants"
msgstr "Habitantes"

#. [event]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/04_A_Whisper_in_the_Sands.cfg:346
msgid "Irad"
msgstr "Irad"

#. [message]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/04_A_Whisper_in_the_Sands.cfg:393
msgid ""
"The bandits are growing stronger and stronger, we can not hold the trading "
"post any longer! You need to help us, travellers!"
msgstr ""
"¡Los bandidos se están volviendo cada vez más fuertes, ya no podemos "
"mantener el puesto comercial! ¡Necesitamos que nos ayuden, viajeros!"

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/04_A_Whisper_in_the_Sands.cfg:431
msgid "A red sun rises. Blood has been spilled this night."
msgstr "Un sol rojo se levanta. Sangre ha sido derramada esta noche."

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/04_A_Whisper_in_the_Sands.cfg:436
msgid "Then Ibn Khazul has reached Serrul."
msgstr "Entonces Ibn Khazul ha llegado a Serrul."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/04_A_Whisper_in_the_Sands.cfg:441
msgid ""
"Let us hope it ends well for him. There's still a two weeks' march before we "
"reach Serrul."
msgstr ""
"Esperemos que termine bien para él. Aún quedan dos semanas de marcha antes "
"de llegar a Serrul."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/04_A_Whisper_in_the_Sands.cfg:446
msgid ""
"We are close to a trading post. One of several in these plains that are used "
"by merchants to take shelter from bandits and the cold of the night. These "
"are guarded by veterans of Serrul. Since we've not encountered wandering "
"tradespeople we should invite the guards to join us. Their combat experience "
"will be of great use to us and to the Dune Warmaster of Serrul. We need any "
"help we can get as Uthman's forces are known to be ruthless."
msgstr ""
"Estamos cerca de un puesto comercial. Uno de varios en estas llanuras que "
"usan los mercaderes para refugiarse de bandidos y del frío de la noche. "
"Están custodiados por veteranos de Serrul. Como no hemos encontrado "
"comerciantes errantes, deberíamos invitar a los guardias a unirse a "
"nosotros. Su experiencia en combate nos será de gran utilidad a nosotros y "
"al Maestro de Guerra de Serrul. Necesitamos toda la ayuda posible, ya que "
"las fuerzas de Uthman son conocidas por ser despiadadas."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/04_A_Whisper_in_the_Sands.cfg:456
msgid ""
"Allied guards are protecting the fortification in the middle of the map. You "
"may rescue them by moving one of your ground units towards the trading post."
msgstr ""
"Guardias aliados protegen la fortificación en el centro del mapa. Puedes "
"rescatarlos moviendo una de tus unidades terrestres hacia el puesto "
"comercial."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/04_A_Whisper_in_the_Sands.cfg:462
msgid ""
"An exclamation mark hovers above the head of the general. Move a unit of "
"yours next to him in order to talk to him."
msgstr ""
"Un signo de exclamación flota sobre la cabeza del general. Mueve una de tus "
"unidades junto a él para hablarle."

#. [note]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/04_A_Whisper_in_the_Sands.cfg:475
msgid ""
"Allied guards are protecting the fortification in the middle of the map. You "
"may rescue them by moving one of your ground units next to the general. An "
"exclamation mark hovers above his head. Some of them will then join your "
"group."
msgstr ""
"Guardias aliados protegen la fortificación en el centro del mapa. Puedes "
"rescatarlos moviendo una de tus unidades terrestres junto al general. Un "
"signo de exclamación flota sobre su cabeza. Algunos se unirán entonces a tu "
"grupo."

#. [note]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/04_A_Whisper_in_the_Sands.cfg:478
msgid ""
"The allied guards won't leave their fortification unless you order them to."
msgstr ""
"Los guardias aliados no abandonarán su fortificación a menos que tú se lo "
"ordenes."

#. [event]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/04_A_Whisper_in_the_Sands.cfg:490
msgid "Piik"
msgstr "Piik"

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/04_A_Whisper_in_the_Sands.cfg:499
msgid "Falcons! The wings of the desert! For sure we are close to Serrul!"
msgstr "¡Halcones! ¡Las alas del desierto! ¡Seguro estamos cerca de Serrul!"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/04_A_Whisper_in_the_Sands.cfg:505
msgid ""
"Elder Falcons bear the telltale scars of veteran warriors from protecting "
"their masters, their bodies proof of repeated dives into a swirling melee. "
"Stronger and faster than their younger kin, they are rumored to hit with "
"enough force to remove an enemy's head. \n"
"\n"
"<i>Falcons can easily and rapidly maneuver across the map, making it easy "
"for its master to explore the map.</i>"
msgstr ""
"Los Halcones Ancianos llevan las cicatrices reveladoras de guerreros "
"veteranos por proteger a sus amos, sus cuerpos son prueba de repetidas "
"inmersiones en un combate caótico. Más fuertes y rápidos que sus parientes "
"jóvenes, se rumorea que golpean con suficiente fuerza como para arrancar la "
"cabeza de un enemigo.\n"
"\n"
"<i>Los halcones pueden maniobrar fácilmente y con rapidez por el mapa, "
"facilitando a su amo explorar el mapa.</i>"

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/04_A_Whisper_in_the_Sands.cfg:526
msgid ""
"Watch out, Scarab beetles! The desert is theirs and some even say that they "
"are the hidden rulers of the vastness. There are certainly more of those "
"beneath the sands! Take care, their horns can easily penetrate through the "
"thickest armours!"
msgstr ""
"¡Cuidado, escarabajos Scarab! El desierto es suyo y algunos incluso dicen "
"que son los gobernantes ocultos de la vastedad. ¡Seguro hay más debajo de "
"las arenas! Tengan cuidado, sus cuernos pueden penetrar fácilmente las "
"armaduras más gruesas."

#. [message], speaker=Uthain
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/04_A_Whisper_in_the_Sands.cfg:539
msgid ""
"Pah, lousy deserts! Even my former brothers in arms went to places far more "
"interesting than these deserts!"
msgstr ""
"¡Pah, desiertos miserables! ¡Incluso mis antiguos hermanos de armas fueron a "
"lugares mucho más interesantes que estos desiertos!"

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/04_A_Whisper_in_the_Sands.cfg:544
msgid ""
"Even places like this hold long forgotten secrets and treasures of old "
"times. It's just that the sands cover those up and make them invisible to "
"the eye of the unaware."
msgstr ""
"Incluso lugares como este guardan secretos olvidados y tesoros de tiempos "
"antiguos. Solo que las arenas los cubren y los hacen invisibles al ojo de "
"los desprevenidos."

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/04_A_Whisper_in_the_Sands.cfg:555
msgid "Ouch!"
msgstr "¡Ay!"

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/04_A_Whisper_in_the_Sands.cfg:560
msgid "Il- Ilriel?!"
msgstr "¡Il- Ilriel!"

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/04_A_Whisper_in_the_Sands.cfg:565
msgid ""
"I'm having bursts of pain . . . like somebody struck me . . . but it is not "
"me . . ."
msgstr ""
"Tengo ataques de dolor... como si alguien me hubiera golpeado... pero no soy "
"yo..."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/04_A_Whisper_in_the_Sands.cfg:570
msgid ""
"That must be your inner connection with the woses of Serrul. It is stronger "
"than I expected."
msgstr ""
"Debe ser tu conexión interna con los woses de Serrul. Es más fuerte de lo "
"que esperaba."

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/04_A_Whisper_in_the_Sands.cfg:575
msgid "Woses? Inside these desert realms? That is impossible."
msgstr "¿Woses? ¿Dentro de estos reinos desérticos? Eso es imposible."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/04_A_Whisper_in_the_Sands.cfg:580
msgid ""
"Nothing is what it seems in these realms. We'd better hurry, though, so that "
"we have a possibility to ease your pain."
msgstr ""
"Nada es lo que parece en estos reinos. Mejor apurémonos, para tener alguna "
"posibilidad de aliviar tu dolor."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/04_A_Whisper_in_the_Sands.cfg:598
msgid "Serrul: southeast"
msgstr "Serrul: sureste"

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/04_A_Whisper_in_the_Sands.cfg:626
msgid ""
"We've banned the bandits from this desert; let us sally forth, a sandstorm "
"is approaching."
msgstr ""
"Hemos expulsado a los bandidos de este desierto; avancemos, se acerca una "
"tormenta de arena."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/04_A_Whisper_in_the_Sands.cfg:636
msgid ""
"Our forces are exhausted from this endless fight, we can't go on anymore..."
msgstr ""
"Nuestras fuerzas están exhaustas de esta pelea interminable, ya no podemos "
"continuar..."

#. [part]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/05_Six_Feet_Under.cfg:7
msgid ""
"After leaving behind the trading outpost, the sandstorms became harsher and "
"harsher. Sand dunes were quickly formed and, at the same pace, they were "
"erased from the surface. The whole desert realms felt like a giant labyrinth "
"with moving walls. Little did they know that it was not the wind that formed "
"these dunes . . "
msgstr ""
"Después de dejar atrás el puesto comercial, las tormentas de arena se "
"volvieron más y más fuertes. Las dunas se formaban rápidamente y, al mismo "
"ritmo, eran borradas de la superficie. Todos los reinos desérticos se "
"sentían como un laberinto gigante con paredes móviles. Poco sabían que no "
"era el viento lo que formaba esas dunas..."

#. [scenario], id=05_Six_Feet_Under
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/05_Six_Feet_Under.cfg:18
msgid "Six Feet Under"
msgstr "A Dos Metros Bajo Tierra"

#. [side]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/05_Six_Feet_Under.cfg:63
msgid "Dune Worms"
msgstr "Gusanos del Desierto"

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/05_Six_Feet_Under.cfg:97
msgid ""
"This sandstorm is stronger than every other Ive experienced. I am not even "
"able to see the hand in front of my face. I hope it ends soon, otherwise we "
"won't reach . . ."
msgstr ""
"Esta tormenta de arena es más fuerte que todas las que he vivido. Ni "
"siquiera puedo ver la mano frente a mi cara. Espero que termine pronto, de "
"lo contrario no llegaremos..."

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/05_Six_Feet_Under.cfg:104
msgid "Wait? Wh. . . what was that?"
msgstr "¿Esperen? ¿Qué... qué fue eso?"

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/05_Six_Feet_Under.cfg:111
msgid "Kar'rhur-Hai!"
msgstr "¡Kar'rhur-Hai!"

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/05_Six_Feet_Under.cfg:116
msgid "Men! To arms! Stand close to each other!"
msgstr "¡Hombres! ¡A las armas! ¡Manténganse juntos!"

#. [message]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/05_Six_Feet_Under.cfg:156
msgid "Zzzzzzzzzziiiishhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhh!!!!"
msgstr "Zzzzzzzzzziiiishhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhh!!!!"

#. [message], speaker=Uthain
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/05_Six_Feet_Under.cfg:169
msgid ""
"Aharrrarrr! Dirty worms! Those beasts are <i>huuuuuuuuge</i>! One tooth of "
"them is as big as a troll, one scale as big as an . . . armour. Right! "
"Finally I can make use of my excellent arts! That suits me better than this "
"mindless slaughter, which reminds me of the eternal war between my brothers "
"and the trolls of the dark caverns of the mountains. Let me finish one of "
"them and I'll hammer you nice armour out of their scales!"
msgstr ""
"¡Aharrrarrr! ¡Gusanos sucios! ¡Esas bestias son <i>enooooormes</i>! Uno de "
"sus dientes es tan grande como un troll, una escama tan grande como una... "
"armadura. ¡Bien! ¡Por fin puedo usar mis excelentes artes! Esto me conviene "
"más que esta matanza sin sentido, que me recuerda la guerra eterna entre mis "
"hermanos y los trolls de las cavernas oscuras de las montañas. ¡Déjenme "
"terminar uno y les martillaré una buena armadura con sus escamas!"

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/05_Six_Feet_Under.cfg:174
msgid "To win this fight, we need every tough man, dwarf."
msgstr "Para ganar esta pelea necesitamos a todos los hombres fuertes, enano."

#. [message], speaker=Uthain
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/05_Six_Feet_Under.cfg:179
msgid "Harhar, sure, eh?"
msgstr "Jajaja, claro, ¿eh?"

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/05_Six_Feet_Under.cfg:184
msgid ""
"Fight them back! Stand afar and let our naphta fire burn through their "
"scales! Protect Ilriel at all costs!"
msgstr ""
"¡Rechácenlos! ¡Manténganse a distancia y dejen que nuestro fuego de nafta "
"queme sus escamas! ¡Protejan a Ilriel a toda costa!"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/05_Six_Feet_Under.cfg:192
msgid "Survive until the end of turns"
msgstr "Sobrevive hasta el final de los turnos"

#. [note]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/05_Six_Feet_Under.cfg:198
msgid ""
"Duneworms are susceptible to fire. Use your Dune Burners to fight them back."
msgstr ""
"Los gusanos del desierto son susceptibles al fuego. Usa tus Incendiarios "
"para rechazarlos."

#. [message], speaker=Uthain
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/05_Six_Feet_Under.cfg:219
msgid ""
"These are the scales I need to make a nice armour for you, Dawoud! Give me "
"some time!"
msgstr ""
"¡Estas son las escamas que necesito para hacerte una buena armadura, Dawoud! "
"¡Dame algo de tiempo!"

#. [message], speaker=Uthain
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/05_Six_Feet_Under.cfg:224
msgid "Harhar! It is amazing! Here it is, I hope you like it!"
msgstr "¡Jajaja! ¡Es increíble! ¡Aquí está, espero que te guste!"

#. [object]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/05_Six_Feet_Under.cfg:228
msgid "Scales of a duneworm"
msgstr "Escamas de gusano del desierto"

#. [object]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/05_Six_Feet_Under.cfg:230
msgid ""
"Scales of a duneworm have been forged into an armour. They grant +10 "
"hitpoints."
msgstr ""
"Las escamas de un gusano del desierto han sido forjadas en una armadura. "
"Otorgan +10 puntos de vida."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/05_Six_Feet_Under.cfg:254
msgid ""
"Even more Kar'rhur-Hai are arising from the sands! Stand close to each other "
"and stay strong!"
msgstr ""
"¡Aún más Kar'rhur-Hai surgen de las arenas! ¡Manténganse juntos y fuertes!"

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/05_Six_Feet_Under.cfg:264
msgid "It seems that you know these creatures, dwarf."
msgstr "Parece que conoces a estas criaturas, enano."

#. [message], speaker=Uthain
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/05_Six_Feet_Under.cfg:269
msgid ""
"Gah! Worms! Dune Worms! Some of us call them Earth Eaters, because of the "
"way they live. They create huge systems of tunnels in the sands underneath "
"our feet. Some dwarvish merchants from the north are known to use those "
"routes to trade with the people of the southern deserts. Sometimes, dwarvish "
"merchants disappear, which is a huge loss to our community. Once, my cousin "
"Dumbledin marched through the tunnels underneath, when he approached a "
"strange looking tunnel, that had not been there before. He went inside. "
"Unfortunately, that tunnel was the mouth opening of a giant duneworm! My "
"cousin went right into the stomach of the worm, where he got slowly "
"dissolved in the acid, that is even strong enough to dissolve stone! "
"Well . . . fortunately he left behind some really valuable artifacts. Too "
"bad . . . for him."
msgstr ""
"¡Gah! ¡Gusanos! ¡Gusanos del Desierto! Algunos los llamamos Devoradores de "
"Tierra por la forma en que viven. Crean enormes sistemas de túneles en las "
"arenas bajo nuestros pies. Algunos mercaderes enanos del norte usan esas "
"rutas para comerciar con la gente de los desiertos del sur. A veces los "
"mercaderes enanos desaparecen, lo que es una gran pérdida para nuestra "
"comunidad. Una vez mi primo Dumbledin marchó por los túneles de abajo, "
"cuando se acercó a un túnel de aspecto extraño que no estaba antes. Entró. "
"Desafortunadamente, ese túnel era la boca de un enorme gusano del desierto. "
"Mi primo entró directo al estómago del gusano, donde se disolvió lentamente "
"en el ácido, que es lo suficientemente fuerte como para disolver piedra. "
"Bueno... afortunadamente dejó atrás algunos artefactos muy valiosos. Qué "
"lástima... para él."

#. [message], speaker=Uthain
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/05_Six_Feet_Under.cfg:274
msgid ""
"And some dwarvish hags sometimes cook the meat of those worms. It doesn't "
"taste well, but those self-proclaimed cooks do not care too much about it."
msgstr ""
"Y algunas brujas enanas a veces cocinan la carne de esos gusanos. No sabe "
"bien, pero a esas autoproclamadas cocineras no les importa mucho."

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/05_Six_Feet_Under.cfg:292
msgid ""
"Apparently we stepped right on a nest of those dune worms! We should flee!"
msgstr ""
"¡Al parecer pisamos justo un nido de esos gusanos del desierto! ¡Deberíamos "
"huir!"

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/05_Six_Feet_Under.cfg:297
msgid ""
"They move as quickly through the sands as a bird through the skies. We can't "
"escape them. Once the soil is plastered with their remains, they will be the "
"ones running away. Hold on!"
msgstr ""
"Se mueven tan rápido a través de las arenas como un pájaro por los cielos. "
"No podemos escapar de ellos. Una vez que el suelo esté cubierto con sus "
"restos, serán ellos los que huyan. ¡Resistan!"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/05_Six_Feet_Under.cfg:313
msgid "Suddenly the earth below the feet of the group started to crumble."
msgstr "De repente la tierra bajo los pies del grupo comenzó a desmoronarse."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/05_Six_Feet_Under.cfg:357
msgid "A . . . a dragon! Dead! It's dead! Run!"
msgstr "¡Un... un dragón! ¡Muerto! ¡Está muerto! ¡Corran!"

#. [message], speaker=Ulruthir
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/05_Six_Feet_Under.cfg:369
msgid ""
"The magic . . . destined to bound . . . destined to destroy . . . will my "
"thralldom ever end?"
msgstr ""
"La magia... destinada a atar... destinada a destruir... ¿alguna vez "
"terminará mi esclavitud?"

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/05_Six_Feet_Under.cfg:399
msgid ""
"The Kar'rhur-Hai are disappearing! It seems like they have had enough of our "
"steel."
msgstr ""
"¡Los Kar'rhur-Hai están desapareciendo! Parece que ya tuvieron suficiente de "
"nuestro acero."

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/05_Six_Feet_Under.cfg:404
msgid "I've never seen creatures that huge."
msgstr "Nunca había visto criaturas tan enormes."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/05_Six_Feet_Under.cfg:409
msgid ""
"And I've never seen them in these sandy wastes. Their home is the vast "
"ashland desert to the south of this place."
msgstr ""
"Y nunca los había visto en estos yermos arenosos. Su hogar es el vasto "
"desierto de ceniza al sur de este lugar."

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/05_Six_Feet_Under.cfg:414
msgid "So something has driven those mighty creatures out of their habitat."
msgstr "Entonces algo ha expulsado a esas poderosas criaturas de su hábitat."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/05_Six_Feet_Under.cfg:419
msgid ""
"I am afraid we will find out soon enough what did this. Yet we have to march "
"on to Serrul now, Uthman's forces don't wait for us, neither does the "
"illness that is slowly harming the Dune Warmaster. Let us sally forth!"
msgstr ""
"Me temo que descubriremos pronto qué hizo esto. Pero ahora debemos marchar "
"hacia Serrul, las fuerzas de Uthman no nos esperan, ni tampoco la enfermedad "
"que lentamente daña al Maestro de Guerra. ¡Avancemos!"

#. [part]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:7
msgid ""
"After a long march, the group finally reached a grand city, a gate from the "
"deserts of the sandy wastes to the endless oceans."
msgstr ""
"Después de una larga marcha, el grupo finalmente llegó a una gran ciudad, "
"una puerta de los desiertos de los yermos arenosos hacia los océanos "
"infinitos."

#. [scenario], id=06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:18
msgid "The Pearl of the Desert"
msgstr "La Perla del Desierto"

#. [side], type=Ridwan
#. [else]
#. [event]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:63
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:69
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/16_Return_to_Tharwya.cfg:151
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/17_The_Great_Wall.cfg:365
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/19_Above_the_Stars_and_below_Earth.cfg:333
msgid "Ridwan"
msgstr "Ridwan"

#. [side], type=Wyvern Rider
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:95
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:101
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/07_Face_to_Face_with_the_Snake.cfg:93
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/07_Face_to_Face_with_the_Snake.cfg:99
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/21_Battle_of_the_Eons.cfg:58
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/21_Battle_of_the_Eons.cfg:63
msgid "Uthman"
msgstr "Uthman"

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:239
msgid ""
"Ah! Serrul, the Pearl of the Desert. I've missed this place that became my "
"new home."
msgstr ""
"¡Ah! Serrul, la Perla del Desierto. Extrañaba este lugar que se convirtió en "
"mi nuevo hogar."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:250
msgid "Yet smoke arises from the city, it has already been attacked!"
msgstr "Sin embargo, sale humo de la ciudad, ¡ya ha sido atacada!"

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:255
msgid ""
"And their attack has not been successful! Look there! Ibn Khazul is here!"
msgstr "¡Y su ataque no tuvo éxito! ¡Miren allá! ¡Ibn Khazul está aquí!"

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:266
msgid ""
"He certainly defended the city! But that was just the vanguard, Uthman's "
"army approaches on the horizon!"
msgstr ""
"¡Seguro defendió la ciudad! Pero eso fue solo la vanguardia, ¡el ejército de "
"Uthman se acerca en el horizonte!"

#. [message], speaker=Uthman
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:273
msgid ""
"Ridwan, your mind is weak, your bones fragile, your soul broken. You can't "
"reign over the Pearl. Serrul is mine! It belongs to me, I claim it!"
msgstr ""
"Ridwan, tu mente es débil, tus huesos frágiles, tu alma rota. No puedes "
"reinar sobre la Perla. ¡Serrul es mía! ¡Me pertenece, la reclamo!"

#. [message], speaker=Ridwan
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:279
msgid "Uthman . . . you . . . you will . . . never . . ."
msgstr "Uthman... tú... tú nunca..."

#. [message], speaker=Uthman
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:286
msgid "Silence!"
msgstr "¡Silencio!"

#. [message], speaker=Ridwan
#. [message], speaker=Uthman
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:292
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:515
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/07_Face_to_Face_with_the_Snake.cfg:432
msgid "Aaaaaahhhhh!"
msgstr "¡Aaaaaahhhhh!"

#. [message], speaker=Uthman
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:297
msgid ""
"Your howling is nothing more than music in my ears. You will bow down to "
"Kesh, Ridwan. And your people will serve as my slaves. Serrul will finally "
"pay for its folly so many years ago."
msgstr ""
"Tus aullidos no son más que música para mis oídos. Te arrodillarás ante "
"Kesh, Ridwan. Y tu pueblo servirá como mis esclavos. Serrul finalmente "
"pagará por su locura de hace tantos años."

#. [message], speaker=Uthman
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:302
msgid "So, whom do you cede Serrul to, Ridwan?"
msgstr "Entonces, ¿a quién cedes Serrul, Ridwan?"

#. [message], speaker=Ridwan
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:308
msgid "I . . . I . . . cede . . . Serrul . . . to . . ."
msgstr "Yo... yo... cedo... Serrul... a..."

#. [message], speaker=Ibn Khazul
#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:313
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/22_Timeless.cfg:230
msgid "No!"
msgstr "¡No!"

#. [message], speaker=Ibn Khazul
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:320
msgid ""
"Ridwan! Clear your mind! The soldiers will lose their hope if the Dune "
"Warmaster surrenders himself. You have to stay strong and withstand the "
"snake!"
msgstr ""
"¡Ridwan! ¡Limpia tu mente! Los soldados perderán la esperanza si el Maestro "
"de Guerra se rinde. ¡Debes permanecer fuerte y resistir a la serpiente!"

#. [message], speaker=Uthman
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:325
msgid "You cede Serrul to whom, Ridwan?"
msgstr "¿A quién cedes Serrul, Ridwan?"

#. [message], speaker=Ridwan
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:331
msgid ". . . you . . . Uthman . . ."
msgstr "... tú... Uthman..."

#. [message], speaker=Uthman
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:336
msgid ""
"Hahaha! You are right, Ridwan! The Pearl of the Desert is mine! Your blood "
"will run down the stairs of your palace nonetheless!"
msgstr ""
"¡Jajajaja! ¡Tienes razón, Ridwan! ¡La Perla del Desierto es mía! ¡Tu sangre "
"correrá por las escaleras de tu palacio de todos modos!"

#. [message], speaker=Ibn Khazul
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:341
msgid ""
"Pah! This is not the end! That's not how it will end! Serrul shall not fall! "
"Men! In formation! We are bound to protect the citizens of Serrul, to "
"protect the Dune Warmaster of Serrul against whatever arises on the horizon!"
msgstr ""
"¡Pah! ¡Esto no es el final! ¡Así no terminará! ¡Serrul no caerá! ¡Hombres! "
"¡En formación! ¡Estamos obligados a proteger a los ciudadanos de Serrul, a "
"proteger al Maestro de Guerra de Serrul contra lo que sea que surja en el "
"horizonte!"

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:349
msgid "You are not alone, Ibn Khazul!"
msgstr "¡No estás solo, Ibn Khazul!"

#. [message], speaker=Ibn Khazul
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:354
msgid ""
"Dawoud! You finally arrived! Then not all hope is lost! Bring Ilriel to "
"Ridwan and, with his mind cured from the poison, we may have a chance to "
"save Serrul!"
msgstr ""
"¡Dawoud! ¡Por fin llegaste! ¡Entonces no toda la esperanza está perdida! "
"¡Lleva a Ilriel con Ridwan y, con su mente curada del veneno, tal vez "
"tengamos una oportunidad de salvar Serrul!"

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:359
msgid "Come with me, Ilriel."
msgstr "Ven conmigo, Ilriel."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:367
msgid "We rely on your magic. Now it is time to cast the spell."
msgstr "Confiamos en tu magia. Ahora es momento de lanzar el hechizo."

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:373
msgid "In the name of the Southwoods!"
msgstr "¡En nombre de los Bosques del Sur!"

#. [message], speaker=Ridwan
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:381
msgid "Ahhahahaa!"
msgstr "¡Ahhahahaa!"

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#. [message], speaker=Uzar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:387
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:798
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:926
msgid "Huh?"
msgstr "¿Eh?"

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:394
msgid "What is happening?"
msgstr "¿Qué está pasando?"

#. [message], speaker=Ridwan
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:400
msgid ""
"You . . . you have no might here! Your era comes to an end, Dawoud! You and "
"your forsaken kin!"
msgstr ""
"¡Tú... tú no tienes poder aquí! ¡Tu era llega a su fin, Dawoud! ¡Tú y tu "
"maldito linaje!"

#. [message], speaker=Ibn Khazul
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:405
msgid "He is out of his mind! Someone is speaking through him."
msgstr "¡Está fuera de sí! Alguien está hablando a través de él."

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:410
msgid "This . . . this is no disease! A curse has been laid upon him!"
msgstr ""
"¡Esto... esto no es una enfermedad! ¡Una maldición ha sido puesta sobre él!"

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:415
msgid ""
"Then it is worse than I expected. He is spewing the poison from his mind. "
"What do you need in order to break the spell, Ilriel?"
msgstr ""
"Entonces es peor de lo que esperaba. Está escupiendo el veneno de su mente. "
"¿Qué necesitas para romper el hechizo, Ilriel?"

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:420
msgid ""
"Time . . . and calmness. The spell to break a curse is one of the highest "
"forms of magic; it needs a lot of commitment to cast. It must not be "
"interrupted."
msgstr ""
"Tiempo... y calma. El hechizo para romper una maldición es una de las formas "
"más altas de magia; requiere mucha dedicación para lanzarlo. No debe ser "
"interrumpido."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:425
msgid "We shall gift you calmness, then."
msgstr "Entonces te regalaremos calma."

#. [message], speaker=Ibn Khazul
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:432
msgid "Hold on!"
msgstr "¡Espera!"

#. [message], speaker=Ibn Khazul
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:437
msgid ""
"A spell? Dawoud, are you sure this is the right decision? It is said the "
"Athvari sense the flames of high magic . . . You know the legends, Dawoud."
msgstr ""
"¿Un hechizo? Dawoud, ¿estás seguro de que es la decisión correcta? Dicen que "
"los athvari sienten las llamas de la alta magia... Conoces las leyendas, "
"Dawoud."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:442
msgid ""
"What may be worse than the death of the Dune Warmaster of Serrul in these "
"times of war and intrigues? The Athvari would understand this case. And for "
"sure they will. Trust me."
msgstr ""
"¿Qué puede ser peor que la muerte del Maestro de Guerra de Serrul en estos "
"tiempos de guerra e intrigas? Los athvari entenderían este caso. Y seguro "
"que lo harán. Confía en mí."

#. [message], speaker=Ibn Khazul
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:447
msgid "I hope you'll be right, Dawoud."
msgstr "Espero que tengas razón, Dawoud."

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:452
msgid "The Athvari?"
msgstr "¿Los athvari?"

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:457
msgid ""
"Nothing more than legends. You are safe, Ilriel. Cast your spell, we shall "
"protect you."
msgstr ""
"Nada más que leyendas. Estás a salvo, Ilriel. Lanza tu hechizo, te "
"protegeremos."

#. [event]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:460
msgid "Yagrasyl"
msgstr "Yagrasyl"

#. [message], speaker=Yagrasyl
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:469
msgid "And so will we."
msgstr "Y nosotros también."

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:474
msgid "Woses!"
msgstr "¡Woses!"

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:479
msgid "We did not lie."
msgstr "No mentimos."

#. [message], speaker=Yagrasyl
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:484
msgid ""
"The keepers of the grove shall lend their roots and barks to destroy your "
"enemies and protect your life. Their maces and pikes can't harm us, yet "
"their magic can. Let the creatures of the grove bolster you up and "
"contribute to the victory against the forces of the sands. It is an honour "
"to see you again, Ilriel."
msgstr ""
"Los guardianes de la arboleda prestarán sus raíces y cortezas para destruir "
"a tus enemigos y proteger tu vida. Sus mazas y picas no pueden dañarnos, "
"pero su magia sí. Deja que las criaturas de la arboleda te fortalezcan y "
"contribuyan a la victoria contra las fuerzas de las arenas. Es un honor "
"verte de nuevo, Ilriel."

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:489
msgid "How . . . how is this even possible?"
msgstr "¿Cómo... cómo es esto posible?"

#. [message], speaker=Yagrasyl
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:495
msgid ""
"War doesn't allow for words, it demands deeds. Cast the spell and we shall "
"share our stories after we've fought back the legions."
msgstr ""
"La guerra no permite palabras, exige acciones. Lanza el hechizo y "
"compartiremos nuestras historias después de haber rechazado las legiones."

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:500
msgid "By the forefathers of the forests! "
msgstr "¡Por los antepasados de los bosques! "

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:520
msgid ""
"Men of Serrul! Protectors of the Pearl of the Desert! Fight back the hordes "
"of the snake and protect Ilriel from both steel and arrow at all costs! "
"Swords high!"
msgstr ""
"¡Hombres de Serrul! ¡Protectores de la Perla del Desierto! ¡Rechacen las "
"hordas de la serpiente y protejan a Ilriel del acero y las flechas a toda "
"costa! ¡Espadas en alto!"

#. [message], speaker=Ibn Khazul
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:525
msgid ""
"Good to see you back, Dawoud! Let us destroy them and protect the one that "
"once protected us! In times of danger, Ridwan always stood by our side! Not "
"behind us, not covering behind riders and shields, behind steel and chains, "
"but he stood at our side, inspired us to fight the best we can and avert the "
"dangers that threatened us. So let us do as he taught us! Today, we are "
"Serrulians! Today, we stand united! Today, the blood of the snake shall turn "
"the sandy oceans red! Into battle!"
msgstr ""
"¡Qué bueno verte de vuelta, Dawoud! ¡Destruyámoslos y protejamos a quien una "
"vez nos protegió! En tiempos de peligro, ¡Ridwan siempre estuvo a nuestro "
"lado! No detrás de nosotros, no cubriéndose detrás de jinetes y escudos, "
"detrás de acero y cadenas, sino a nuestro lado, inspirándonos a luchar lo "
"mejor posible y alejar los peligros que nos amenazaban. ¡Hagamos entonces lo "
"que él nos enseñó! ¡Hoy somos serrulianos! ¡Hoy nos mantenemos unidos! ¡Hoy "
"la sangre de la serpiente teñirá de rojo los océanos de arena! ¡A la batalla!"

#. [object]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:542
msgid ""
"\n"
"The Dune Rider are the only horsemen. Use their superior speed and agility "
"to circle and harass their foes."
msgstr ""
"\n"
"Los Jinetes Barjanes son los únicos jinetes. Usa su velocidad y agilidad "
"superiores para rodear y hostigar a sus enemigos."

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:552
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/07_Face_to_Face_with_the_Snake.cfg:318
msgid "Defeat Uthman, the Dune Warmaster of Kesh"
msgstr "Derrota a Uthman, el Maestro de Guerra de Kesh"

#. [objective], condition=lose
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:556
msgid "Ilriel is attacked by the forces of Kesh"
msgstr "Ilriel es atacada por las fuerzas de Kesh"

#. [note]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:562
msgid "You can now recruit and Dune Rider"
msgstr "Ahora puedes reclutar Jinetes Barjanes"

#. [note]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:565
msgid "Ibn Khazul will leave your troops after the scenario."
msgstr "Ibn Khazul abandonará tus tropas después del escenario."

#. [note]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:568
msgid ""
"The Dune Greatlance will leave their position and attack enemies, once they "
"are near."
msgstr ""
"Los Grandes Alabarderos Barjanes abandonarán su posición y atacarán a los "
"enemigos una vez que estén cerca."

#. [message], speaker=Uthain
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:586
msgid ""
"Duneworms, wyverns, wild savages! This all reminds of my poor cousin, that "
"old stonehead. He was even more stubborn than I am, can you imagine that? He "
"ended up in between hundreds of trolls and he for sure got a good beating "
"there, just for the sake of sniffing some ancient items. Such a fool!"
msgstr ""
"¡Gusanos del desierto, guivernos, salvajes! Todo esto me recuerda a mi pobre "
"primo, ese viejo cabeza de piedra. Era aún más terco que yo, ¿puedes "
"imaginarlo? Terminó en medio de cientos de trolls y seguro recibió una buena "
"paliza allí, solo por olfatear algunos objetos antiguos. ¡Qué idiota!"

#. [message], speaker=Ibn Khazul
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:591
msgid ""
"That's ironic, small man. Look at all the stuff you're wearing, a hammer "
"with an eagle's head, a crown of shining diamonds, boots that seem to carry "
"you across all sorts of terrain with ease. Those certainly have not been "
"crafted these days."
msgstr ""
"Qué irónico, hombrecito. Mira todas las cosas que llevas, un martillo con "
"cabeza de águila, una corona de diamantes brillantes, botas que parecen "
"llevarte con facilidad por todo tipo de terreno. Seguro que no fueron "
"fabricadas en estos días."

#. [message], speaker=Uthain
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:596
msgid ""
"My quest bears its fruits in this crazy world. And I've paid a high price "
"for those, a price not measurable by gold coins."
msgstr ""
"Mi búsqueda da sus frutos en este mundo loco. Y he pagado un alto precio por "
"ellos, un precio que no se mide con monedas de oro."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:627
msgid "You are not healing anyone here, elf."
msgstr "No estás sanando a nadie aquí, elfa."

#. [message], speaker=Ibn Khazul
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:640
msgid ""
"Dawoud! Let the enemy army shatter at the walls of Serrul! There is no need "
"to fight them in open terrain!"
msgstr ""
"¡Dawoud! ¡Deja que el ejército enemigo se estrelle contra las murallas de "
"Serrul! ¡No hay necesidad de luchar contra ellos en terreno abierto!"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:661
msgid ""
"You can hear noises from the inside of the tent, yet you cannot see the "
"merchant himself."
msgstr ""
"Puedes oír ruidos desde el interior de la tienda, pero no puedes ver al "
"mercader mismo."

#. [message], speaker=Uthain
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:666
msgid ""
"Arrh! Merchant! Do ye sell hammers? I need one! A mighty hammer! I need the "
"best you can offer!"
msgstr ""
"¡Arrh! ¡Mercader! ¿Vendes martillos? ¡Necesito uno! ¡Un martillo poderoso! "
"¡Necesito lo mejor que puedas ofrecer!"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:672
msgid "How much are you able to spend?"
msgstr "¿Cuánto puedes gastar?"

#. [message], speaker=Uthain
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:677
msgid "10 gold coins!!"
msgstr "¡10 monedas de oro!"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:683
msgid ""
"By the beard of Thursagan! An avaricious dwarf! Finally like-minded people!"
msgstr ""
"¡Por la barba de Thursagan! ¡Un enano avaro! ¡Por fin gente con ideas afines!"

#. [event]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:686
msgid "Glondolin"
msgstr "Glondolin"

#. [message], speaker=Uthain
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:690
msgid "By the beard of my hammer! Another dwarf!"
msgstr "¡Por la barba de mi martillo! ¡Otro enano!"

#. [message], speaker=Glondolin
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:695
msgid "Just another dwarf? Ha! I'm your cousin, Uthain!"
msgstr "¿Solo otro enano? ¡Ja! ¡Soy tu primo, Uthain!"

#. [message], speaker=Uthain
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:700
msgid ""
"By the beard of my beard! How is this possible? I thought you landed in the "
"cooking pot of a troll family!"
msgstr ""
"¡Por la barba de mi barba! ¿Cómo es posible? ¡Pensé que habías terminado en "
"la olla de una familia de trolls!"

#. [message], speaker=Glondolin
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:705
msgid ""
"Do not be a fool, Uthain! I found valuable jewels in these caves! "
"Unfortunately, nobody was interested in it . . . except these desert men. "
"They paid a good price and we established a nice trade. Just take a look at "
"this thunderstick and this shiny thing here and that blinky thing there. Did "
"I already show you my thunderstick?"
msgstr ""
"¡No seas tonto, Uthain! ¡Encontré joyas valiosas en estas cuevas! "
"Desafortunadamente, nadie estaba interesado... excepto estos hombres del "
"desierto. Pagaron un buen precio y establecimos un buen comercio. Solo mira "
"este bastón de trueno y esta cosa brillante aquí y esa cosa parpadeante "
"allá. ¿Ya te mostré mi bastón de trueno?"

#. [message], speaker=Uthain
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:710
msgid "By the beard of the thunderstick! You are a genius, Glondolin!"
msgstr "¡Por la barba del bastón de trueno! ¡Eres un genio, Glondolin!"

#. [message], speaker=Glondolin
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:715
msgid ""
"Forsooth, I am! And now let us fight back Uthman! He is endangering my trade "
"network!"
msgstr ""
"¡Por supuesto que lo soy! ¡Y ahora luchemos contra Uthman! ¡Está poniendo en "
"peligro mi red comercial!"

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:732
msgid "Mm . . . master . . ."
msgstr "Mm... amo..."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:750
msgid "Serrul: a weeks march to the south\n"
msgstr "Serrul: una jornada de marcha al sur\n"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:751
msgid "Kesh: eight weeks marches to the east"
msgstr "Kesh: ocho jornadas de marcha al este"

#. [message], speaker=Uthman
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:763
msgid "This . . . is not . . . the . . .  end! Ha- . . . ha- . . . haaa!"
msgstr "¡Esto... no es... el... final! ¡Ja-... ja-... jaaa!"

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:784
msgid "The spineless snake fled! Heavily wounded."
msgstr "¡La serpiente sin espina dorsal huyó! Gravemente herido."

#. [message], speaker=Ibn Khazul
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:789
msgid ""
"Forsooth, this is a victory for the people of Serrul. You've fought well, "
"Dawoud. I knew it was a good choice to pick you as my general."
msgstr ""
"Por supuesto, esta es una victoria para el pueblo de Serrul. Has luchado "
"bien, Dawoud. Sabía que fue una buena elección escogerte como mi general."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:794
msgid "It was your valor that inspired our men."
msgstr "Fue tu valor lo que inspiró a nuestros hombres."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:799
msgid ""
"But enough said. Now the spell may find its end and Ridwan can be cured, we "
"need him."
msgstr ""
"Pero basta de palabras. Ahora el hechizo puede llegar a su fin y Ridwan "
"puede ser curado, lo necesitamos."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:806
msgid "You are safe, Ilriel."
msgstr "Estás a salvo, Ilriel."

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:812
msgid "Ilra kha mal rha zul!"
msgstr "¡Ilra kha mal rha zul!"

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:859
msgid "Whoa!"
msgstr "¡Whoa!"

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:864
msgid "Ilriel!"
msgstr "¡Ilriel!"

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:869
msgid "I . . . I feel weak . . ."
msgstr "Yo... me siento débil..."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:874
msgid "Men! Bring the Dune Apothecary!"
msgstr "¡Hombres! ¡Traigan al Boticario!"

#. [message], speaker=Yusar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:881
msgid "Aight! Here, drink that, woman, it will ease the pain."
msgstr "¡Bien! Toma, bebe esto, mujer, aliviará el dolor."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:886
msgid "Ridwan."
msgstr "Ridwan."

#. [message], speaker=Ridwan
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:891
msgid ". . . what . . . what has happened?"
msgstr "... ¿qué... qué ha pasado?"

#. [message], speaker=Ibn Khazul
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:896
msgid ""
"Your mind got poisoned. A curse has been laid upon you by the forces of "
"Kesh. But Dawoud had been able to . . ."
msgstr ""
"Tu mente fue envenenada. Una maldición fue puesta sobre ti por las fuerzas "
"de Kesh. Pero Dawoud pudo..."

#. [message], speaker=Ridwan
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:901
msgid "Dawoud? Who . . . who is Dawoud?"
msgstr "¿Dawoud? ¿Quién... quién es Dawoud?"

#. [message], speaker=Ibn Khazul
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:906
msgid "My general."
msgstr "Mi general."

#. [message], speaker=Ridwan
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:911
msgid "I . . . I . . . I don't remember his name."
msgstr "Yo... yo... yo no recuerdo su nombre."

#. [message], speaker=Ibn Khazul
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:916
msgid ""
"My mounted squad found him in the deserts, shortly after you fell victim to "
"the poison of Kesh. That was months ago. He proved to be my most loyal "
"general. I can't dispense with his strength and advice."
msgstr ""
"Mi escuadrón montado lo encontró en los desiertos, poco después de que "
"cayeras víctima del veneno de Kesh. Eso fue hace meses. Demostró ser mi "
"general más leal. No puedo prescindir de su fuerza y consejo."

#. [message], speaker=Ibn Khazul
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:921
msgid ""
"After taking his advice, we could acquire the help of a woman of the forests "
"of the northwest. A woman that could deal with the poison. Ilriel. You have "
"been granted another chance, Ridwan."
msgstr ""
"Después de seguir su consejo, pudimos conseguir la ayuda de una mujer de los "
"bosques del noroeste. Una mujer que podía lidiar con el veneno. Ilriel. Te "
"ha sido concedida otra oportunidad, Ridwan."

#. [message], speaker=Ridwan
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:926
msgid "Then . . . I owe my life to you, Dawoud and Ilriel."
msgstr "Entonces... les debo la vida a ti, Dawoud e Ilriel."

#. [message], speaker=Uthain
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:931
msgid "Hmppf!"
msgstr "¡Hmppf!"

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:936
msgid ""
"It was our duty and our pledge of allegiance was the answer. There was no "
"other choice."
msgstr ""
"Fue nuestro deber y nuestro juramento de lealtad fue la respuesta. No había "
"otra opción."

#. [message], speaker=Ibn Khazul
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:941
msgid ""
"Uthman took advantage of your weakened state and he tried to attack Serrul. "
"But we were able to repel them. For today, life triumphed over death."
msgstr ""
"Uthman aprovechó tu estado debilitado e intentó atacar Serrul. Pero pudimos "
"rechazarlos. Por hoy, la vida triunfó sobre la muerte."

#. [message], speaker=Ridwan
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:946
msgid ""
"Uthman? This damned snake! Surely he is to to blame for the curse as well!"
msgstr ""
"¡¿Uthman?! ¡Esa maldita serpiente! ¡Seguro él también es culpable de la "
"maldición!"

#. [message], speaker=Ibn Khazul
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:951
msgid "Yet he escaped into the deserts."
msgstr "Sin embargo, escapó hacia los desiertos."

#. [message], speaker=Ridwan
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:956
msgid ""
"That coward! He can't even face death! Hunt him down, chase him, let the "
"desert gnaw on his miserable life until his last breath is a hymn for the "
"heroes of today's battle! Squash him like the snake he is! The snake shall "
"be no longer!"
msgstr ""
"¡Ese cobarde! ¡Ni siquiera puede enfrentar la muerte! ¡Cázenlo, persíganlo, "
"dejen que el desierto carcoma su miserable vida hasta que su último aliento "
"sea un himno para los héroes de la batalla de hoy! ¡Aplástenlo como la "
"serpiente que es! ¡La serpiente ya no existirá!"

#. [message], speaker=Ibn Khazul
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:961
msgid ""
"We will find him! And then his head will grace the walls of Serrul. As a "
"warning throughout the lands, that we, as Serrulians, won't bow down to the "
"darkness of the sands."
msgstr ""
"¡Lo encontraremos! Y entonces su cabeza adornará las murallas de Serrul. "
"Como advertencia en todas las tierras, que nosotros, como serrulianos, no "
"nos arrodillaremos ante la oscuridad de las arenas."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:966
msgid ""
"No! Let me and Ilriel deal with him. He caused so much pain to our men. We "
"shall return that favor."
msgstr ""
"¡No! Déjenme a mí e Ilriel encargarnos de él. Causó tanto dolor a nuestros "
"hombres. Le devolveremos ese favor."

#. [message], speaker=Ibn Khazul
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:971
msgid ""
"Then it is decided. I can't decline your offer. I shall protect the Dune "
"Warmaster with my riders. Be careful out there!"
msgstr ""
"Entonces está decidido. No puedo rechazar tu oferta. Protegeré al Maestro de "
"Guerra Barján con mis jinetes. ¡Tengan cuidado allá afuera!"

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:976
msgid ""
"Worry not.  It is an honour, my duty and a pleasure to bring the snake down. "
"Come, Ilriel."
msgstr ""
"No te preocupes. Es un honor, mi deber y un placer acabar con la serpiente. "
"Ven, Ilriel."

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:986
msgid "You are not the one you are pretending to be, Dawoud. Who are you?"
msgstr "No eres quien finges ser, Dawoud. ¿Quién eres?"

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:991
msgid ""
"A friend of humanity. But there's a power beneath the sands that is "
"endangering it. We have to move on, someone is awaiting us already. But take "
"care that no one is following us. We need the people of Serrul, but they may "
"not yet know their important role in the battle of the ancients that is "
"being fought these days. A battle that'll decide about the continuance of "
"the world we know. Uthman is just a gear in the giant clockwork that is "
"working against us. Let us sally forth and bring him down."
msgstr ""
"Un amigo de la humanidad. Pero hay un poder bajo las arenas que lo está "
"amenazando. Debemos continuar, alguien ya nos espera. Pero asegúrate de que "
"nadie nos siga. Necesitamos al pueblo de Serrul, pero aún pueden no conocer "
"su importante rol en la batalla de los antiguos que se libra estos días. Una "
"batalla que decidirá la continuidad del mundo que conocemos. Uthman es solo "
"un engranaje en el enorme reloj que trabaja contra nosotros. Avancemos y "
"acabemos con él."

#. [message], speaker=Ridwan
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/06_The_Pearl_of_the_Desert.cfg:1019
msgid ""
"Fools! The mind of your weak leader has been lost, as well as your hopes of "
"resisting Kesh!"
msgstr ""
"¡Idiotas! La mente de su débil líder se ha perdido, al igual que sus "
"esperanzas de resistir a Kesh!"

#. [part]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/07_Face_to_Face_with_the_Snake.cfg:7
msgid ""
"After leaving behind Serrul and following up the trail of Uthman, Ilriel and "
"Dawoud came across a forest. But it was not just a forest. It was a grove of "
"woses that had been destroyed; woses that were of the same kind as the woses "
"of the Southwoods. It seems that the living woses they encountered at Serrul "
"were just a mere rudiment of the wose population that once inhabited this "
"place. Ilriel fell to her knees and bemoaned the loss of the woses."
msgstr ""
"Después de dejar atrás Serrul y seguir el rastro de Uthman, Ilriel y Dawoud "
"se encontraron con un bosque. Pero no era solo un bosque. Era una arboleda "
"de woses que había sido destruida; woses del mismo tipo que los de los "
"Bosques del Sur. Parece que los woses vivos que encontraron en Serrul eran "
"solo un mero vestigio de la población de woses que alguna vez habitó este "
"lugar. Ilriel cayó de rodillas y lamentó la pérdida de los woses."

#. [part]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/07_Face_to_Face_with_the_Snake.cfg:11
msgid ""
"The woses, however, had not been chopped recently. The death of the wose "
"population dates back to early ages, yet the dryness of the desert conserved "
"their stumps well. But who was responsible for their death?"
msgstr ""
"Sin embargo, los woses no habían sido talados recientemente. La muerte de la "
"población de woses se remonta a épocas tempranas, pero la sequedad del "
"desierto conservó bien sus tocones. ¿Pero quién fue responsable de su muerte?"

#. [part]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/07_Face_to_Face_with_the_Snake.cfg:15
msgid ""
"Making sure that no one was following them just as Dawoud said, Ilriel and "
"Dawoud marched through the sands, following a trail of blood and they soon "
"encountered high dunes. Surely they knew what lay behind. And they surely "
"knew that the snake would pay the price."
msgstr ""
"Asegurándose de que nadie los seguía tal como dijo Dawoud, Ilriel y Dawoud "
"marcharon a través de las arenas, siguiendo un rastro de sangre y pronto "
"encontraron altas dunas. Seguramente sabían qué había detrás. Y seguramente "
"sabían que la serpiente pagaría el precio."

#. [scenario], id=07_Face_to_Face_with_the_Snake
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/07_Face_to_Face_with_the_Snake.cfg:26
msgid "Face to Face with the Snake"
msgstr "Cara a Cara con la Serpiente"

#. [side]
#. [side], type=High Athvari
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/07_Face_to_Face_with_the_Snake.cfg:122
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/08_Isanbar.cfg:57
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/22_Timeless.cfg:57
msgid "The Athvari"
msgstr "Los Athvari"

#. [event]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/07_Face_to_Face_with_the_Snake.cfg:146
msgid "Athavael"
msgstr "Athavael"

#. [event]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/07_Face_to_Face_with_the_Snake.cfg:147
msgid "Aerandir "
msgstr "Aerandir "

#. [event]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/07_Face_to_Face_with_the_Snake.cfg:148
msgid "Elan"
msgstr "Elan"

#. [event]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/07_Face_to_Face_with_the_Snake.cfg:149
msgid "Delayar"
msgstr "Delayar"

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/07_Face_to_Face_with_the_Snake.cfg:195
msgid ""
"There he is. Like the coward he is, Uthman hides in the woods. And "
"apparently, he set up a camp to which his wounded soldiers return to tend "
"their wounds. But this time, this time he won't escape. Their blood shall "
"soak the sands."
msgstr ""
"Ahí está. Como el cobarde que es, Uthman se esconde en los bosques. Y "
"aparentemente, montó un campamento al que regresan sus soldados heridos para "
"curar sus heridas. Pero esta vez, esta vez no escapará. Su sangre empapará "
"las arenas."

#. [message], speaker=Uthman
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/07_Face_to_Face_with_the_Snake.cfg:200
msgid "So you found me, Dawoud? Haha. . . ha ha haha!"
msgstr "¡Así que me encontraste, Dawoud? ¡Jaja... ja ja jaja!"

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/07_Face_to_Face_with_the_Snake.cfg:205
msgid ""
"I hope you've familiarised with this oasis, as this will be your place of "
"death, snake!"
msgstr ""
"Espero que te hayas familiarizado con este oasis, porque este será tu lugar "
"de muerte, ¡serpiente!"

#. [message], speaker=Uthman
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/07_Face_to_Face_with_the_Snake.cfg:210
msgid ""
"My death won't change your miserable situation! The future belongs to Kesh!"
msgstr ""
"¡Mi muerte no cambiará su miserable situación! ¡El futuro pertenece a Kesh!"

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/07_Face_to_Face_with_the_Snake.cfg:215
msgid "Your words are nothing but poison!"
msgstr "¡Tus palabras no son más que veneno!"

#. [message], speaker=Nuvdael
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/07_Face_to_Face_with_the_Snake.cfg:220
msgid ""
"There she is! Elves of the Southwoods, as fast as the winds and silent as "
"the whispers of the woses! Make haste!"
msgstr ""
"¡Allí está! ¡Elfos de los Bosques del Sur, tan rápidos como los vientos y "
"silenciosos como los susurros de los woses! ¡Apúrense!"

#. [message], speaker=Nuvdael
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/07_Face_to_Face_with_the_Snake.cfg:237
msgid "Finally we've found you, Ilriel! I thought we had lost you forever."
msgstr ""
"¡Por fin te encontramos, Ilriel! Pensé que te habíamos perdido para siempre."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/07_Face_to_Face_with_the_Snake.cfg:242
msgid ""
"I'm glad Kartal and the message has reached you, Nuvdael. Serrul is "
"isolated, we need any man and any woman to avert the chaos."
msgstr ""
"Me alegra que Kartal y el mensaje te hayan llegado, Nuvdael. Serrul está "
"aislada, necesitamos a cualquier hombre y mujer para evitar el caos."

#. [message], speaker=Nuvdael
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/07_Face_to_Face_with_the_Snake.cfg:247
msgid ""
"I didn't know things were going that badly. I am there if you need me. And I "
"am here for you, Ilriel. If something would have happened to you, I'd never "
"forgive myself for leaving you to the dangers of the deserts while I stayed "
"at the Southwoods."
msgstr ""
"No sabía que las cosas iban tan mal. Estoy aquí si me necesitas. Y estoy "
"aquí por ti, Ilriel. Si algo te hubiera pasado, nunca me perdonaría haberte "
"dejado a los peligros de los desiertos mientras yo me quedaba en los Bosques "
"del Sur."

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/07_Face_to_Face_with_the_Snake.cfg:252
msgid ""
"It is nice to have you at my side again. I am afraid the desert puts chains "
"on us, we can't escape its conflicts."
msgstr ""
"Es bueno tenerte a mi lado de nuevo. Me temo que el desierto nos pone "
"cadenas, no podemos escapar de sus conflictos."

#. [message], speaker=Kenlaed
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/07_Face_to_Face_with_the_Snake.cfg:257
msgid "The sand is moving!"
msgstr "¡La arena se mueve!"

#. [message], speaker=Nuvdael
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/07_Face_to_Face_with_the_Snake.cfg:271
msgid "Ambush!"
msgstr "¡Emboscada!"

#. [message], speaker=Uthman
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/07_Face_to_Face_with_the_Snake.cfg:276
msgid ""
"Ahahaha! If I can not capture Serrul by myself, I can at least stamp out "
"some of its puny generals! You are nothing more than a worm to me, Dawoud!"
msgstr ""
"¡Jajajaja! Si no puedo capturar Serrul yo solo, ¡al menos puedo aplastar a "
"algunos de sus insignificantes generales! ¡No eres más que un gusano para "
"mí, Dawoud!"

#. [message], speaker=Uthman
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/07_Face_to_Face_with_the_Snake.cfg:281
msgid ""
"And even your friends won't shield you from the consequences of your doing."
msgstr ""
"Y ni siquiera tus amigos te protegerán de las consecuencias de tus acciones."

#. [message], speaker=Uthman
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/07_Face_to_Face_with_the_Snake.cfg:286
msgid ""
"So the time has come! Face to face on the battlefield! The armies clash, a "
"bloodshed! Dying the way we lived! Fighting! Men! For Kesh!"
msgstr ""
"¡Así que ha llegado el momento! ¡Cara a cara en el campo de batalla! ¡Los "
"ejércitos chocan, un baño de sangre! ¡Muriendo como vivimos! ¡Luchando! "
"¡Hombres! ¡Por Kesh!"

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/07_Face_to_Face_with_the_Snake.cfg:291
msgid "To arms!"
msgstr "¡A las armas!"

#. [message], speaker=Nuvdael
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/07_Face_to_Face_with_the_Snake.cfg:296
msgid "Wind wafts, wind storms! Swords high!"
msgstr "¡Vientos soplen, tormentas de viento! ¡Espadas en alto!"

#. [message], speaker=Uthain
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/07_Face_to_Face_with_the_Snake.cfg:339
msgid "Oh-oh, elves! Even more of them! What do you think of that, Petz?"
msgstr "Oh-oh, ¡elfos! ¡Aún más de ellos! ¿Qué piensas de eso, Petz?"

#. [message], speaker=Uthain
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/07_Face_to_Face_with_the_Snake.cfg:344
msgid "<i>Roar!</i>"
msgstr "<i>¡Rugido!</i>"

#. [message], speaker=Uthain
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/07_Face_to_Face_with_the_Snake.cfg:349
msgid ""
"Don't be so rude, Petz! But why do the elves leave behind their forests?"
msgstr ""
"¡No seas tan grosero, Petz! Pero ¿por qué los elfos dejan atrás sus bosques?"

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/07_Face_to_Face_with_the_Snake.cfg:354
msgid ""
"Our people might heavily favor the forests, but the most valuable thing in "
"our society is elvish lives."
msgstr ""
"Nuestro pueblo puede favorecer mucho los bosques, pero lo más valioso en "
"nuestra sociedad son las vidas elfas."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/07_Face_to_Face_with_the_Snake.cfg:365
msgid ""
"I feel a strange power flowing through him! We should quickly bring forth "
"his downfall before he can utilize that strange power!"
msgstr ""
"¡Siento un extraño poder fluyendo a través de él! ¡Debemos causar "
"rápidamente su caída antes de que pueda utilizar ese extraño poder!"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/07_Face_to_Face_with_the_Snake.cfg:383
msgid "<i>Serrul: one week's marches to the west</i>\n"
msgstr "<i>Serrul: una jornada de marcha al oeste</i>\n"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/07_Face_to_Face_with_the_Snake.cfg:384
msgid "<i>Kesh: eight week's marches to the east</i>"
msgstr "<i>Kesh: ocho jornadas de marcha al este</i>"

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/07_Face_to_Face_with_the_Snake.cfg:422
msgid "Your days are counted, snake."
msgstr "Tus días están contados, serpiente."

#. [message], speaker=Uthman
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/07_Face_to_Face_with_the_Snake.cfg:427
msgid ""
"You . . . you . . . think. . . this is . . . over? The Sphere . . . is ours. "
"The war. . . is . . . already won."
msgstr ""
"Tú... tú... crees... ¿esto está... terminado? La Esfera... es nuestra. La "
"guerra... ya... está ganada."

#. [message], speaker=Nuvdael
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/07_Face_to_Face_with_the_Snake.cfg:441
msgid "So the battle is over."
msgstr "Así que la batalla ha terminado."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/07_Face_to_Face_with_the_Snake.cfg:446
msgid "I am afraid it is not."
msgstr "Me temo que no."

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/07_Face_to_Face_with_the_Snake.cfg:451
msgid "See his dead body? Something is sparkling there."
msgstr "¿Ven su cuerpo muerto? Algo está brillando allí."

#. [message], speaker=Nuvdael
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/07_Face_to_Face_with_the_Snake.cfg:456
msgid "Wh . . . what is this?"
msgstr "¿Qué... qué es esto?"

#. [message], speaker=Uthman
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/07_Face_to_Face_with_the_Snake.cfg:473
msgid "You . . . you can't win this battle."
msgstr "Ustedes... no pueden ganar esta batalla."

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/07_Face_to_Face_with_the_Snake.cfg:478
msgid ""
"What . . . what is going on here? His body got pierced by our spears and "
"arrows. There is no chance he could have survived that."
msgstr ""
"¿Qué... qué está pasando aquí? Su cuerpo fue atravesado por nuestras lanzas "
"y flechas. No hay posibilidad de que haya sobrevivido a eso."

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/07_Face_to_Face_with_the_Snake.cfg:483
msgid "D . . .Dawoud?"
msgstr "¿D... Dawoud?"

#. [message], speaker=Uthman
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/07_Face_to_Face_with_the_Snake.cfg:488
msgid ""
"Eternity is on our side, Dawoud. How do you plan to defeat eternity itself?"
msgstr ""
"La eternidad está de nuestro lado, Dawoud. ¿Cómo planeas derrotar a la "
"eternidad misma?"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/07_Face_to_Face_with_the_Snake.cfg:503
msgid ""
"Suddenly it felt like time became slower, grains of sand were slowly raised "
"from the ground, soon forming a whirlwind of sand around Ilriel."
msgstr ""
"De repente pareció que el tiempo se volvía más lento, granos de arena se "
"levantaban lentamente del suelo, formando pronto un torbellino de arena "
"alrededor de Ilriel."

#. [event]
#. [side], type=High Athvari
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/07_Face_to_Face_with_the_Snake.cfg:516
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/08_Isanbar.cfg:62
msgid "Sinan"
msgstr "Sinan"

#. [message], speaker=Sinan
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/07_Face_to_Face_with_the_Snake.cfg:529
msgid "The Athvari are on their side, snake."
msgstr "Los athvari están de su lado, serpiente."

#. [message], speaker=Uthman
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/07_Face_to_Face_with_the_Snake.cfg:534
msgid "Athvari! The last of the Athvari! Your bloodline comes to an end!"
msgstr "¡Athvari! ¡Los últimos de los athvari! ¡Su linaje llega a su fin!"

#. [message], speaker=Sinan
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/07_Face_to_Face_with_the_Snake.cfg:539
msgid ""
"We have to go now, come close to us. The immortal one can't be brought down "
"and his presence is poisoning your minds."
msgstr ""
"Debemos irnos ahora, acérquense a nosotros. El inmortal no puede ser "
"derribado y su presencia está envenenando sus mentes."

#. [message], speaker=Sinan
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/07_Face_to_Face_with_the_Snake.cfg:544
msgid "There is no time for explanations. Quickly, get close to us!"
msgstr "No hay tiempo para explicaciones. ¡Rápido, acérquense a nosotros!"

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/07_Face_to_Face_with_the_Snake.cfg:549
msgid "Hurry up, Ilriel! We can trust them!"
msgstr "¡Apúrate, Ilriel! ¡Podemos confiar en ellos!"

#. [message], speaker=Sinan
#. [message], speaker=unit
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/07_Face_to_Face_with_the_Snake.cfg:554
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/16_Return_to_Tharwya.cfg:75
msgid "By the power of the Athvari!"
msgstr "¡Por el poder de los athvari!"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/07_Face_to_Face_with_the_Snake.cfg:560
msgid ""
"Standing right next to the mysterious wizards, Ilriel feels a strange power "
"flowing through her body."
msgstr ""
"De pie justo al lado de los misteriosos magos, Ilriel siente un extraño "
"poder fluyendo a través de su cuerpo."

#. [message], speaker=Nuvdael
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/07_Face_to_Face_with_the_Snake.cfg:586
msgid "What's happening? I'm feeling so weak right now."
msgstr "¿Qué está pasando? Me siento tan débil ahora."

#. [message], speaker=Uthain
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/07_Face_to_Face_with_the_Snake.cfg:591
msgid ""
"You weaklings are no match for the might of Kesh, soon your minds will be "
"gone and your futile resistance will be no more than a footnote on our "
"history!"
msgstr ""
"¡Ustedes débiles no son rivales para el poder de Kesh, pronto sus mentes "
"desaparecerán y su inútil resistencia no será más que una nota al pie en "
"nuestra historia!"

#. [part]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/08_Isanbar.cfg:7
msgid ""
"After the foreign wizards finished their ritual, Ilriel, Dawoud and Nuvdael "
"find themselves on top of a mountainside; great dunes and sand form the "
"horizon."
msgstr ""
"Después de que los magos extranjeros terminaron su ritual, Ilriel, Dawoud y "
"Nuvdael se encuentran en la cima de una ladera montañosa; grandes dunas y "
"arena forman el horizonte."

#. [scenario], id=08_Isanbar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/08_Isanbar.cfg:18
msgid "Isanbar"
msgstr "Isanbar"

#. [side], type=Black Dragon
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/08_Isanbar.cfg:77
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/08_Isanbar.cfg:82
msgid "Khazran"
msgstr "Khazran"

#. [event]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/08_Isanbar.cfg:104
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/19_Above_the_Stars_and_below_Earth.cfg:338
msgid "Iskandar"
msgstr "Iskandar"

#. [message], speaker=Nuvdael
#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/08_Isanbar.cfg:146
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/08_Isanbar.cfg:151
msgid "Huh!"
msgstr "¡Eh!"

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/08_Isanbar.cfg:156
msgid ""
"Ah, the great mountains of Isanbar, I've missed this place of my origin."
msgstr ""
"Ah, las grandes montañas de Isanbar, extrañaba este lugar de mi origen."

#. [message], speaker=Sinan
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/08_Isanbar.cfg:161
msgid "Follow me."
msgstr "Síganme."

#. [message], speaker=Sinan
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/08_Isanbar.cfg:178
msgid "Khazran, we brought them to you. They survived."
msgstr "Khazran, los trajimos ante ti. Sobrevivieron."

#. [message], speaker=Khazran
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/08_Isanbar.cfg:183
msgid ""
"Ilarøth? Is it you? I've not seen you since ages, forgotten brother. I'm "
"glad to have you back at our side."
msgstr ""
"¿Ilarøth? ¿Eres tú? No te había visto desde hace siglos, hermano olvidado. "
"Me alegra tenerte de vuelta a nuestro lado."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/08_Isanbar.cfg:188
msgid ""
"Indeed fate forced us to take different paths, but it also decided that we "
"would meet again. And today is that day."
msgstr ""
"En verdad el destino nos obligó a tomar caminos diferentes, pero también "
"decidió que nos encontraríamos de nuevo. Y hoy es ese día."

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/08_Isanbar.cfg:199
msgid ""
"'Ilarøth', so that's your true name, your true self? You knew about all of "
"this?"
msgstr ""
"«Ilarøth», ¿ese es tu verdadero nombre, tu verdadero ser? ¿Sabías todo esto?"

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/08_Isanbar.cfg:204
msgid ""
"I apologize for not letting you know earlier about, Ilriel, but this is far "
"too important to let destiny take its path. Forgive me. Soon, you'll "
"understand."
msgstr ""
"Me disculpo por no habértelo dicho antes, Ilriel, pero esto es demasiado "
"importante como para dejar que el destino siga su curso. Perdóname. Pronto "
"lo entenderás."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/08_Isanbar.cfg:209
msgid ""
"I thought you'd never come, Sinan. Things weren't going that well for us."
msgstr ""
"Pensé que nunca vendrías, Sinan. Las cosas no iban tan bien para nosotros."

#. [message], speaker=Sinan
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/08_Isanbar.cfg:214
msgid ""
"We were able to sense the magic of the fragment Uthman wore. It was only a "
"matter of time."
msgstr ""
"Pudimos sentir la magia del fragmento que llevaba Uthman. Era solo cuestión "
"de tiempo."

#. [message], speaker=Khazran
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/08_Isanbar.cfg:219
msgid "I see, you have not yet sworn in Ilriel. But she is our key to victory."
msgstr ""
"Veo que aún no has jurado a Ilriel. Pero ella es nuestra clave para la "
"victoria."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/08_Isanbar.cfg:224
msgid ""
"Ilriel, do you remember the green sparkling object in the body of Uthman? It "
"is a shiver from the Sphere, granting him powers unknown to this world."
msgstr ""
"Ilriel, ¿recuerdas el objeto verde brillante en el cuerpo de Uthman? Es un "
"fragmento de la Esfera, que le otorga poderes desconocidos para este mundo."

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/08_Isanbar.cfg:229
msgid "The Sphere?"
msgstr "¿La Esfera?"

#. [message], speaker=Sinan
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/08_Isanbar.cfg:234
msgid ""
"A magical construct crafted by us, the Athvari, eleven years after the "
"northern king you call Konrad II ascended to the throne. An astral prison."
msgstr ""
"Una construcción mágica creada por nosotros, los athvari, once años después "
"de que el rey del norte que llaman Konrad II ascendiera al trono. Una "
"prisión astral."

#. [message], speaker=Nuvdael
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/08_Isanbar.cfg:239
msgid ""
"A great sphere? I remember old prophecies being told about it. The stories "
"of the Sphere have never been verified by the wise prophets of the "
"Southwoods."
msgstr ""
"¿Una gran esfera? Recuerdo antiguas profecías que se contaban sobre ella. "
"Las historias de la Esfera nunca fueron verificadas por los sabios profetas "
"de los Bosques del Sur."

#. [message], speaker=Khazran
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/08_Isanbar.cfg:244
msgid ""
"Because they fear its power! They can't control it! And even the Athvari "
"lost control over it."
msgstr ""
"¡Porque temen su poder! ¡No pueden controlarla! E incluso los athvari "
"perdieron el control sobre ella."

#. [message], speaker=Sinan
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/08_Isanbar.cfg:249
msgid ""
"It was crafted when the Three Kings of K'thar, the former capitol of the "
"lands of the deserts, fell victim to the great powers of magic. During their "
"rule in the nine years prior to the Spheres creation, their lust for more "
"power grew and they learned the arts of magic to extend and strengthen their "
"realm and influence across the deserts. Soon had they lost control over "
"their own minds in the acquisition of the dark arts, plunging the lands into "
"an era of chaos. The people and creatures of the desert had to pay for it, "
"with their blood."
msgstr ""
"Fue creada cuando los Tres Reyes de K'thar, la antigua capital de las "
"tierras de los desiertos, cayeron víctimas de los grandes poderes de la "
"magia. Durante su reinado en los nueve años previos a la creación de la "
"Esfera, su deseo de más poder creció y aprendieron las artes de la magia "
"para extender y fortalecer su reino e influencia a través de los desiertos. "
"Pronto perdieron el control sobre sus propias mentes en la adquisición de "
"las artes oscuras, sumiendo las tierras en una era de caos. El pueblo y las "
"criaturas del desierto tuvieron que pagarlo con su sangre."

#. [message], speaker=Khazran
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/08_Isanbar.cfg:254
msgid "We needed the Sphere."
msgstr "Necesitábamos la Esfera."

#. [message], speaker=Sinan
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/08_Isanbar.cfg:259
msgid ""
"Neither man nor woman were powerful enough to bring forth the downfall of "
"the Three Kings of K'thar. In the year of their confinement, Serrul, Kesh "
"and Th'arwya united to overthrow the Three, but they failed. So the Sphere "
"was created by Thrang'ual, the first of the Athvari, and his brothers in "
"order to imprison the Three Kings with magic and thus inhibit their power. "
"Fighting united, Kesh, Serrul, Th'arwya and the power of the Athvari were "
"able to bring about the downfall of the Three Kings. It was the last time "
"Kesh and Serrul fought united. The lust for the city of K'thar was unbound "
"and the conflict never settled. The conflict lasted for 8 years and it ended "
"in a stalemate."
msgstr ""
"Ni hombre ni mujer eran lo suficientemente poderosos para provocar la caída "
"de los Tres Reyes de K'thar. En el año de su confinamiento, Serrul, Kesh y "
"Th'arwya se unieron para derrocar a los Tres, pero fallaron. Así que la "
"Esfera fue creada por Thrang'ual, el primero de los athvari, y sus hermanos "
"para aprisionar a los Tres Reyes con magia e inhibir así su poder. Luchando "
"unidos, Kesh, Serrul, Th'arwya y el poder de los athvari lograron provocar "
"la caída de los Tres Reyes. Fue la última vez que Kesh y Serrul lucharon "
"unidos. La codicia por la ciudad de K'thar quedó desatada y el conflicto "
"nunca se resolvió. El conflicto duró 8 años y terminó en empate."

#. [message], speaker=Sinan
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/08_Isanbar.cfg:264
msgid ""
"Years passed and many followers of the Three Kings, who used magic to follow "
"in the footsteps of the Three Kings, found their end in the Sphere. It was "
"at that time that the first of the Athvari swore to protect the lands from "
"magic, as it has always led to catastrophes and death. We've sworn that "
"never again shall anyone rediscover the secrets of magic and throw these "
"lands into another era of darkness. And if someone tried to, they'd pay with "
"their lives - or what is left of them . . . That's what we call The Law, a "
"rule that prohibits the use of magic."
msgstr ""
"Pasaron los años y muchos seguidores de los Tres Reyes, que usaban magia "
"para seguir los pasos de los Tres Reyes, encontraron su fin en la Esfera. "
"Fue en ese tiempo que el primero de los athvari juró proteger las tierras de "
"la magia, ya que siempre había llevado a catástrofes y muerte. Hemos jurado "
"que nunca más nadie redescubrirá los secretos de la magia y arrojará estas "
"tierras a otra era de oscuridad. Y si alguien lo intentaba, pagaría con sus "
"vidas, o lo que quedara de ellas... Eso es lo que llamamos La Ley, una regla "
"que prohíbe el uso de la magia."

#. [message], speaker=Khazran
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/08_Isanbar.cfg:269
msgid ""
"The Athvari managed to imprison hundreds and thousands of men after the "
"Three Kings got imprisoned. The might of the Sphere grew and grew and soon "
"it developed a life of its own, breaking loose from the control of the "
"Athvari and disappearing into the vastness of the deserts, never to be seen "
"again. Something happened inside the Sphere. Something invisible to us. The "
"power the Sphere overwhelmed the Athvari. Their own creation grew stronger "
"than they."
msgstr ""
"Los athvari lograron aprisionar a cientos y miles de hombres después de que "
"los Tres Reyes fueran encarcelados. El poder de la Esfera creció y creció y "
"pronto desarrolló vida propia, escapando del control de los athvari y "
"desapareciendo en la vastedad de los desiertos, para nunca más ser vista. "
"Algo sucedió dentro de la Esfera. Algo invisible para nosotros. El poder de "
"la Esfera abrumó a los athvari. Su propia creación se volvió más fuerte que "
"ellos."

#. [message], speaker=Khazran
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/08_Isanbar.cfg:274
msgid ""
"This was yet again nine years later - after their imprisonment. And since "
"that time, magical events took place in these lands, caravans went missing, "
"creatures never seen before arose from the sands, destroying and ravaging "
"the lands, men died, not by nature, but by the force of the Sphere. And we, "
"our own kin, the Athvari, got abducted by the Sphere. It searched for us."
msgstr ""
"Esto fue nueve años después, nuevamente, tras su encarcelamiento. Y desde "
"entonces, eventos mágicos ocurrieron en estas tierras, caravanas "
"desaparecieron, criaturas nunca vistas antes surgieron de las arenas, "
"destruyendo y asolando las tierras, hombres murieron, no por la naturaleza, "
"sino por la fuerza de la Esfera. Y nosotros, nuestro propio linaje, los "
"athvari, fuimos secuestrados por la Esfera. Nos buscaba."

#. [message], speaker=Sinan
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/08_Isanbar.cfg:279
msgid ""
"And the price is being paid. By the descendants of the first Athvari. The "
"Athvari of our time. Bereft of the power that rightfully belongs to us and "
"ensures the fundament of life. Bereft of the power that was intended to "
"secure peace."
msgstr ""
"Y el precio se está pagando. Por los descendientes del primer athvari. Los "
"athvari de nuestro tiempo. Privados del poder que legítimamente nos "
"pertenece y que asegura el fundamento de la vida. Privados del poder que "
"estaba destinado a asegurar la paz."

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/08_Isanbar.cfg:284
msgid ""
"So the Sphere poisoned the Dune Warmaster of Serrul to sow destruction and "
"chaos?"
msgstr ""
"¿Entonces la Esfera envenenó al Maestro de Guerra de Serrul para sembrar "
"destrucción y caos?"

#. [message], speaker=Sinan
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/08_Isanbar.cfg:289
msgid ""
"We don't know for sure whether it is the Sphere itself or someone that took "
"control of it and conjured its power."
msgstr ""
"No sabemos con certeza si es la Esfera misma o alguien que tomó control de "
"ella e invocó su poder."

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/08_Isanbar.cfg:294
msgid "Uthman said that Kesh is in control of the Sphere."
msgstr "Uthman dijo que Kesh tiene el control de la Esfera."

#. [message], speaker=Sinan
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/08_Isanbar.cfg:299
msgid "Then things are worse than expected."
msgstr "Entonces las cosas están peor de lo esperado."

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/08_Isanbar.cfg:304
msgid "Why didn't you cure Ridwan?"
msgstr "¿Por qué no curaron a Ridwan?"

#. [message], speaker=Sinan
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/08_Isanbar.cfg:309
msgid ""
"The Sphere can sense our blood, our magic, our lives. And it would have "
"crushed us. We needed you, Ilriel, someone with a pure heart and blood "
"unknown to the Sphere. Someone immune to the magic of the Sphere. If we "
"went, it would have been the direct downfall of the Athvari."
msgstr ""
"La Esfera puede sentir nuestra sangre, nuestra magia, nuestras vidas. Y nos "
"habría aplastado. Te necesitábamos a ti, Ilriel, alguien con un corazón puro "
"y sangre desconocida para la Esfera. Alguien inmune a la magia de la Esfera. "
"Si hubiéramos ido, habría sido la caída directa de los athvari."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/08_Isanbar.cfg:314
msgid ""
"The voice speaking through the Dune Warmaster of Serrul, Uthman being "
"revived by the fragment of the Sphere. It all makes sense now. It seems that "
"our enemy is stronger than we thought."
msgstr ""
"La voz que hablaba a través del Maestro de Guerra de Serrul, Uthman siendo "
"revivido por el fragmento de la Esfera. Ahora todo tiene sentido. Parece que "
"nuestro enemigo es más fuerte de lo que pensábamos."

#. [message], speaker=Khazran
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/08_Isanbar.cfg:319
msgid "You can consider yourself fortunate, though; time is on your side."
msgstr "Aunque pueden considerarse afortunados; el tiempo está de su lado."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/08_Isanbar.cfg:324
msgid ""
"Time means nothing in these lands, only life and death does. And it is "
"death, that is creeping towards our lives."
msgstr ""
"El tiempo no significa nada en estas tierras, solo la vida y la muerte "
"importan. Y es la muerte la que se arrastra hacia nuestras vidas."

#. [message], speaker=Khazran
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/08_Isanbar.cfg:329
msgid ""
"Time is merciful. The line of the Athvari rescinds, their power diminished "
"and their minds poisoned by the thoughts of their past. They are in an "
"invidious situation, Ilarøth, and you can sense it. Although you've "
"deliberately lost your powers."
msgstr ""
"El tiempo es misericordioso. La línea de los athvari se reduce, su poder "
"disminuido y sus mentes envenenadas por los pensamientos de su pasado. Están "
"en una situación envidiable, Ilarøth, y puedes sentirlo. Aunque "
"deliberadamente perdiste tus poderes."

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/08_Isanbar.cfg:334
msgid "You . . . you are one of the Athvari, Ilarøth?"
msgstr "¿Tú... tú eres uno de los athvari, Ilarøth?"

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/08_Isanbar.cfg:339
msgid ""
"I once was. But when the Sphere was created . . . I . . . I could not . . ."
msgstr "Una vez lo fui. Pero cuando se creó la Esfera... yo... no pude..."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/08_Isanbar.cfg:344
msgid ""
"The creation of the Sphere was a mistake, Ilriel. Humanity was not suited "
"for it at that time. I feared it would become a tool for the mighty, leading "
"to not only the followers of K'thar getting imprisoned."
msgstr ""
"La creación de la Esfera fue un error, Ilriel. La humanidad no estaba "
"preparada para ella en ese tiempo. Temía que se convirtiera en una "
"herramienta para los poderosos, llevando no solo a que los seguidores de "
"K'thar fueran aprisionados."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/08_Isanbar.cfg:349
msgid ""
"I refused to help create the Sphere. And I gave my blood, as I no longer "
"identified myself with the goal of the Athvari. There had to be another way "
"to defeat the Three Kings of K'thar."
msgstr ""
"Me negué a ayudar a crear la Esfera. Y di mi sangre, ya que ya no me "
"identificaba con el objetivo de los athvari. Tenía que haber otra forma de "
"derrotar a los Tres Reyes de K'thar."

#. [message], speaker=Iskandar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/08_Isanbar.cfg:354
msgid ""
"But when the Sphere overwhelmed our power years later, our relationship "
"changed. We needed Ilarøth again, for a task of the highest importance."
msgstr ""
"Pero cuando la Esfera abrumó nuestro poder años después, nuestra relación "
"cambió. Necesitábamos a Ilarøth nuevamente, para una tarea de la más alta "
"importancia."

#. [message], speaker=Iskandar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/08_Isanbar.cfg:359
msgid ""
"Leaving the great mountains of Isanbar two years after the Spheres loss, "
"Ilarøth entered the lives of the people of Serrul, gained the backing of "
"their community and finally was able to suggest a journey to the west to "
"find you unnoticed by the Sphere and break the curse afflicting Ridwan. "
"Ilarøth has given his life to find you, Ilriel. And for that, we thank him."
msgstr ""
"Saliendo de las grandes montañas de Isanbar dos años después de la pérdida "
"de la Esfera, Ilarøth entró en las vidas del pueblo de Serrul, ganó el "
"respaldo de su comunidad y finalmente pudo sugerir un viaje al oeste para "
"encontrarte sin ser notado por la Esfera y romper la maldición que afligía a "
"Ridwan. Ilarøth ha dado su vida para encontrarte, Ilriel. Y por eso, le "
"agradecemos."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/08_Isanbar.cfg:364
msgid ""
"The name 'Dawoud' was given to me by the people of Serrul, it means 'present "
"of the gods' and they hoped that I could free Ridwan from the curse. But we "
"needed you, Ilriel."
msgstr ""
"El nombre «Dawoud» me fue dado por el pueblo de Serrul, significa «presente "
"de los dioses» y esperaban que pudiera liberar a Ridwan de la maldición. "
"Pero te necesitábamos a ti, Ilriel."

#. [message], speaker=Iskandar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/08_Isanbar.cfg:369
msgid ""
"And your task is not yet done. Our lifeblood diminishes and soon there won't "
"be any barrier between the Sphere and what lurks inside and the rest of the "
"world. The bulwark that is the circle of the Athvari is slowly falling "
"apart. We have to stop the Sphere and whatever is controlling it from the "
"inside."
msgstr ""
"Y tu tarea aún no ha terminado. Nuestra sangre vital se reduce y pronto no "
"habrá ninguna barrera entre la Esfera y lo que acecha dentro y el resto del "
"mundo. El baluarte que es el círculo de los athvari se está desmoronando "
"lentamente. Debemos detener la Esfera y lo que sea que la controla desde "
"adentro."

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/08_Isanbar.cfg:374
msgid "How can we stop the Sphere?"
msgstr "¿Cómo podemos detener la Esfera?"

#. [message], speaker=Iskandar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/08_Isanbar.cfg:379
msgid ""
"We have to find it first, but I am afraid the Sphere lies in Kesh, behind "
"walls as high as the mountains. We have to go there, it'll take months, but "
"there is no choice. Maybe we are too late already."
msgstr ""
"Primero tenemos que encontrarla, pero me temo que la Esfera yace en Kesh, "
"detrás de murallas tan altas como las montañas. Debemos ir allí, tomará "
"meses, pero no hay otra opción. Tal vez ya sea demasiado tarde."

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/08_Isanbar.cfg:384
msgid "What will happen to Serrul, now that Uthman is still alive?"
msgstr "¿Qué le pasará a Serrul, ahora que Uthman sigue vivo?"

#. [message], speaker=Sinan
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/08_Isanbar.cfg:389
msgid ""
"Another army from Kesh pours out over the eastern ashlands. The people of "
"Serrul will all die. It is their destiny, but they will give us time. "
"Valuable time in order to find the Sphere. We can't help them. They are dead."
msgstr ""
"Otro ejército de Kesh se derrama sobre las tierras de ceniza del este. El "
"pueblo de Serrul morirá por completo. Es su destino, pero nos darán tiempo. "
"Tiempo valioso para encontrar la Esfera. No podemos ayudarlos. Están muertos."

#. [message], speaker=Khazran
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/08_Isanbar.cfg:396
msgid "And so are you, Athvari!"
msgstr "¡Y ustedes también, athvari!"

#. [message], speaker=Sinan
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/08_Isanbar.cfg:401
msgid "Kh . . . Khazran?"
msgstr "¿Kh... Khazran?"

#. [message], speaker=Khazran
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/08_Isanbar.cfg:406
msgid "Fly! Fly, you fools!"
msgstr "¡Vuelen! ¡Vuelen, tontos!"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/08_Isanbar.cfg:419
msgid "A lightning strikes Khazran, green fog evaporating from his body."
msgstr "Un rayo golpea a Khazran, una niebla verde evaporándose de su cuerpo."

#. [message], speaker=Khazran
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/08_Isanbar.cfg:425
msgid ""
"My names are many, fools! It was foolish to imprison the unimprisonable! Our "
"will shall bring forth your death!"
msgstr ""
"¡Mis nombres son muchos, idiotas! ¡Fue una tontería aprisionar a lo "
"inaprisionable! ¡Nuestra voluntad traerá su muerte!"

#. [message], speaker=Nuvdael
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/08_Isanbar.cfg:430
msgid "Something must have entered his mind!"
msgstr "¡Algo debe haber entrado en su mente!"

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/08_Isanbar.cfg:435
msgid "Evil glows inside him!"
msgstr "¡El mal brilla dentro de él!"

#. [message], speaker=Khazran
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/08_Isanbar.cfg:441
msgid "'Evil'? Future lies inside me!"
msgstr "¿«Mal»? ¡El futuro yace dentro de mí!"

#. [message], speaker=Iskandar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/08_Isanbar.cfg:446
msgid "It's the Sphere!"
msgstr "¡Es la Esfera!"

#. [message], speaker=Khazran
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/08_Isanbar.cfg:452
msgid "Your reign is over and we shall return! The world's throne is ours!"
msgstr ""
"¡Su reinado ha terminado y regresaremos! ¡El trono del mundo es nuestro!"

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/08_Isanbar.cfg:457
msgid "Khazran wouldn't prefer ending as a host of evil! Strike hard!"
msgstr ""
"¡Khazran no preferiría terminar como anfitrión del mal! ¡Golpeen con fuerza!"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/08_Isanbar.cfg:473
msgid "Defeat Khazran"
msgstr "Derrota a Khazran"

#. [objective], condition=lose
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/08_Isanbar.cfg:477
msgid "Any Athvari dies"
msgstr "Muere cualquier athvari"

#. [message], speaker=Khazran
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/08_Isanbar.cfg:519
msgid "Your time has come! We will be free! Free once again!"
msgstr "¡Ha llegado su tiempo! ¡Seremos libres! ¡Libres una vez más!"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/08_Isanbar.cfg:525
msgid "A shockwave emanates from the body of the dragon, raising dust."
msgstr "Una onda de choque emana del cuerpo del dragón, levantando polvo."

#. [message], speaker=Khazran
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/08_Isanbar.cfg:530
msgid ""
"Ilarøth. . . forgive . . . me . . . for I had not . . . been strong . . . "
"enough . . . to withstand . . . the Three."
msgstr ""
"Ilarøth... perdóname... por no haber sido... lo suficientemente fuerte... "
"para resistir... a los Tres."

#. [message], speaker=Khazran
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/08_Isanbar.cfg:535
msgid ""
"I . . . hope . . . at least . . . in death . . . I can be . . . of help . . ."
msgstr "Espero... al menos... en la muerte... pueda ser... de ayuda..."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/08_Isanbar.cfg:541
msgid ""
"Khazran's horn glows, spawning sparks and generating what looks like a "
"mighty thunder strike that strucks down Ilarøth. Then Khazran's horn loses "
"its light."
msgstr ""
"El cuerno de Khazran brilla, generando chispas y produciendo lo que parece "
"un poderoso rayo que derriba a Ilarøth. Luego el cuerno de Khazran pierde su "
"luz."

#. [object]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/08_Isanbar.cfg:545
msgid "Gift of Khazran"
msgstr "Regalo de Khazran"

#. [object]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/08_Isanbar.cfg:547
msgid "The prismatic horn of Khazran grants +2 damage."
msgstr "El cuerno prismático de Khazran otorga +2 de daño."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/08_Isanbar.cfg:565
msgid "Sleep well, brother. For we shall meet again."
msgstr "Duerme bien, hermano. Porque nos volveremos a encontrar."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/08_Isanbar.cfg:570
msgid ""
"The voice. It bears the signature of the Sphere. It is decimating us one by "
"one. It wants to destroy us."
msgstr ""
"La voz. Lleva la firma de la Esfera. Nos está diezmando uno por uno. Quiere "
"destruirnos."

#. [message], speaker=Sinan
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/08_Isanbar.cfg:575
msgid ""
"The Three Kings were speaking through the body of Khazran. I still remember "
"their voices. Are they returning? Then the prophecies are true?"
msgstr ""
"Los Tres Reyes hablaban a través del cuerpo de Khazran. Aún recuerdo sus "
"voces. ¿Están regresando? ¿Entonces las profecías son ciertas?"

#. [message], speaker=Iskandar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/08_Isanbar.cfg:580
msgid ""
"Then we have to take action now. I will warn the Dune Warmaster of Serrul, "
"for his purpose is not yet fulfilled. Ilarøth and Ilriel, march through the "
"ancient prisons underneath this mighty mountain of Isanbar, that for a long "
"time compensated our loss of the Sphere, and covertly sneak past the powers "
"of the sands. The Sphere is watching us. We will meet in the ruins of "
"K'thar, next to the Cloud River. Expect me there."
msgstr ""
"Entonces debemos actuar ahora. Advertiré al Maestro de Guerra de Serrul, "
"porque su propósito aún no se ha cumplido. Ilarøth e Ilriel, marchen a "
"través de las antiguas prisiones debajo de esta poderosa montaña de Isanbar, "
"que durante mucho tiempo compensó nuestra pérdida de la Esfera, y "
"escabúllanse en secreto más allá de los poderes de las arenas. La Esfera nos "
"observa. Nos encontraremos en las ruinas de K'thar, junto al Río de las "
"Nubes. Espérenme allí."

#. [message], speaker=Iskandar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/08_Isanbar.cfg:585
msgid ""
"Yet you can't go alone, your loyal soldiers shall accompany you, they shall "
"not fall in the upcoming battle at Serrul."
msgstr ""
"Sin embargo, no pueden ir solos, sus leales soldados los acompañarán, no "
"deben caer en la próxima batalla en Serrul."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/08_Isanbar.cfg:620
msgid "Then let us take wings, Ilriel."
msgstr "Entonces tomemos alas, Ilriel."

#. [message], speaker=Sinan
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/08_Isanbar.cfg:626
msgid ""
"The Sphere has its eye right above us! Ilarøth and Ilriel, hurry up! We "
"shall protect you!"
msgstr ""
"¡La Esfera tiene su ojo justo sobre nosotros! ¡Ilarøth e Ilriel, apúrense! "
"¡Los protegeremos!"

#. [message], speaker=Sinan
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/08_Isanbar.cfg:631
msgid "Brothers! Cast the shield!"
msgstr "¡Hermanos! ¡Lancen el escudo!"

#. [message], speaker=Sinan
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/08_Isanbar.cfg:636
msgid "And Ilarøth, might the power of the Athvari be with you."
msgstr "Y Ilarøth, que el poder de los athvari esté contigo."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/08_Isanbar.cfg:641
msgid "Ilriel, quick!"
msgstr "¡Ilriel, rápido!"

#. [message], speaker=Khazran
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/08_Isanbar.cfg:696
msgid "Do you really thought you could overcome the inevitable?"
msgstr "¿Realmente pensaron que podían vencer lo inevitable?"

#. [message], speaker=Iskandar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/08_Isanbar.cfg:703
msgid "You cannot fight against us!"
msgstr "¡No pueden luchar contra nosotros!"

#. [part]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/09_Shadows_of_Isanbar.cfg:7
msgid ""
"The clouds became darker than usual. The ones coming are already near. Now "
"allow me to tell you a story. The story of an . . ."
msgstr ""
"Las nubes se volvieron más oscuras de lo habitual. Los que vienen ya están "
"cerca. Ahora permítanme contarles una historia. La historia de un..."

#. [scenario], id=09_Shadows_of_Isanbar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/09_Shadows_of_Isanbar.cfg:22
msgid "Shadows of Isanbar"
msgstr "Sombras de Isanbar"

#. [side]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/09_Shadows_of_Isanbar.cfg:64
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/15_Blackhands.cfg:197
msgid "Prisoners"
msgstr "Prisioneros"

#. [side], type=Apparition
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/09_Shadows_of_Isanbar.cfg:83
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/09_Shadows_of_Isanbar.cfg:88
msgid "Au'la"
msgstr "Au'la"

#. [event]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/09_Shadows_of_Isanbar.cfg:147
msgid "Aildar"
msgstr "Aildar"

#. [event]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/09_Shadows_of_Isanbar.cfg:148
msgid "Nirkend"
msgstr "Nirkend"

#. [unit], id=Karlensog, type=Red Mage
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/09_Shadows_of_Isanbar.cfg:178
msgid "Karlensog"
msgstr "Karlensog"

#. [message], speaker=Karlensog
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/09_Shadows_of_Isanbar.cfg:191
msgid "Hmmpf! Screw those Athvari! They've got the wrong one!"
msgstr "¡Hmmpf! ¡Al diablo con esos athvari! ¡Han atrapado al equivocado!"

#. [message], speaker=Uthain
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/09_Shadows_of_Isanbar.cfg:196
msgid "Seems like nobody belongs to this place . . ."
msgstr "Parece que nadie pertenece a este lugar..."

#. [message], speaker=Karlensog
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/09_Shadows_of_Isanbar.cfg:201
msgid "Ugh? A dwarf? May the gods have mercy with me!"
msgstr "¿Ugh? ¿Un enano? ¡Que los dioses se apiaden de mí!"

#. [message], speaker=Uthain
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/09_Shadows_of_Isanbar.cfg:206
msgid "Uh-uh?"
msgstr "¿Uh-uh?"

#. [message], speaker=Karlensog
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/09_Shadows_of_Isanbar.cfg:211
msgid ""
"I can tolerate this prison and I can tolerate rotting in this forsaken "
"place! But I can't bear with a dwarf!"
msgstr ""
"¡Puedo tolerar esta prisión y puedo tolerar pudrirme en este lugar "
"abandonado! ¡Pero no puedo soportar a un enano!"

#. [message], speaker=Nirkend
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/09_Shadows_of_Isanbar.cfg:216
msgid "Oh, Karlensog. You've lost your mind!"
msgstr "Oh, Karlensog. ¡Has perdido la cabeza!"

#. [message], speaker=Uthain
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/09_Shadows_of_Isanbar.cfg:221
msgid "I'm sure he never had one!"
msgstr "¡Estoy seguro de que nunca tuvo una!"

#. [message], speaker=Karlensog
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/09_Shadows_of_Isanbar.cfg:226
msgid "Wait! Wait! A mind?! Yes . . . yes . . . Where is it? Hey there!"
msgstr "¡Espera! ¡Espera! ¿Una mente? ¡Sí... sí... ¿Dónde está? ¡Hey allí!"

#. [message], speaker=Karlensog
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/09_Shadows_of_Isanbar.cfg:231
msgid "No . . . no . . . where is it? Is it here?"
msgstr "No... no... ¿dónde está? ¿Está aquí?"

#. [message], speaker=Karlensog
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/09_Shadows_of_Isanbar.cfg:236
msgid "Ah, there it is! Come here!"
msgstr "¡Ah, aquí está! ¡Ven aquí!"

#. [message], speaker=Uthain
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/09_Shadows_of_Isanbar.cfg:241
msgid "That's a rat, you fool."
msgstr "Eso es una rata, idiota."

#. [message], speaker=Karlensog
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/09_Shadows_of_Isanbar.cfg:246
msgid "Ah? Uh? Is it?"
msgstr "¿Ah? ¿Uh? ¿Lo es?"

#. [message], speaker=Karlensog
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/09_Shadows_of_Isanbar.cfg:251
msgid "You're having me on!"
msgstr "¡Me estás tomando el pelo!"

#. [message], speaker=Karlensog
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/09_Shadows_of_Isanbar.cfg:256
msgid ""
"Ex . . . excuse me. The methods of the Athvari . . . they did strange things "
"to me . . ."
msgstr ""
"Ex... disculpen. Los métodos de los athvari... me hicieron cosas extrañas..."

#. [message], speaker=Karlensog
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/09_Shadows_of_Isanbar.cfg:261
msgid "But no! No! Don't leave me here! The walls are coming closer! Quick!"
msgstr "¡Pero no! ¡No! ¡No me dejen aquí! ¡Las paredes se acercan! ¡Rápido!"

#. [message], speaker=Uthain
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/09_Shadows_of_Isanbar.cfg:273
msgid "Hmpfh, it'd be better for our sanity to just keep him locked up here."
msgstr "Hmpfh, sería mejor para nuestra cordura mantenerlo encerrado aquí."

#. [message], speaker=Aula
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/09_Shadows_of_Isanbar.cfg:284
msgid "Oh, Nirkend, you're visiting me?"
msgstr "Oh, Nirkend, ¿vienes a visitarme?"

#. [message], speaker=Nirkend
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/09_Shadows_of_Isanbar.cfg:289
msgid ""
"We are in need of your help, Au'la. The presence of the Sphere is slowly "
"crawling towards these depths. You've experienced it once."
msgstr ""
"Necesitamos tu ayuda, Au'la. La presencia de la Esfera se arrastra "
"lentamente hacia estas profundidades. Ya la has experimentado una vez."

#. [message], speaker=Aula
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/09_Shadows_of_Isanbar.cfg:294
msgid "And yet it was of no harm to me."
msgstr "Y sin embargo no me hizo daño."

#. [message], speaker=Nirkend
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/09_Shadows_of_Isanbar.cfg:299
msgid "You're the only one being immune to its magic. We need you."
msgstr "Eres la única inmune a su magia. Te necesitamos."

#. [message], speaker=Aula
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/09_Shadows_of_Isanbar.cfg:304
msgid ""
"All your lifes are like a marionette whose strings lay in my hands? We could "
"just end it here. One cut - and the marionette will fall down, only waiting "
"to be covered by dust to be forgotten for all times. You'll be playing by "
"the rules I laid down."
msgstr ""
"¿Todas sus vidas son como una marioneta cuyos hilos están en mis manos? "
"Podríamos terminarlo aquí. Un corte, y la marioneta caerá, solo esperando "
"ser cubierta de polvo para ser olvidada por siempre. Ustedes jugarán según "
"las reglas que yo establezca."

#. [message], speaker=Nirkend
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/09_Shadows_of_Isanbar.cfg:309
msgid "What is it, that you demand?"
msgstr "¿Qué es lo que exiges?"

#. [message], speaker=Aula
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/09_Shadows_of_Isanbar.cfg:314
msgid ""
"Your kin knows that I am imprisoned, not by the walls and bars of this "
"prison, but by my earthly manifestation. For too long am I bound and I want "
"you to set me free when the time is right. The wind shall bear my very "
"existence to unknown places. Swear to do so and I will help you to find a "
"way out."
msgstr ""
"Tu linaje sabe que estoy prisionera, no por las paredes y barrotes de esta "
"prisión, sino por mi manifestación terrenal. Demasiado tiempo estoy atada y "
"quiero que me liberes cuando sea el momento adecuado. El viento llevará mi "
"propia existencia a lugares desconocidos. Jura hacerlo y te ayudaré a "
"encontrar una salida."

#. [message], speaker=Nuvdael
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/09_Shadows_of_Isanbar.cfg:319
msgid "Wait! So she is not . . ."
msgstr "¡Espera! Entonces ella no es..."

#. [message], speaker=Uthain
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/09_Shadows_of_Isanbar.cfg:324
msgid ""
"There are things out there, that our kins do not understand, elf. Things, "
"that are not bound to the laws of the earth."
msgstr ""
"Hay cosas allá afuera que nuestros linajes no entienden, elfa. Cosas que no "
"están sujetas a las leyes de la tierra."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/09_Shadows_of_Isanbar.cfg:329
msgid ""
"If setting her free is our only way to have a chance at wresting the Sphere, "
"then so shall it be. Even if I am scared at what lurks inside her."
msgstr ""
"Si liberarla es nuestra única forma de tener una oportunidad de arrebatar la "
"Esfera, que así sea. Aunque me asuste lo que acecha dentro de ella."

#. [message], speaker=Nirkend
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/09_Shadows_of_Isanbar.cfg:334
msgid ""
"We will adhere to your demands then, Au'la. Aildar, I'll need your help."
msgstr "Entonces cumpliremos tus demandas, Au'la. Aildar, necesitaré tu ayuda."

#. [message], speaker=Aildar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/09_Shadows_of_Isanbar.cfg:339
msgid "I am right here. Let us do this."
msgstr "Estoy aquí. Hagámoslo."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/09_Shadows_of_Isanbar.cfg:347
msgid "Nirkend and Aildar are channeling their magic."
msgstr "Nirkend y Aildar están canalizando su magia."

#. [message], speaker=Aula
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/09_Shadows_of_Isanbar.cfg:405
msgid "Free! Free once again!"
msgstr "¡Libre! ¡Libre una vez más!"

#. [message], speaker=Nirkend
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/09_Shadows_of_Isanbar.cfg:410
msgid ""
"Not yet. You're still bound to your oath. You have to get us out of here now."
msgstr ""
"Todavía no. Sigues atada a tu juramento. Tienes que sacarnos de aquí ahora."

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/09_Shadows_of_Isanbar.cfg:432
msgid ""
"Leave the prison of Isanbar by moving Ilriel or Ilaroth to the signpost in "
"the north"
msgstr ""
"Abandona la prisión de Isanbar moviendo a Ilriel o Ilaroth al poste de "
"señalización del norte"

#. [objective], condition=lose
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/09_Shadows_of_Isanbar.cfg:437
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/09_Shadows_of_Isanbar.cfg:581
msgid "Nirkend or Aildar dies"
msgstr "Nirkend o Aildar muere"

#. [note]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/09_Shadows_of_Isanbar.cfg:446
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/09_Shadows_of_Isanbar.cfg:590
msgid "You can open certain prison doors by walking on a red icon."
msgstr "Puedes abrir ciertas puertas de prisión caminando sobre un ícono rojo."

#. [message], speaker=Aula
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/09_Shadows_of_Isanbar.cfg:461
msgid "That's the way out. It leads to K'thar."
msgstr "Ese es el camino de salida. Lleva a K'thar."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/09_Shadows_of_Isanbar.cfg:466
msgid "To K'thar? I did not expect Isanbar to have a passage to K'thar."
msgstr "¿A K'thar? No esperaba que Isanbar tuviera un pasaje a K'thar."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/09_Shadows_of_Isanbar.cfg:501
msgid ""
"Forsooth, this has to be the prison of Isanbar. I heard stories being told "
"about it, yet I never had the chance to confirm them."
msgstr ""
"Por supuesto, esta debe ser la prisión de Isanbar. Escuché historias sobre "
"ella, pero nunca tuve la oportunidad de confirmarlas."

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/09_Shadows_of_Isanbar.cfg:506
msgid "Who is imprisoned here?"
msgstr "¿Quién está prisionero aquí?"

#. [message], speaker=Nirkend
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/09_Shadows_of_Isanbar.cfg:514
msgid ""
"Servants of the three kings and whoever sided with them or stood in our way "
"to find the Sphere."
msgstr ""
"Servidores de los tres reyes y cualquiera que se puso de su lado o se "
"interpuso en nuestro camino para encontrar la Esfera."

#. [message], speaker=Nirkend
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/09_Shadows_of_Isanbar.cfg:519
msgid ""
"Welcome Ilaroth, it is nice to meet you again. Yet it is unfortunate to meet "
"at this . . . place."
msgstr ""
"Bienvenido Ilaroth, es bueno verte de nuevo. Sin embargo, es desafortunado "
"encontrarnos en este... lugar."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/09_Shadows_of_Isanbar.cfg:524
msgid "Nirkend? Aildar? It must've been years since we last met."
msgstr ""
"¿Nirkend? ¿Aildar? Deben haber pasado años desde la última vez que nos vimos."

#. [message], speaker=Nirkend
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/09_Shadows_of_Isanbar.cfg:529
msgid ""
"Any mage, any foe of the Athvari ended up here instead of within the Sphere, "
"when the Sphere got seized from our hands. As we couldn't rely on the Sphere "
"to inhibit the magic of the prisoners, we had to delegate Athvari to take "
"care of the imprisoned ones."
msgstr ""
"Cualquier mago, cualquier enemigo de los athvari terminó aquí en lugar de "
"dentro de la Esfera, cuando la Esfera fue arrebatada de nuestras manos. Como "
"no podíamos confiar en la Esfera para inhibir la magia de los prisioneros, "
"tuvimos que delegar athvari para cuidar de los encarcelados."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/09_Shadows_of_Isanbar.cfg:534
msgid "And I see that you're doing well."
msgstr "Y veo que están bien."

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/09_Shadows_of_Isanbar.cfg:539
msgid ""
"These are chambers of pain and sorrow. What is happening within these halls?"
msgstr ""
"Estas son cámaras de dolor y tristeza. ¿Qué está pasando dentro de estos "
"salones?"

#. [message], speaker=Nirkend
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/09_Shadows_of_Isanbar.cfg:544
msgid ""
"For a long time, we are trying to find out more about the Sphere and where "
"it is. Yet some beings refuse to talk about it . . . we needed a tool "
"to . . . convince . . . them to speak. Some wouldn't talk, others wouldn't "
"know that they indeed . . . know more than is known to them. The grace of "
"the Sphere has burned into their memories and we are here to extract exactly "
"that and hope that the memories will lead us to the Sphere."
msgstr ""
"Durante mucho tiempo, intentamos descubrir más sobre la Esfera y dónde está. "
"Sin embargo, algunos seres se niegan a hablar de ella... necesitábamos una "
"herramienta para... convencerlos... de hablar. Algunos no hablarían, otros "
"no sabrían que en realidad... saben más de lo que se sabe. La gracia de la "
"Esfera se ha quemado en sus memorias y estamos aquí para extraer exactamente "
"eso y esperar que las memorias nos lleven a la Esfera."

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/09_Shadows_of_Isanbar.cfg:549
msgid "Break in the memories of the defeated? What a horrible thing to do."
msgstr " ¿Invadir las memorias de los derrotados? Qué cosa tan horrible."

#. [message], speaker=Nirkend
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/09_Shadows_of_Isanbar.cfg:554
msgid ""
"They are not the victims. Most of the imprisoned ones once swore allegiance "
"to the three kings. They deserve much worse."
msgstr ""
"Ellos no son las víctimas. La mayoría de los prisioneros una vez juraron "
"lealtad a los tres reyes. Merecen algo mucho peor."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/09_Shadows_of_Isanbar.cfg:559
msgid ""
"And now we have all the answers that we are searching for. The three kings "
"might return to these earthly plains and their power is able to outreach the "
"boundaries of the Sphere. Isanbar is in great danger, we have to get out of "
"here."
msgstr ""
"Y ahora tenemos todas las respuestas que buscábamos. Los tres reyes podrían "
"regresar a estas llanuras terrenales y su poder puede extenderse más allá de "
"los límites de la Esfera. Isanbar está en gran peligro, tenemos que salir de "
"aquí."

#. [message], speaker=Nirkend
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/09_Shadows_of_Isanbar.cfg:564
msgid ""
"It is always a problem to leave a prison that is not meant to be left. The "
"ancient passages that lead out of the prison and beneath the sands of the "
"great desert are blocked up by stone and metal alike. But I know one who "
"could get us out of here. Her name is Au'la."
msgstr ""
"Siempre es un problema salir de una prisión que no está hecha para ser "
"abandonada. Los pasajes antiguos que llevan fuera de la prisión y debajo de "
"las arenas del gran desierto están bloqueados por piedra y metal por igual. "
"Pero conozco a alguien que podría sacarnos de aquí. Su nombre es Au'la."

#. [message], speaker=Nirkend
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/09_Shadows_of_Isanbar.cfg:569
msgid "And she is an imprisoned one. We'll find her in a cell. Follow me."
msgstr "Y ella es una prisionera. La encontraremos en una celda. Síganme."

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/09_Shadows_of_Isanbar.cfg:576
msgid "Find Au'la"
msgstr "Encuentra a Au'la"

#. [note]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/09_Shadows_of_Isanbar.cfg:593
msgid "You can recruit units in the middle of the map."
msgstr "Puedes reclutar unidades en el centro del mapa."

#. [message], speaker=Nuvdael
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/09_Shadows_of_Isanbar.cfg:608
msgid ""
"These are not normal undead! They are sturdier, slower, yet filled with "
"blackness."
msgstr ""
"¡Estos no son no-muertos normales! Son más resistentes, más lentos, pero "
"llenos de oscuridad."

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/09_Shadows_of_Isanbar.cfg:613
msgid "And darkness is what we will purge out of them!"
msgstr "¡Y oscuridad es lo que purificaremos de ellos!"

#. [message], speaker=Nuvdael
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/09_Shadows_of_Isanbar.cfg:618
msgid ""
"Don't let their appearance fool you. They might be slow, yet your magic "
"won't harm them. I can still feel their magical presence. These creatures "
"once were mages, but their hearts are filled with evil now. Watch out!"
msgstr ""
"No dejen que su apariencia los engañe. Pueden ser lentos, pero tu magia no "
"les hará daño. Todavía puedo sentir su presencia mágica. Estas criaturas una "
"vez fueron magos, pero ahora sus corazones están llenos de maldad. ¡Cuidado!"

#. [message], speaker=Uthain
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/09_Shadows_of_Isanbar.cfg:628
msgid ""
"Aye, this place stinks of death and darkness. You said Au'la is a woman? "
"What is a woman searching down here? What did she do to end up being locked "
"up here?"
msgstr ""
"¡Sí, este lugar apesta a muerte y oscuridad! ¿Dijiste que Au'la es una "
"mujer? ¿Qué hace una mujer buscando aquí abajo? ¿Qué hizo para terminar "
"encerrada aquí?"

#. [message], speaker=Nirkend
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/09_Shadows_of_Isanbar.cfg:633
msgid ""
"When we reconstructed the way that the Sphere took after wresting free from "
"our magic, she was the first one to encounter it in the vastness of the "
"deserts. Yet the magic of the Sphere did not harm her. We do not know how, "
"but it just did not affect her, while the surroundings burned to ashes, "
"devastated by the magic of the Sphere. And we needed to understand why."
msgstr ""
"Cuando reconstruimos el camino que tomó la Esfera después de liberarse de "
"nuestra magia, ella fue la primera en encontrarla en la vastedad de los "
"desiertos. Sin embargo, la magia de la Esfera no le hizo daño. No sabemos "
"cómo, pero simplemente no la afectó, mientras los alrededores se quemaban "
"hasta las cenizas, devastados por la magia de la Esfera. Y necesitábamos "
"entender por qué."

#. [message], speaker=Uthain
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/09_Shadows_of_Isanbar.cfg:638
msgid "Aight, a magical lady! And did you find out why she resisted it?"
msgstr "¡Bien, una dama mágica! ¿Y descubrieron por qué ella resistió?"

#. [message], speaker=Nirkend
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/09_Shadows_of_Isanbar.cfg:643
msgid ""
"Even the wisest of the Athvari are not sure. Some suggest, that she is not a "
"living being, she's rather a . . . a projection of something bigger. Of "
"something that lies behind the curtains of uncertainty."
msgstr ""
"Incluso los más sabios de los athvari no están seguros. Algunos sugieren que "
"ella no es un ser vivo, sino más bien una... proyección de algo más grande. "
"De algo que yace detrás de las cortinas de la incertidumbre."

#. [message], speaker=Uthain
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/09_Shadows_of_Isanbar.cfg:653
msgid ""
"Aye, elf! Forsooth this is no place for your kin! Neither is it for my "
"people."
msgstr ""
"¡Sí, elfa! ¡Por supuesto que este no es lugar para los tuyos! Tampoco lo es "
"para mi pueblo."

#. [message], speaker=Nuvdael
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/09_Shadows_of_Isanbar.cfg:658
msgid ""
"What's the difference anyway? Your people lurk in the depths, surrounded by "
"stone and rocks. And here . . . we are surrounded by bars. Both are "
"imprisoning."
msgstr ""
"¿Qué diferencia hay de todos modos? Tu pueblo se esconde en las "
"profundidades, rodeado de piedra y rocas. Y aquí... estamos rodeados de "
"barrotes. Ambos son prisiones."

#. [message], speaker=Uthain
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/09_Shadows_of_Isanbar.cfg:663
msgid ""
"Arhh! A dwarf can move through the earth like an elf through the winds! "
"Rocks don't pose a threat to us!"
msgstr ""
"¡Arhh! ¡Un enano puede moverse a través de la tierra como un elfo a través "
"de los vientos! ¡Las rocas no representan una amenaza para nosotros!"

#. [message], speaker=Uthain
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/09_Shadows_of_Isanbar.cfg:668
msgid ""
"But you . . . elf! This is no place for you! I can see it . . . but don't "
"worry . . . a dwarf is here. And although our kin don't like each other, "
"I'll make an exception for you. For now."
msgstr ""
"¡Pero tú... elfa! ¡Este no es lugar para ti! Puedo verlo... pero no te "
"preocupes... aquí hay un enano. Y aunque nuestros pueblos no se agradan, "
"haré una excepción contigo. Por ahora."

#. [message], speaker=Nuvdael
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/09_Shadows_of_Isanbar.cfg:673
msgid "Big words, small dwarf. You're speaking to the High King of the elves."
msgstr ""
"Grandes palabras, enano pequeño. Estás hablando con el Gran Rey de los elfos."

#. [message], speaker=Uthain
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/09_Shadows_of_Isanbar.cfg:678
msgid ""
"A High King, you say? I've never heard about such a guy. But then again, "
"rumor don't spread across the lands. They stay inside the forests."
msgstr ""
"¿Un Gran Rey, dices? Nunca había oído de alguien así. Pero bueno, los "
"rumores no se esparcen por las tierras. Se quedan dentro de los bosques."

#. [message], speaker=Nirkend
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/09_Shadows_of_Isanbar.cfg:683
msgid ""
"I don't want to interrupt you, but the darkness thickens. We should not stay "
"longer in here than needed. The powers of the Sphere might slowly overcome "
"the magical boundaries, that is keeping the darkness in place. "
msgstr ""
"No quiero interrumpirlos, pero la oscuridad se espesa. No deberíamos "
"quedarnos aquí más tiempo del necesario. Los poderes de la Esfera podrían "
"lentamente superar las barreras mágicas que mantienen la oscuridad en su "
"lugar."

#. [message], speaker=Uthain
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/09_Shadows_of_Isanbar.cfg:688
msgid ""
"Aye, then you'll have to shed light on your role sometime later, 'High King' "
"Nuvdael!"
msgstr ""
"¡Sí, entonces tendrás que aclarar tu rol en algún momento después, «Gran "
"Rey» Nuvdael!"

#. [message], speaker=Aula
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/09_Shadows_of_Isanbar.cfg:697
msgid "Right, that's the way that'll lead us out of here."
msgstr "Correcto, ese es el camino que nos sacará de aquí."

#. [message], speaker=Nirkend
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/09_Shadows_of_Isanbar.cfg:702
msgid "Thank you for showing us."
msgstr "Gracias por mostrárnoslo."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/09_Shadows_of_Isanbar.cfg:723
msgid "We'll never get out of here in time!"
msgstr "¡Nunca saldremos de aquí a tiempo!"

#. [part]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/10_Gaze_of_the_Three.cfg:7
msgid ""
"The group was amazed by the light that emerged from Au'la. The once dark "
"caves became enlightened and it seemed as it was day. Unfortunately, the "
"passages of the prison were longer than expected. After walking for what "
"seemed like days, but also could've been weeks, they finally reached a grand "
"hall."
msgstr ""
"El grupo quedó asombrado por la luz que emanaba de Au'la. Las cuevas antes "
"oscuras se iluminaron y parecía de día. Desafortunadamente, los pasajes de "
"la prisión eran más largos de lo esperado. Después de caminar lo que "
"parecían días, pero también podrían haber sido semanas, finalmente llegaron "
"a un gran salón."

#. [scenario], id=10_Gaze_of_the_Three
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/10_Gaze_of_the_Three.cfg:19
msgid "Gaze of the Three"
msgstr "Mirada de los Tres"

#. [side], type=Yrialdhe
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/10_Gaze_of_the_Three.cfg:66
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/10_Gaze_of_the_Three.cfg:73
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/11_Root_of_Evil.cfg:61
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/11_Root_of_Evil.cfg:68
msgid "Yrialdhe"
msgstr "Yrialdhe"

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/10_Gaze_of_the_Three.cfg:148
msgid ""
"The catacombs of K'thar! I never thought they were connected to the depths "
"of Isanbar. This has to be the throne room. We are close to the ruins of "
"K'thar and next to the Cloud River. Let us get out of here, Iskandar expects "
"us outside."
msgstr ""
"¡Las catacumbas de K'thar! Nunca pensé que estuvieran conectadas con las "
"profundidades de Isanbar. Este debe ser el salón del trono. Estamos cerca de "
"las ruinas de K'thar y junto al Río de las Nubes. Salgamos de aquí, Iskandar "
"nos espera afuera."

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/10_Gaze_of_the_Three.cfg:153
msgid ""
"K'thar. Then this was the place the Three Kings resided in and ruled the "
"lands with a reign of terror."
msgstr ""
"K'thar. Entonces este fue el lugar donde residieron los Tres Reyes y "
"gobernaron las tierras con un reinado de terror."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/10_Gaze_of_the_Three.cfg:158
msgid ""
"Exactly, this is the place where my brothers caught them and threw them into "
"the Sphere. One can still feel the presence of the magic once cast. The "
"walls, the sand and even the air seem to have taken up the magic."
msgstr ""
"Exacto, este es el lugar donde mis hermanos los capturaron y los arrojaron a "
"la Esfera. Todavía se puede sentir la presencia de la magia que una vez se "
"lanzó. Las paredes, la arena e incluso el aire parecen haber absorbido la "
"magia."

#. [message], speaker=Nuvdael
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/10_Gaze_of_the_Three.cfg:163
msgid ""
"Forsooth, this place invokes fear. Let us move out of here, the darkness is "
"slowly creeping onto our feet."
msgstr ""
"Por supuesto, este lugar invoca miedo. Salgamos de aquí, la oscuridad se "
"arrastra lentamente hacia nuestros pies."

#. [message], speaker=Aula
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/10_Gaze_of_the_Three.cfg:168
msgid ""
"Indeed we are not alone in these depths. An ancient being lurks inside here, "
"already waiting for us."
msgstr ""
"En verdad no estamos solos en estas profundidades. Un ser antiguo acecha "
"aquí adentro, ya esperándonos."

#. [message], speaker=Uthain
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/10_Gaze_of_the_Three.cfg:182
msgid "A'ight! I smell treasures of old times! Very old, ooh!"
msgstr "¡Bien! ¡Huelo tesoros de tiempos antiguos! Muy antiguos, ¡ooh!"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/10_Gaze_of_the_Three.cfg:189
msgid "Defeat the enemy leader"
msgstr "Derrota al líder enemigo"

#. [note]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/10_Gaze_of_the_Three.cfg:199
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/10_Gaze_of_the_Three.cfg:276
msgid ""
"You may set braziers on fire, which will then result in a bonus for nearby "
"lawful units for one turn."
msgstr ""
"Puedes encender braseros, lo que otorgará un bono a las unidades legales "
"cercanas durante un turno."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/10_Gaze_of_the_Three.cfg:218
msgid ""
"Those bones look like a remnant spell of the caverns old inhabitants! Watch "
"out!"
msgstr ""
"¡Esos huesos parecen un hechizo residual de los antiguos habitantes de las "
"cavernas! ¡Cuidado!"

#. [message], speaker=Uthain
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/10_Gaze_of_the_Three.cfg:236
msgid "In the name of the beards of the wisest, what is THAT?"
msgstr "¡En nombre de las barbas de los más sabios, ¿qué es ESO?!"

#. [message], speaker=Nuvdael
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/10_Gaze_of_the_Three.cfg:249
msgid "An abyssmal creature! Both woman and snake?"
msgstr "¡Una criatura abismal! ¿Tanto mujer como serpiente?"

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/10_Gaze_of_the_Three.cfg:254
msgid ""
"Yrialdhe, the first general of the three kings and created by their very own "
"magical powers. Don't let her appearance fool you, she led the charge "
"against the forces of Serrul, Kesh and Th'arwya, when their forces intended "
"to overthrow the three kings. She is responsible for one of the worst "
"massacres of our time."
msgstr ""
"Yrialdhe, la primera general de los tres reyes y creada por sus propios "
"poderes mágicos. No dejen que su apariencia los engañe, ella lideró la carga "
"contra las fuerzas de Serrul, Kesh y Th'arwya, cuando sus fuerzas intentaron "
"derrocar a los tres reyes. Es responsable de una de las peores masacres de "
"nuestro tiempo."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/10_Gaze_of_the_Three.cfg:259
msgid "One glimpse of her and one turns into stone. Don't look into her eyes!"
msgstr "Un vistazo de ella y uno se convierte en piedra. ¡No miren sus ojos!"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/10_Gaze_of_the_Three.cfg:266
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/11_Root_of_Evil.cfg:389
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/11_Root_of_Evil.cfg:454
msgid "Defeat Yrialdhe"
msgstr "Derrota a Yrialdhe"

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/10_Gaze_of_the_Three.cfg:287
msgid ""
"The throne room of the Three Kings. For a long time, they were responsible "
"for the pain and hate that roamed these lands. Their reign made the people "
"of the desert realms fearful of the power that few individuals could have, "
"that's why the desert realms got split once the reign of the Three Kings "
"ended. So, tell me, Nuvdael, why does your kin obey to you?"
msgstr ""
"El salón del trono de los Tres Reyes. Durante mucho tiempo fueron "
"responsables del dolor y el odio que recorrió estas tierras. Su reinado hizo "
"que el pueblo de los reinos del desierto temiera el poder que pocos "
"individuos podían tener, por eso los reinos del desierto se dividieron una "
"vez que terminó el reinado de los Tres Reyes. Así que dime, Nuvdael, ¿por "
"qué tu pueblo te obedece?"

#. [message], speaker=Uthain
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/10_Gaze_of_the_Three.cfg:292
msgid ""
"Right, ye still owe me that story of how ye elves ended up with a High King!"
msgstr ""
"¡Cierto, todavía me debes esa historia de cómo ustedes los elfos terminaron "
"con un Gran Rey!"

#. [message], speaker=Nuvdael
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/10_Gaze_of_the_Three.cfg:297
msgid ""
"Usually the elves are led by a council and by the advice of sages. Centuries "
"ago, the Southwoods were inhabited by elves, but not the kind of elves that "
"currently live inside those woods. Shadows from the black forests soon held "
"the Southwoods in a tight grip, enslaving the poor souls that once lived "
"there and the council of the Aethenwoods, the woods of my origin, did "
"nothing to stop the darkness from crawling into the Southwoods. Instead,they "
"made a pact with the sorcerers of the Black Forest, as they were ready to "
"give away the lives of the elves of the Southwoods in exchange for an "
"artifact that once belonged to them."
msgstr ""
"Normalmente los elfos son liderados por un consejo y por el consejo de "
"sabios. Hace siglos, los Bosques del Sur estaban habitados por elfos, pero "
"no del tipo de elfos que actualmente viven dentro de esos bosques. Sombras "
"de los bosques negros pronto sujetaron fuertemente los Bosques del Sur, "
"esclavizando a las pobres almas que una vez vivieron allí y el consejo de "
"los Bosques de Edén, los bosques de mi origen, no hizo nada para detener la "
"oscuridad que se arrastraba hacia los Bosques del Sur. En cambio, hicieron "
"un pacto con los hechiceros del Bosque Negro, ya que estaban dispuestos a "
"entregar las vidas de los elfos de los Bosques del Sur a cambio de un "
"artefacto que una vez les perteneció."

#. [message], speaker=Nuvdael
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/10_Gaze_of_the_Three.cfg:302
msgid ""
"They gave away the lives of their own brothers, which I couldn't accept, so "
"I formed a resistance with several other elves. That was the reason the "
"council forced me to leave my home. Being ruled by a council may imply that "
"there is never a time when darkness overtakes every one of them, but they "
"were wrong, nevertheless. In the end, they were consumed by it and it was my "
"task to strike back the darkness. With no more than 12 elves, I marched into "
"the Southwoods, fought back the shadows and corrupted souls of the ones that "
"once were my brothers and reclaimed it. The darkness was no longer."
msgstr ""
"Entregaron las vidas de sus propios hermanos, lo que no pude aceptar, así "
"que formé una resistencia con varios otros elfos. Esa fue la razón por la "
"que el consejo me obligó a dejar mi hogar. Ser gobernados por un consejo "
"puede implicar que nunca haya un momento en que la oscuridad los domine a "
"todos, pero se equivocaron. Al final, fueron consumidos por ella y fue mi "
"tarea rechazar la oscuridad. Con no más de 12 elfos, marché hacia los "
"Bosques del Sur, luché contra las sombras y las almas corruptas de quienes "
"una vez fueron mis hermanos y lo reclamé. La oscuridad ya no estaba."

#. [message], speaker=Nuvdael
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/10_Gaze_of_the_Three.cfg:307
msgid ""
"And there in the woods, surrounded by darkness, was Ilriel. The heart of the "
"Southwoods. Some say forests consist of thousands of individuals, but that's "
"not true for all forests. She had been weakened by the dark arts of the "
"sorcerers and that accelerated the forests decay alarmingly. However, after "
"defeating the sorcerers, she regained her health and the elves who were not "
"ready to live under the banner of the betrayers of the council on the "
"Aethenwoods moved to live in the Southwoods."
msgstr ""
"Y allí en los bosques, rodeada de oscuridad, estaba Ilriel. El corazón de "
"los Bosques del Sur. Algunos dicen que los bosques consisten en miles de "
"individuos, pero eso no es cierto para todos los bosques. Ella había sido "
"debilitada por las artes oscuras de los hechiceros y eso aceleró "
"alarmantemente la decadencia del bosque. Sin embargo, después de derrotar a "
"los hechiceros, recuperó su salud y los elfos que no estaban dispuestos a "
"vivir bajo la bandera de los traidores del consejo en los Bosques de Edén se "
"mudaron a vivir en los Bosques del Sur."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/10_Gaze_of_the_Three.cfg:312
msgid ""
"A king, that became king not by the blood that is flowing in his veins but "
"by his deeds."
msgstr ""
"Un rey que se convirtió en rey no por la sangre que corre por sus venas sino "
"por sus acciones."

#. [message], speaker=Nuvdael
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/10_Gaze_of_the_Three.cfg:317
msgid ""
"After cleansing the Southwoods from the darkness, we returned to the "
"Aethenwoods to bring forth the downfall of the betrayers. And since that "
"time, the shackles that held the elves down and bound them to the darkness "
"were broken. And they accepted me as a high king, the king of both the "
"Southwoods and the Aethenwoods, the king of the elves of the southwest."
msgstr ""
"Después de limpiar los Bosques del Sur de la oscuridad, regresamos a los "
"Bosques de Edén para provocar la caída de los traidores. Y desde ese tiempo, "
"las cadenas que sujetaban a los elfos y los ataban a la oscuridad se "
"rompieron. Y me aceptaron como gran rey, el rey de tanto los Bosques del Sur "
"como los Bosques de Edén, el rey de los elfos del suroeste."

#. [message], speaker=Uthain
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/10_Gaze_of_the_Three.cfg:330
msgid "*sniff sniff* What's that? A rune? Gold! I smell gold!"
msgstr "*olfatea* ¿Qué es eso? ¿Una runa? ¡Oro! ¡Huelo oro!"

#. [message], speaker=Uthain
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/10_Gaze_of_the_Three.cfg:342
msgid "Huh, what's that? A hidden path?"
msgstr "¿Eh, qué es eso? ¿Un camino oculto?"

#. [message], speaker=Nuvdael
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/10_Gaze_of_the_Three.cfg:361
msgid "By the forefathers! A creature of an enormous size! What is that?"
msgstr "¡Por los antepasados! ¡Una criatura de un tamaño enorme! ¿Qué es eso?"

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/10_Gaze_of_the_Three.cfg:366
msgid ""
"These creatures are known as 'Sandmares'. Serrul used those as a kind of "
"heavy cavalry to overrun the forces of K'thar."
msgstr ""
"Estas criaturas son conocidas como «Pesadillas de Arena». Serrul las usaba "
"como una especie de caballería pesada para arrollar las fuerzas de K'thar."

#. [message], speaker=Nuvdael
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/10_Gaze_of_the_Three.cfg:371
msgid "For sure these deserts keep secrets unknown to anyone outside."
msgstr ""
"Seguro estos desiertos guardan secretos desconocidos para cualquiera de "
"afuera."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/10_Gaze_of_the_Three.cfg:404
msgid ""
"We have dispelled the darkness in these catacombs and it seems that light is "
"slowly crawling in again now that Yrialdhe is gone. Be careful, however, I "
"am not sure if we've successfully dealt with her. She slithered around our "
"blades and spears. We have to make sure that she is dead. Forward!"
msgstr ""
"Hemos disipado la oscuridad en estas catacumbas y parece que la luz se "
"arrastra lentamente de nuevo ahora que Yrialdhe se ha ido. Sin embargo, "
"tengan cuidado, no estoy seguro de si hemos lidiado con éxito con ella. Se "
"deslizó alrededor de nuestras espadas y lanzas. Tenemos que asegurarnos de "
"que esté muerta. ¡Adelante!"

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/10_Gaze_of_the_Three.cfg:427
msgid ""
"The magic in this place has been infecting our minds, I fear we will not "
"last long enough to get out of here safely anymore."
msgstr ""
"La magia en este lugar ha estado infectando nuestras mentes. Temo que ya no "
"duraremos lo suficiente para salir de aquí con seguridad."

#. [part]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/11_Root_of_Evil.cfg:7
msgid ""
"The darkness of the depths was not suited for Ilriel. When leaving behind "
"the blackness, she embraced the warmth of the sun and its light. What is a "
"forest without the light of the sun? But when they took a look at the "
"surroundings, they noticed that they now stand inside the great palace of "
"K'thar. The place where once the three kings ruled."
msgstr ""
"La oscuridad de las profundidades no era adecuada para Ilriel. Al dejar "
"atrás la negrura, ella abrazó el calor del sol y su luz. ¿Qué es un bosque "
"sin la luz del sol? Pero cuando miraron los alrededores, notaron que ahora "
"estaban dentro del gran palacio de K'thar. El lugar donde una vez gobernaron "
"los tres reyes."

#. [scenario], id=11_Root_of_Evil
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/11_Root_of_Evil.cfg:18
msgid "Root of Evil"
msgstr "Raíz del Mal"

#. [side]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/11_Root_of_Evil.cfg:85
msgid "?"
msgstr "?"

#. [event]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/11_Root_of_Evil.cfg:132
msgid "Ethernthril"
msgstr "Ethernthril"

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/11_Root_of_Evil.cfg:140
msgid ""
"I cannot believe that dwarves fought against the three kings. Their heads "
"are sturdy and their feet small. Their people rather sticks to themselves. "
"What has driven this dwarf to leave his home and kin and fight at the side "
"of Th'arwya and Serrul?"
msgstr ""
"No puedo creer que enanos lucharan contra los tres reyes. Sus cabezas son "
"duras y sus pies pequeños. Su pueblo prefiere mantenerse entre ellos. ¿Qué "
"impulsó a este enano a dejar su hogar y su gente y luchar al lado de "
"Th'arwya y Serrul?"

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/11_Root_of_Evil.cfg:145
msgid ""
"The ones searching for adventure and might often ended up in Serrul or "
"Th'arwya. The deserts house secrets that attract not only the bad-hearted. "
"It seems as though the whole world sits side by side in those cities. While "
"the dwellers of the deserts do not have contact with the great dwarven "
"kingdoms from the north, individuals often take the risk to come here, "
"because they sense the possibility to trade and learn from the ones from all "
"over the Great Continent. And some value this so much, they dare to fight "
"and die for it."
msgstr ""
"Los que buscan aventura y poder a menudo terminaban en Serrul o Th'arwya. "
"Los desiertos albergan secretos que atraen no solo a los de mal corazón. "
"Parece que el mundo entero se sienta lado a lado en esas ciudades. Mientras "
"los habitantes de los desiertos no tienen contacto con los grandes reinos "
"enanos del norte, los individuos a menudo se arriesgan a venir aquí, porque "
"sienten la posibilidad de comerciar y aprender de los que vienen de todo el "
"Gran Continente. Y algunos valoran esto tanto que se atreven a luchar y "
"morir por ello."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/11_Root_of_Evil.cfg:288
msgid ""
"The palace of K'thar! The root of all evil! The thrones of the three, now "
"claimed by the one who had been left behind. Yrialdhe."
msgstr ""
"¡El palacio de K'thar! ¡La raíz de todo mal! Los tronos de los tres, ahora "
"reclamados por quien fue dejado atrás. Yrialdhe."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/11_Root_of_Evil.cfg:293
msgid ""
"Yet again she tries to flee, just as she did when her kings were banned and "
"locked up in the Sphere by the Athvari. The Athvari thought she'd be a "
"broken creature, as she lost everything she was destined to protect. But "
"they were fooled. Yrialdhe is still a servant to them. She can sense the "
"growing power of the three."
msgstr ""
"Una vez más intenta huir, tal como lo hizo cuando sus reyes fueron "
"prohibidos y encerrados en la Esfera por los athvari. Los athvari pensaron "
"que sería una criatura rota, ya que perdió todo lo que estaba destinada a "
"proteger. Pero fueron engañados. Yrialdhe sigue siendo su servidora. Puede "
"sentir el creciente poder de los tres."

#. [message], speaker=Yrialdhe
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/11_Root_of_Evil.cfg:298
msgid ""
"The three kings had lost the battle, that took place exactly here, Ilaroth. "
"Where were you, then? Hiding behind the warriors of Kesh, Serrul and "
"Th'arwya! Knowing that their swords cannot wound us, knowing that their "
"wills are just those of humans. You've sent them into certain death!"
msgstr ""
"Los tres reyes perdieron la batalla que tuvo lugar exactamente aquí, "
"Ilaroth. ¿Dónde estabas entonces? ¡Escondiéndote detrás de los guerreros de "
"Kesh, Serrul y Th'arwya! Sabiendo que sus espadas no pueden herirnos, "
"sabiendo que sus voluntades son solo las de humanos. ¡Los enviaste a una "
"muerte segura!"

#. [message], speaker=Yrialdhe
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/11_Root_of_Evil.cfg:303
msgid ""
"Yet their death gave you time. Time for the Athvari to construct the astral "
"prison. We have lost the battle, Ilaroth, but in the end, victory shall be "
"ours! The war is not over yet!"
msgstr ""
"Sin embargo, su muerte te dio tiempo. Tiempo para que los athvari "
"construyeran la prisión astral. Perdimos la batalla, Ilaroth, pero al final, "
"¡la victoria será nuestra! ¡La guerra aún no ha terminado!"

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/11_Root_of_Evil.cfg:308
msgid ""
"You have spread enough terror already, Yrialdhe! This time, you won't "
"escape, snake!"
msgstr ""
"¡Ya has esparcido suficiente terror, Yrialdhe! Esta vez no escaparás, "
"¡serpiente!"

#. [message], speaker=Yrialdhe
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/11_Root_of_Evil.cfg:315
msgid ""
"You're a fool, Ilaroth, if you truly believe you puny maggot can avert the "
"return of the kings."
msgstr ""
"Eres un tonto, Ilaroth, si realmente crees que tú, insignificante gusano, "
"puedes evitar el regreso de los reyes."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/11_Root_of_Evil.cfg:363
msgid "A strange power flows through the body of Yrialdhe."
msgstr "Un extraño poder fluye a través del cuerpo de Yrialdhe."

#. [message], speaker=Yrialdhe
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/11_Root_of_Evil.cfg:372
msgid ""
"The three kings! They are calling my name! The return of the kings is near! "
"And so is your end, Ilaroth, and of your forsaken kin!"
msgstr ""
"¡Los tres reyes! ¡Están llamando mi nombre! ¡El regreso de los reyes está "
"cerca! ¡Y también tu fin, Ilaroth, y el de tu linaje abandonado!"

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/11_Root_of_Evil.cfg:377
msgid ""
"The Sphere is channeling its magic through her! Quick, we have to stop her!"
msgstr ""
"¡La Esfera está canalizando su magia a través de ella! ¡Rápido, tenemos que "
"detenerla!"

#. [message], speaker=Aula
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/11_Root_of_Evil.cfg:382
msgid "Yrialdhe. A name of fear. Let her be my problem, Ilaroth."
msgstr "Yrialdhe. Un nombre de miedo. Déjala ser mi problema, Ilaroth."

#. [note]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/11_Root_of_Evil.cfg:395
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/11_Root_of_Evil.cfg:463
msgid "Yrialdhe is able to unpetrify nearby units, that then fight for her."
msgstr ""
"Yrialdhe puede despetrificar unidades cercanas, que luego luchan por ella."

#. [message], speaker=Aula
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/11_Root_of_Evil.cfg:432
msgid "All these fallen ones, all these petrified poor beings."
msgstr "Todos estos caídos, todos estos pobres seres petrificados."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/11_Root_of_Evil.cfg:437
msgid ""
"Yrialdhe is responsible for their gruesome death. One gaze and their hearts "
"turn to stone. The battle at K'thar had been no easy one and many were "
"slain. Every grain of sand might be the remains of a once heroic warrior "
"that fought here at the heart of evil and got petrified by the forbidden one."
msgstr ""
"Yrialdhe es responsable de su muerte espantosa. Una mirada y sus corazones "
"se convierten en piedra. La batalla en K'thar no fue fácil y muchos fueron "
"asesinados. Cada grano de arena podría ser los restos de un guerrero una vez "
"heroico que luchó aquí en el corazón del mal y fue petrificado por la "
"prohibida."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/11_Root_of_Evil.cfg:442
msgid ""
"But she will pay the price for her deeds. Let me get to her and her remains "
"might become useful to us . . . I've got a plan . . ."
msgstr ""
"Pero ella pagará el precio por sus acciones. Déjenme llegar a ella y sus "
"restos podrían sernos útiles... Tengo un plan..."

#. [message], speaker=Aula
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/11_Root_of_Evil.cfg:447
msgid ""
"And you're not the only one seeking revenge. The warriors of long forgotten "
"times . . . their hearts still beat and lust for the blood of the snake! I "
"can awake their poor souls, but my powers won't suffice for all of them."
msgstr ""
"Y no eres el único que busca venganza. Los guerreros de tiempos olvidados... "
"sus corazones aún laten y ansían la sangre de la serpiente! Puedo despertar "
"sus pobres almas, pero mis poderes no bastarán para todos ellos."

#. [note]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/11_Root_of_Evil.cfg:466
msgid ""
"Au'la can unpetrify one of the marked units. The group will then be able to "
"recruit more of that unit type."
msgstr ""
"Au'la puede despetrificar una de las unidades marcadas. El grupo entonces "
"podrá reclutar más de ese tipo de unidad."

#. [event]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/11_Root_of_Evil.cfg:479
msgid "Bombathrin"
msgstr "Bombathrin"

#. [message], speaker=Bombathrin
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/11_Root_of_Evil.cfg:486
msgid "It has to be somewhere here! We need to find it!"
msgstr "¡Tiene que estar por aquí en alguna parte! ¡Necesitamos encontrarlo!"

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/11_Root_of_Evil.cfg:491
msgid "Dwarves? Here?"
msgstr "¿Enanos? ¿Aquí?"

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/11_Root_of_Evil.cfg:496
msgid ""
"And they are searching for something - in the very heart of the former "
"catastrophe. The dwarves are foolish or naive - or both. Little do they know "
"that the location itself is still infested with the three."
msgstr ""
"Y están buscando algo en el mismo corazón de la antigua catástrofe. Los "
"enanos son tontos o ingenuos, o ambos. Poco saben que el lugar mismo todavía "
"está infestado con los tres."

#. [message], speaker=Aula
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/11_Root_of_Evil.cfg:501
msgid ""
"They will not find anything here, only death. We need to save them from "
"their own stupidity. Let me get to them and soon they shall fight by our "
"side."
msgstr ""
"No encontrarán nada aquí, solo muerte. Necesitamos salvarlos de su propia "
"estupidez. Déjenme llegar a ellos y pronto lucharán a nuestro lado."

#. [message], speaker=Aula
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/11_Root_of_Evil.cfg:510
msgid "Dwarves! How . . . did you end up here - in the midst of a desert?"
msgstr "¡Enanos! ¿Cómo... terminaron aquí en medio de un desierto?"

#. [message], speaker=Bombathrin
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/11_Root_of_Evil.cfg:520
msgid "We are just explorers in the search of ancient artifacts"
msgstr "Solo somos exploradores en busca de artefactos antiguos"

#. [message], speaker=Aula
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/11_Root_of_Evil.cfg:525
msgid "We will get you out of here once we killed the snake."
msgstr "Los sacaremos de aquí una vez que matemos a la serpiente."

#. [object]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/11_Root_of_Evil.cfg:544
msgid "quest-character-Bombathrin-release"
msgstr "personaje-de-mision-liberacion-Bombathrin"

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/11_Root_of_Evil.cfg:587
msgid ""
"The snake is no more. Now let us head to the Cloud River, where we'll meet "
"Iskandar."
msgstr ""
"La serpiente ya no existe. Ahora dirijámonos al Río de las Nubes, donde nos "
"encontraremos con Iskandar."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/11_Root_of_Evil.cfg:615
msgid "Yrialdhe managed to flee and now the enemy forces will bulk up again!"
msgstr ""
"¡Yrialdhe logró huir y ahora las fuerzas enemigas se reforzarán de nuevo!"

#. [part]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/12_Cloud_River.cfg:7
msgid ""
"The heroic group moved forward towards the Cloud River where Iskandar would "
"meet them."
msgstr ""
"El grupo heroico avanzó hacia el Río de las Nubes donde Iskandar se "
"encontraría con ellos."

#. [scenario], id=12_Cloud_River
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/12_Cloud_River.cfg:18
msgid "Cloud River"
msgstr "Río de las Nubes"

#. [side], type=Dune Prophet
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/12_Cloud_River.cfg:60
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/12_Cloud_River.cfg:65
msgid "Abbas"
msgstr "Abbas"

#. [event]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/12_Cloud_River.cfg:127
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/19_Above_the_Stars_and_below_Earth.cfg:336
msgid "Azyan"
msgstr "Azyan"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/12_Cloud_River.cfg:174
msgid "Words of a long forgotten language are echoing throughout the deserts."
msgstr "Palabras de una lengua olvidada hace mucho resuenan por los desiertos."

#. [message], speaker=Azyan
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/12_Cloud_River.cfg:219
msgid "Look, the Cloud River ran dry in a matter of seconds! It is . . . "
msgstr "¡Miren, el Río de las Nubes se secó en cuestión de segundos! Es..."

#. [message], speaker=Azyan
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/12_Cloud_River.cfg:224
msgid ""
". . . impossible. This is the kind of magic that is described in our "
"legends! The kind of magic that led to an era of destruction!"
msgstr ""
"... imposible. ¡Este es el tipo de magia que se describe en nuestras "
"leyendas! ¡El tipo de magia que llevó a una era de destrucción!"

#. [message], speaker=Azyan
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/12_Cloud_River.cfg:231
msgid "Men, an Athvari!"
msgstr "¡Hombres, un athvari!"

#. [message], speaker=Iskandar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/12_Cloud_River.cfg:236
msgid ""
"Hasten into the deserts if you value your life. This is no place for anyone, "
"not even for men like you."
msgstr ""
"Apresúrense hacia los desiertos si valoran su vida. Este no es lugar para "
"nadie, ni siquiera para hombres como ustedes."

#. [message], speaker=Azyan
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/12_Cloud_River.cfg:241
msgid "I . . . I can't believe . . . my eyes! S. . . sure. . . my lord."
msgstr "Yo... no puedo creer... mis ojos! S... seguro... mi señor."

#. [message], speaker=Iskandar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/12_Cloud_River.cfg:250
msgid "Draw back, henchmen of Kesh! This realm belongs to the Athvari."
msgstr "¡Retrocedan, esbirros de Kesh! Este reino pertenece a los athvari."

#. [message], speaker=Abbas
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/12_Cloud_River.cfg:255
msgid ""
"Your words mean nothing in this world anymore, Athvari. The presence of the "
"Sphere protects us from your magic! The forces of Kesh will pour out into "
"your lands and destroy anything that is on their path, now that the cloud "
"river ran dry. The barrier that protects your realm from the great army of "
"Kesh is no more. Your realm will be ours in a matter of months."
msgstr ""
"Tus palabras ya no significan nada en este mundo, athvari. ¡La presencia de "
"la Esfera nos protege de tu magia! Las fuerzas de Kesh se derramarán en tus "
"tierras y destruirán todo lo que esté en su camino, ahora que el río de las "
"nubes se secó. La barrera que protegía tu reino del gran ejército de Kesh ya "
"no existe. Tu reino será nuestro en cuestión de meses."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/12_Cloud_River.cfg:260
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:874
msgid "Iskandar!"
msgstr "¡Iskandar!"

#. [message], speaker=Iskandar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/12_Cloud_River.cfg:265
msgid "Ilarøth! I am glad you two made it here safely."
msgstr "¡Ilarøth! Me alegra que ustedes dos hayan llegado aquí sanos y salvos."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/12_Cloud_River.cfg:270
msgid "The . . . the whole river ran dry."
msgstr "El... el río entero se secó."

#. [message], speaker=Iskandar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/12_Cloud_River.cfg:275
msgid ""
"We are too late, the natural barrier has been broken and the forces of Kesh "
"are on the brink of war. They are resting just a few miles south to the "
"river and wait for the right time to march towards Serrul."
msgstr ""
"Llegamos demasiado tarde, la barrera natural ha sido rota y las fuerzas de "
"Kesh están al borde de la guerra. Están descansando a solo unas millas al "
"sur del río y esperan el momento adecuado para marchar hacia Serrul."

#. [message], speaker=Abbas
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/12_Cloud_River.cfg:280
msgid ""
"Your era is over! The secrets of magic belong to Kesh! And so does your "
"life! Men! Seize him! Bring him to Kesh so the ritual can find its end!"
msgstr ""
"¡Tu era ha terminado! ¡Los secretos de la magia pertenecen a Kesh! ¡Y "
"también tu vida! ¡Hombres! ¡Captúrenlo! ¡Llévenlo a Kesh para que el ritual "
"llegue a su fin!"

#. [message], speaker=Iskandar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/12_Cloud_River.cfg:288
msgid ""
"Ilarøth, we are the last two Athvari walking freely on these plains. Our "
"brothers fell victim to the power of the Sphere. I do not know for sure what "
"they are planning to do. Yet one thing is clear. They want to end the "
"bloodline of the Athvari and decipher the secrets of magic. It will throw "
"the lands into an era of chaos, an era of destruction under the banner of "
"Kesh!"
msgstr ""
"Ilarøth, somos los últimos dos athvari que caminan libremente por estas "
"llanuras. Nuestros hermanos cayeron víctimas del poder de la Esfera. No sé "
"con certeza qué planean hacer. Pero una cosa está clara. Quieren terminar "
"con el linaje de los athvari y descifrar los secretos de la magia. Eso "
"arrojará las tierras a una era de caos, una era de destrucción bajo la "
"bandera de Kesh!"

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/12_Cloud_River.cfg:293
msgid "Kesh . . . this name equals the poison that is dissolving these lands!"
msgstr ""
"¡Kesh... ese nombre equivale al veneno que está disolviendo estas tierras!"

#. [message], speaker=Azyan
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/12_Cloud_River.cfg:300
msgid ""
"Athvari! We could not help overhearing what you've said. Let us join you in "
"this fight!"
msgstr ""
"¡Athvari! No pudimos evitar escuchar lo que dijeron. ¡Déjennos unirnos a "
"ustedes en esta pelea!"

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/12_Cloud_River.cfg:305
msgid ""
"Bandits! You are nothing more than bandits! How can we make sure you won't "
"betray us and murder us in our sleep?"
msgstr ""
"¡Bandidos! ¡No son más que bandidos! ¿Cómo podemos asegurarnos de que no nos "
"traicionen y nos asesinen mientras dormimos?"

#. [message], speaker=Azyan
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/12_Cloud_River.cfg:310
msgid ""
"We . . . we did not decide for this life. We were pushed into it. We once "
"lived in a small village next to Kesh. The city of Kesh decided to recruit "
"us for their army but we declined, as we had seen enough wars in our "
"lifetime. They killed most people of our village but we were able to escape. "
"No city of the deserts wanted to take us in, so we had to live in the "
"deserts. Water and resources are rare here, we had to steal from caravans in "
"order to survive."
msgstr ""
"Nosotros... no elegimos esta vida. Nos empujaron a ella. Una vez vivimos en "
"un pequeño pueblo cerca de Kesh. La ciudad de Kesh decidió reclutarnos para "
"su ejército pero nos negamos, ya que habíamos visto suficientes guerras en "
"nuestra vida. Mataron a la mayoría de la gente de nuestro pueblo pero "
"logramos escapar. Ninguna ciudad de los desiertos quiso acogernos, así que "
"tuvimos que vivir en los desiertos. El agua y los recursos son escasos aquí, "
"tuvimos que robar a las caravanas para sobrevivir."

#. [message], speaker=Iskandar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/12_Cloud_River.cfg:315
msgid ""
"They are speaking the truth Ilarøth, their heart is pure. I can sense it. "
"For sure we need everyone we can get, as the power of Kesh affects any man "
"and woman on this continent."
msgstr ""
"Dicen la verdad Ilarøth, su corazón es puro. Puedo sentirlo. Seguro "
"necesitamos a todos los que podamos conseguir, ya que el poder de Kesh "
"afecta a cualquier hombre y mujer en este continente."

#. [message], speaker=Abbas
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/12_Cloud_River.cfg:327
msgid ""
"Some desert bandits won't get you out of your miserable situation, Athvari."
msgstr ""
"Algunos bandidos del desierto no los sacarán de su miserable situación, "
"athvari."

#. [message], speaker=Abbas
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/12_Cloud_River.cfg:332
msgid "But before . . . let us have some fun!"
msgstr "Pero antes... ¡divirtámonos un poco!"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/12_Cloud_River.cfg:349
msgid ""
"The vizier of kesh spews out words of a long forgotten language, slowly "
"raising the dead underneath the sands."
msgstr ""
"El visir de Kesh escupe palabras de una lengua olvidada hace mucho, "
"levantando lentamente a los muertos bajo las arenas."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/12_Cloud_River.cfg:354
msgid ""
"The soldiers of old, fallen soldiers of the battle that took place here a "
"long time ago, at the battle of K'thar to bring down the Three Kings. "
"Warriors of both Serrul and Kesh, once friends, now foes. Yet both of them "
"are now controlled by the poison of Kesh."
msgstr ""
"Los soldados de antaño, soldados caídos de la batalla que tuvo lugar aquí "
"hace mucho tiempo, en la batalla de K'thar para derribar a los Tres Reyes. "
"Guerreros tanto de Serrul como de Kesh, una vez amigos, ahora enemigos. Sin "
"embargo, ambos ahora están controlados por el veneno de Kesh."

#. [message], speaker=Iskandar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/12_Cloud_River.cfg:359
msgid ""
"Then take wings and march through the river bed to decapitate the vizier of "
"Kesh. Yet stand close to each other, the fallen ones will keep resurrecting "
"until he's dead."
msgstr ""
"Entonces tomen alas y marchen a través del lecho del río para decapitar al "
"visir de Kesh. Pero manténganse juntos, los caídos seguirán resucitando "
"hasta que él esté muerto."

#. [object]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/12_Cloud_River.cfg:371
msgid ""
"\n"
"The Dune Sharpshooter is a range-orientated unit with a marksman attack "
"making him a reliable unit to wear down enemies that focus on melee attacks."
msgstr ""
"\n"
"El Tirador Certero Barján es una unidad orientada al rango con un ataque de "
"tirador que lo convierte en una unidad confiable para desgastar enemigos que "
"se enfocan en ataques cuerpo a cuerpo."

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/12_Cloud_River.cfg:380
msgid "Defeat the vizier of Kesh"
msgstr "Derrota al visir de Kesh"

#. [note]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/12_Cloud_River.cfg:386
msgid "You can now recruit Dune Sharpshooter."
msgstr "Ahora puedes reclutar Tirador Certero Barján."

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/12_Cloud_River.cfg:401
msgid "What are you, desert man?"
msgstr "¿Qué eres, hombre del desierto?"

#. [message], speaker=Azyan
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/12_Cloud_River.cfg:406
msgid ""
"What I am? Oh, I am many. When the Three Kings of K'thar abused the powers "
"of magic, arcane beings such as genie were the first targeted. They sought "
"for shelter in man-made object such as swords, shields or lamps. Some also "
"sought for shelter in man themselves. I offered my life to secure the life "
"of a genie."
msgstr ""
"¿Qué soy? Oh, soy muchos. Cuando los Tres Reyes de K'thar abusaron de los "
"poderes de la magia, seres arcanos como los genios fueron los primeros "
"objetivos. Buscaron refugio en objetos hechos por el hombre como espadas, "
"escudos o lámparas. Algunos también buscaron refugio en los mismos hombres. "
"Ofrecí mi vida para asegurar la vida de un genio."

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/12_Cloud_River.cfg:411
msgid "That is a sign of true loyalty and brotherhood."
msgstr "Eso es una señal de verdadera lealtad y hermandad."

#. [message], speaker=Azyan
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/12_Cloud_River.cfg:416
msgid ""
"When the first of our people arrived here in the desert lands, the genie "
"welcomed us. They helped us build our mighty cities in exchange for security "
"against the red-skinned Afariyaten, arcane beings from the depths of the "
"desert. Genie and men are friends and friends help each other."
msgstr ""
"Cuando los primeros de nuestro pueblo llegaron aquí a las tierras del "
"desierto, los genios nos dieron la bienvenida. Nos ayudaron a construir "
"nuestras poderosas ciudades a cambio de seguridad contra los afariyaten de "
"piel roja, seres arcanos de las profundidades del desierto. Genios y hombres "
"son amigos y los amigos se ayudan mutuamente."

#. [message], speaker=Uthain
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/12_Cloud_River.cfg:481
msgid ""
"Oh, look at the vizier. I'd like to knock him out and take a look at his "
"relics that allow him to cast forth such magic."
msgstr ""
"Oh, mira al visir. Me gustaría noquearlo y echar un vistazo a sus reliquias "
"que le permiten lanzar tal magia."

#. [message], speaker=Iskandar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/12_Cloud_River.cfg:486
msgid ""
"Those relics corrupt the mind of the bearer, don't meddle with those dark "
"affairs, dwarf, if you value your clear mind. Those viziers were not always "
"blinded and devoured by power."
msgstr ""
"Esas reliquias corrompen la mente de quien las lleva, no te metas con esos "
"asuntos oscuros, enano, si valoras tu mente clara. Esos visires no siempre "
"estuvieron cegados y devorados por el poder."

#. [message], speaker=Nuvdael
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/12_Cloud_River.cfg:496
msgid ""
"These dark arts remind me of the dark sorcerers of the Black Forest that "
"once infested the Southwoods. It seems like those arts are not unknown to "
"your kin either."
msgstr ""
"Estas artes oscuras me recuerdan a los hechiceros oscuros del Bosque Negro "
"que una vez infestaron los Bosques del Sur. Parece que esas artes tampoco "
"son desconocidas para tu pueblo."

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/12_Cloud_River.cfg:501
msgid ""
"It's not them. His power is coupled with the relic he is using, while the "
"sorcerers of the Black Forest were able to cast forth magic by will."
msgstr ""
"No son ellos. Su poder está acoplado a la reliquia que usa, mientras que los "
"hechiceros del Bosque Negro podían lanzar magia por voluntad."

#. [message], speaker=Iskandar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/12_Cloud_River.cfg:545
msgid "His magic won't help him now. Examine his body!"
msgstr "Su magia ya no lo ayudará ahora. ¡Examinen su cuerpo!"

#. [message], speaker=Iskandar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/12_Cloud_River.cfg:552
msgid ""
"Hmmph. See this stone here? Another artifact broken apart from the Sphere, "
"allowing him to cast the spells of old times. If these are handed out to "
"many warriors of Kesh, we will face hard times."
msgstr ""
"Hmmph. ¿Ven esta piedra aquí? Otro artefacto roto de la Esfera, "
"permitiéndole lanzar los hechizos de tiempos antiguos. Si estos se entregan "
"a muchos guerreros de Kesh, enfrentaremos tiempos difíciles."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/12_Cloud_River.cfg:557
msgid "What will we do now?"
msgstr "¿Qué haremos ahora?"

#. [message], speaker=Iskandar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/12_Cloud_River.cfg:562
msgid ""
"We have to sneak through the army of Kesh that is resting next to the bay of "
"Clouds."
msgstr ""
"Tenemos que escabullirnos a través del ejército de Kesh que descansa junto a "
"la bahía de las Nubes."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/12_Cloud_River.cfg:567
msgid "That is insane!"
msgstr "¡Eso es una locura!"

#. [message], speaker=Iskandar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/12_Cloud_River.cfg:572
msgid ""
"It's also our only option. The minds of Kesh would never expect that and "
"once we are through their army, we can head to Th'arwya and convince the "
"Dune Warmaster to send his army to support our cause."
msgstr ""
"También es nuestra única opción. Las mentes de Kesh nunca lo esperarían y "
"una vez que estemos a través de su ejército, podemos dirigirnos a Th'arwya y "
"convencer al Maestro de Guerra de enviar su ejército para apoyar nuestra "
"causa."

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/12_Cloud_River.cfg:577
msgid "Serrul will fall if no one stops the army of Kesh."
msgstr "Serrul caerá si nadie detiene al ejército de Kesh."

#. [message], speaker=Iskandar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/12_Cloud_River.cfg:582
msgid ""
"That is right. Offer death and grant life. We can't defend Serrul. Not "
"against an army like that."
msgstr ""
"Eso es correcto. Ofrecer muerte y conceder vida. No podemos defender Serrul. "
"No contra un ejército como ese."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/12_Cloud_River.cfg:587
msgid ""
"He is right, Ilriel. An army consisting of thousands of men, spears as long "
"as trees, shields as hard as the mountain itself. Those are not normal "
"warriors. They were trained for war, they've never seen anything besides it. "
"Some even doubt they are men. Yet we are lucky. The giant is sleeping."
msgstr ""
"Tiene razón, Ilriel. Un ejército compuesto por miles de hombres, lanzas tan "
"largas como árboles, escudos tan duros como la montaña misma. Esos no son "
"guerreros normales. Fueron entrenados para la guerra, nunca han visto nada "
"más que eso. Algunos incluso dudan que sean hombres. Sin embargo, somos "
"afortunados. El gigante está dormido."

#. [message], speaker=Iskandar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/12_Cloud_River.cfg:592
msgid ""
"While the forces of Kesh attack Serrul, we travel to Th'arwya and convince "
"the Dune Warmaster to station his army next to the Cloud River. Then the "
"forces of Kesh attacking Serrul can't return to Kesh as they are blocked by "
"the army of Th'arwya. That will give us time to deal with whatever evil lies "
"within Kesh."
msgstr ""
"Mientras las fuerzas de Kesh atacan Serrul, viajamos a Th'arwya y "
"convencemos al Maestro de Guerra de estacionar su ejército junto al Río de "
"las Nubes. Entonces las fuerzas de Kesh que atacan Serrul no podrán regresar "
"a Kesh porque están bloqueadas por el ejército de Th'arwya. Eso nos dará "
"tiempo para lidiar con cualquier mal que yace dentro de Kesh."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/12_Cloud_River.cfg:597
msgid "And if the Dune Warmaster doesn't play along?"
msgstr "¿Y si el Maestro de Guerra no coopera?"

#. [message], speaker=Iskandar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/12_Cloud_River.cfg:602
msgid "That isn't an option, we have to convince him."
msgstr "Esa no es una opción, tenemos que convencerlo."

#. [message], speaker=Iskandar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/12_Cloud_River.cfg:607
msgid ""
"Then let us move on towards the Bay of Clouds. At night, we shall sneak "
"through the forces of Kesh."
msgstr ""
"Entonces avancemos hacia la Bahía de las Nubes. Por la noche, nos "
"escabulliremos a través de las fuerzas de Kesh."

#. [message], speaker=Iskandar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/12_Cloud_River.cfg:622
msgid ""
"The curse upon this river has been placed for far too long, I fear we won't "
"be able to reverse its effects even if we kill the vizier."
msgstr ""
"La maldición sobre este río ha sido puesta por demasiado tiempo, temo que no "
"podremos revertir sus efectos incluso si matamos al visir."

#. [part]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/13_Eye_of_the_Hurricane.cfg:7
msgid ""
"So it has been decided. Passing through the entire army of Kesh at the Bay "
"of Clouds, through trained men that can kill without a blink. When the group "
"got closer to the army, they searched for a spot to spy their forces. It is "
"a lot larger than they'd imagine. With the army being so vast, they have no "
"other choice but to bypass the army by its eastern flank. It'd mean a delay "
"of several weeks."
msgstr ""
"Así ha sido decidido. Atravesar todo el ejército de Kesh en la Bahía de las "
"Nubes, a través de hombres entrenados que pueden matar sin pestañear. Cuando "
"el grupo se acercó al ejército, buscaron un lugar para espiar sus fuerzas. "
"Es mucho más grande de lo que imaginaban. Con el ejército siendo tan vasto, "
"no tienen otra opción más que rodear al ejército por su flanco este. Eso "
"significaría un retraso de varias semanas."

#. [part]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/13_Eye_of_the_Hurricane.cfg:11
msgid ""
"Watching the fearless warriors, Ilriel and Ilaroth think about a plan to "
"sneak through the army. But what would that plan look like? They have "
"nothing else to compare it to, no battle or skirmish they'd ever fought told "
"them on how to sneak through the army of Kesh. It is an insane undertaking. "
"But . . . maybe it isn't. Ilriel proposes to wander next to the coast, where "
"their footsteps would be silenced by the waves crashing onto shore. Waiting "
"for the sun to set, the group prepares itself. Tonight, they'll be the "
"shadows."
msgstr ""
"Observando a los guerreros intrépidos, Ilriel e Ilaroth piensan en un plan "
"para escabullirse a través del ejército. Pero ¿cómo sería ese plan? No "
"tienen nada más con qué compararlo, ninguna batalla o escaramuza que "
"hubieran librado les dijo cómo escabullirse a través del ejército de Kesh. "
"Es una empresa loca. Pero... tal vez no lo sea. Ilriel propone caminar junto "
"a la costa, donde sus pasos serían silenciados por las olas que chocan "
"contra la orilla. Esperando a que el sol se ponga, el grupo se prepara. Esta "
"noche, serán las sombras."

#. [scenario], id=13_Eye_of_the_Hurricane
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/13_Eye_of_the_Hurricane.cfg:34
msgid "Eye of the Hurricane"
msgstr "Ojo del Huracán"

#. [side], type=Dune Prophet
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/13_Eye_of_the_Hurricane.cfg:75
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/13_Eye_of_the_Hurricane.cfg:81
msgid "Bahar"
msgstr "Bahar"

#. [side]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/13_Eye_of_the_Hurricane.cfg:102
msgid "Slaves"
msgstr "Esclavos"

#. [side]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/13_Eye_of_the_Hurricane.cfg:110
msgid "Catapults"
msgstr "Catapultas"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/13_Eye_of_the_Hurricane.cfg:320
msgid ""
"At night, the group reached the forces of Kesh that were resting next to the "
"Bay of Clouds."
msgstr ""
"Por la noche, el grupo llegó a las fuerzas de Kesh que descansaban junto a "
"la Bahía de las Nubes."

#. [message], speaker=Iskandar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/13_Eye_of_the_Hurricane.cfg:325
msgid ""
"Stay silent and move quickly. They don't know we are here, so don't walk too "
"close to them or they'll hear us. We can't fight them, though, so just stay "
"afar. In case they see too many bodies laying around, we are done."
msgstr ""
"Permanezcan en silencio y muévanse rápido. No saben que estamos aquí, así "
"que no caminen demasiado cerca de ellos o nos oirán. Sin embargo, no podemos "
"luchar contra ellos, así que manténganse a distancia. En caso de que vean "
"demasiados cuerpos tirados, estamos acabados."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/13_Eye_of_the_Hurricane.cfg:330
msgid ""
"See the catapults? If we manipulate them, they won't be of use when they "
"siege Serrul. Sabotaging them will grant our cause more time."
msgstr ""
"¿Ven las catapultas? Si las manipulamos, no servirán de nada cuando asedien "
"Serrul. Sabotearlas le dará más tiempo a nuestra causa."

#. [message], speaker=Iskandar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/13_Eye_of_the_Hurricane.cfg:335
msgid "You are right, brother, let us take care of these."
msgstr "Tienes razón, hermano, ocupémonos de estas."

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/13_Eye_of_the_Hurricane.cfg:342
msgid ""
"Ilarøth reaches the southern border after destroying all catapults: $|"
"number_cat/12 left."
msgstr ""
"Ilarøth llega a la frontera sur después de destruir todas las catapultas: $|"
"number_cat/12 restantes."

#. [objective], condition=lose
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/13_Eye_of_the_Hurricane.cfg:346
msgid "Kill more than 7 enemy units."
msgstr "Mata más de 7 unidades enemigas."

#. [note]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/13_Eye_of_the_Hurricane.cfg:352
msgid ""
"Sleeping enemies are not aware there is an enemy. They have no zone of "
"control, so your units can move right through them. In case you are in a "
"radius of 2 when the turn of the enemy starts, they will notice you, gaining "
"up to 6 movespeed and regaining their zone of control."
msgstr ""
"Los enemigos dormidos no son conscientes de que hay un enemigo. No tienen "
"zona de control, por lo que tus unidades pueden pasar justo a través de "
"ellos. En caso de que estés en un radio de 2 cuando comience el turno del "
"enemigo, te notarán, ganando hasta 6 de velocidad de movimiento y "
"recuperando su zona de control."

#. [note]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/13_Eye_of_the_Hurricane.cfg:355
msgid ""
"Minotaurs can be set free, but they won't be taken over to the next "
"scenarios."
msgstr ""
"Los minotauros pueden ser liberados, pero no se llevarán al siguiente "
"escenario."

#. [message], speaker=Iskandar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/13_Eye_of_the_Hurricane.cfg:381
msgid ""
"Be careful! We can not kill too many of them or they will notice us. We have "
"already killed "
msgstr ""
"¡Cuidado! No podemos matar a demasiados de ellos o nos notarán. Ya hemos "
"matado"

#. [message], speaker=Iskandar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/13_Eye_of_the_Hurricane.cfg:393
msgid ""
"That's it, there's no chance they won't know about us now that we've killed "
"more than half a dozen of them."
msgstr ""
"Eso es todo, no hay posibilidad de que no sepan de nosotros ahora que hemos "
"matado a más de media docena de ellos."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/13_Eye_of_the_Hurricane.cfg:409
msgid ""
"See those minotaurs? Mighty creatures from the east, caught inside an iron "
"cage. If we can get to them, we should be able to set them free to distract "
"the warriors of Kesh."
msgstr ""
"¿Ven esos minotauros? Poderosas criaturas del este, atrapadas dentro de una "
"jaula de hierro. Si podemos llegar a ellos, deberíamos poder liberarlos para "
"distraer a los guerreros de Kesh."

#. [message], speaker=Azyan
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/13_Eye_of_the_Hurricane.cfg:414
msgid ""
"It's cruel to use the lives of the uninvolved as a pure distraction in war, "
"no matter the race. When the forces of Kesh tried to recruit my people for "
"war, we've declined and yet were driven into the vast desert plains. But can "
"they? Can they oversee the consequences of taking part in the war and fight "
"for our cause? We can overcome the obstacle that is Kesh without committing "
"such an act."
msgstr ""
"Es cruel usar las vidas de los no involucrados como pura distracción en la "
"guerra, sin importar la raza. Cuando las fuerzas de Kesh intentaron reclutar "
"a mi pueblo para la guerra, nos negamos y sin embargo fuimos empujados a las "
"vastas llanuras del desierto. Pero ¿pueden ellos? ¿Pueden supervisar las "
"consecuencias de participar en la guerra y luchar por nuestra causa? Podemos "
"superar el obstáculo que es Kesh sin cometer tal acto."

#. [message], speaker=Iskandar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/13_Eye_of_the_Hurricane.cfg:419
msgid ""
"How can you say the minotaurs are uninvolved in the fight against Kesh, if "
"their control of the Sphere does not only endanger us, but the whole desert "
"realms? Every being on these realms plays a role, either in favor of Kesh or "
"against it. There's no inbetween, no grey, just black and white. Using the "
"lives of the minotaurs is a lesser evil than the evil that would result from "
"Kesh overthrowing the desert realms, a lesser evil than the return of the "
"Three Kings."
msgstr ""
"¿Cómo puedes decir que los minotauros no están involucrados en la lucha "
"contra Kesh, si su control de la Esfera no solo nos pone en peligro a "
"nosotros, sino a todos los reinos del desierto? Cada ser en estos reinos "
"juega un rol, ya sea a favor de Kesh o en contra. No hay intermedio, no hay "
"gris, solo negro y blanco. Usar las vidas de los minotauros es un mal menor "
"que el mal que resultaría de que Kesh derroque los reinos del desierto, un "
"mal menor que el regreso de los Tres Reyes."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/13_Eye_of_the_Hurricane.cfg:500
msgid "We've made it. Quick, let us leave and head to Th'arwya."
msgstr "Lo logramos. Rápido, salgamos y dirijámonos a Th'arwya."

#. [message], speaker=Azyan
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/13_Eye_of_the_Hurricane.cfg:505
msgid ""
"Wait, no! We can't just take the minotaurs with us. They don't understand "
"our war and for sure it's not their war. Not everyone has the same weight on "
"their shoulders in the fight against Kesh. We should let them free, so they "
"can return to their eastern mountains. They've seen enough war already."
msgstr ""
"¡Espera, no! No podemos simplemente llevarnos a los minotauros con nosotros. "
"No entienden nuestra guerra y seguro no es su guerra. No todos tienen el "
"mismo peso sobre sus hombros en la lucha contra Kesh. Deberíamos dejarlos "
"libres, para que puedan regresar a sus montañas del este. Ya han visto "
"suficiente guerra."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/13_Eye_of_the_Hurricane.cfg:510
msgid ""
"You're right. They've contributed enough to our cause and it's our duty to "
"gift them freedom for it. It's our very own burden to fight back Kesh. And a "
"plan shall be made in Th'arwya. Let us sally forth!"
msgstr ""
"Tienes razón. Han contribuido lo suficiente a nuestra causa y es nuestro "
"deber regalarles la libertad por ello. Es nuestra propia carga luchar contra "
"Kesh. Y se hará un plan en Th'arwya. ¡Avancemos!"

#. [message], speaker=Bahar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/13_Eye_of_the_Hurricane.cfg:562
msgid "You . . . will not . . . stop Kesh . . ."
msgstr "Ustedes... no... detendrán a Kesh..."

#. [message]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/13_Eye_of_the_Hurricane.cfg:595
msgid ""
"Who dares to walk among our camp? Alert the vizier, we have intruders among "
"our ranks!"
msgstr ""
"¿Quién se atreve a caminar entre nuestro campamento? ¡Alerten al visir, "
"tenemos intrusos entre nuestras filas!"

#. [part]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/14_Tharwya.cfg:7
msgid ""
"The army of Kesh slowly fades at the horizon. They did it. They really "
"managed to sneak through the greatest army to grace the surface of the "
"earth. Yet during their undertaking, they felt like somebody was observing "
"them. Or something. Was the success the result of their skill, their luck or "
"had it been determined and enforced by something beyond? Ilriel and Ilaroth "
"are happy nonetheless to survive the enterprise and they calmy move towards "
"Th'arwya. Being able to see it from a long distance, the tower of Th'arwya "
"even overtops the clouds. Walking along the coast of the Bay of Clouds for "
"some weeks, the group finally reached the grand trading city."
msgstr ""
"El ejército de Kesh se desvanece lentamente en el horizonte. Lo lograron. "
"Realmente lograron escabullirse a través del mayor ejército que ha pisado la "
"superficie de la tierra. Sin embargo, durante su empresa, sintieron que "
"alguien los observaba. O algo. ¿El éxito fue resultado de su habilidad, su "
"suerte o había sido determinado y forzado por algo más allá? Ilriel e "
"Ilaroth están felices de todos modos de haber sobrevivido a la empresa y se "
"mueven tranquilamente hacia Th'arwya. Al poder verla desde lejos, la torre "
"de Th'arwya incluso sobresale por encima de las nubes. Caminando a lo largo "
"de la costa de la Bahía de las Nubes durante algunas semanas, el grupo "
"finalmente llegó a la gran ciudad comercial."

#. [scenario], id=14_Tharwya
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/14_Tharwya.cfg:18
msgid "Th'arwya"
msgstr "Th'arwya"

#. [side], type=Athvari Counselor
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/14_Tharwya.cfg:61
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/14_Tharwya.cfg:67
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/16_Return_to_Tharwya.cfg:349
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/16_Return_to_Tharwya.cfg:355
msgid "Ma'ralek"
msgstr "Ma'ralek"

#. [side]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/14_Tharwya.cfg:88
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/16_Return_to_Tharwya.cfg:377
msgid "merchants"
msgstr "mercaderes"

#. [side]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/14_Tharwya.cfg:100
msgid "thieves"
msgstr "ladrones"

#. [event]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/14_Tharwya.cfg:131
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/19_Above_the_Stars_and_below_Earth.cfg:335
msgid "Wahdet"
msgstr "Wahdet"

#. [unit], id=Ashuar, type=Afariyat_Dune Slaughterer
#. [side]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/14_Tharwya.cfg:147
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/15_Blackhands.cfg:186
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/15_Blackhands.cfg:682
msgid "Ashuar"
msgstr "Ashuar"

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/14_Tharwya.cfg:196
msgid ""
"Th'arwya, the City of Gold. It surely deserves this name. Here we shall find "
"help."
msgstr ""
"Th'arwya, la Ciudad de Oro. Seguramente merece este nombre. Aquí "
"encontraremos ayuda."

#. [message], speaker=Iskandar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/14_Tharwya.cfg:201
msgid "Then let us see if we are welcomed here."
msgstr "Entonces veamos si somos bienvenidos aquí."

#. [message]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/14_Tharwya.cfg:214
msgid ""
"Welcome to Th'arwya, travellers. The City of Gold! Make sure to trade with "
"our excellent merchants!"
msgstr ""
"¡Bienvenidos a Th'arwya, viajeros. ¡La Ciudad de Oro! ¡Asegúrense de "
"comerciar con nuestros excelentes mercaderes!"

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/14_Tharwya.cfg:219
msgid "Thank you, guard."
msgstr "Gracias, guardia."

#. [message], speaker=Azyan
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/14_Tharwya.cfg:226
msgid ""
"I am happy to see Th'arwya, a city where both men and genie happily live and "
"prosper together. This reminds me of the early ages of these desert realms, "
"where genie helped men to build their gigantic cities. But something is odd "
"here, I can feel the presence of someone with a divided heart. Someone like "
"me . . ."
msgstr ""
"Me alegra ver Th'arwya, una ciudad donde tanto hombres como genios viven y "
"prosperan felices juntos. Esto me recuerda a las primeras épocas de estos "
"reinos del desierto, donde los genios ayudaron a los hombres a construir sus "
"ciudades gigantes. Pero algo es extraño aquí, puedo sentir la presencia de "
"alguien con un corazón dividido. Alguien como yo..."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/14_Tharwya.cfg:231
msgid ""
"We should let Iskandar ascend to the top of the tower of Th'arwya and let "
"him speak with the vicegerent of this city. Iskandar's kin is most respected "
"amongst the people of the desert."
msgstr ""
"Deberíamos dejar que Iskandar ascienda a la cima de la torre de Th'arwya y "
"le permita hablar con el vicegerente de esta ciudad. El linaje de Iskandar "
"es el más respetado entre el pueblo del desierto."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/14_Tharwya.cfg:236
msgid "Do your best, Iskandar."
msgstr "Haz lo mejor que puedas, Iskandar."

#. [message], speaker=Iskandar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/14_Tharwya.cfg:246
msgid "Dune Warmaster of Th'arwya! Ma'ralek, my old friend!"
msgstr "¡Maestro de Guerra de Th'arwya! ¡Ma'ralek, mi viejo amigo!"

#. [message], speaker=Maralek
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/14_Tharwya.cfg:251
msgid "Iskandar? An Athvari? How . . . precious."
msgstr "¿Iskandar? ¿Un athvari? Qué... precioso."

#. [message], speaker=Iskandar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/14_Tharwya.cfg:256
msgid ""
"It must've been ages since we last met. We are in need of the help of the "
"Dune Warmaster of Th'arwya. Where is he?"
msgstr ""
"Deben haber pasado siglos desde la última vez que nos vimos. Necesitamos la "
"ayuda del Maestro de Guerra de Th'arwya. ¿Dónde está?"

#. [message], speaker=Maralek
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/14_Tharwya.cfg:261
msgid "The Dune Warmaster of Th'arwya? There is none. Not anymore."
msgstr "¿El Maestro de Guerra de Th'arwya? No hay ninguno. Ya no."

#. [message], speaker=Iskandar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/14_Tharwya.cfg:266
msgid "What has happened to him?"
msgstr "¿Qué le pasó a él?"

#. [message], speaker=Maralek
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/14_Tharwya.cfg:271
msgid ""
"When he decided to visit the tomb of his forefathers with a loyal group of "
"his own, the desert winds surprised him and led him astray. His fate didn't "
"led him head back to Th'arwya. It is though as the desert itself swallowed "
"him up."
msgstr ""
"Cuando decidió visitar la tumba de sus antepasados con un grupo leal propio, "
"los vientos del desierto lo sorprendieron y lo desviaron. Su destino no lo "
"llevó de regreso a Th'arwya. Es como si el desierto mismo lo hubiera tragado."

#. [message], speaker=Maralek
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/14_Tharwya.cfg:276
msgid ""
"And in times of abscence of the Dune Warmaster, his advisor and vicegerent "
"is supposed to rule in his name. I am the Dune Warmaster of Th'arwya now."
msgstr ""
"Y en tiempos de ausencia del Maestro de Guerra, su asesor y vicegerente se "
"supone que gobierna en su nombre. Ahora yo soy el Maestro de Guerra del "
"Desierto de Th'arwya."

#. [message], speaker=Iskandar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/14_Tharwya.cfg:281
msgid ""
"Then it is you, whose help we are in need of, Ma'ralek. The forces of "
"Kesh . . ."
msgstr ""
"Entonces eres tú, cuya ayuda necesitamos, Ma'ralek. Las fuerzas de Kesh..."

#. [message], speaker=Maralek
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/14_Tharwya.cfg:286
msgid ""
"Of course you are in need of my help. I know your situation, Iskandar. But "
"why would I help you? What's the price you are willing to pay?"
msgstr ""
"Por supuesto que necesitan mi ayuda. Conozco tu situación, Iskandar. Pero "
"¿por qué te ayudaría? ¿Qué precio estás dispuesto a pagar?"

#. [message], speaker=Iskandar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/14_Tharwya.cfg:291
msgid ""
"What price seems to be appropriate to you when facing certain destruction of "
"the desert lands? In death, your wealth means nothing."
msgstr ""
"¿Qué precio te parece apropiado cuando enfrentas la destrucción segura de "
"las tierras del desierto? En la muerte, tu riqueza no significa nada."

#. [message], speaker=Maralek
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/14_Tharwya.cfg:296
msgid ""
"It is not my life that is endangered. Kesh did not dare to oppose the might "
"of Th'arwya for a long time."
msgstr ""
"No es mi vida la que está en peligro. Kesh no se atrevió a oponerse al poder "
"de Th'arwya durante mucho tiempo."

#. [message], speaker=Iskandar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/14_Tharwya.cfg:301
msgid ""
"The army of Kesh is marching towards Serrul in order to destroy it. If they "
"return, they'll head for Th'arwya. It is just a matter of time until your "
"life is endangered."
msgstr ""
"El ejército de Kesh marcha hacia Serrul para destruirlo. Si regresan, se "
"dirigirán a Th'arwya. Es solo cuestión de tiempo hasta que tu vida esté en "
"peligro."

#. [message], speaker=Maralek
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/14_Tharwya.cfg:306
msgid ""
"Then prove to me that you are worthy of fighting within the ranks of the "
"army of Th'arwya."
msgstr ""
"Entonces demuéstrame que eres digno de luchar dentro de las filas del "
"ejército de Th'arwya."

#. [message], speaker=Iskandar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/14_Tharwya.cfg:311
msgid "What do you demand then?"
msgstr "¿Qué exiges entonces?"

#. [message], speaker=Maralek
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/14_Tharwya.cfg:316
msgid ""
"There's a group of bandits below the sands of Th'arwya. In the canalisation. "
"We are experiencing an increase of attacks from that group. You'll have to "
"help the town guards out and bring an end to the thieves' guild."
msgstr ""
"Hay un grupo de bandidos debajo de las arenas de Th'arwya. En la "
"canalización. Estamos experimentando un aumento de ataques de ese grupo. "
"Tendrán que ayudar a los guardias de la ciudad y poner fin al gremio de "
"ladrones."

#. [message], speaker=Maralek
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/14_Tharwya.cfg:321
msgid ""
"Once you're done, visit me again and I'll think about supporting your cause."
msgstr "Una vez que terminen, visítenme de nuevo y pensaré en apoyar su causa."

#. [message], speaker=Iskandar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/14_Tharwya.cfg:326
msgid "We will be back."
msgstr "Volveremos."

#. [message], speaker=Iskandar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/14_Tharwya.cfg:335
msgid "Hmpph."
msgstr "Hmpph."

#. [message], speaker=Iskandar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/14_Tharwya.cfg:340
msgid "That should not have happened, we don't have much time left."
msgstr "Eso no debería haber pasado, no nos queda mucho tiempo."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/14_Tharwya.cfg:345
msgid "Maybe we should . . . convince . . . him by other means?"
msgstr "¿Tal vez deberíamos... convencerlo... por otros medios?"

#. [message], speaker=Iskandar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/14_Tharwya.cfg:350
msgid ""
"No, no, I can't use my power to play a mindtrick on him. Ma'ralek is also an "
"Athvari and the Sphere would recognize us."
msgstr ""
"No, no, no puedo usar mi poder para jugarle una treta mental. Ma'ralek "
"también es un athvari y la Esfera nos reconocería."

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/14_Tharwya.cfg:355
msgid ""
"He said the Dune Warmaster went through the deserts with a small group? That "
"does not sound realistic. Why would a man of such importance travel through "
"the vastness of the deserts with just a small group?"
msgstr ""
"¿Dijo que el Maestro de Guerra cruzó los desiertos con un pequeño grupo? Eso "
"no suena realista. ¿Por qué un hombre de tanta importancia viajaría a través "
"de la vastedad de los desiertos con solo un pequeño grupo?"

#. [message], speaker=Iskandar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/14_Tharwya.cfg:360
msgid ""
"The Dune Warmaster of Th'arwya, Ibn Ghani, is no Athvari, Ilriel. He can't "
"foresee fate, nor is he able to foretell the dangers that are invisible to "
"the eye of the unaware. But Ma'ralek. He is."
msgstr ""
"El Maestro de Guerra de Th'arwya, Ibn Ghani, no es un athvari, Ilriel. No "
"puede prever el destino, ni puede predecir los peligros invisibles al ojo de "
"los desprevenidos. Pero Ma'ralek. Él sí."

#. [message], speaker=Iskandar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/14_Tharwya.cfg:365
msgid ""
"Ma'ralek is an Athvari, Ilriel. He is one of my kin and as such, he is able "
"to foresee the future - to a certain degree. He should have foreseen the "
"things that eventually happened to Ibn Ghani. But why didn't he warn him?"
msgstr ""
"Ma'ralek es un athvari, Ilriel. Es uno de mi linaje y como tal, es capaz de "
"prever el futuro, hasta cierto punto. Debería haber previsto las cosas que "
"eventualmente le pasaron a Ibn Ghani. Pero ¿por qué no lo advirtió?"

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/14_Tharwya.cfg:370
msgid "Maybe it was the clouds of Kesh that nebulized his senses."
msgstr "Tal vez fueron las nubes de Kesh las que nublaron sus sentidos."

#. [message], speaker=Iskandar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/14_Tharwya.cfg:375
msgid ""
"Maybe it was, maybe not. It is all just hypotheses. Yet time is against us. "
"Just at this moment, the forces of Kesh are marching, earth shattering below "
"their feet. We have to do as Ma'ralek commands. Let us head to the "
"canalisation and banish the bandits from these deserts. I don't feel good "
"about it either, but it has to be done. It is our only option."
msgstr ""
"Tal vez lo fue, tal vez no. Todo son solo hipótesis. Sin embargo, el tiempo "
"está en contra nuestra. Justo en este momento, las fuerzas de Kesh marchan, "
"la tierra se agrieta bajo sus pies. Tenemos que hacer lo que Ma'ralek "
"ordena. Dirijámonos a la canalización y expulsemos a los bandidos de estos "
"desiertos. A mí tampoco me gusta, pero tiene que hacerse. Es nuestra única "
"opción."

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/14_Tharwya.cfg:385
msgid "The group descends into the canalisation of Th'arwya"
msgstr "El grupo desciende a la canalización de Th'arwya"

#. [note]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/14_Tharwya.cfg:389
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/14_Tharwya.cfg:534
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/16_Return_to_Tharwya.cfg:735
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/16_Return_to_Tharwya.cfg:757
msgid ""
"The Wyvern Trader offers special deals for Dune Spearguard, Spearmaster, "
"Greatlance, Azyan and Sandstalker."
msgstr ""
"El Comerciante de Guivernos ofrece ofertas especiales para Lancero, "
"Alabardero, Gran Alabardero, Azyan y Acechador Barján."

#. [note]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/14_Tharwya.cfg:392
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/14_Tharwya.cfg:537
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/16_Return_to_Tharwya.cfg:738
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/16_Return_to_Tharwya.cfg:760
msgid ""
"The Mercenary Buyer Trader buys regular units. lvl 1: 10 gold, lvl 2: 40 "
"gold, lvl 3: 65 gold and lvl 4: 90 gold."
msgstr ""
"El Comprador de Mercenarios adquiere unidades normales. Nivel 1: 10 de oro, "
"nivel 2: 40 de oro, nivel 3: 65 de oro y nivel 4: 90 de oro."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/14_Tharwya.cfg:410
msgid "That must be the entrance to the canalisation. Let us head in!"
msgstr "Ese debe ser la entrada a la canalización. ¡Entremos!"

#. [message], speaker=Wahdet
#. [message], speaker=Azyan
#. [message], speaker=Uthman
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/14_Tharwya.cfg:415
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/15_Blackhands.cfg:498
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/21_Battle_of_the_Eons.cfg:337
msgid "Wait!"
msgstr "¡Esperen!"

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/14_Tharwya.cfg:423
msgid "Mercenary, speak."
msgstr "Mercenario, habla."

#. [message], speaker=Wahdet
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/14_Tharwya.cfg:428
msgid "It is dangerous in there, you shouldn't go alone! Let me accompany you."
msgstr ""
"Es peligroso allí adentro, ¡no deberían ir solos! Déjenme acompañarlos."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/14_Tharwya.cfg:433
msgid "You didn't bring your weapons."
msgstr "No trajiste tus armas."

#. [message], speaker=Wahdet
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/14_Tharwya.cfg:438
msgid ""
"It is not the weapons that make a good warrior. The ones lurking in the "
"depths don't care about your weapons. How do you plan to strike the shadows "
"themselves?"
msgstr ""
"No son las armas las que hacen a un buen guerrero. Los que acechan en las "
"profundidades no se preocupan por tus armas. ¿Cómo planean golpear a las "
"sombras mismas?"

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/14_Tharwya.cfg:443
msgid "It seems that the depths aren't unknown to you."
msgstr "Parece que las profundidades no te son desconocidas."

#. [message], speaker=Wahdet
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/14_Tharwya.cfg:448
msgid ""
"It is my task to expel the bandits from the depths. Currently, I am hiring "
"mercenaries to support my cause. But maybe . . . I should join you. There "
"are not many travellers around these days."
msgstr ""
"Es mi tarea expulsar a los bandidos de las profundidades. Actualmente estoy "
"contratando mercenarios para apoyar mi causa. Pero tal vez... debería unirme "
"a ustedes. No hay muchos viajeros en estos días."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/14_Tharwya.cfg:453
msgid ""
"Then join our group. Fighting together, they won't stand a chance. And "
"fighting together, we'll quickly cleanse the depths and gain more time."
msgstr ""
"Entonces únete a nuestro grupo. Luchando juntos, no tendrán oportunidad. Y "
"luchando juntos, limpiaremos rápidamente las profundidades y ganaremos más "
"tiempo."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/14_Tharwya.cfg:471
msgid ""
"Meanwhile we can take a look at the merchants items. For sure we can find "
"excellent armor, weapons and more here. Maybe we can even find some "
"mercenaries here that support our cause."
msgstr ""
"Mientras tanto podemos echar un vistazo a los artículos de los mercaderes. "
"Seguro podemos encontrar excelente armadura, armas y más aquí. Tal vez "
"incluso encontremos algunos mercenarios aquí que apoyen nuestra causa."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/14_Tharwya.cfg:478
msgid "Dondolin sells heavy armor."
msgstr "Dondolin vende armadura pesada."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/14_Tharwya.cfg:485
msgid "You can hire mercenaries at Karah."
msgstr "Puedes contratar mercenarios en Karah."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/14_Tharwya.cfg:492
msgid "You can sell your units to Wahdet."
msgstr "Puedes vender tus unidades a Wahdet."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/14_Tharwya.cfg:499
msgid "You can buy weapons at Jadar."
msgstr "Puedes comprar armas en Jadar."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/14_Tharwya.cfg:506
msgid ""
"Sakran sells potions. Potions behave like normal items. A unit may only "
"drink one potion. It can't wear any further item then or drink another "
"potion."
msgstr ""
"Sakran vende pociones. Las pociones se comportan como objetos normales. Una "
"unidad solo puede beber una poción. Entonces no puede llevar ningún otro "
"objeto ni beber otra poción."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/14_Tharwya.cfg:513
msgid "Sharaf sells mighty wyverns."
msgstr "Sharaf vende poderosos guivernos."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/14_Tharwya.cfg:520
msgid ""
"A unit is able to walk up the stairs and reach the next plateau of the tower "
"of Th'arwya."
msgstr ""
"Una unidad puede subir las escaleras y llegar al siguiente nivel de la torre "
"de Th'arwya."

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/14_Tharwya.cfg:530
msgid "Iskandar convinces Ma'ralek to send his army to support his cause."
msgstr ""
"Iskandar convence a Ma'ralek de enviar su ejército para apoyar su causa."

#. [message], speaker=Uthain
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/14_Tharwya.cfg:556
msgid ""
"Ohhh! All these merchants! All those relics and artifacts! Now it's time to "
"get some goodies for myself, right? Kesh isn't the true problem, the true "
"problem is that I don't have enough gold to buy all this stuff!"
msgstr ""
"¡Ohhh! ¡Todos estos mercaderes! ¡Todas esas reliquias y artefactos! ¡Ahora "
"es momento de conseguir algunas golosinas para mí, verdad? Kesh no es el "
"verdadero problema, el verdadero problema es que no tengo suficiente oro "
"para comprar todas estas cosas!"

#. [message]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/14_Tharwya.cfg:577
msgid "I tell you, yesterday I saw a scarab as large as a minotaur!"
msgstr "Te digo, ayer vi un escarabajo tan grande como un minotauro!"

#. [message]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/14_Tharwya.cfg:581
msgid "As large as a minotaur? I saw one like the tower of Th'arwya!"
msgstr "¿Tan grande como un minotauro? ¡Vi uno como la torre de Th'arwya!"

#. [message]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/14_Tharwya.cfg:585
msgid "You are lying!"
msgstr "¡Estás mintiendo!"

#. [message]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/14_Tharwya.cfg:589
msgid "Uhm, no?"
msgstr "¿Uhm, no?"

#. [message]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/14_Tharwya.cfg:611
msgid "Whatch'a looking at, sand eater? You better get out of Th'arwya!"
msgstr "¿Qué estás mirando, come arena? ¡Mejor sal de Th'arwya!"

#. [message], speaker=Azyan
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/14_Tharwya.cfg:616
msgid ""
"Something is indeed wrong here. Th'arwya, a city where both men and genie "
"prosper. Yet take a look at their faces. They lost their hope. Even the "
"genie refuse to smile."
msgstr ""
"Algo está mal aquí. Th'arwya, una ciudad donde tanto los hombres como los "
"genios prosperan. Sin embargo, miren sus rostros. Han perdido la esperanza. "
"Incluso los genios se niegan a sonreír."

#. [message], speaker=Azyan
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/14_Tharwya.cfg:621
msgid ""
"It seems like Afariyaten are tolerated in this city. This has never been the "
"case before."
msgstr ""
"Parece que los afariyaten son tolerados en esta ciudad. Esto nunca había "
"sido el caso antes."

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/14_Tharwya.cfg:626
msgid "Afariyaten?"
msgstr "¿Afariyaten?"

#. [message], speaker=Azyan
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/14_Tharwya.cfg:631
msgid ""
"Inherently evil beings. Beings that lost all senses of moral and honour. "
"Beings that were magically created by the sands of the deserts when the "
"three kings claimed the thrones. Here, take a look at their mercenary."
msgstr ""
"Seres inherentemente malignos. Seres que perdieron todo sentido de moral y "
"honor. Seres que fueron creados mágicamente por las arenas de los desiertos "
"cuando los tres reyes reclamaron los tronos. Aquí, mira a su mercenario."

#. [message], speaker=Azyan
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/14_Tharwya.cfg:642
msgid ""
"A half-afariyat. Just as I am a half-genie. This man took up the very "
"essence of evil itself. Ilriel, the afariyaten are the foes of the genie, "
"that once created Th'arwya, and they should not be here. They've sided with "
"the three kings. Why are they tolerated here? We have to watch out."
msgstr ""
"Un medio afariyat. Igual que yo soy un medio genio. Este hombre tomó la "
"esencia misma del mal. Ilriel, los afariyaten son los enemigos de los "
"genios, que una vez crearon Th'arwya, y no deberían estar aquí. Se aliaron "
"con los tres reyes. ¿Por qué son tolerados aquí? Tenemos que estar atentos."

#. [message]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/14_Tharwya.cfg:659
msgid ""
"Hmpfh, these wyverns are huge. They can probably be ridden just like "
"gryphons!"
msgstr ""
"Hmpfh, estos guivernos son enormes. ¡Probablemente se puedan montar igual "
"que grifos!"

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/14_Tharwya.cfg:664
msgid "Dwarves?!"
msgstr "¡¿Enanos?!"

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/14_Tharwya.cfg:675
msgid ""
"The citizen, the merchants . . . they don't look like they've experienced "
"happiness for a long time. This is not the Th'arwya that I used to know."
msgstr ""
"Los ciudadanos, los mercaderes... no parecen haber experimentado felicidad "
"desde hace mucho tiempo. Esta no es la Th'arwya que yo conocía."

#. [message], speaker=Iskandar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/14_Tharwya.cfg:680
msgid "Something is plaguing them and we'll have to find out what it is."
msgstr "Algo los está atormentando y tendremos que descubrir qué es."

#. [message], speaker=Iskandar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/14_Tharwya.cfg:685
msgid ""
"Ma'ralek is an old friend of mine. And he is one of us. He'll have the "
"answers that we are searching for."
msgstr ""
"Ma'ralek es un viejo amigo mío. Y es uno de los nuestros. Tendrá las "
"respuestas que buscamos."

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/14_Tharwya.cfg:690
msgid "Yet the tower guardian doesn't look like he'd let us through."
msgstr "Sin embargo, el guardián de la torre no parece que nos dejará pasar."

#. [message], speaker=Biqu
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/14_Tharwya.cfg:701
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/16_Return_to_Tharwya.cfg:409
msgid "Hold! You shall not pass!"
msgstr "¡Alto! ¡No pasarán!"

#. [message], speaker=Biqu
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/14_Tharwya.cfg:707
msgid "Oh . . . an . . . an Athvari. Pass through."
msgstr "Oh... un... un athvari. Pasen."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/14_Tharwya.cfg:715
msgid ""
"The higher plains of the tower of Th'arwya are reserved for the ones deemed "
"worthy. They don't know our potential . . .  not yet."
msgstr ""
"Las llanuras superiores de la torre de Th'arwya están reservadas para los "
"considerados dignos. No conocen nuestro potencial... todavía no."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/14_Tharwya.cfg:720
msgid "But they do know yours, Iskandar. They'll let you pass."
msgstr "Pero sí conocen el tuyo, Iskandar. Te dejarán pasar."

#. [message]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/14_Tharwya.cfg:735
msgid "What does that woman cost?"
msgstr "¿Cuánto cuesta esa mujer?"

#. [message], speaker=Karah
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/14_Tharwya.cfg:740
msgid "I don't sell her!"
msgstr "¡No la vendo!"

#. [part]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/15_Blackhands.cfg:7
msgid ""
"The group entered the canalisation of Th'arwya just as the Dune Warmaster "
"told them to. Being engulfed by darkness once again, Ilriel wondered what "
"human beings would live in this darkness. Would they even be human? Or would "
"they just be a mere shadow of their former lives?"
msgstr ""
"El grupo entró en la canalización de Th'arwya tal como les dijo el Maestro "
"de Guerra Barján. Envuelta en oscuridad una vez más, Ilriel se preguntaba "
"qué seres humanos vivirían en esta oscuridad. ¿Serían siquiera humanos? ¿O "
"solo serían una mera sombra de sus vidas anteriores?"

#. [scenario], id=15_Blackhands
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/15_Blackhands.cfg:18
msgid "Blackhands"
msgstr "Manos Negras"

#. [side], type=Dune Assassin
#. [side], type=Dune Combuster
#. [side], type=Dune Sandlurker
#. [side], type=Dune Wayfarer
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/15_Blackhands.cfg:63
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/15_Blackhands.cfg:91
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/15_Blackhands.cfg:119
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/15_Blackhands.cfg:148
msgid "Thieves"
msgstr "Ladrones"

#. [side], type=Dune Assassin
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/15_Blackhands.cfg:69
msgid "Shab"
msgstr "Shab"

#. [side], type=Dune Combuster
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/15_Blackhands.cfg:97
msgid "Zala"
msgstr "Zala"

#. [side], type=Dune Sandlurker
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/15_Blackhands.cfg:126
msgid "Alshafq"
msgstr "Alshafq"

#. [side], type=Dune Wayfarer
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/15_Blackhands.cfg:155
msgid "Mady"
msgstr "Mady"

#. [side]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/15_Blackhands.cfg:177
msgid "Shrooms"
msgstr "Hongos"

#. [event]
#. [side]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/15_Blackhands.cfg:209
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/17_The_Great_Wall.cfg:86
msgid "Ibn Ghani"
msgstr "Ibn Ghani"

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/15_Blackhands.cfg:383
msgid ""
"This is the canalisation, the thieves that Ma'ralek told us about must be "
"somewhere in here."
msgstr ""
"Esta es la canalización, los ladrones de los que nos habló Ma'ralek deben "
"estar por aquí en alguna parte."

#. [message], speaker=Azyan
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/15_Blackhands.cfg:388
msgid ""
"This place houses evil men, but they surely don't rest inbetween these "
"sewers. Watch out and see if we can find an entrance to their guild!"
msgstr ""
"Este lugar alberga hombres malvados, pero seguro no descansan entre estas "
"alcantarillas. ¡Estén atentos y vean si podemos encontrar una entrada a su "
"gremio!"

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/15_Blackhands.cfg:393
msgid "Tell us, mercenary, what do you know about this place?"
msgstr "Dinos, mercenario, ¿qué sabes de este lugar?"

#. [message], speaker=Wahdet
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/15_Blackhands.cfg:398
msgid ""
"The canalisation is like a labyrinth, passages fill with water, yet dry out "
"again. It's like the walls themselves are moving. Behind every wall might be "
"a foe - or just a rat that is feasting on the remains of the ones who were "
"here before us . . . and didn't find out again."
msgstr ""
"La canalización es como un laberinto, los pasajes se llenan de agua, pero se "
"secan de nuevo. Es como si las paredes mismas se movieran. Detrás de cada "
"pared podría haber un enemigo, o solo una rata que se alimenta de los restos "
"de los que estuvieron aquí antes que nosotros... y no salieron de nuevo."

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/15_Blackhands.cfg:403
msgid "Then we shouldn't dwell here for too long. Where's the thieve's guild?"
msgstr ""
"Entonces no deberíamos quedarnos aquí demasiado tiempo. ¿Dónde está el "
"gremio de ladrones?"

#. [message], speaker=Wahdet
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/15_Blackhands.cfg:408
msgid ""
"I've never seen it with my own eyes, yet during my last approach to find it, "
"it seemed that the bandits were emerging from within the walls. There must "
"be a hidden entrance somewhere in the canalisation."
msgstr ""
"Nunca lo he visto con mis propios ojos, pero durante mi último intento de "
"encontrarlo, parecía que los bandidos emergían desde dentro de las paredes. "
"Debe haber una entrada oculta en alguna parte de la canalización."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/15_Blackhands.cfg:413
msgid ""
"Then it is clear what we are searching for. Men! Pay attention to every "
"crack in the walls and to every bone that's not lying on one another. And in "
"case, be prepared to turn every stone thrice."
msgstr ""
"Entonces está claro qué buscamos. ¡Hombres! Presten atención a cada grieta "
"en las paredes y a cada hueso que no esté uno sobre otro. Y en caso, estén "
"preparados para voltear cada piedra tres veces."

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/15_Blackhands.cfg:421
msgid "Find the thieves' guild and defeat the leader of the thieves."
msgstr "Encuentra el gremio de ladrones y derrota al líder de los ladrones."

#. [note]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/15_Blackhands.cfg:431
msgid "This is not the final objective."
msgstr "Este no es el objetivo final."

#. [message], speaker=Azyan
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/15_Blackhands.cfg:442
msgid ""
"These bandits . . . their faces . . . I know them. They once belonged to the "
"survivors of my tribe, even before the servants of Kesh tried to recruit us. "
"It seems like the destruction of our homes by the hands of Kesh led them to "
"dark paths. But they seem to be so different, so fierce. I don't remember "
"them being like that."
msgstr ""
"Estos bandidos... sus rostros... los conozco. Una vez pertenecieron a los "
"sobrevivientes de mi tribu, incluso antes de que los sirvientes de Kesh "
"intentaran reclutarnos. Parece que la destrucción de nuestros hogares por "
"manos de Kesh los llevó a caminos oscuros. Pero parecen tan diferentes, tan "
"feroces. No los recuerdo así."

#. [message], speaker=Iskandar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/15_Blackhands.cfg:447
msgid "It is Kesh, these bandits pledged allegiance to it."
msgstr "Es Kesh, estos bandidos le juraron lealtad."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/15_Blackhands.cfg:465
msgid "Look there!"
msgstr "¡Miren allá!"

#. [message], speaker=Ibn Ghani
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/15_Blackhands.cfg:470
msgid "Help!"
msgstr "¡Ayuda!"

#. [message], speaker=Iskandar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/15_Blackhands.cfg:475
msgid "Ibn Ghani! The Dune Warmaster of Th'arwya!"
msgstr "¡Ibn Ghani! ¡El Maestro de Guerra de Th'arwya!"

#. [message], speaker=Ibn Ghani
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/15_Blackhands.cfg:480
msgid "Pay attention, the leader of the bandit's is near!"
msgstr "¡Estén atentos, el líder de los bandidos está cerca!"

#. [message], speaker=Azyan
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/15_Blackhands.cfg:503
msgid "Sh . . . Shab? Is it you?"
msgstr "¿Sh... Shab? ¿Eres tú?"

#. [message], speaker=Shab
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/15_Blackhands.cfg:508
msgid "Azyan, my brother?"
msgstr "¿Azyan, mi hermano?"

#. [message], speaker=Azyan
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/15_Blackhands.cfg:513
msgid "What did you become? A thief? A murderer?"
msgstr "¿En qué te convertiste? ¿Un ladrón? ¿Un asesino?"

#. [message], speaker=Shab
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/15_Blackhands.cfg:518
msgid ""
"A lost one. Everything I had, everything I've ever dreamed of, is lost. "
"Destroyed by Kesh."
msgstr ""
"Un perdido. Todo lo que tenía, todo lo que alguna vez soñé, se perdió. "
"Destruido por Kesh."

#. [message], speaker=Azyan
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/15_Blackhands.cfg:523
msgid ""
"Yet it was your decision to live the life of a monster. It's not the fault "
"of Kesh."
msgstr ""
"Sin embargo, fue tu decisión vivir la vida de un monstruo. No es culpa de "
"Kesh."

#. [message], speaker=Shab
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/15_Blackhands.cfg:528
msgid ""
"Maybe it is not, maybe it is. What does that even matter? These lands are "
"cursed since the reign of the Three and another era of chaos soon will come. "
"Why not experience ultimate freedom until then? Freedom that isn't limited "
"by anything."
msgstr ""
"Tal vez no lo sea, tal vez sí. ¿Qué importa eso? Estas tierras están "
"malditas desde el reinado de los Tres y pronto vendrá otra era de caos. ¿Por "
"qué no experimentar la libertad absoluta hasta entonces? Libertad que no "
"está limitada por nada."

#. [message], speaker=Azyan
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/15_Blackhands.cfg:533
msgid "You are sickening me, brother."
msgstr "Me das asco, hermano."

#. [message], speaker=Shab
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/15_Blackhands.cfg:538
msgid "Come on, join us, Azyan. You can't imagine what you're missing."
msgstr ""
"Vamos, únete a nosotros, Azyan. No puedes imaginarte lo que te estás "
"perdiendo."

#. [message], speaker=Azyan
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/15_Blackhands.cfg:543
msgid ""
"No! There's still a chance to expel the poison of Kesh and bring back the "
"fortune of these lands!"
msgstr ""
"¡No! ¡Todavía hay una oportunidad de expulsar el veneno de Kesh y traer de "
"vuelta la fortuna de estas tierras!"

#. [message], speaker=Shab
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/15_Blackhands.cfg:548
msgid "You can't expel what's part of us, Azyan! We are Kesh!"
msgstr "¡No puedes expulsar lo que es parte de nosotros, Azyan! ¡Somos Kesh!"

#. [message], speaker=Azyan
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/15_Blackhands.cfg:553
msgid "You've sided with the ones who tried to enslave you? You are insane!"
msgstr "¿Te has aliado con los que intentaron esclavizarte? ¡Estás loco!"

#. [message], speaker=Shab
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/15_Blackhands.cfg:558
msgid "It's a bummer, such a bummer . . ."
msgstr "Es una lástima, qué lástima..."

#. [message], speaker=Shab
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/15_Blackhands.cfg:563
msgid "Men, bring me his head!"
msgstr "¡Hombres, tráiganme su cabeza!"

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/15_Blackhands.cfg:577
msgid "You've plagued Th'arwya for too long, bandit."
msgstr "Has atormentado Th'arwya por demasiado tiempo, bandido."

#. [message], speaker=Azyan
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/15_Blackhands.cfg:582
msgid "Any deed has its consequences, brother."
msgstr "Cualquier acción tiene sus consecuencias, hermano."

#. [message], speaker=Shab
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/15_Blackhands.cfg:587
msgid "What . . . what do . . . you know about . . . it all? No . . . Nothing!"
msgstr "¿Qué... qué sabes... tú de... todo esto? ¡No... nada!"

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/15_Blackhands.cfg:592
msgid "Your brother gave us no choice."
msgstr "Tu hermano no nos dejó otra opción."

#. [message], speaker=Azyan
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/15_Blackhands.cfg:597
msgid "He isn't my brother, at least . . . not anymore."
msgstr "No es mi hermano, al menos... ya no."

#. [message], speaker=Wahdet
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/15_Blackhands.cfg:602
msgid "Then let us free our former Dune Warmaster, Ibn Ghani, the fallen king."
msgstr ""
"Entonces liberemos a nuestro antiguo Maestro de Guerra, Ibn Ghani, el rey "
"caído."

#. [message], speaker=Ibn Ghani
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/15_Blackhands.cfg:620
msgid "I am indebted to you, brave warriors."
msgstr "Estoy en deuda con ustedes, valientes guerreros."

#. [message], speaker=Iskandar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/15_Blackhands.cfg:625
msgid "Ibn Ghani! What happened to you? Ma'ralek told . . . "
msgstr "¡Ibn Ghani! ¿Qué te pasó? Ma'ralek dijo..."

#. [message], speaker=Ibn Ghani
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/15_Blackhands.cfg:630
msgid ""
"Screw Ma'ralek! He is a traitor and responsible for my capture. I should've "
"never trusted him."
msgstr ""
"¡Al diablo con Ma'ralek! Es un traidor y responsable de mi captura. Nunca "
"debí confiar en él."

#. [message], speaker=Iskandar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/15_Blackhands.cfg:635
msgid "It seems as your intuition was right, Ilriel."
msgstr "Parece que tu intuición era correcta, Ilriel."

#. [message], speaker=Ibn Ghani
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/15_Blackhands.cfg:640
msgid ""
"He made a pact with Kesh behind my back, at times, when I was still king. "
"Slowly, agents of Kesh infiltrated the city and the canalisation in order "
"the overthrow my reign. The poison of Kesh infested his mind, Iskandar. I "
"hope that's not happening to you."
msgstr ""
"Hizo un pacto con Kesh a mis espaldas, en tiempos cuando aún era rey. "
"Lentamente, agentes de Kesh se infiltraron en la ciudad y en la canalización "
"para derrocar mi reinado. El veneno de Kesh infestó su mente, Iskandar. "
"Espero que eso no te esté pasando a ti."

#. [message], speaker=Iskandar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/15_Blackhands.cfg:645
msgid ""
"We will get you out of here, Ibn Ghani, and Ma'ralek will pay the price for "
"selling all what is worth to him to Kesh. He surely was an advisor and "
"vicegerent, yet not for the city of Th'arwya."
msgstr ""
"Te sacaremos de aquí, Ibn Ghani, y Ma'ralek pagará el precio por vender todo "
"lo que vale a Kesh. Seguramente fue un asesor y vicegerente, pero no para la "
"ciudad de Th'arwya."

#. [message], speaker=Wahdet
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/15_Blackhands.cfg:650
msgid "It is not my wish to interrupt you, but do you hear that?"
msgstr "No es mi deseo interrumpirlos, pero ¿oyen eso?"

#. [message], speaker=Nuvdael
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/15_Blackhands.cfg:657
msgid "Footsteps! At least of a dozen of heavily armoured men!"
msgstr "¡Pisadas! ¡Al menos de una docena de hombres fuertemente armados!"

#. [message], speaker=Uthain
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/15_Blackhands.cfg:662
msgid "Seems like someone doesn't want us to sniff in these depths."
msgstr "Parece que alguien no quiere que husmeemos en estas profundidades."

#. [message], speaker=Ibn Ghani
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/15_Blackhands.cfg:667
msgid ""
"Ma'ralek surely got notice of the cleansing of the thieves guild and my "
"release. But now he can't stop us anymore. Iskandar and your loyal group, "
"stand at my side when we face Ma'ralek and his servants. He knows what will "
"happen to him, yet he won't change it. I'll take his head and claim what "
"once belonged to me. The throne of Th'arwya."
msgstr ""
"Ma'ralek seguro se enteró de la limpieza del gremio de ladrones y mi "
"liberación. Pero ahora ya no puede detenernos. Iskandar y tu leal grupo, "
"permanezcan a mi lado cuando enfrentemos a Ma'ralek y sus servidores. Él "
"sabe lo que le pasará, pero no lo cambiará. Tomaré su cabeza y reclamaré lo "
"que una vez me perteneció. El trono de Th'arwya."

#. [message], speaker=Azyan
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/15_Blackhands.cfg:672
msgid "Whatever it is, that is coming at us, pay attention."
msgstr "Sea lo que sea que viene hacia nosotros, estén atentos."

#. [message], speaker=Ashuar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/15_Blackhands.cfg:706
msgid "Forward! It's time to smoke them out!"
msgstr "¡Adelante! ¡Es hora de sacarlos!"

#. [message], speaker=Azyan
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/15_Blackhands.cfg:711
msgid "Indeed, mercenaries from Th'arwya!"
msgstr "¡En efecto, mercenarios de Th'arwya!"

#. [message], speaker=Nuvdael
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/15_Blackhands.cfg:716
msgid "There is no chance they moved unseen infront of the eyes of Ma'ralek."
msgstr ""
"No hay posibilidad de que se movieran sin ser vistos frente a los ojos de "
"Ma'ralek."

#. [message], speaker=Azyan
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/15_Blackhands.cfg:721
msgid "And they've taken a shortcut! They knew about our doings and dealings!"
msgstr "¡Y tomaron un atajo! ¡Sabían de nuestras acciones y tratos!"

#. [message], speaker=Ibn Ghani
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/15_Blackhands.cfg:726
msgid "These are Ma'ralek's servants!"
msgstr "¡Estos son los sirvientes de Ma'ralek!"

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/15_Blackhands.cfg:731
msgid "Quick, into formation!"
msgstr "¡Rápido, en formación!"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/15_Blackhands.cfg:738
msgid "Defeat Ashuar"
msgstr "Derrota a Ashuar"

#. [note]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/15_Blackhands.cfg:742
msgid ""
"You can recruit from the fields in the northeast of Ibn Ghani's former cage."
msgstr ""
"Puedes reclutar de los campos al noreste de la antigua jaula de Ibn Ghani."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/15_Blackhands.cfg:760
msgid ""
"A dirty swashbuckler sent by Ma'ralek. It's time to face the traitor and do "
"whatever is needed to deal with him."
msgstr ""
"Un sucio espadachín enviado por Ma'ralek. Es hora de enfrentar al traidor y "
"hacer lo que sea necesario para lidiar con él."

#. [message], speaker=Azyan
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/15_Blackhands.cfg:789
msgid ""
"They are beginning to corner us, we'll never make it out alive from here now!"
msgstr "¡Están comenzando a acorralarnos, nunca saldremos vivos de aquí ahora!"

#. [part]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/16_Return_to_Tharwya.cfg:7
msgid ""
"Entering the thieves' guild, Ilriel and Ilaroth soon found out that the "
"bandits lurking in the depths were indeed just ordinary mortals. They didn't "
"show mercy to the ones who pledged allegiance to Kesh. Feeling the cold grip "
"of Kesh at his neck, Ilaroth didn't feel like wasting too much time in the "
"depths. The people of the desert realms needed them and Ilaroth quickly "
"prepared a trophy for Ma'ralek - a trophy to prove that they've dealt with "
"the bandits, thieves and cutpurses."
msgstr ""
"Al entrar al gremio de ladrones, Ilriel e Ilaroth pronto descubrieron que "
"los bandidos que acechaban en las profundidades eran en efecto solo mortales "
"ordinarios. No mostraron misericordia a los que juraron lealtad a Kesh. "
"Sintiendo el frío agarre de Kesh en su cuello, Ilaroth no sentía ganas de "
"perder demasiado tiempo en las profundidades. El pueblo de los reinos del "
"desierto los necesitaba e Ilaroth rápidamente preparó un trofeo para "
"Ma'ralek, un trofeo para probar que habían lidiado con los bandidos, "
"ladrones y cortabolsas."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/16_Return_to_Tharwya.cfg:109
msgid ""
"Hold on! Don't close the portal! A ship arises on the horizon! It bears the "
"flag of Serrul!"
msgstr ""
"¡Esperen! ¡No cierren el portal! ¡Un barco surge en el horizonte! ¡Lleva la "
"bandera de Serrul!"

#. [message], speaker=Iskandar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/16_Return_to_Tharwya.cfg:114
msgid "Wh . . .what?"
msgstr "¿Qu... qué?"

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/16_Return_to_Tharwya.cfg:119
msgid "Take care of the portal, we will need it very soon."
msgstr "Cuida del portal, lo necesitaremos muy pronto."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/16_Return_to_Tharwya.cfg:124
msgid "Look! It must be Ridwan and Ibn Khazul!"
msgstr "¡Miren! ¡Deben ser Ridwan e Ibn Khazul!"

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/16_Return_to_Tharwya.cfg:167
msgid "Ridwan! Ibn Khazul!"
msgstr "¡Ridwan! ¡Ibn Khazul!"

#. [message], speaker=Iskandar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/16_Return_to_Tharwya.cfg:172
msgid ""
"So you made it out safely, you truly never disappoint me, Ridwan and Ibn "
"Khazul."
msgstr ""
"Así que lograron salir sanos y salvos, realmente nunca me decepcionan, "
"Ridwan e Ibn Khazul."

#. [message], speaker=Ridwan
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/16_Return_to_Tharwya.cfg:177
msgid ""
"Serrul. . .  the whole city is burned down to ashes and yet we were able to "
"find shelter on the high seas. But . . . the citizens. . . they fell victim "
"to the iron of Kesh."
msgstr ""
"Serrul... toda la ciudad fue quemada hasta las cenizas y aun así pudimos "
"encontrar refugio en alta mar. Pero... los ciudadanos... cayeron víctimas "
"del hierro de Kesh."

#. [message], speaker=Ibn Khazul
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/16_Return_to_Tharwya.cfg:182
msgid "Life is just a blink of eternity, Ridwan. We shall see them once again."
msgstr ""
"La vida es solo un parpadeo de la eternidad, Ridwan. Los veremos de nuevo."

#. [message], speaker=Ridwan
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/16_Return_to_Tharwya.cfg:187
msgid ""
"Maybe we will. But what will they do to us then? We should have protected "
"them. They relied on us and we let them down."
msgstr ""
"Tal vez lo hagamos. Pero ¿qué nos harán entonces? Deberíamos haberlos "
"protegido. Confiaron en nosotros y los decepcionamos."

#. [message], speaker=Iskandar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/16_Return_to_Tharwya.cfg:192
msgid ""
"Their deaths weigh heavy upon your souls, I can feel it. But there was "
"nothing you could have done to save them. You should be grateful that fate "
"spared your life."
msgstr ""
"Sus muertes pesan mucho sobre sus almas, puedo sentirlo. Pero no había nada "
"que pudieran haber hecho para salvarlos. Deberían estar agradecidos de que "
"el destino salvó sus vidas."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/16_Return_to_Tharwya.cfg:197
msgid ""
"We are in need of your help, Ridwan. Do you see this portal here? It leads "
"to Kesh."
msgstr "Necesitamos tu ayuda, Ridwan. ¿Ves este portal aquí? Lleva a Kesh."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/16_Return_to_Tharwya.cfg:202
msgid "We might as well use it."
msgstr "Bien podríamos usarlo."

#. [message], speaker=Ridwan
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/16_Return_to_Tharwya.cfg:207
msgid ""
"Kesh . . .  then it is time to strike back. I'll fell one hundred of them "
"for each dead citizen of Serrul!"
msgstr ""
"Kesh... entonces es momento de contraatacar. ¡Derribaré a cien de ellos por "
"cada ciudadano muerto de Serrul!"

#. [message], speaker=Iskandar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/16_Return_to_Tharwya.cfg:212
msgid ""
"I can understand your anger, but anger is not a good advisor. You can't come "
"with us, yet."
msgstr ""
"Puedo entender tu ira, pero la ira no es un buen consejero. Todavía no "
"puedes venir con nosotros."

#. [message], speaker=Ridwan
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/16_Return_to_Tharwya.cfg:217
msgid ""
"My swords are sharp and the citizens I've sworn to protect are dead. I will "
"find the ones responsible for this. Their blood shall be shed across the "
"desert realms."
msgstr ""
"Mis espadas están afiladas y los ciudadanos que juré proteger están muertos. "
"Encontraré a los responsables de esto. Su sangre se derramará por los reinos "
"del desierto."

#. [message], speaker=Iskandar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/16_Return_to_Tharwya.cfg:222
msgid "Your time will come, Ridwan. But not yet. We have another task for you."
msgstr ""
"Tu momento llegará, Ridwan. Pero todavía no. Tenemos otra tarea para ti."

#. [message], speaker=Iskandar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/16_Return_to_Tharwya.cfg:227
msgid ""
"Ridwan, you have to take your soldiers to escort the catapults of Th'arwya "
"to Kesh as they can't be moved through the portals. Lead them through the "
"Ashland deserts and the weight on your shoulders will lighten up. Meanwhile, "
"our group shall move through the portals and attack Kesh from within - or "
"from whatever place those lead to."
msgstr ""
"Ridwan, tienes que llevar a tus soldados para escoltar las catapultas de "
"Th'arwya a Kesh ya que no pueden moverse a través de los portales. Llévalos "
"a través de los desiertos de Ceniza y el peso sobre tus hombros se "
"aligerará. Mientras tanto, nuestro grupo se moverá a través de los portales "
"y atacará Kesh desde adentro, o desde cualquier lugar al que lleven."

#. [message], speaker=Ridwan
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/16_Return_to_Tharwya.cfg:232
msgid ""
"Catapults . . . then we will destroy their city and return what they've done "
"to us. For sure I will bring them to Kesh. We will be at the walls of Kesh "
"in less than a week."
msgstr ""
"Catapultas... entonces destruiremos su ciudad y devolveremos lo que nos "
"hicieron. Seguro las llevaré a Kesh. Estaremos en las murallas de Kesh en "
"menos de una semana."

#. [message], speaker=Iskandar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/16_Return_to_Tharwya.cfg:237
msgid ""
"Ibn Ghani, prepare your warriors and send them to the Cloud River, in case "
"you want this terror to stop. The great army of Kesh was sieging Serrul "
"until now. The Cloud River is a natural defensive line you can easily hold. "
"Hold them off of us and we'll deal with Kesh."
msgstr ""
"Ibn Ghani, prepara a tus guerreros y envíalos al Río de las Nubes, en caso "
"de que quieras que este terror se detenga. El gran ejército de Kesh estaba "
"asediando Serrul hasta ahora. El Río de las Nubes es una línea defensiva "
"natural que puedes mantener fácilmente. Manténlos alejados de nosotros y "
"nosotros lidiaremos con Kesh."

#. [message], speaker=Ibn Ghani
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/16_Return_to_Tharwya.cfg:250
msgid "Bring me my mighty steed!"
msgstr "¡Traiganme a mi poderoso corcel!"

#. [object]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/16_Return_to_Tharwya.cfg:254
msgid "Mounted Ibn Ghani"
msgstr "Ibn Ghani montado"

#. [object]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/16_Return_to_Tharwya.cfg:256
msgid "Ibn Ghani now rides a sandmare."
msgstr "Ibn Ghani ahora cabalga una pesadilla de arena."

#. [message], speaker=Uthain
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/16_Return_to_Tharwya.cfg:270
msgid "Uff!"
msgstr "¡Uff!"

#. [message], speaker=Ibn Ghani
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/16_Return_to_Tharwya.cfg:275
msgid ""
"We stand at your side, Athvari. You've saved our lives, so now it is our "
"duty to save yours. I'll order my soldiers to defend the Cloud River. I "
"shall lead my troops into battle personally. These days, Th'arwya marches, "
"not as individuals, but as a whole. During the days and weeks to come, the "
"different people of all kins and of all places of the world shall stand "
"united, side by side and sword and shield in hand. The might of Th'arwya "
"shall crush its foes and annihilate those, who seek evil!"
msgstr ""
"Estamos a su lado, athvari. Ustedes salvaron nuestras vidas, así que ahora "
"es nuestro deber salvar las suyas. Ordenaré a mis soldados defender el Río "
"de las Nubes. Yo mismo lideraré a mis tropas en batalla. En estos días, "
"Th'arwya marcha, no como individuos, sino como un todo. Durante los días y "
"semanas por venir, la gente diferente de todos los linajes y de todos los "
"lugares del mundo se mantendrá unida, lado a lado, con espada y escudo en "
"mano. ¡El poder de Th'arwya aplastará a sus enemigos y aniquilará a aquellos "
"que buscan el mal!"

#. [message], speaker=Ibn Ghani
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/16_Return_to_Tharwya.cfg:280
msgid ""
"Men! Pack your belongings and all that is worth to you! The earth shall "
"crumble beneath our feet and the mountains standing in our way shall break! "
"Th'arwya will march into war!"
msgstr ""
"¡Hombres! ¡Empaquen sus pertenencias y todo lo que les importe! ¡La tierra "
"se agrietará bajo nuestros pies y las montañas que se interpongan en nuestro "
"camino se romperán! ¡Th'arwya marchará a la guerra!"

#. [message], speaker=Iskandar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/16_Return_to_Tharwya.cfg:285
msgid "Thanks Ibn Ghani. May fortune guide you."
msgstr "Gracias Ibn Ghani. Que la fortuna te guíe."

#. [message], speaker=Iskandar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/16_Return_to_Tharwya.cfg:290
msgid "Then let us move through the portal, Ilarøth and Ilriel. Follow me!"
msgstr "Entonces movámonos a través del portal, Ilarøth e Ilriel. ¡Síganme!"

#. [scenario], id=16_Return_to_Tharwya
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/16_Return_to_Tharwya.cfg:305
msgid "Return to Th'arwya"
msgstr "Regreso a Th'arwya"

#. [side]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/16_Return_to_Tharwya.cfg:389
msgid "Forces of Kesh"
msgstr "Fuerzas de Kesh"

#. [message], speaker=Biqu
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/16_Return_to_Tharwya.cfg:415
msgid "Oh . . . it's you again . . . an . . . an Athvari. Pass through."
msgstr "Oh... son ustedes otra vez... un... un athvari. Pasen."

#. [message], speaker=Iskandar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/16_Return_to_Tharwya.cfg:440
msgid ""
"Ma'ralek lost most of his servants within the depths. We shouldn't face any "
"enemy towards the top of the tower of Th'arwya. Ibn Ghani, accompany me, and "
"revenge shall be yours to have. "
msgstr ""
"Ma'ralek perdió a la mayoría de sus sirvientes en las profundidades. No "
"deberíamos enfrentar ningún enemigo hacia la cima de la torre de Th'arwya. "
"Ibn Ghani, acompáñame, y la venganza será tuya."

#. [message], speaker=Maralek
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/16_Return_to_Tharwya.cfg:451
msgid ""
"You've cleansed the depths of the bandits and thieves. The news already "
"reached me and I am impressed, Iskandar."
msgstr ""
"Han limpiado las profundidades de los bandidos y ladrones. La noticia ya me "
"llegó y estoy impresionado, Iskandar."

#. [message], speaker=Maralek
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/16_Return_to_Tharwya.cfg:456
msgid "Forsooth, you've earned my . . . support for your cause."
msgstr "Por supuesto, se han ganado mi... apoyo para su causa."

#. [message], speaker=Iskandar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/16_Return_to_Tharwya.cfg:463
msgid ""
"We don't need anything from you, Ma'ralek, as your treason is known to us."
msgstr ""
"No necesitamos nada de ti, Ma'ralek, ya que tu traición es conocida por "
"nosotros."

#. [message], speaker=Maralek
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/16_Return_to_Tharwya.cfg:468
msgid "Wha . . . what?!"
msgstr "¿Qu... qué?!"

#. [message], speaker=Iskandar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/16_Return_to_Tharwya.cfg:473
msgid ""
"Oh, you need a reminder for your deeds? Shall we present you the one you've "
"sworn to protect? You've sworn to advice during hard times? The one you've "
"sworn an oath of allegiance to?"
msgstr ""
"Oh, ¿necesitas un recordatorio de tus acciones? ¿Debemos presentarte a quien "
"juraste proteger? ¿A quien juraste aconsejar en tiempos difíciles? ¿A quien "
"juraste un juramento de lealtad?"

#. [message], speaker=Maralek
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/16_Return_to_Tharwya.cfg:478
msgid "Guards! Guards!"
msgstr "¡Guardias! ¡Guardias!"

#. [message], speaker=Biqu
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/16_Return_to_Tharwya.cfg:484
msgid ""
"Your reign is over, Ma'ralek, as it was never yours to reign! Hold on, "
"guards!"
msgstr ""
"Tu reinado ha terminado, Ma'ralek, ¡ya que nunca fue tuyo para reinar! "
"¡Deténganse, guardias!"

#. [message], speaker=Maralek
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/16_Return_to_Tharwya.cfg:489
msgid "No! Noo!"
msgstr "¡No! ¡Noo!"

#. [message], speaker=Iskandar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/16_Return_to_Tharwya.cfg:494
msgid "Ibn Ghani!"
msgstr "¡Ibn Ghani!"

#. [message], speaker=Ibn Ghani
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/16_Return_to_Tharwya.cfg:501
msgid "You should've killed me when you had the opportunity to do so, traitor."
msgstr "Deberías haberme matado cuando tuviste la oportunidad, traidor."

#. [message], speaker=Maralek
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/16_Return_to_Tharwya.cfg:506
msgid ""
"Gifting you death? No, no, Kesh has better things to do with you . . . or "
"whatever remains of you."
msgstr ""
"¿Regalarte la muerte? No, no, Kesh tiene mejores cosas que hacer contigo... "
"o con lo que quede de ti."

#. [message], speaker=Ibn Ghani
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/16_Return_to_Tharwya.cfg:511
msgid "Kesh will fall and so will you."
msgstr "Kesh caerá y tú también."

#. [message], speaker=Maralek
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/16_Return_to_Tharwya.cfg:516
msgid ""
"It is Kesh that is laying down the laws of the game, Ibn Ghani. Some will "
"understand it earlier than others. Some will understand it never - some even "
"later. Maybe in death you will understand."
msgstr ""
"Es Kesh quien establece las leyes del juego, Ibn Ghani. Algunos lo "
"entenderán antes que otros. Algunos nunca lo entenderán, algunos incluso más "
"tarde. Tal vez en la muerte lo entiendas."

#. [message], speaker=Maralek
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/16_Return_to_Tharwya.cfg:521
msgid ""
"I'm sorry, Ibn Ghani. I had been your advisor, yet you refused to listen to "
"me."
msgstr "Lo siento, Ibn Ghani. Fui tu asesor, pero te negaste a escucharme."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/16_Return_to_Tharwya.cfg:527
msgid ""
"Ma'ralek brings forth a great crystal that he held underneath his robe, "
"white sparks emanating from it."
msgstr ""
"Ma'ralek saca un gran cristal que tenía debajo de su túnica, con chispas "
"blancas emanando de él."

#. [message], speaker=Ibn Ghani
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/16_Return_to_Tharwya.cfg:544
msgid "You've already dealt enough damage!"
msgstr "¡Ya has causado suficiente daño!"

#. [message], speaker=Maralek
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/16_Return_to_Tharwya.cfg:572
msgid "Ha . . . ha . . . . ha!"
msgstr "Ja... ja... ja!"

#. [message], speaker=Ibn Ghani
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/16_Return_to_Tharwya.cfg:590
msgid "The traitor is no more."
msgstr "El traidor ya no existe."

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/16_Return_to_Tharwya.cfg:595
msgid "There's magic emananating from his crystal!"
msgstr "¡Hay magia emanando de su cristal!"

#. [message], speaker=Iskandar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/16_Return_to_Tharwya.cfg:602
msgid ""
"The Sphere! Prepare yourselves, men! I can sense the power of the Sphere!"
msgstr "¡La Esfera! ¡Prepárense, hombres! ¡Puedo sentir el poder de la Esfera!"

#. [message], speaker=Iskandar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/16_Return_to_Tharwya.cfg:607
msgid "Ibn Ghani! Take your stand and be the leader of your men!"
msgstr "¡Ibn Ghani! Toma tu posición y sé el líder de tus hombres!"

#. [event]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/16_Return_to_Tharwya.cfg:632
msgid "Krath"
msgstr "Krath"

#. [event]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/16_Return_to_Tharwya.cfg:635
msgid "Right Hand of Krath"
msgstr "Mano Derecha de Krath"

#. [event]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/16_Return_to_Tharwya.cfg:638
msgid "Left Hand of Krath"
msgstr "Mano Izquierda de Krath"

#. [message], speaker=Krath
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/16_Return_to_Tharwya.cfg:643
msgid "Hail, Ibn Ghani."
msgstr "Saludos, Ibn Ghani."

#. [message], speaker=Krath
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/16_Return_to_Tharwya.cfg:648
msgid ""
"I see you are doing well. Ma'ralek, however, is not. Take a look at what "
"you've done to him."
msgstr ""
"Veo que estás bien. Ma'ralek, sin embargo, no. Mira lo que le has hecho."

#. [message], speaker=Ibn Ghani
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/16_Return_to_Tharwya.cfg:653
msgid ""
"He was a traitor and sold the powers of Th'arwya to your kin, Krath. He did "
"not deserve any mercy."
msgstr ""
"Era un traidor y vendió los poderes de Th'arwya a tu gente, Krath. No "
"merecía ninguna misericordia."

#. [message], speaker=Krath
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/16_Return_to_Tharwya.cfg:658
msgid ""
"That is the right mindset, Ibn Ghani! He deserved it with every inch of his "
"body. He tried to overthrow you, yet had to deal with the consequences. "
"You're just one step away from the philosophy of Kesh. Kesh reaches out to "
"you and great powers await you. But for a price. Kiss my sigil ring and "
"you'll be a part of the new reign . . ."
msgstr ""
"Esa es la mentalidad correcta, Ibn Ghani! Lo merecía con cada centímetro de "
"su cuerpo. Intentó derrocarte, pero tuvo que enfrentar las consecuencias. "
"Estás solo a un paso de la filosofía de Kesh. Kesh te tiende la mano y "
"grandes poderes te esperan. Pero a un precio. Besa mi anillo de sigilo y "
"serás parte del nuevo reinado..."

#. [message], speaker=Iskandar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/16_Return_to_Tharwya.cfg:663
msgid "Silence, slave of Kesh!"
msgstr "¡Silencio, esclavo de Kesh!"

#. [message], speaker=Krath
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/16_Return_to_Tharwya.cfg:670
msgid ""
"An Athvari? Iskandar? Is it you? Then you've already determined your fate, "
"Ibn Ghani. I am disappointed."
msgstr ""
"¿Un athvari? ¿Iskandar? ¿Eres tú? Entonces ya has determinado tu destino, "
"Ibn Ghani. Estoy decepcionado."

#. [message], speaker=Krath
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/16_Return_to_Tharwya.cfg:675
msgid "Men! Burn this tower down and take everything of value with you!"
msgstr "¡Hombres! ¡Quemen esta torre y lleven todo lo de valor con ustedes!"

#. [message], speaker=Ibn Ghani
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/16_Return_to_Tharwya.cfg:690
msgid "No force will ever overthrow Th'arwya! Men! To arms!"
msgstr "¡Ninguna fuerza derrocará jamás a Th'arwya! ¡Hombres! ¡A las armas!"

#. [message], speaker=Biqu
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/16_Return_to_Tharwya.cfg:696
msgid "Aight, Ibn Ghani, our king, we will stand at your side!"
msgstr "¡Bien, Ibn Ghani, nuestro rey, estaremos a tu lado!"

#. [message], speaker=Ibn Ghani
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/16_Return_to_Tharwya.cfg:714
msgid ""
"Take this, Ilaroth and Iskandar. This is all I can get right now. You need "
"to help the people of Th'arwya to withstand the forces of Kesh!"
msgstr ""
"Tomen esto, Ilaroth e Iskandar. Esto es todo lo que puedo conseguir ahora. "
"¡Necesitan ayudar al pueblo de Th'arwya a resistir las fuerzas de Kesh!"

#. [message], speaker=Iskandar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/16_Return_to_Tharwya.cfg:719
msgid ""
"Fear not, Ibn Ghani! I know the kind of magic that brought forth those "
"portals. Magic from the far east. I am able to close those rifts once I am "
"near them. Stay strong!"
msgstr ""
"¡No temas, Ibn Ghani! Conozco el tipo de magia que creó esos portales. Magia "
"del lejano este. Soy capaz de cerrar esas grietas una vez que estoy cerca de "
"ellas. ¡Mantente fuerte!"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/16_Return_to_Tharwya.cfg:727
msgid "Iskandar closes the portals"
msgstr "Iskandar cierra los portales"

#. [objective], condition=lose
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/16_Return_to_Tharwya.cfg:731
msgid "Any merchant dies"
msgstr "Cualquier mercader muere"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/16_Return_to_Tharwya.cfg:753
msgid "Iskandar meets with Ma'ralek."
msgstr "Iskandar se encuentra con Ma'ralek."

#. [message]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/16_Return_to_Tharwya.cfg:787
msgid "In the name of the sands! They returned from the depths! They made it!"
msgstr ""
"¡En nombre de las arenas! ¡Regresaron de las profundidades! ¡Lo lograron!"

#. [message]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/16_Return_to_Tharwya.cfg:792
msgid ""
". . . and . . . who is that? Ibn Ghani?! The Great Dune Warmaster returned! "
"Look, boys!"
msgstr ""
"... y... ¿quién es ese? ¡¿Ibn Ghani?! ¡El Gran Maestro de Guerra del "
"Desierto regresó! ¡Miren, muchachos!"

#. [part]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/17_The_Great_Wall.cfg:7
msgid ""
"Time passed slowly as the group entered the portal. After feeling like they "
"were trapped in it for years, the portal finally spewed them out."
msgstr ""
"El tiempo pasó lentamente mientras el grupo entraba al portal. Después de "
"sentir que estuvieron atrapados en él durante años, el portal finalmente los "
"escupió."

#. [scenario], id=17_The_Great_Wall
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/17_The_Great_Wall.cfg:18
msgid "The Great Wall"
msgstr "La Gran Muralla"

#. [side], type=Dune Shieldguard
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/17_The_Great_Wall.cfg:61
msgid "Wall guards"
msgstr "Guardias de la muralla"

#. [side], type=Dune Shieldguard
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/17_The_Great_Wall.cfg:66
msgid "Equaba"
msgstr "Equaba"

#. [event]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/17_The_Great_Wall.cfg:187
msgid "Cradgan"
msgstr "Cradgan"

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/17_The_Great_Wall.cfg:227
msgid "Quick! Get away from that portal before it closes permanently"
msgstr ""
"¡Rápido! ¡Aléjense de ese portal antes de que se cierre permanentemente!"

#. [message], speaker=Cradgan
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/17_The_Great_Wall.cfg:241
msgid ""
"You are too predictable, Athvari. The Sphere is ours and, forsooth, it will "
"remain ours. When our men return, your limbs and head will be brought to the "
"borders of the realm of Kesh, as a warning for anyone that dares to "
"challenge Kesh and their sovereigns."
msgstr ""
"Eres demasiado predecible, athvari. La Esfera es nuestra y, por supuesto, "
"seguirá siendo nuestra. Cuando regresen nuestros hombres, sus extremidades y "
"cabeza serán llevadas a las fronteras del reino de Kesh, como advertencia "
"para cualquiera que se atreva a desafiar a Kesh y a sus soberanos."

#. [message], speaker=Iskandar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/17_The_Great_Wall.cfg:246
msgid ""
"Yet you won't see those times with your own eyes. Men, swords high! Cleanse "
"this place!"
msgstr ""
"Sin embargo, no verás esos tiempos con tus propios ojos. ¡Hombres, espadas "
"en alto! ¡Limpien este lugar!"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#. [note]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/17_The_Great_Wall.cfg:252
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/17_The_Great_Wall.cfg:265
msgid "You can recruit and recall from the area around the portal."
msgstr "Puedes reclutar y reincorporar desde el área alrededor del portal."

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/17_The_Great_Wall.cfg:259
msgid "Defeat the enemies surrounding the portal in less than 6 turns"
msgstr "Derrota a los enemigos que rodean el portal en menos de 6 turnos"

#. [message], speaker=Iskandar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/17_The_Great_Wall.cfg:313
msgid "Hear the thunder rolling? Our friends have arrived."
msgstr "¿Oyen el trueno rodando? Nuestros amigos han llegado."

#. [message]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/17_The_Great_Wall.cfg:333
msgid ""
"Look if it isn't the great Dune Warmaster of Serrul. It's time to finish "
"this loose end!"
msgstr ""
"Mira si no es el gran Maestro de Guerra de Serrul. ¡Es hora de terminar este "
"cabo suelto!"

#. [message], speaker=Ibn Khazul
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/17_The_Great_Wall.cfg:362
msgid "Everyone is safe!"
msgstr "¡Todos están a salvo!"

#. [message], speaker=Ridwan
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/17_The_Great_Wall.cfg:385
msgid "We promised to not disappoint you and here we are."
msgstr "Prometimos no decepcionarlos y aquí estamos."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/17_The_Great_Wall.cfg:390
msgid ""
"And we promised to grant you a chance to lighten up the weight that lies on "
"your shoulders since the Fall of Serrul. Let us cast out the demon that is "
"Kesh."
msgstr ""
"Y prometimos darles una oportunidad de aligerar el peso que recae sobre sus "
"hombros desde la Caída de Serrul. Expulsemos al demonio que es Kesh."

#. [message], speaker=Ridwan
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/17_The_Great_Wall.cfg:395
msgid ""
"So be it. Let earth devour them! Raze the wall to the ground! Catapults!"
msgstr ""
"Así sea. ¡Que la tierra los devore! ¡Arrasen la muralla hasta el suelo! "
"¡Catapultas!"

#. [message], speaker=Ridwan
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/17_The_Great_Wall.cfg:455
msgid "Hahahaha! I've sworn to be their end! Their end is here!"
msgstr "¡Jajajaja! ¡He jurado ser su fin! ¡Su fin está aquí!"

#. [message], speaker=Uthain
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/17_The_Great_Wall.cfg:460
msgid "This man is insane!"
msgstr "¡Este hombre está loco!"

#. [message], speaker=Azyan
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/17_The_Great_Wall.cfg:465
msgid ""
"People are losing their minds when they lose everything. I can understand "
"him just too well . . ."
msgstr ""
"La gente pierde la cabeza cuando lo pierde todo. Puedo entenderlo demasiado "
"bien..."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/17_The_Great_Wall.cfg:470
msgid ""
"Their walls are high and sturdy and our catapults can not harm them that "
"much. We have to open the gates manually! Fortunately, the catapults were "
"able to damage the walls and carve a path up to the walls."
msgstr ""
"Sus murallas son altas y resistentes y nuestras catapultas no pueden "
"dañarlas tanto. ¡Tenemos que abrir las puertas manualmente! Afortunadamente, "
"las catapultas pudieron dañar las murallas y abrir un camino hasta ellas."

#. [message], speaker=Ridwan
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/17_The_Great_Wall.cfg:480
msgid "What are we waiting for, then?"
msgstr "¿Entonces qué estamos esperando?"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/17_The_Great_Wall.cfg:497
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/17_The_Great_Wall.cfg:547
msgid "Open the gates of Kesh by reaching the anvil"
msgstr "Abre las puertas de Kesh alcanzando el yunque"

#. [message], speaker=Azyan
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/17_The_Great_Wall.cfg:519
msgid "Look! The warrior upon the wall, their general!"
msgstr "¡Miren! ¡El guerrero sobre la muralla, su general!"

#. [message], speaker=Azyan
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/17_The_Great_Wall.cfg:530
msgid ""
"Equaba! That's his name! I remember him! He was the one who ordered his "
"troops to destroy the home of my people once we refused to fight in the name "
"of Kesh."
msgstr ""
"¡Equaba! ¡Ese es su nombre! ¡Lo recuerdo! Fue él quien ordenó a sus tropas "
"destruir el hogar de mi pueblo una vez que nos negamos a luchar en nombre de "
"Kesh."

#. [message], speaker=Azyan
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/17_The_Great_Wall.cfg:535
msgid ""
"He gave this order with a smile on his face. I'd love to return that favor "
"and let him pay the price for his misdeeds."
msgstr ""
"Dio esa orden con una sonrisa en su rostro. Me encantaría devolverle ese "
"favor y hacerle pagar el precio por sus fechorías."

#. [message], speaker=Ibn Khazul
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/17_The_Great_Wall.cfg:540
msgid ""
"Then it is time for you to take revenge on him, we shall stand at your side! "
"The time for the payback is near, Kesh will pay for its misdeeds and for "
"sure it will pay a heavy price."
msgstr ""
"Entonces es momento de que tomes venganza contra él, ¡estaremos a tu lado! "
"El momento de la revancha está cerca, Kesh pagará por sus fechorías y seguro "
"pagará un precio alto."

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/17_The_Great_Wall.cfg:551
msgid "Optional: Azyan defeats Equaba"
msgstr "Opcional: Azyan derrota a Equaba"

#. [message], speaker=Ridwan
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/17_The_Great_Wall.cfg:587
msgid "Mercenaries from the south are supporting Kesh!"
msgstr "¡Mercenarios del sur están apoyando a Kesh!"

#. [message], speaker=Wahdet
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/17_The_Great_Wall.cfg:602
msgid ""
"Good or evil doesn't matter to them if the price is right. Their way of "
"living is honorless, I'll gladly send them to the earth's guts!"
msgstr ""
"Bueno o malo no les importa si el precio es correcto. Su forma de vivir es "
"sin honor, ¡con gusto los enviaré a las entrañas de la tierra!"

#. [message], speaker=Nuvdael
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/17_The_Great_Wall.cfg:610
msgid ""
"I am afraid they still have a reserve army that can't be ignored. Their main "
"force should be sieging Serrul at the very moment, but we're still facing "
"lots of soldiers of Kesh. We should hasten, otherwise we'll get encircled by "
"opposing forces."
msgstr ""
"Temo que todavía tienen un ejército de reserva que no puede ignorarse. Su "
"fuerza principal debería estar asediando Serrul en este mismo momento, pero "
"aún enfrentamos a muchos soldados de Kesh. Deberíamos apurarnos, de lo "
"contrario seremos rodeados por fuerzas enemigas."

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/17_The_Great_Wall.cfg:615
msgid ""
"Fear not, Nuvdael, we've prevailed so many times in Wesnoth and in the "
"desert lands. What danger could be an obstacle to us? We will fight on and "
"we will prevail. We have to!"
msgstr ""
"No temas, Nuvdael, hemos prevalecido tantas veces en Wesnoth y en las "
"tierras del desierto. ¿Qué peligro podría ser un obstáculo para nosotros? "
"Seguiremos luchando y prevaleceremos. ¡Tenemos que hacerlo!"

#. [message], speaker=Ridwan
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/17_The_Great_Wall.cfg:626
msgid "Look! Even more!"
msgstr "¡Miren! ¡Aún más!"

#. [message], speaker=Azyan
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/17_The_Great_Wall.cfg:654
msgid ""
"That's it. I've got my revenge. And no, he shall not rest in peace, he shall "
"suffer like the squashed rat that he is."
msgstr ""
"Eso es todo. He obtenido mi venganza. Y no, no descansará en paz, sufrirá "
"como la rata aplastada que es."

#. [object]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/17_The_Great_Wall.cfg:658
msgid "Necklace of Equaba"
msgstr "Collar de Equaba"

#. [object]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/17_The_Great_Wall.cfg:660
msgid "The necklace of Equaba grants +15 hitpoints."
msgstr "El collar de Equaba otorga +15 puntos de vida."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/17_The_Great_Wall.cfg:704
msgid "We made it! Let us move on into the city of Kesh!"
msgstr "¡Lo logramos! ¡Avancemos hacia la ciudad de Kesh!"

#. [message], speaker=Iskandar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/17_The_Great_Wall.cfg:720
msgid ""
"Something isn't right. . . it feels like a surge of powerful magic is coming "
"from the north. . ."
msgstr ""
"Algo no está bien... se siente como una oleada de magia poderosa que viene "
"del norte..."

#. [part]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:7
msgid ""
"Ilriel and Ilaroth entered the city of Kesh that lay behind the great wall. "
"Most of the city had been laid to waste and there weren't any ordinary "
"citizens. Kesh was nothing more than a shadow of its former self. But there, "
"at the horizon, they saw it. They'd reached their goal."
msgstr ""
"Ilriel e Ilaroth entraron a la ciudad de Kesh que yacía detrás de la gran "
"muralla. La mayor parte de la ciudad había sido arrasada y no había "
"ciudadanos ordinarios. Kesh no era más que una sombra de lo que fue. Pero "
"allí, en el horizonte, la vieron. Habían alcanzado su objetivo."

#. [scenario], id=18_Uzar_the_Betrayer
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:18
msgid "Uzar the Betrayer"
msgstr "Uzar el Traidor"

#. [side], type=Lost Athvari
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:59
msgid "Dune Prophet of Kesh"
msgstr "Profeta Barján de Kesh"

#. [side], type=Lost Athvari
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:64
msgid "Uzar"
msgstr "Uzar"

#. [side]
#. [unit_type], id=Athvari, race=athvari
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:86
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/units/athvari/athvari.cfg:5
msgid "Athvari"
msgstr "Athvari"

#. [event]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:132
msgid "Akale"
msgstr "Akale"

#. [message], speaker=Iskandar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:191
msgid "Kesh, the root of all evil. We will find the Sphere here, I sense it."
msgstr "Kesh, la raíz de todo mal. Encontraremos la Esfera aquí, la siento."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:196
msgid ""
"Forsooth, Kesh is no gem of the human civilisation. Built on the bones of "
"its former enemies, Kesh is also called 'The City of Iron'. A cue to the "
"weapons they used to crush their enemies."
msgstr ""
"Por supuesto, Kesh no es una joya de la civilización humana. Construida "
"sobre los huesos de sus antiguos enemigos, Kesh también es llamada «La "
"Ciudad de Hierro». Una pista de las armas que usaron para aplastar a sus "
"enemigos."

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:201
msgid ""
"Yet the whole city has been destroyed. No stone lies on another one, homes "
"destroyed, no life to be found here. What has happened?"
msgstr ""
"Sin embargo, toda la ciudad ha sido destruida. Ninguna piedra yace sobre "
"otra, hogares destruidos, no hay vida que encontrar aquí. ¿Qué ha pasado?"

#. [message], speaker=Iskandar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:206
msgid ""
"The Sphere overwhelmed the ones trying to control it from the outside. The "
"price for such an evil act was their lives."
msgstr ""
"La Esfera abrumó a quienes intentaban controlarla desde afuera. El precio "
"por tal acto malvado fueron sus vidas."

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:211
msgid "What lurks inside the Sphere?"
msgstr "¿Qué acecha dentro de la Esfera?"

#. [message], speaker=Iskandar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:216
msgid ""
"When the Sphere was created by our forefather Thrang'ual and the Athvari, it "
"was used as an astral prison for the Three Kings, who brought destructive "
"magic to our lands. But even the Sphere had not been strong enough to "
"withstand their power. "
msgstr ""
"Cuando la Esfera fue creada por nuestro antepasado Thrang'ual y los athvari, "
"se usó como una prisión astral para los Tres Reyes, quienes trajeron magia "
"destructiva a nuestras tierras. Pero ni siquiera la Esfera fue lo "
"suficientemente fuerte para resistir su poder."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:221
msgid ""
"My refusal in helping my brothers made the Circle of the Athvari an "
"incomplete creation."
msgstr ""
"Mi negativa a ayudar a mis hermanos hizo que el Círculo de los Athvari fuera "
"una creación incompleta."

#. [message], speaker=Iskandar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:226
msgid ""
"Thrang'ual knew what was at stake and he was ready to pay the ultimate "
"price. The highest price to pay."
msgstr ""
"Thrang'ual sabía lo que estaba en juego y estaba dispuesto a pagar el precio "
"definitivo. El precio más alto."

#. [message], speaker=Iskandar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:231
msgid ""
"Our forefather asked us to imprison him. Caught inside the Sphere, he would "
"then fight against the Three Kings of K'thar for eternity, hindering them "
"from casting their poisonous magic from inside."
msgstr ""
"Nuestro antepasado nos pidió que lo aprisionáramos. Atrapado dentro de la "
"Esfera, lucharía contra los Tres Reyes de K'thar por la eternidad, "
"impidiéndoles lanzar su magia venenosa desde adentro."

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:236
msgid "Then that battle has been lost."
msgstr "Entonces esa batalla se ha perdido."

#. [message], speaker=Iskandar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:241
msgid ""
"The Sphere leads to a realm isolated from these earthly plains, isolated "
"from life and death, from the heavens and earths, a realm where neither "
"light nor darkness ruled for a long time, a realm above the stars and below "
"earth. But things have changed. Inside, death triumphed over life, darkness "
"over light. The Three Kings of K'thar defeated Thrang'ual and now they are "
"crawling back into our lives, Ilriel, they are escaping the astral prison, "
"leaving the plains of the Sphere and returning to this world."
msgstr ""
"La Esfera conduce a un reino aislado de estas llanuras terrenales, aislado "
"de la vida y la muerte, de los cielos y las tierras, un reino donde ni la "
"luz ni la oscuridad reinaron durante mucho tiempo, un reino por encima de "
"las estrellas y por debajo de la tierra. Pero las cosas han cambiado. "
"Adentro, la muerte triunfó sobre la vida, la oscuridad sobre la luz. Los "
"Tres Reyes de K'thar derrotaron a Thrang'ual y ahora se arrastran de vuelta "
"a nuestras vidas, Ilriel, están escapando de la prisión astral, dejando las "
"llanuras de la Esfera y regresando a este mundo."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:246
msgid ""
"The continent will fall on its knees when that happens. Do you remember the "
"Sandy Wastes, Ilriel? The deserts around Serrul? They were once a fruitful "
"forest; fresh grass covering the earth and life springing from that place. "
"But these times are gone. The Three Kings infested the deserts with their "
"harmful magic, fighting back life. Lifeless sands claimed what once was "
"green."
msgstr ""
"El continente caerá de rodillas cuando eso suceda. ¿Recuerdas los Yermos "
"Arenados, Ilriel? ¿Los desiertos alrededor de Serrul? Una vez fueron un "
"bosque fructífero; hierba fresca cubriendo la tierra y vida brotando de ese "
"lugar. Pero esos tiempos se han ido. Los Tres Reyes infestaron los desiertos "
"con su magia dañina, combatiendo la vida. Arenas sin vida reclamaron lo que "
"una vez fue verde."

#. [message], speaker=Iskandar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:251
msgid ""
"The descendants of anyone who once fought against the Three Kings will be "
"facing destruction, if we don't stop them."
msgstr ""
"Los descendientes de cualquiera que una vez luchó contra los Tres Reyes "
"enfrentarán la destrucción, si no los detenemos."

#. [message], speaker=Iskandar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:256
msgid ""
"Look at the eyes of the petrified. It was the Sphere and they've seen it "
"face to face. Their faces tell the stories of old times when the Three Kings "
"ruled."
msgstr ""
"Mira los ojos de los petrificados. Fue la Esfera y la vieron cara a cara. "
"Sus rostros cuentan las historias de tiempos antiguos cuando los Tres Reyes "
"gobernaban."

#. [message], speaker=Nuvdael
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:262
msgid ""
"In the name of the Southwoods! Look, on the horizon! This has to be the "
"Sphere!"
msgstr ""
"¡En nombre de los Bosques del Sur! ¡Miren, en el horizonte! ¡Esa tiene que "
"ser la Esfera!"

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:270
msgid ""
"The Sphere is radiating! A kind of magic I've never encountered before! This "
"place displeases me, we shouldn't be here!"
msgstr ""
"¡La Esfera está radiando! ¡Un tipo de magia que nunca había encontrado "
"antes! Este lugar me desagrada, ¡no deberíamos estar aquí!"

#. [message], speaker=Uzar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:275
msgid ""
"So is there still someone who refuses to be a part . . . of the new reign?"
msgstr ""
"¿Así que todavía hay alguien que se niega a ser parte... del nuevo reinado?"

#. [message], speaker=Uzar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:280
msgid "You, I see it in your eyes!"
msgstr "¡Tú, lo veo en tus ojos!"

#. [message], speaker=Uzar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:290
msgid ""
"You are fearing the powers that'll be unleashed. You are afraid of the Three."
msgstr "Temes los poderes que se desatarán. Tienes miedo de los Tres."

#. [message], speaker=Alwat
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:295
msgid "My . . . my ancestors were victims of them . . ."
msgstr "Mis... mis antepasados fueron víctimas de ellos..."

#. [message], speaker=Uzar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:300
msgid ""
"You mean your bloodline fought the Three? Then you are worth less than the "
"sand under my foot!"
msgstr ""
"¿Quieres decir que tu linaje luchó contra los Tres? ¡Entonces vales menos "
"que la arena bajo mi pie!"

#. [message], speaker=Alwat
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:305
msgid "No! No! <b> Noooo!</b>"
msgstr "¡No! ¡No! <b>¡Nooo!</b>"

#. [message], speaker=Alwat
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:323
msgid "Aahhh!"
msgstr "¡Aahhh!"

#. [message], speaker=Alwat
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:334
msgid "FLEE AS LONG AS YOU CAN! SAVE YOURSELVES! THEY ARE COMING!"
msgstr "¡HUID MIENTRAS PUEDAN! ¡SÁLVENSE! ¡VIENEN!"

#. [message], speaker=Uzar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:348
msgid "Anyone else? Eh?"
msgstr "¿Alguien más? ¿Eh?"

#. [message]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:359
msgid "No, master! Let us swear the Oath of Allegiance to the new kings!"
msgstr "¡No, amo! ¡Déjanos jurar el Juramento de Lealtad a los nuevos reyes!"

#. [message], speaker=Uzar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:364
msgid ""
"Haha, forsooth, you brave men will stand under direct commandment of the "
"Three. You can pledge allegiance to them when the ceremony has ended, not "
"yet, servant! "
msgstr ""
"Jaja, por supuesto, ustedes valientes hombres estarán bajo el mando directo "
"de los Tres. Pueden jurar lealtad a ellos cuando la ceremonia haya "
"terminado, ¡todavía no, sirviente!"

#. [message], speaker=Uzar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:369
msgid ""
"The world known to your eyes will bow down to us again, the laws of these "
"plains will abide to the will of the Three! For too long have they been held "
"down! The Athvari are a bloodline of kings and rulers! We are destined to "
"rule over men and women alike and bring order!"
msgstr ""
"El mundo conocido para tus ojos se arrodillará ante nosotros de nuevo, ¡las "
"leyes de estas llanuras se someterán a la voluntad de los Tres! ¡Por "
"demasiado tiempo han sido oprimidos! ¡Los athvari son un linaje de reyes y "
"gobernantes! ¡Estamos destinados a gobernar sobre hombres y mujeres por "
"igual y traer orden!"

#. [message], speaker=Uzar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:377
msgid ""
"And you, brother! You'll be the next one to meet our forefathers. Forgive "
"me, brother, it has to be done."
msgstr ""
"Y tú, hermano! Serás el siguiente en unirte a nuestros antepasados. "
"Perdóname, hermano, tiene que hacerse."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:409
msgid ""
"As the dagger of the coated man pierced the heart of the Athvari, the "
"Athvari turned to dust before his body could fall on the ground."
msgstr ""
"Mientras la daga del hombre encapuchado atravesaba el corazón del athvari, "
"el athvari se convirtió en polvo antes de que su cuerpo pudiera caer al "
"suelo."

#. [message], speaker=Uzar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:418
msgid "Hahahaha!"
msgstr "¡Jajajaja!"

#. [message], speaker=Nuvdael
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:423
msgid "The body turned to dust! In the blink of an eye!"
msgstr "¡El cuerpo se convirtió en polvo! ¡En un parpadeo!"

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:428
msgid ""
"Absorbed by the sphere! Ilarøth, break your silence! For better or worse, "
"what is happening here?!"
msgstr ""
"¡Absorbido por la esfera! ¡Ilarøth, rompe tu silencio! ¡Para bien o para "
"mal, ¿qué está pasando aquí?!"

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:433
msgid ""
"Uzar! The right hand of Uthman! The consultant of the snake and traitor to "
"the Athvari! He is performing a ritual to unite the Athvari with the Three "
"Kings. Once united inside the Sphere, they will be able to . . ."
msgstr ""
"¡Uzar! ¡La mano derecha de Uthman! ¡El consejero de la serpiente y traidor a "
"los athvari! Está realizando un ritual para unir a los athvari con los Tres "
"Reyes. Una vez unidos dentro de la Esfera, podrán..."

#. [message], speaker=Iskandar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:438
msgid ""
"The Three Kings, Ilriel, they are like us. We share the same blood. They are "
"Athvari. . ."
msgstr ""
"Los Tres Reyes, Ilriel, son como nosotros. Compartimos la misma sangre. Son "
"athvari..."

#. [message], speaker=Nahj
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:443
msgid "Uzar! A group approaches! The last of the Athvari is with them!"
msgstr "¡Uzar! ¡Un grupo se acerca! ¡El último de los athvari está con ellos!"

#. [message], speaker=Uzar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:448
msgid ""
"Ah, Iskandar! Those have to be the servants of Ridwan! Now the ceremony can "
"come to an end!"
msgstr ""
"¡Ah, Iskandar! ¡Esos deben ser los sirvientes de Ridwan! ¡Ahora la ceremonia "
"puede llegar a su fin!"

#. [message], speaker=Iskandar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:453
msgid "Your deeds are inexcusable, Uzar!"
msgstr "¡Tus acciones son imperdonables, Uzar!"

#. [message], speaker=Uzar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:458
msgid ""
"Don't you understand, Iskandar? We should be kings and rule these lands! We "
"are destined to rule, lead men and bring order to their lands! It was wrong "
"to imprison our three brothers. Do you see these lands? A civil war is "
"reigning across Wesnoth, the eternal war between Serrul and Kesh has not yet "
"settled. Do you call that a true order? With our current deeds, we can't "
"bring order, Iskandar. Chaos inherits in men and there can only be order "
"without men!"
msgstr ""
"¿No entiendes, Iskandar? ¡Deberíamos ser reyes y gobernar estas tierras! "
"Estamos destinados a gobernar, liderar a los hombres y traer orden a sus "
"tierras! Fue un error aprisionar a nuestros tres hermanos. ¿Ves estas "
"tierras? Una guerra civil reina a través de Wesnoth, la guerra eterna entre "
"Serrul y Kesh aún no se ha resuelto. ¿Llamas a eso un orden verdadero? Con "
"nuestras acciones actuales, no podemos traer orden, Iskandar. El caos hereda "
"en los hombres y solo puede haber orden sin hombres!"

#. [message], speaker=Uzar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:463
msgid ""
"The line of the Athvari is weak and only the Three are able to bring us back "
"to glory! In the Sphere, we shall unite and rise again from the ashes like a "
"phoenix . . . with the Three as our wings. Brother, join us for we shall be "
"kings once again!"
msgstr ""
"El linaje de los athvari es débil y solo los Tres son capaces de traernos de "
"vuelta a la gloria! En la Esfera, nos uniremos y nos levantaremos de las "
"cenizas como un fénix... con los Tres como nuestras alas. ¡Hermano, únete a "
"nosotros para que seamos reyes una vez más!"

#. [message], speaker=Iskandar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:468
msgid ""
"The Athvari were destined to rule these lands in peace, Uzar, not with an "
"iron fist, spreading death. We are the order, not chaos. It is our task to "
"protect mankind and not to bring forth its downfall! You've left the path of "
"righteousness, just as the Three! And righteousness is what will bring death "
"to you!"
msgstr ""
"Los athvari estaban destinados a gobernar estas tierras en paz, Uzar, no con "
"puño de hierro, esparciendo muerte. Somos el orden, no el caos. ¡Es nuestra "
"tarea proteger a la humanidad y no provocar su caída! ¡Has abandonado el "
"camino de la rectitud, igual que los Tres! ¡Y la rectitud es lo que te "
"traerá la muerte!"

#. [message], speaker=Uzar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:473
msgid ""
"Mankind can't be saved, Iskandar! Chaos and hate is a part of them! We will "
"rule again and end this chaos, and you'll be a part of our reign . . . after "
"we are done with you. For we shall bring order by death!"
msgstr ""
"¡La humanidad no puede ser salvada, Iskandar! ¡El caos y el odio son parte "
"de ellos! Gobernaremos de nuevo y terminaremos con este caos, y tú serás "
"parte de nuestro reinado... después de que terminemos contigo. ¡Porque "
"traeremos orden mediante la muerte!"

#. [message], speaker=Uzar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:478
msgid ""
"Men! Seize him and bring him to me! For the ritual shall find its end . . . "
"we just need . . .  a bit more time!"
msgstr ""
"¡Hombres! ¡Captúrenlo y tráiganmelo! ¡Para que el ritual llegue a su fin... "
"solo necesitamos... un poco más de tiempo!"

#. [message], speaker=Uzar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:483
msgid "Abram! Put up the defenses!"
msgstr "¡Abram! ¡Levanta las defensas!"

#. [message], speaker=Abram
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:488
msgid "Aye!"
msgstr "¡Sí!"

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:516
msgid "Your misdeeds are inexcusable!"
msgstr "¡Tus fechorías son imperdonables!"

#. [message], speaker=Ibn Khazul
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:521
msgid ""
"The wise men of our kin have prophesied the demise of the Athvari! Yet sharp "
"steel can change things that wisdom does not even understand! We are here to "
"change fate! And fate we will change!"
msgstr ""
"¡Los sabios de nuestro linaje han profetizado la caída de los athvari! ¡Sin "
"embargo, el acero afilado puede cambiar cosas que ni siquiera la sabiduría "
"entiende! ¡Estamos aquí para cambiar el destino! ¡Y el destino lo "
"cambiaremos!"

#. [message], speaker=Iskandar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:526
msgid ""
"I know we could count on you, my friends. We have to prevent Uzar from "
"finishing the ceremony! Ridwan, the sword I gave to you after the siege of "
"Serrul; it is not just a sword. It's an artifact that once belonged to your "
"father. To Thrang'ual. It can break through the shield that is protecting "
"Uzar."
msgstr ""
"Sé que podíamos contar con ustedes, mis amigos. ¡Tenemos que evitar que Uzar "
"termine la ceremonia! Ridwan, la espada que te di después del asedio de "
"Serrul; no es solo una espada. Es un artefacto que una vez perteneció a tu "
"padre. A Thrang'ual. Puede romper el escudo que protege a Uzar."

#. [message], speaker=Ridwan
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:531
msgid ""
"Then let me interrupt him. The presence of the Sphere . . . my people . . . "
"I need to do it. In their name. It is too dangerous for you."
msgstr ""
"Entonces déjenme interrumpirlo. La presencia de la Esfera... mi pueblo... "
"necesito hacerlo. En su nombre. Es demasiado peligroso para ustedes."

#. [message], speaker=Wahdet
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:536
msgid ""
"I used to risk my life for money, but never was I truly willing to give it "
"away. Today there is no hiding in the face of such danger and injustice. We "
"will carve a way to that traitor for you, Ridwan. May the winds of the "
"ashland deserts guide you!"
msgstr ""
"Solía arriesgar mi vida por dinero, pero nunca estuve realmente dispuesto a "
"entregarla. Hoy no hay escondite ante tal peligro e injusticia. Te abriremos "
"un camino hacia ese traidor, Ridwan. ¡Que los vientos de los desiertos de "
"ceniza te guíen!"

#. [message], speaker=Iskandar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:543
msgid ""
"Then so be it. But be careful, the power of the Sphere might awake those "
"petrified warriors of theirs!"
msgstr ""
"Entonces que así sea. Pero tengan cuidado, ¡el poder de la Esfera podría "
"despertar a esos guerreros petrificados suyos!"

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:548
msgid "Warriors of Serrul! Attack!"
msgstr "¡Guerreros de Serrul! ¡Ataquen!"

#. [message], speaker=Nuvdael
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:553
msgid "Elves of the Southwoods! Bows high!"
msgstr "¡Elfos de los Bosques del Sur! ¡Arcos en alto!"

#. [message], speaker=Ibn Khazul
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:558
msgid "Horsemen! For glory, fame and death!"
msgstr "¡Jinetes! ¡Por la gloria, la fama y la muerte!"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:566
msgid "Ridwan attacks Uzar"
msgstr "Ridwan ataca a Uzar"

#. [objective], condition=lose
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:570
msgid "Uzar dies"
msgstr "Uzar muere"

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:589
msgid ""
"You have the blood of kings and rulers? You are not of the same blood as the "
"desert men themselves?"
msgstr ""
"¿Tienes la sangre de reyes y gobernantes? ¿No eres de la misma sangre que "
"los mismos hombres del desierto?"

#. [message], speaker=Iskandar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:594
msgid ""
"The deserts aren't our home. We have come from a land where the water of the "
"rivers shines silver and both sun and moon never set. A land in the far "
"east. Centuries ago, we've migrated to these lands to rule over the people "
"and make sure that peace and order reign. The desert men think we are of "
"their blood, but we aren't. We are different."
msgstr ""
"Los desiertos no son nuestro hogar. Venimos de una tierra donde el agua de "
"los ríos brilla plateada y tanto el sol como la luna nunca se ponen. Una "
"tierra en el lejano este. Hace siglos, migramos a estas tierras para "
"gobernar sobre la gente y asegurarnos de que reine la paz y el orden. Los "
"hombres del desierto creen que somos de su sangre, pero no lo somos. Somos "
"diferentes."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:599
msgid ""
"Ilriel, for a long time there were many Athvari throughout the continent. "
"They were kings, generals, leaders and heroes. The gift of the Athvari has "
"been given to many. Many don't know they are Athvari, though, yet a few "
"managed to unlock their inherent powers. Do you know the name 'Delfador'? He "
"was a wizard of Wesnoth and our blood ran strong in him. He saved the "
"kingdom many times and guided the forces that freed the land from a queen "
"sowing chaos. We, the Athvari, have been making sure that order reigns and "
"chaos is fought back. But the Three Kings were poisoned by the might that "
"they inherited."
msgstr ""
"Ilriel, durante mucho tiempo hubo muchos athvari a lo largo del continente. "
"Eran reyes, generales, líderes y héroes. El don de los athvari se ha dado a "
"muchos. Muchos no saben que son athvari, sin embargo, unos pocos lograron "
"desbloquear sus poderes inherentes. ¿Conoces el nombre «Delfador»? Fue un "
"mago de Wesnoth y nuestra sangre corría fuerte en él. Salvó el reino muchas "
"veces y guió a las fuerzas que liberaron la tierra de una reina que sembraba "
"caos. Nosotros, los athvari, nos hemos asegurado de que reine el orden y se "
"combata el caos. Pero los Tres Reyes fueron envenenados por el poder que "
"heredaron."

#. [message], speaker=Uthain
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:608
msgid ""
"Hmmpff, this is taking too long! Let me just get there and hammer that "
"Sphere into pieces!"
msgstr ""
"Hmmpff, ¡esto está tardando demasiado! ¡Déjenme llegar allí y martillar esa "
"Esfera hasta hacerla pedazos!"

#. [message], speaker=Iskandar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:613
msgid ""
"You'd burn to ashes before your hammer hit the Sphere, dwarf. There is no "
"way to destroy it."
msgstr ""
"Te quemarías hasta las cenizas antes de que tu martillo golpeara la Esfera, "
"enano. No hay forma de destruirla."

#. [message], speaker=Uthain
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:618
msgid "Pah!"
msgstr "¡Pah!"

#. [message], speaker=Ridwan
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:636
msgid "The ritual has not been stopped. I fear we were too late!"
msgstr "El ritual no se ha detenido. ¡Temo que llegamos demasiado tarde!"

#. [message], speaker=Ridwan
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:688
msgid "We shall bring judgement to you, Uzar!"
msgstr "¡Te traeremos juicio, Uzar!"

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:693
msgid "Ridwan!"
msgstr "¡Ridwan!"

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:698
msgid "No, Ilriel! Let fate take its course! Don't interfere!"
msgstr "¡No, Ilriel! ¡Deja que el destino siga su curso! ¡No intervengas!"

#. [message], speaker=Ridwan
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:703
msgid ""
"It was nice to know you, Ilriel. But I have lost everything. Who can be a "
"worse enemy than a man that lost everything? My people demand my sacrifice."
msgstr ""
"Fue bueno conocerte, Ilriel. Pero lo he perdido todo. ¿Quién puede ser un "
"peor enemigo que un hombre que lo perdió todo? Mi pueblo exige mi sacrificio."

#. [message], speaker=Ridwan
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:708
msgid "Witness me and my burden shall lighten!"
msgstr "¡Sean testigos y mi carga se aligerará!"

#. [message], speaker=Uzar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:727
msgid "YOU! YOU! YOU'VE BROKEN THE RITUAL!"
msgstr "¡TÚ! ¡TÚ! ¡HAS ROTO EL RITUAL!"

#. [message], speaker=Ridwan
#. [message], speaker=Uzar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:743
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:791
msgid "Hahaha!"
msgstr "¡Jajajaja!"

#. [message], speaker=Uzar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:748
msgid ""
"But . . . but this won't change anything! The Three Kings are too powerful "
"already . . . it is just a matter of time!"
msgstr ""
"Pero... pero esto no cambiará nada! ¡Los Tres Reyes ya son demasiado "
"poderosos... es solo cuestión de tiempo!"

#. [message], speaker=Ibn Khazul
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:781
msgid "Ridwan! No! <b>Nooo!</b>"
msgstr "¡Ridwan! ¡No! <b>¡Nooo!</b>"

#. [message], speaker=Ibn Khazul
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:786
msgid "Your time is over, Uzar!"
msgstr "¡Tu tiempo ha terminado, Uzar!"

#. [message], speaker=Uzar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:807
msgid "Aaaah!"
msgstr "¡Aaaah!"

#. [message], speaker=Uzar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:816
msgid "AAAAAAHHHHH!"
msgstr "¡AAAAAAHHHHH!"

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:837
msgid "Absorbed by the Sphere!"
msgstr "¡Absorbido por la Esfera!"

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:862
msgid "It . . .  it knows we are here!"
msgstr "¡Lo... lo sabe, estamos aquí!"

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:881
msgid "Iskandar! No!"
msgstr "¡Iskandar! ¡No!"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:898
msgid "The last of the Athvari! Iskandar, you are ours!"
msgstr "¡El último de los athvari! ¡Iskandar, eres nuestro!"

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:908
msgid "Ilriel! Protect us with your magic!"
msgstr "¡Ilriel! ¡Protégenos con tu magia!"

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:915
msgid "By the powers of the Southwoods?"
msgstr "¿Por los poderes de los Bosques del Sur?"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:934
msgid "Silence, woman! You can't stop the return of the kings!"
msgstr "¡Silencio, mujer! ¡No puedes detener el regreso de los reyes!"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:951
msgid "A magical shield spawned, preventing Ilriel from casting magic."
msgstr "Apareció un escudo mágico, impidiendo que Ilriel lanzara magia."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:956
msgid "No, Ilriel!"
msgstr "¡No, Ilriel!"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:964
msgid "And now . . . Iskandar . . . we shall meet again!"
msgstr "¡Y ahora... Iskandar... nos encontraremos de nuevo!"

#. [message], speaker=Iskandar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:982
msgid "Ugghhhh!"
msgstr "¡Ugghhhh!"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:996
msgid "RISE!"
msgstr "¡LEVÁNTENSE!"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:1014
msgid "NOOOOOOO!"
msgstr "¡NOOOOOOO!"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:1024
msgid "Where is the last brother? Answer us! It's you! You!"
msgstr "¿Dónde está el último hermano? ¡Respóndenos! ¡Eres tú! ¡Tú!"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:1147
msgid ""
"We can sense the blood of the Athvari, but it is not you! No man nor woman! "
"Show yourself! Athvari!"
msgstr ""
"Podemos sentir la sangre de los athvari, ¡pero no eres tú! ¡Ningún hombre ni "
"mujer! ¡Muéstrate! ¡Athvari!"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:1157
msgid "WHERE IS HE?"
msgstr "¿DÓNDE ESTÁ ÉL?"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:1165
msgid "You! I remember your face!"
msgstr "¡Tú! ¡Recuerdo tu rostro!"

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:1177
msgid "Urrgghhhh."
msgstr "Urrgghhhh."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:1183
msgid ""
"Ilriel! Open up the Acorn I gave to you at the beginning of our journey!"
msgstr "¡Ilriel! ¡Abre la Bellota que te di al comienzo de nuestro viaje!"

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:1198
msgid "H- huh?"
msgstr "¿Eh?"

#. [object]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:1202
msgid "Phiole with the Blood of Ilarøth"
msgstr "Frasco con la Sangre de Ilarøth"

#. [object]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:1204
msgid ""
"A phiole filled with blood of Ilarøth. It was hidden inside the Acorn of the "
"Great Tree."
msgstr ""
"Un frasco lleno de sangre de Ilarøth. Estaba oculto dentro de la Bellota del "
"Gran Árbol."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:1213
msgid ""
"Quick, hand it to me! It's the only way to stop them! We have to fight magic "
"with magic . . ."
msgstr ""
"¡Rápido, dámelo! ¡Es la única forma de detenerlos! Tenemos que combatir "
"magia con magia..."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:1218
msgid ". . . and the Athvari with their own blood."
msgstr "... y a los athvari con su propia sangre."

#. [object]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:1264
msgid "Phiole with the blood of Ilarøth"
msgstr "Frasco con la sangre de Ilarøth"

#. [object]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:1266
msgid ""
"A phiole filled with the blood of Ilarøth. It was hidden inside the Acorn of "
"the Great Tree."
msgstr ""
"Un frasco lleno de la sangre de Ilarøth. Estaba oculto dentro de la Bellota "
"del Gran Árbol."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:1292
msgid "Fear not, Ilriel. Come close to me! We shall enter the Sphere."
msgstr "No temas, Ilriel. ¡Acércate a mí! Entraremos a la Esfera."

#. [message], speaker=Uzar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/18_Uzar_the_Betrayer.cfg:1312
msgid ""
"Finally, the Three Kings will come upon this world and clean all the "
"unworthy from it!"
msgstr ""
"¡Finalmente, los Tres Reyes vendrán sobre este mundo y limpiarán a todos los "
"indignos de él!"

#. [part]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/19_Above_the_Stars_and_below_Earth.cfg:7
msgid ""
"Uzar had been defeated, but the ones inside the Sphere are not. Their call "
"can be heard throughout the lands and for sure Ilriel and Ilaroth would "
"answer that call."
msgstr ""
"Uzar había sido derrotado, pero los que están dentro de la Esfera no. Su "
"llamada puede ser escuchada a través de las tierras y seguro Ilriel e "
"Ilaroth responderían a esa llamada."

#. [scenario], id=19_Above_the_Stars_and_below_Earth
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/19_Above_the_Stars_and_below_Earth.cfg:35
msgid "Above the Stars and below Earth"
msgstr "Por encima de las Estrellas y por debajo de la Tierra"

#. [side]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/19_Above_the_Stars_and_below_Earth.cfg:74
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/21_Battle_of_the_Eons.cfg:79
msgid "The Three Kings"
msgstr "Los Tres Reyes"

#. [event]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/19_Above_the_Stars_and_below_Earth.cfg:92
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/19_Above_the_Stars_and_below_Earth.cfg:437
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/21_Battle_of_the_Eons.cfg:274
msgid "Askyal"
msgstr "Askyal"

#. [event]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/19_Above_the_Stars_and_below_Earth.cfg:95
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/19_Above_the_Stars_and_below_Earth.cfg:440
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/21_Battle_of_the_Eons.cfg:277
msgid "Malykh"
msgstr "Malykh"

#. [event]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/19_Above_the_Stars_and_below_Earth.cfg:99
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/19_Above_the_Stars_and_below_Earth.cfg:444
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/21_Battle_of_the_Eons.cfg:281
msgid "Zebhan"
msgstr "Zebhan"

#. [message], speaker=Malykh
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/19_Above_the_Stars_and_below_Earth.cfg:175
msgid "It was you, Ilarøth. It was you all the time."
msgstr "Eras tú, Ilarøth. Eras tú todo el tiempo."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/19_Above_the_Stars_and_below_Earth.cfg:180
msgid ""
"The Athvari are united once again. Years ago, when you left the path of "
"righteousness, we, the Athvari with a pure heart, were too weak to inhibit "
"your powers."
msgstr ""
"Los athvari están unidos una vez más. Hace años, cuando abandonaste el "
"camino de la rectitud, nosotros, los athvari de corazón puro, éramos "
"demasiado débiles para inhibir tus poderes."

#. [message], speaker=Malykh
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/19_Above_the_Stars_and_below_Earth.cfg:185
msgid ""
"And it was all your fault, Ilarøth! You were the one not supporting "
"Thrang'ual in the creation of the Sphere!"
msgstr ""
"¡Y todo fue culpa tuya, Ilarøth! ¡Fuiste tú quien no apoyó a Thrang'ual en "
"la creación de la Esfera!"

#. [message], speaker=Malykh
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/19_Above_the_Stars_and_below_Earth.cfg:190
msgid ""
"Yet we have to thank you for that! Your demise means our rise. We will "
"return and rule at last! We've for so long to sit on the world's throne!"
msgstr ""
"¡Sin embargo, tenemos que agradecerte por eso! Tu caída significa nuestro "
"ascenso. ¡Regresaremos y gobernaremos al fin! ¡Hemos esperado demasiado para "
"sentarnos en el trono del mundo!"

#. [message], speaker=Malykh
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/19_Above_the_Stars_and_below_Earth.cfg:274
msgid ""
"And still you were foolish enough to enter our realm, that'll already "
"outreaches the boundaries of the Sphere. A realm, where the laws are set by "
"us. You'll be playing by our rules, Ilarøth! Zebhan! Askyal! They're not "
"worth our time!"
msgstr ""
"Y aun así fuiste lo suficientemente tonto como para entrar a nuestro reino, "
"que ya supera los límites de la Esfera. Un reino donde las leyes son "
"establecidas por nosotros. ¡Jugarás según nuestras reglas, Ilarøth! ¡Zebhan! "
"¡Askyal! ¡No valen nuestro tiempo!"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/19_Above_the_Stars_and_below_Earth.cfg:280
msgid "The three kings cast a spell."
msgstr "Los tres reyes lanzan un hechizo."

#. [event]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/19_Above_the_Stars_and_below_Earth.cfg:331
msgid "Ilaroth"
msgstr "Ilaroth"

#. [event]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/19_Above_the_Stars_and_below_Earth.cfg:339
msgid "Aula"
msgstr "Aula"

#. [message], speaker=Malykh
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/19_Above_the_Stars_and_below_Earth.cfg:356
msgid "Fine then. "
msgstr "Está bien entonces. "

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/19_Above_the_Stars_and_below_Earth.cfg:422
msgid "Defeat the Three Kings"
msgstr "Derrota a los Tres Reyes"

#. [message], speaker=Malykh
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/19_Above_the_Stars_and_below_Earth.cfg:449
msgid "Enough!"
msgstr "¡Basta!"

#. [message], speaker=Malykh
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/19_Above_the_Stars_and_below_Earth.cfg:454
msgid "We are not wasting our time anymore! We will return."
msgstr "¡Ya no perderemos más nuestro tiempo! Regresaremos."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/19_Above_the_Stars_and_below_Earth.cfg:488
msgid "Quick! They are weakened! We have to follow them and end their lifes!"
msgstr ""
"¡Rápido! ¡Están debilitados! ¡Tenemos que seguirlos y terminar con sus vidas!"

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/19_Above_the_Stars_and_below_Earth.cfg:512
msgid "No! The portal closed!"
msgstr "¡No! ¡El portal se cerró!"

#. [message], speaker=Iskandar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/19_Above_the_Stars_and_below_Earth.cfg:517
msgid "Then it is up to her now to defeat the Three Kings."
msgstr "Entonces ahora depende de ella derrotar a los Tres Reyes."

#. [scenario], id=20_All_Alone
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/20_All_Alone.cfg:5
msgid "All Alone"
msgstr "Completamente Solo"

#. [message]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/20_All_Alone.cfg:86
msgid "Ilriel! There you are again!"
msgstr "¡Ilriel! ¡Aquí estás de nuevo!"

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/20_All_Alone.cfg:91
msgid ""
"My loyal soldier! Did you see three men appearing in front of the sphere?"
msgstr "¡Mi leal soldado! ¿Viste a tres hombres aparecer frente a la esfera?"

#. [message]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/20_All_Alone.cfg:96
msgid ""
"Three Men? Here? No, Ilriel, there was no one leaving this place. We are "
"resting here since you've disappeared into the Sphere, our eyes would've "
"noticed anyone spawning from it."
msgstr ""
"¿Tres hombres? ¿Aquí? No, Ilriel, no había nadie saliendo de este lugar. "
"Estamos descansando aquí desde que desapareciste dentro de la Esfera, "
"nuestros ojos habrían notado a cualquiera que surgiera de ella."

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/20_All_Alone.cfg:101
msgid "This is impossible! You must've seen them!"
msgstr "¡Esto es imposible! ¡Debes haberlos visto!"

#. [message]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/20_All_Alone.cfg:106
msgid "There was no one. But there was a messenger from Ibn Ghani."
msgstr "No había nadie. Pero hubo un mensajero de Ibn Ghani."

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/20_All_Alone.cfg:111
msgid "A messenger?"
msgstr "¿Un mensajero?"

#. [message]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/20_All_Alone.cfg:116
msgid ""
"Ibn Ghani and his army . . . they were overwhelmed by the force that is the "
"army of Kesh. They are returning, they are coming for us!"
msgstr ""
"Ibn Ghani y su ejército... fueron abrumados por la fuerza que es el ejército "
"de Kesh. Están regresando, ¡vienen por nosotros!"

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/20_All_Alone.cfg:121
msgid "This is bad news, when will they arrive?"
msgstr "Son malas noticias, ¿cuándo llegarán?"

#. [message]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/20_All_Alone.cfg:126
msgid ""
"I fear they are in front of the gates of Kesh already. And there is no way "
"to escape from this place here!"
msgstr ""
"Temo que ya están frente a las puertas de Kesh. ¡Y no hay forma de escapar "
"de este lugar!"

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/20_All_Alone.cfg:131
msgid ""
"We will not flee, we will fight. The Three Kings have returned and the "
"forces of Kesh were the key to their return. We will find them there."
msgstr ""
"No huiremos, lucharemos. Los Tres Reyes han regresado y las fuerzas de Kesh "
"fueron la clave para su regreso. Los encontraremos allí."

#. [message]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/20_All_Alone.cfg:136
msgid "Ilriel, we will be at your side until death separates our paths!"
msgstr ""
"Ilriel, estaremos a tu lado hasta que la muerte separe nuestros caminos!"

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/20_All_Alone.cfg:141
msgid ""
"It's good to have you at my side. But first we have to wait until Ilarøth "
"and the others return from within the Sphere."
msgstr ""
"Es bueno tenerte a mi lado. Pero primero tenemos que esperar hasta que "
"Ilarøth y los demás regresen desde dentro de la Esfera."

#. [message]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/20_All_Alone.cfg:150
msgid "There is no one coming."
msgstr "No viene nadie."

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/20_All_Alone.cfg:155
msgid "They have to!"
msgstr "¡Tienen que hacerlo!"

#. [message]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/20_All_Alone.cfg:160
msgid "The jarring of irons can be heard already."
msgstr "Ya se pueden oír los chirridos de hierros."

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/20_All_Alone.cfg:165
msgid "Then we have to position ourselves and fight this fight on our own!"
msgstr ""
"¡Entonces tenemos que posicionarnos y luchar esta batalla por nuestra cuenta!"

#. [part]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/21_Battle_of_the_Eons.cfg:7
msgid ""
"Knowing what was coming at them, Ilriel and her loyal soldiers marched "
"through the gates of Kesh. She knew it would be the last day of many of her "
"soldiers."
msgstr ""
"Sabiendo lo que se les venía encima, Ilriel y sus leales soldados marcharon "
"a través de las puertas de Kesh. Sabía que sería el último día para muchos "
"de sus soldados."

#. [scenario], id=21_Battle_of_the_Eons
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/21_Battle_of_the_Eons.cfg:18
msgid "Battle of the Eons"
msgstr "Batalla de los Eones"

#. [message], speaker=Uthman
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/21_Battle_of_the_Eons.cfg:293
msgid "So we meet again, Ilriel. I am surprised that you are still alive."
msgstr "Así que nos encontramos de nuevo, Ilriel. Me sorprende que sigas viva."

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/21_Battle_of_the_Eons.cfg:298
msgid ""
"And I am surprised by your arrogance. We've killed you once already, and we "
"will do it again."
msgstr ""
"Y me sorprende tu arrogancia. Ya te matamos una vez, y lo haremos de nuevo."

#. [message], speaker=Uthman
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/21_Battle_of_the_Eons.cfg:303
msgid ""
"Arrogance? An attitude of kings and I will become one under the banner of "
"the Three."
msgstr ""
"¿Arrogancia? Una actitud de reyes y me convertiré en uno bajo la bandera de "
"los Tres."

#. [message], speaker=Uthman
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/21_Battle_of_the_Eons.cfg:308
msgid "Malykh, Zebhan, Askyal! Join me!"
msgstr "¡Malykh, Zebhan, Askyal! ¡Únanse a mí!"

#. [message], speaker=Malykh
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/21_Battle_of_the_Eons.cfg:313
msgid "You are not the one giving us orders!"
msgstr "¡Tú no eres quien nos da órdenes!"

#. [message], speaker=Uthman
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/21_Battle_of_the_Eons.cfg:318
msgid "Of . . . course not."
msgstr "Por... supuesto que no."

#. [message], speaker=Malykh
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/21_Battle_of_the_Eons.cfg:329
msgid ""
"And now that you've done what you were asked to, we don't need you anymore."
msgstr "Y ahora que has hecho lo que te pidieron, ya no te necesitamos."

#. [message], speaker=Uthman
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/21_Battle_of_the_Eons.cfg:352
msgid "No!!"
msgstr "¡No!!"

#. [message], speaker=Malykh
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/21_Battle_of_the_Eons.cfg:376
msgid ""
"Now it's your turn, elvish woman. You're on the wrong side. You could be on "
"the side of the kings, yet you decided to side with the servants."
msgstr ""
"Ahora es tu turno, mujer elfa. Estás del lado equivocado. Podrías estar del "
"lado de los reyes, sin embargo decidiste ponerte del lado de los sirvientes."

#. [message], speaker=Malykh
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/21_Battle_of_the_Eons.cfg:392
msgid "And for that, you'll have to pay."
msgstr "Y por eso, tendrás que pagar."

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/21_Battle_of_the_Eons.cfg:397
msgid "Your era will be over. Once and for all."
msgstr "Tu era terminará. De una vez por todas."

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/21_Battle_of_the_Eons.cfg:402
msgid ""
"Men! Now it is up to us to strike back the Three Kings and end their reign. "
"At the end of the day, you will be heroes, your lives shall become the "
"legends that will be told 200 years from now on. Today, we are making "
"history!"
msgstr ""
"¡Hombres! Ahora depende de nosotros contraatacar a los Tres Reyes y terminar "
"su reinado. Al final del día, serán héroes, sus vidas se convertirán en las "
"leyendas que se contarán dentro de 200 años. ¡Hoy, estamos haciendo historia!"

#. [message], speaker=Malykh
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/21_Battle_of_the_Eons.cfg:407
msgid ""
"History belongs to the Three! And so does the future. Once we are done with "
"you, your existence will be no more. Any knowledge about you, any of your "
"deeds and anyone you knew will be purged from existence. It will be like "
"you've never even existed!"
msgstr ""
"¡La historia pertenece a los Tres! Y también el futuro. Una vez que "
"terminemos contigo, tu existencia ya no será. Cualquier conocimiento sobre "
"ti, cualquiera de tus acciones y cualquiera que conociste será purgado de la "
"existencia. ¡Será como si nunca hubieras existido!"

#. [message], speaker=Malykh
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/21_Battle_of_the_Eons.cfg:414
msgid "Arrrghhh!"
msgstr "¡Arrrghhh!"

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/21_Battle_of_the_Eons.cfg:457
msgid "That implies that you win this war, you lost souls!"
msgstr "Eso implica que ganen esta guerra, ¡almas perdidas!"

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/21_Battle_of_the_Eons.cfg:462
msgid "Ilarøth!"
msgstr "¡Ilarøth!"

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/21_Battle_of_the_Eons.cfg:467
msgid "You thought we'd leave them up to you, Ilriel?"
msgstr "¿Pensaste que los dejaríamos a tu cargo, Ilriel?"

#. [message], speaker=Iskandar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/21_Battle_of_the_Eons.cfg:489
msgid ""
"And there's many of us with a pure heart. Fighting side by side, they won't "
"stand a chance."
msgstr ""
"Y hay muchos de nosotros con corazón puro. Luchando lado a lado, no tendrán "
"oportunidad."

#. [message], speaker=Nuvdael
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/21_Battle_of_the_Eons.cfg:511
msgid "The reign of the Three will end. And we will be a part of their end."
msgstr "El reinado de los Tres terminará. Y seremos parte de su fin."

#. [message], speaker=Ridwan
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/21_Battle_of_the_Eons.cfg:533
msgid "And peace shall once again cover these lands."
msgstr "Y la paz cubrirá estas tierras una vez más."

#. [message], speaker=Ibn Khazul
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/21_Battle_of_the_Eons.cfg:555
msgid ""
"The deserts shall recover from the poison of the Three. And for that, we "
"stand at your side."
msgstr ""
"Los desiertos se recuperarán del veneno de los Tres. Y para eso, estamos a "
"tu lado."

#. [message], speaker=Azyan
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/21_Battle_of_the_Eons.cfg:577
msgid "With bow and sword! Their magic won't save them now!"
msgstr "¡Con arco y espada! ¡Su magia no los salvará ahora!"

#. [message], speaker=Uthain
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/21_Battle_of_the_Eons.cfg:599
msgid "Aye, we will kill them, I guess!"
msgstr "¡Sí, los mataremos, supongo!"

#. [message], speaker=Wahdet
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/21_Battle_of_the_Eons.cfg:621
msgid "And the Three Kings will become <i>our</i> slaves."
msgstr "Y los Tres Reyes se convertirán en <i>nuestros</i> esclavos."

#. [message], speaker=Aula
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/21_Battle_of_the_Eons.cfg:643
msgid "While the world will once again be a free world!"
msgstr "¡Mientras el mundo volverá a ser un mundo libre!"

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/21_Battle_of_the_Eons.cfg:668
msgid "Ilriel, now it is up to us to destroy them. We stand at your side."
msgstr "Ilriel, ahora depende de nosotros destruirlos. Estamos a tu lado."

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/21_Battle_of_the_Eons.cfg:673
msgid ""
"Why is it up to me? You're an Athvari, if you can't destroy them, I can "
"neither."
msgstr ""
"¿Por qué depende de mí? Eres un athvari, si tú no puedes destruirlos, yo "
"tampoco."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/21_Battle_of_the_Eons.cfg:678
msgid "There's a power within you that can. Trust us."
msgstr "Hay un poder dentro de ti que puede. Confía en nosotros."

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/21_Battle_of_the_Eons.cfg:685
msgid "Ilriel destroys the Three Kings"
msgstr "Ilriel destruye a los Tres Reyes"

#. [objective], condition=lose
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/21_Battle_of_the_Eons.cfg:689
msgid "Any other unit defeats the Three Kings"
msgstr "Cualquier otra unidad derrota a los Tres Reyes"

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/21_Battle_of_the_Eons.cfg:714
msgid "By the power of the Southwoods!"
msgstr "¡Por el poder de los Bosques del Sur!"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/21_Battle_of_the_Eons.cfg:720
msgid ""
"Ilriel feels a strange power flowing through her body when striking the "
"deathly blow on the king."
msgstr ""
"Ilriel siente un extraño poder fluyendo a través de su cuerpo al asestar el "
"golpe mortal al rey."

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/21_Battle_of_the_Eons.cfg:736
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/21_Battle_of_the_Eons.cfg:794
msgid ""
"No! No <b>No!</b> The mortals cannot harm them. I'll have to attack them in "
"order to get rid of their magic!"
msgstr ""
"¡No! ¡No <b>No!</b> Los mortales no pueden dañarlos. ¡Tendré que atacarlos "
"para deshacerme de su magia!"

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/21_Battle_of_the_Eons.cfg:803
msgid "They are no more. We did it."
msgstr "Ya no existen. Lo logramos."

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/21_Battle_of_the_Eons.cfg:812
msgid "Look, the enemies are retreating. Victory is ours!"
msgstr "Miren, los enemigos se retiran. ¡La victoria es nuestra!"

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/21_Battle_of_the_Eons.cfg:817
msgid "Now let us take care of the Sphere."
msgstr "Ahora ocupémonos de la Esfera."

#. [part]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/22_Timeless.cfg:7
msgid ""
"The Three Kings have been defeated and their attempt to reconquer their "
"former rule has been stopped."
msgstr ""
"Los Tres Reyes han sido derrotados y su intento de reconquistar su antiguo "
"dominio ha sido detenido."

#. [scenario], id=22_Timeless
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/22_Timeless.cfg:18
msgid "Timeless"
msgstr "Atemporal"

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/22_Timeless.cfg:117
msgid "What will happen to the Sphere?"
msgstr "¿Qué pasará con la Esfera?"

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/22_Timeless.cfg:122
msgid ""
"It can't stay here in these plains. It will be abused again, not now, not "
"tomorrow, but men will come and be attracted by the power of the Sphere, "
"they'll find a way to control the powers it gained from absorbing the magic "
"of the imprisoned."
msgstr ""
"No puede quedarse aquí en estas llanuras. Será abusada de nuevo, no ahora, "
"no mañana, pero los hombres vendrán y serán atraídos por el poder de la "
"Esfera, encontrarán una forma de controlar los poderes que ganó al absorber "
"la magia de los aprisionados."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/22_Timeless.cfg:127
msgid "The world is not suited to use the Sphere correctly. At least, not now."
msgstr ""
"El mundo no está preparado para usar la Esfera correctamente. Al menos, no "
"ahora."

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/22_Timeless.cfg:132
msgid "Then it has to be destroyed."
msgstr "Entonces tiene que ser destruida."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/22_Timeless.cfg:137
msgid ""
"But the indestructible can not be destroyed. The power of the Sphere is "
"greater than ours, now that Thrang'ual is gone."
msgstr ""
"Pero lo indestructible no puede ser destruido. El poder de la Esfera es "
"mayor que el nuestro, ahora que Thrang'ual se ha ido."

#. [message], speaker=Iskandar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/22_Timeless.cfg:142
msgid "But time is stronger yet."
msgstr "Pero el tiempo es aún más fuerte."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/22_Timeless.cfg:147
msgid ""
"Forsooth, we will shift the Sphere into the hereafter. It will reappear in "
"these lands, not tomorrow, neither in a week or a month, but it will return. "
"Maybe in a decade, maybe in a century. Let us just hope there's powers in "
"these deserts then, that are able to destroy it once and for all, for we "
"can't destroy our own creation."
msgstr ""
"Por supuesto, desplazaremos la Esfera al más allá. Reaparecerá en estas "
"tierras, no mañana, ni en una semana o un mes, pero regresará. Tal vez en "
"una década, tal vez en un siglo. Solo esperemos que haya poderes en estos "
"desiertos entonces, que sean capaces de destruirla de una vez por todas, "
"porque no podemos destruir nuestra propia creación."

#. [message], speaker=Iskandar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/22_Timeless.cfg:152
msgid "Once and for all."
msgstr "De una vez por todas."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/22_Timeless.cfg:157
msgid "Let us recall our brothers from within the Sphere and start the ritual."
msgstr ""
"Reincorporamos a nuestros hermanos desde dentro de la Esfera y comencemos el "
"ritual."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/22_Timeless.cfg:193
msgid ""
"Brothers, we are united again in these plains, for we have to expel the "
"Sphere from this world. For too long has the Sphere been abused and even "
"before, it was wrong to create it. We have to expel it, it is our duty."
msgstr ""
"Hermanos, estamos unidos de nuevo en estas llanuras, porque tenemos que "
"expulsar la Esfera de este mundo. Por demasiado tiempo la Esfera ha sido "
"abusada e incluso antes, fue un error crearla. Tenemos que expulsarla, es "
"nuestro deber."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/22_Timeless.cfg:198
msgid ""
"The sons of the sons of todays heroic men will face the Sphere once again."
msgstr ""
"Los hijos de los hijos de los hombres heroicos de hoy enfrentarán la Esfera "
"una vez más."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/22_Timeless.cfg:203
msgid ""
"Ridwan! Spread the word among your kin. A story of both fortune and bale "
"will lead your bloodline. The burden lies on the shoulders of generations to "
"come. Make sure your people recognize it, Ridwan."
msgstr ""
"¡Ridwan! Propaga la palabra entre tu gente. Una historia de fortuna y "
"desgracia guiará tu linaje. La carga recae sobre los hombros de las "
"generaciones venideras. Asegúrate de que tu pueblo la reconozca, Ridwan."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/22_Timeless.cfg:208
msgid ""
"And Ilriel, I . . . I thank you. We thank you for everything you've done."
msgstr ""
"Y Ilriel, yo... te agradezco. Te agradecemos por todo lo que has hecho."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/22_Timeless.cfg:213
msgid "Farewell."
msgstr "Adiós."

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/22_Timeless.cfg:218
msgid "You . . . you are leaving?"
msgstr "¿Tú... te vas?"

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/22_Timeless.cfg:241
msgid ""
"I am an Athvari, Ilriel. Destined to protect mankind. The people of the "
"hereafter will need the advice of the Athvari once the Sphere reappears in "
"their times."
msgstr ""
"Soy un athvari, Ilriel. Destinado a proteger a la humanidad. La gente del "
"más allá necesitará el consejo de los athvari una vez que la Esfera "
"reaparezca en sus tiempos."

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/22_Timeless.cfg:252
msgid "Ilarøth! No!"
msgstr "¡Ilarøth! ¡No!"

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/22_Timeless.cfg:263
msgid ""
"Fear not, there's plenty of Athvari to take care of todays chaos. And we've "
"gained the backing of another one."
msgstr ""
"No temas, hay muchos athvari para encargarse del caos de hoy. Y hemos ganado "
"el respaldo de otro más."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/22_Timeless.cfg:273
msgid "Don't you recognize your powers, Ilriel? You are an Athvari."
msgstr "¿No reconoces tus poderes, Ilriel? Eres una athvari."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/22_Timeless.cfg:283
msgid ""
"Man or elf, man or female alike, there is nothing that divides the Athvari, "
"yet our goal unites us. And we needed you to unite all the Athvari of these "
"days and to fight back the Three Kings side by side. It was all planned. We "
"could not leave it all to chance as it would mean chaos."
msgstr ""
"Hombre o elfo, hombre o mujer por igual, no hay nada que divida a los "
"athvari, sin embargo nuestro objetivo nos une. Y te necesitábamos para unir "
"a todos los athvari de estos días y combatir a los Tres Reyes lado a lado. "
"Todo estaba planeado. No podíamos dejarlo todo al azar porque eso "
"significaría caos."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/22_Timeless.cfg:288
msgid "But your powers are unknown to you. Let me show you your true self."
msgstr ""
"Pero tus poderes te son desconocidos. Déjame mostrarte tu verdadero yo."

#. [object]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/22_Timeless.cfg:293
msgid "Gift of Ilaroth"
msgstr "Don de Ilaroth"

#. [object]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/22_Timeless.cfg:295
msgid "Ilaroth reveals the Athvari-powers of Ilriel."
msgstr "Ilaroth revela los poderes athvari de Ilriel."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/22_Timeless.cfg:308
msgid ""
"Forsooth, you are worthy to take my place, Ilriel, for I shall be no longer. "
"I have to go now, the Sphere is already attracting the ones hungry for power."
msgstr ""
"Por supuesto, eres digna de tomar mi lugar, Ilriel, porque yo ya no estaré. "
"Tengo que irme ahora, la Esfera ya está atrayendo a los hambrientos de poder."

#. [message], speaker=Dawoud
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/22_Timeless.cfg:313
msgid "Let the ritual find its end, brothers."
msgstr "Que el ritual llegue a su fin, hermanos."

#. [message], speaker=Iskandar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/22_Timeless.cfg:380
msgid "Then it is done. The Sphere is no longer. And so is Ilarøth."
msgstr "Entonces está hecho. La Esfera ya no existe. Y tampoco Ilarøth."

#. [message], speaker=Iskandar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/22_Timeless.cfg:385
msgid "But I see you've found your inner powers, Ilriel. I am glad you did."
msgstr ""
"Pero veo que has encontrado tus poderes internos, Ilriel. Me alegra que lo "
"hayas hecho."

#. [message], speaker=Ilriel
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/22_Timeless.cfg:390
msgid "How can I use these powers? What has to be done?"
msgstr "¿Cómo puedo usar estos poderes? ¿Qué hay que hacer?"

#. [message], speaker=Iskandar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/22_Timeless.cfg:395
msgid ""
"Nothing changes for you, Ilriel. You already acted like an Athvari, you were "
"just not aware of your powers. Return to the Southwoods, as the ancient "
"beings there demand your protection."
msgstr ""
"Nada cambia para ti, Ilriel. Ya actuabas como una athvari, simplemente no "
"eras consciente de tus poderes. Regresa a los Bosques del Sur, ya que los "
"seres antiguos allí demandan tu protección."

#. [message], speaker=Iskandar
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/22_Timeless.cfg:400
msgid ""
"And maybe, maybe we will see each other once more. But for now, our paths "
"shall diverge again as our task demands it."
msgstr ""
"Y tal vez, tal vez nos veamos una vez más. Pero por ahora, nuestros caminos "
"se separarán de nuevo ya que nuestra tarea lo exige."

#. [scenario], id=23_Epilogue
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/23_Epilogue.cfg:5
msgid "Epilogue"
msgstr "Epílogo"

#. [part]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/23_Epilogue.cfg:23
msgid ""
"The Three Kings are no more. Defeated by the united powers of the Great "
"Continent, their very existence has been destroyed by the Athvari. Even the "
"Sphere no longer poses as a threat, as Ilaroth managed to disappear with it. "
"But is that all? What has happened to our heroes? "
msgstr ""
"Los Tres Reyes ya no existen. Derrotados por los poderes unidos del Gran "
"Continente, su misma existencia ha sido destruida por los athvari. Incluso "
"la Esfera ya no representa una amenaza, ya que Ilaroth logró desaparecer con "
"ella. Pero ¿eso es todo? ¿Qué les pasó a nuestros héroes?"

#. [part]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/23_Epilogue.cfg:33
msgid ""
"Azyan moved to Th'arwya, knowing that a place, where both men and genie live "
"united, is the only place he deemed worthy to live in. Due to the death of "
"Ibn Ghani, who formed a bulwark against the forces of Uthman that attacked "
"Serrul and hindered them to pass the Cloud River, Th'arwya had - for some "
"time - no Great Dune Warmaster. Knowing that it is neither blood nor "
"heritage that determines a king of the grand city states, the people of "
"Th'arwya wished Azyan to be their Dune Warmaster, as he is the greatest "
"symbol for the union of genie and mankind and took part in the destruction "
"of the three kings. Iskandar then crowned Azyan king. Remembering his own "
"past, Azyan prove to be a merciful leader, often welcoming caravans and "
"wanderers in his city. Across the ashland deserts, Th'arwya became a steady "
"sign of peace."
msgstr ""
"Azyan se mudó a Th'arwya, sabiendo que un lugar donde tanto hombres como "
"genios viven unidos es el único lugar que consideró digno para vivir. Debido "
"a la muerte de Ibn Ghani, quien formó un baluarte contra las fuerzas de "
"Uthman que atacaron Serrul e impidieron que pasaran el Río de las Nubes, "
"Th'arwya no tuvo -por algún tiempo- un Gran Maestro de Guerra. Sabiendo que "
"no es ni la sangre ni la herencia lo que determina a un rey de las grandes "
"ciudades estado, el pueblo de Th'arwya deseó que Azyan fuera su Maestro de "
"Guerra, ya que es el mayor símbolo de la unión entre genios y humanidad y "
"participó en la destrucción de los tres reyes. Iskandar entonces coronó rey "
"a Azyan. Recordando su propio pasado, Azyan demostró ser un líder "
"misericordioso, recibiendo a menudo caravanas y viajeros en su ciudad. A "
"través de los desiertos de ceniza, Th'arwya se convirtió en un signo "
"constante de paz."

#. [part]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/23_Epilogue.cfg:44
msgid ""
"Uthain continued his quest for powerful artifacts of ancient times. During "
"his continuing journey, only his hairy friend Petz accompanied him, "
"wandering across the mountains and beneath the sands. As he descended into "
"old ruins that he found in the Ashland deserts, it is said that he found a "
"magical artifact of long forgotten times. It was a staff of a now dead "
"wizard. The staff was not a stabile one, it was rather semi-liquid, slowly "
"forming strands and bonds that diminished after a short time. For years "
"after, he was not seen again. Some say, his greed for valuable items drove "
"him crazy, others say, he landed in a cooking pot of a troll familiy. Even "
"more say, that the weight of all the artifacts, that he accumulated during "
"his journey, finally broke his back. Whatever happened to him, he took his "
"mighty artifacts with him. Yet one day, Petz was seen again near Th'arwya - "
"without Uthain."
msgstr ""
"Uthain continuó su búsqueda de artefactos poderosos de tiempos antiguos. "
"Durante su viaje continuo, solo su amigo peludo Petz lo acompañó, vagando a "
"través de las montañas y bajo las arenas. Al descender a antiguas ruinas que "
"encontró en los desiertos de Ceniza, se dice que encontró un artefacto "
"mágico de tiempos olvidados hace mucho. Era un bastón de un mago ahora "
"muerto. El bastón no era estable, más bien era semi-líquido, formando "
"lentamente hebras y enlaces que se desvanecían después de un corto tiempo. "
"Durante años después, no se le vio de nuevo. Algunos dicen que su avaricia "
"por objetos valiosos lo volvió loco, otros dicen que terminó en una olla de "
"una familia de trolls. Aún más dicen que el peso de todos los artefactos que "
"acumuló durante su viaje finalmente le rompió la espalda. Sea lo que le haya "
"pasado, se llevó sus poderosos artefactos con él. Sin embargo, un día, Petz "
"fue visto de nuevo cerca de Th'arwya, sin Uthain."

#. [part]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/23_Epilogue.cfg:55
msgid ""
"Wahdet returned to Th'arwya and continued hiring soldiers for his own deeds. "
"Building up a respectable group of experienced warriors, mostly consisting "
"of soldiers that took part in the great battle against the three kings and "
"were not content with returning to live the life as an ordinary man, Wahdet "
"and his exactly 100 men went out to far away lands. They explored the "
"regions north- and eastwards of the mountains of Kesh in order to examine "
"possible friends and foes for the people of the deserts; a region, where no "
"known man set a footprint before. Reaching deeper and deeper into unexplored "
"lands, they encountered vast plains, that were filled with grass. Huge "
"creatures, both bull and man and thrice as tall as a man, lived there in "
"tribes. Although being underdeveloped in craftsmanship, the group of Wahdet "
"did not dare to step near them, as their raw force and huge weight would "
"easily lead to them being impaled by the horns of the bull-like creatures. "
msgstr ""
"Wahdet regresó a Th'arwya y continuó contratando soldados para sus propias "
"hazañas. Formando un respetable grupo de guerreros experimentados, compuesto "
"principalmente por soldados que participaron en la gran batalla contra los "
"tres reyes y no estaban contentos con regresar a vivir la vida como un "
"hombre ordinario, Wahdet y sus exactos 100 hombres partieron hacia tierras "
"lejanas. Exploraron las regiones al norte y este de las montañas de Kesh "
"para examinar posibles amigos y enemigos para el pueblo de los desiertos; "
"una región donde ningún hombre conocido había dejado una huella antes. Al "
"adentrarse cada vez más en tierras inexploradas, encontraron vastas llanuras "
"llenas de hierba. Enormes criaturas, tanto toro como hombre y tres veces más "
"altas que un hombre, vivían allí en tribus. Aunque estaban subdesarrollados "
"en artesanía, el grupo de Wahdet no se atrevió a acercarse a ellos, ya que "
"su fuerza bruta y enorme peso fácilmente los llevaría a ser empalados por "
"los cuernos de las criaturas parecidas a toros."

#. [part]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/23_Epilogue.cfg:66
msgid ""
"During her first encounter with the Sphere, Au'la became the being that she "
"is now. A being full of light, that is able to avert the destructive powers "
"of the Sphere. Yet all the time, even after the Athvari freed her from her "
"physical existence in Isanbar, she felt that the Sphere left a mark on her, "
"that bound her to the earthly plains of the Great Continent and acted like a "
"prison to her. But now that the Sphere is no more, she felt free again. "
"Leaving behind her physical form, she was never seen again. Some people "
"however, such as Iskandar or Ilriel, still felt that she was around. Since "
"that day, no harm happened to the ones she had seemed worthy during her "
"journey with Ilaroth and Ilriel. Arrows shot by bandits and human vermin "
"towards her former companions never seemed to hit, quicksands quickly "
"diminished once they were approached and illnesses were as weak as a slight "
"sunburn. The ordinary people noticing it believed it was pure luck. Ilriel, "
"however, knew that it was Au'la that kept harm from them. Au'la's quest has "
"not been done, yet. She knows that a great danger will return and will "
"endanger her very existence. And she knows who to trust."
msgstr ""
"Durante su primer encuentro con la Esfera, Au'la se convirtió en el ser que "
"es ahora. Un ser lleno de luz, capaz de desviar los poderes destructivos de "
"la Esfera. Sin embargo, todo el tiempo, incluso después de que los athvari "
"la liberaran de su existencia física en Isanbar, sentía que la Esfera había "
"dejado una marca en ella, que la ataba a las llanuras terrenales del Gran "
"Continente y actuaba como una prisión para ella. Pero ahora que la Esfera ya "
"no existe, se sintió libre de nuevo. Dejando atrás su forma física, nunca "
"más fue vista. Sin embargo, algunas personas, como Iskandar o Ilriel, "
"todavía sentían que ella estaba cerca. Desde ese día, ningún daño les "
"ocurrió a los que ella había considerado dignos durante su viaje con Ilaroth "
"e Ilriel. Las flechas disparadas por bandidos y sabandijas humanas hacia sus "
"antiguos compañeros nunca parecían acertar, las arenas movedizas se reducían "
"rápidamente una vez que se acercaban y las enfermedades eran tan débiles "
"como una ligera quemadura solar. La gente común que lo notaba creía que era "
"pura suerte. Ilriel, sin embargo, sabía que era Au'la quien los protegía del "
"daño. La misión de Au'la aún no ha terminado. Sabe que un gran peligro "
"regresará y pondrá en peligro su misma existencia. Y sabe en quién confiar."

#. [part]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/23_Epilogue.cfg:77
msgid ""
"Nuvdael neither got used to the vast deserts, nor to the few and patchy "
"forests that are disperesed across the vastness. Having accompanied Ilriel "
"for their long journey, he decided that he had enough of the deserts and "
"returned to his beloved Southwoods. Being away for such a long time, he "
"feared that elves came into being that tried to proclaim the crown for "
"themselves. Fortunately, on the day of his return, he noticed, that his "
"reign had not been questioned by the people of the Southwoods. Neither did "
"the elves of the Aethenwoods, nor the elves of Lintanir question his reign. "
"Wherever an elf might be, he knew that Nuvdael would take revenge on anyone "
"that tried to stab him in his back, as Nuvdael had single-handedly led "
"charge against dark forces that endangered elvenkin. "
msgstr ""
"Nuvdael ni se acostumbró a los vastos desiertos, ni a los pocos y dispersos "
"bosques que están esparcidos por la vastedad. Habiendo acompañado a Ilriel "
"en su largo viaje, decidió que había tenido suficiente de los desiertos y "
"regresó a sus amados Bosques del Sur. Al estar ausente por tanto tiempo, "
"temía que hubieran surgido elfos que intentaran proclamar la corona para sí "
"mismos. Afortunadamente, el día de su regreso, notó que su reinado no había "
"sido cuestionado por el pueblo de los Bosques del Sur. Ni los elfos de los "
"Bosques de Edén, ni los elfos de Lintanir cuestionaron su reinado. "
"Dondequiera que hubiera un elfo, sabía que Nuvdael tomaría venganza contra "
"cualquiera que intentara apuñalarlo por la espalda, ya que Nuvdael había "
"liderado solo la carga contra fuerzas oscuras que ponían en peligro al "
"pueblo elfo."

#. [part]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/23_Epilogue.cfg:88
msgid ""
"Ibn Khazul returned to Serrul, the place where his heart belonged to, and it "
"was quickly repopulated and built up again. Being a man of war for all of "
"his life, Ibn Khazul swore that he'd fight evil until his last of days. "
"Wherever a skirmish approached, wherever bandits endangered caravans, "
"wherever the guilty seeked to harm the innocent, one could be sure, that "
"sooner or later Ibn Khazul and his mighty rider would appear, impaling the "
"foes with their mighty lances. In most cases, the evil men were former "
"followers of the three kings. Not many years after, the attacks of those "
"stopped, as most were captured or destroyed by the mighty cavalry of Ibn "
"Khazul. Since then, many skulls of former generals of the three kings grace "
"the armour of his mighty steed."
msgstr ""
"Ibn Khazul regresó a Serrul, el lugar al que pertenecía su corazón, y fue "
"rápidamente repoblada y reconstruida. Siendo un hombre de guerra toda su "
"vida, Ibn Khazul juró que lucharía contra el mal hasta su último día. "
"Dondequiera que se acercara una escaramuza, dondequiera que bandidos "
"pusieran en peligro a caravanas, dondequiera que los culpables buscaran "
"dañar a los inocentes, se podía estar seguro de que tarde o temprano Ibn "
"Khazul y su poderoso jinete aparecerían, empalando a los enemigos con sus "
"poderosas lanzas. En la mayoría de los casos, los hombres malvados eran "
"antiguos seguidores de los tres reyes. No muchos años después, los ataques "
"de aquellos se detuvieron, ya que la mayoría fueron capturados o destruidos "
"por la poderosa caballería de Ibn Khazul. Desde entonces, muchos cráneos de "
"antiguos generales de los tres reyes adornan la armadura de su poderoso "
"corcel."

#. [part]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/23_Epilogue.cfg:99
msgid ""
"Just as Ibn Khazul, Ridwan returned to Serrul. Accompanied by hundreds of "
"workers , both of human and genie heritage, Serrul was quickly rebuilt and "
"filled with life once more. Serrul had been able to re-establish its trading "
"routes with Th'arwya and in later days it even managed to open a new route "
"through the Mountains of Peril to the Southwoods. While Ridwan remained as "
"the Dune Warmaster of Serrul, he swore to live his life for its people. And "
"soon after rebuilding Serrul, it regained its former status of a trading "
"city and became the target of many caravans and wanderers. "
msgstr ""
"Al igual que Ibn Khazul, Ridwan regresó a Serrul. Acompañado por cientos de "
"trabajadores, tanto de herencia humana como de genios, Serrul fue "
"rápidamente reconstruida y llenada de vida una vez más. Serrul había podido "
"restablecer sus rutas comerciales con Th'arwya y en días posteriores incluso "
"logró abrir una nueva ruta a través de las Montañas del Peligro hacia los "
"Bosques del Sur. Mientras Ridwan permaneció como el Maestro de Guerra del "
"Desierto de Serrul, juró vivir su vida por su gente. Y poco después de "
"reconstruir Serrul, recuperó su antiguo estatus de ciudad comercial y se "
"convirtió en el objetivo de muchas caravanas y viajeros."

#. [part]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/23_Epilogue.cfg:110
msgid ""
"After Ilaroth gave his life to disappear with the Sphere, Iskandar returned "
"to Kesh, cleansing the city state from the remaining magic of the three "
"kings and the Sphere. As the city state of Kesh was destroyed and all of its "
"population had either been killed or fled to Th'arwya or Serrul, it was "
"decided to not build up Kesh again. After fulfilling his task, Iskandar was "
"seen across the desert lands, either crowning Azyan Dune Warmaster of "
"Th'arwya or helping Ridwan and Ibn Khazul to rebuild Serrul and using his "
"magic to cast protective spells across it. When order reigned once again "
"across the desert lands, Iskandar seemed to be more and more distant and he "
"soon returned to the summit of Isanbar, where he meditated for what seemed "
"like years. Deep in his heart he knew, that his task has not been done yet."
msgstr ""
"Después de que Ilaroth dio su vida para desaparecer con la Esfera, Iskandar "
"regresó a Kesh, limpiando la ciudad estado de la magia restante de los tres "
"reyes y la Esfera. Como la ciudad estado de Kesh fue destruida y toda su "
"población había sido asesinada o huido a Th'arwya o Serrul, se decidió no "
"reconstruir Kesh de nuevo. Después de cumplir su tarea, Iskandar fue visto a "
"través de las tierras del desierto, ya sea coronando a Azyan como Maestro de "
"Guerra Barján de Th'arwya o ayudando a Ridwan e Ibn Khazul a reconstruir "
"Serrul y usando su magia para lanzar hechizos protectores sobre ella. Cuando "
"el orden reinó una vez más a través de las tierras del desierto, Iskandar "
"parecía estar cada vez más distante y pronto regresó a la cima de Isanbar, "
"donde meditó durante lo que parecieron años. En lo profundo de su corazón "
"sabía que su tarea aún no había terminado."

#. [part]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/23_Epilogue.cfg:121
msgid ""
"Although the companions separated, they still felt connected to each other. "
"And despite living peacefully for years, the Sphere never truly left their "
"minds . . ."
msgstr ""
"Aunque los compañeros se separaron, todavía se sentían conectados entre sí. "
"Y a pesar de vivir en paz durante años, la Esfera nunca abandonó realmente "
"sus mentes..."

#. [part]
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/scenarios/23_Epilogue.cfg:133
msgid ". . . knowing that one day in the future it would return."
msgstr "... sabiendo que un día en el futuro regresaría."

