msgstr "El Temerario"

#. [unit_type], id=Ibn Ghani, race=dunefolk
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/units/heroes/ibnghani.cfg:112
msgid ""
"Ibn Ghani is the Great Khalid of Th'arwya, one of the three great cities in "
"the desert lands. He is one of the few rulers that stands side by side with "
"his people, which has often lead to Ibn Ghani leading his army into war, "
"whenever a danger approaches. Riding into battle and overrunning enemy lines "
"with his mighty sandmare, Ibn Ghani is certainly not hiding behind his "
"soldiers. In his city, he is respected among his kin, yet several attempts "
"to assassinate him where planned by evil minds in order to wear down "
"Th'arwya's influence across the desert lands."
msgstr ""
"Ibn Ghani es el Gran Khalid de Th'arwya, una de las tres grandes ciudades en "
"las tierras del desierto. Es uno de los pocos gobernantes que se mantiene "
"lado a lado con su pueblo, lo que a menudo ha llevado a Ibn Ghani a liderar "
"a su ejército en la guerra, cada vez que se acerca un peligro. Cabalgando "
"hacia la batalla y arrollando las líneas enemigas con su poderosa pesadilla "
"de arena, Ibn Ghani ciertamente no se esconde detrás de sus soldados. En su "
"ciudad, es respetado entre su gente, sin embargo, varios intentos de "
"asesinarlo fueron planeados por mentes malvadas para desgastar la influencia "
"de Th'arwya a través de las tierras del desierto."

