msgid "The Renegade"
msgstr "El Renegado"

#. [unit_type], id=Ilaroth, race=human
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/units/heroes/ilaroth.cfg:90
msgid ""
"Dawoud was found in the desert by Ibn Khazuls mounted squad. He proved to be "
"the most loyal general of Ibn Khazul."
msgstr ""
"Dawoud fue encontrado en el desierto por el escuadrón montado de Ibn Khazul. "
"Demostró ser el general más leal de Ibn Khazul."

#. [variation], id=Ascended Ilaroth
#. [variation], id=Ascended Ustura
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/units/heroes/ilaroth.cfg:183
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/units/heroes/ilaroth.cfg:198
msgid ""
"Ilaroth is an Athvari from the eastern lands of the Great Continent and "
"refused to help the other Athvari to create the Sphere that was meant to "
"imprison the three kings of K'thar and eventually did so. As he could no "
"longer identify with the means of the Athvari, he put his blood into a "
"phiole, leaving behind his Athvari powers and becoming an ordinary mortal. "
"As time passed, the imprisoned three kings' power rose and soon could "
"outreach the boundaries of the flawed arcane prison, leading to death and "
"destruction in the desert lands. Ilaroth noticed the upcoming demise of the "
"Athvari and decided to bring their inner circle back to their former power. "
"The search for Ilriel, the spirit of the Southwoods, marked the start for "
"that journey."
msgstr ""
"Ilaroth es un athvari de las tierras orientales del Gran Continente y se "
"negó a ayudar a los otros athvari a crear la Esfera que estaba destinada a "
"aprisionar a los tres reyes de K'thar y eventualmente lo hizo. Como ya no "
"podía identificarse con los medios de los athvari, puso su sangre en un "
"frasco, dejando atrás sus poderes athvari y convirtiéndose en un mortal "
"ordinario. Con el tiempo, el poder de los tres reyes aprisionados aumentó y "
"pronto pudo superar los límites de la defectuosa prisión arcana, llevando a "
"muerte y destrucción en las tierras del desierto. Ilaroth notó la inminente "
"caída de los athvari y decidió traer su círculo interno de vuelta a su "
"antiguo poder. La búsqueda de Ilriel, el espíritu de los Bosques del Sur, "
"marcó el comienzo de ese viaje."

#. [advancement], id=amla_ilriel_fairie_fire
