msgstr "      otorga un ataque a distancia que ralentiza"

#. [unit_type], id=Ilriel, race=elf, gender=female
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/units/heroes/ilriel.cfg:73
msgid "The Spirit of the Southwoods"
msgstr "El Espíritu de los Bosques del Sur"

#. [unit_type], id=Ilriel, race=elf, gender=female
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/units/heroes/ilriel.cfg:90
msgid ""
"Every forest in Wesnoth is inhabited by a forest spirit, the very heart of a "
"forest itself, the being that keeps the forest and its inhabitants alive. "
"Having a strong bond with the world of the fairies, the Forest Spirits are - "
"just like Elvish Sylphs - able to cast forth higher forms of magic. Ilriel "
"is the forest spirit of the Southwoods. Due to the help of Nuvdael, a former "
"general from the northern Aethenwoods, she survived an attempt of the "
"witches of the black forests to establigh a reign over the Southwoods."
msgstr ""
"Cada bosque en Wesnoth está habitado por un espíritu del bosque, el "
"mismísimo corazón del bosque, el ser que mantiene vivo al bosque y a sus "
"habitantes. Teniendo un fuerte vínculo con el mundo de las hadas, los "
"Espíritus del Bosque son -al igual que las Sílfides Elfas- capaces de lanzar "
"formas superiores de magia. Ilriel es el espíritu del bosque de los Bosques "
"del Sur. Gracias a la ayuda de Nuvdael, un antiguo general de los Bosques de "
"Edén del norte, sobrevivió a un intento de las brujas de los bosques negros "
"de establecer un reinado sobre los Bosques del Sur."

