"estático para limitar los ataques de los enemigos a uno. Solo cuerpo a "
"cuerpo."

#. [unit_type], id=Uthain, race=dwarf
#. [variation], id=Dwarvish Bear Hammerdin
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/units/heroes/uthain.cfg:126
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/units/heroes/uthain.cfg:199
msgid "The Adventurer"
msgstr "El Aventurero"

#. [unit_type], id=Uthain, race=dwarf
#. [variation], id=Dwarvish Bear Hammerdin
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/units/heroes/uthain.cfg:139
#: Oath_of_Allegiance_Ref/units/heroes/uthain.cfg:208
msgid ""
"Eager to explore the world in search of ancient and forgotten artifacts, "
"Uthain is a mostly lone survivor who will, nevertheless, embrace the company "
"of others if that helps to advance his cause. His travels and artifacts "
"collected in the span of this life have made him tough adversaries for any "
"foe foolish enough to pose an obstacle to his everlasting quest, leading "
"them away from the usual paths of the dwarvish people."
msgstr ""
"Ansioso por explorar el mundo en busca de artefactos antiguos y olvidados, "
"Uthain es un sobreviviente mayormente solitario que, sin embargo, abrazará "
"la compañía de otros si eso ayuda a avanzar su causa. Sus viajes y "
"artefactos recolectados en el transcurso de esta vida lo han convertido en "
"adversarios duros para cualquier enemigo lo suficientemente tonto como para "
"representar un obstáculo a su búsqueda eterna, alejándolos de los caminos "
"usuales del pueblo enano."

#. [advancement], id=amla_wahdet_MAX_slow
